NK133(po)003:1: // rgyal bstan snga 'gyur bka' ma theg rim dgu'i phrin
NK133(po)003:2: chog gzhung phyi mo rnams dang bcas pa'i dkar chag
NK133(po)003:3: bstan pa rgya mtsho'i gru gzings bkra shis dpal brgya'i
NK133(po)003:4: 'byung gnas zhes bya ba bzhugs so //
NK133(po)003:5: gdod nas rnam dag chos dbyings klong chen srid zhi'i dge legs kun gyi dpal //
NK133(po)003:6: 'od gsal lhun grub nam mkha'i rang bzhin mi 'gyur rnam kun rtag pa'i gshis //
NK133(po)003:7: sku dang ye shes 'du 'bral mi mnga' gdod ma'i rgyal ba kun tu bzang //
NK133(po)003:8: ngur smrig 'chang ba'i rnam par rol pa rdo rje 'dzin der mgos phyag 'tshal /
NK133(po)003:10: 1 / spros bral chos dbyings ye shes rang bzhin 'og min chen por nges pa lnga ldan longs spyod rdzogs //
NK133(po)003:11: ma 'gags rol pa zhing khams rgya mtshor dus gsum gshegs pa rgyal ba'i sprin chen rnam bkod bzhin //
NK133(po)003:12: mi mjed 'di na mtshan dpe'i gser ri nyin byed 'bum gyi 'od zer d+r+wa bas mdzes 'bar ba //
NK133(po)003:13: ston mchog mnyam med sh+aakya'i rgyal por rab tu 'dud do rnam kun shis pa'i snang ba rtsol /
NK133(po)003:15: 2 / bya ba lam gyi bden pas bsdus pa 'dul ba mdo sde chos mngon rig 'dzin sde snod bcas //
NK133(po)003:16: 'bras bu 'gog bden rab dga' nas bzung sa mchog ye shes bla ma'i bar //
NK133(po)003:17: byang chub phyogs chos rig 'dzin bzhi dang rnal 'byor che lnga 'od gsal snang ba rnam bzhi bcas //
NK133(po)003:18: sdug bsngal kun 'byung tsha gdung bsil mdzad dam chos bdud rtsi'i zla bar bsnyen /
NK133(po)003:20: 3 / byang chub spyod pa rgya mtsho'i grur zhugs gsang ba bsam mi khyab pa'i mdzod //
NK133(po)003:21: rgyal ba'i myu gu nyan thos rang rgyal theg gsum 'phags pa'i tshogs chen dang //
NK133(po)003:22: lung dang rtogs pa'i spyan stong rab bkra legs bshad rgyal rnga 'khor mor brdung //
NK133(po)003:23: bshad dang sgrub pas rgyal bstan skyong mkhas thub pa'i sras rnams spyi bos mchod /
NK133(po)003:25: 4 / nges don theg mchog snang ba ston mkhas gsang 'dzin
NK133(po)003:26: dbang po rigs can lnga dang rgyal po dzah dga'
NK133(po)003:27: rab rdo rje 'jam dpal bshes gnyen dpal gyi seng
NK133(po)003:28: ge dz+nya na su tra bi ma la //
NK133(po)003:29: khyad par rgyal kun spyi gzugs mtsho skyes rdo rje'i zhabs sen zla ba snying gi 'o mtshor bsnyen /
NK133(po)003:31: 5 / thugs bskyed smon lam gser gyi shing rtas 'phags yul chos kyi gsang mdzod nas //
NK133(po)003:32: dri med thub bstan nor bu'i gter chen bsil ldan ljongs su legs drangs nas //
NK133(po)003:33: bshad sgub dpal gyis rgud pa kun bsal phan bde 'byor pa'i mchog sbyin mkhan //
NK133(po)003:34: rgya bod 'phags chen lo pan tshogs dang chos rgyal mes dbon bka' drin dran /
NK133(po)003:36: 6 / gangs ri'i ljongs 'dir thub bstan gsal byed nyi ma'i dpal 'dzin sad mi bdun dang dmar g.yor gtsang //
NK133(po)003:37: ka cog zhang sogs 'jig rten mig dang gnubs so zur sogs grub pa'i rig 'dzin rgya mtsho dang //
NK133(po)003:38: mdo dang sngags kyi bstan pa'i rgyal mtshan srid rtser sbreng zhing 'gro mang phan bde la /
NK133(po)003:39: 'god mdzad ris med dam pa'i bshes gnyen gang yin kun la zol sbyor spang ba'i gus phyag brtsegs /
NK133(po)003:40: 7 thub mchog legs gsung 'dzam bu'i tshal na snying po go bi d+aa ra'i ljon //
NK133(po)003:41: bstan pa yongs rdzogs snga 'gyur theg dgu dri med rgyal ba'i bka' gzhung gi //
NK133(po)003:42: yig tshogs mi zad chos sbyin par gyi bdud rtsi'i char rgyun 'jo bu'i dpyid //
NK133(po)003:43: skal bzang ris med 'gro ba'i dga' ston dkar chag yid bzhin mdzod sgo phye /
NK133(po)003:44: 8 /'dir rgyal ba nyi ma'i gnyen gyi bstan pa
NK133(po)003:45: gangs ri'i ljongs 'dir snga 'gyur bka' ma theg rim
NK133(po)003:46: dgu'i phrin chog gzhung phyi mo rnams bcas phyogs gcig
NK133(po)003:47: tu bkod pa'i dkar chag 'god pa la /
NK133(po)003:48: bstan pa rin po che spyi'i babs tshul lo rgyus su brjod pa dang /
NK133(po)003:49: bye brag deng sang gi rnying ma'i gdan sa rnams kyi byung tshul /
NK133(po)003:50: so byang sngags kyi bla ma brgyud pa'i mtshan tho /
NK133(po)003:51: ji ltar spar du sgrub tshul bzhugs byang dkar chag dngos 'god pa dang /
NK133(po)003:52: de ltar bsgrub pa'i dgos ched phan yon bstan pa bsngo smon shis brjod dang bcas pa'o //
NK133(po)003:53: dang po la'ang ston pa mchog gi sprul pa'i skus
NK133(po)003:54: byang chub brnyes nas chos kyi 'khor lo bskor zhing
NK133(po)003:56: de nas rgyu dang 'bras bu'i theg pa so sor 'phags pa'i yul du ji ltar bskyangs tshul /
NK133(po)003:57: phyis gangs can gyi ljongs 'dir mdo sngags kyi bstan
NK133(po)003:58: pa dar tshul skabs babs kyi brgyud pa'i lo rgyus
NK133(po)003:59: dang bcas pa ste gsum las /
NK133(po)003:61: theg pa thun mong gi 'dod pa brjod pa dang /
NK133(po)003:62: thun mong ma yin pa theg mchog rdo rje rtse mo'i lugs bzhag pa'o //
NK133(po)003:64: theg pa che chung gi phyogs gnyis las /
NK133(po)003:65: nyan thos spyi'i lugs ltar na /
NK133(po)003:66: bdag cag gi ston pa 'dis bskal pa grangs med
NK133(po)003:67: gsum gyi sngon rol du sangs rgyas sh+aakya thub pa
NK133(po)003:68: chen po'i drung du byang chub mchog tu thugs bskyed
NK133(po)003:69: pa nas brtsams te byang chub snying po'i shing drung
NK133(po)003:70: du bzhugs pa'i bar la so so'i skye bo dbang
NK133(po)003:71: rnon tshogs kyi lam pa zhig yin pa las /
NK133(po)003:72: de nas gdan thog gcig tu lam lnga rdzogs par mdzad nas mngon par sangs rgyas par 'dod de /
NK133(po)003:74: ston dang bse ru byang chub pa //
NK133(po)003:75: bsam gtan mtha' rten gcig la kun //
NK133(po)003:77: theg pa chen po la'ang 'ga' zhig gis ni /
NK133(po)003:78: thog mar sems bskyed nas grangs med dang por tshogs sbyor gyi lam gnyis dang /
NK133(po)003:79: gnyis par ma dag sa bdun /
NK133(po)003:80: gsum par dag pa sa gsum rnams rdzogs par mdzad
NK133(po)003:81: nas 'og min rnam mdzes chen por mngon par sangs
NK133(po)003:82: rgyas nas / slar yang 'dod pa'i khams 'dir 'tshang rgya ba'i tshul bstan par bzhed de /
NK133(po)003:83: rgyan stug po bkod pa las /
NK133(po)003:84: yang dag sangs rgyas 'og min du //
NK133(po)003:85: sangs rgyas ma gyur 'dod khams su //
NK133(po)003:86: sangs rgyas mdzad pa mi mdzad do //
NK133(po)003:88: chos dang longs spyod mngon par sangs rgyas pa'i mdo las /
NK133(po)003:89: rin chen sna tshogs mdzes pa yi //
NK133(po)003:90: 'og min gnas ni nyams dga' ba //
NK133(po)003:91: gtsang ma'i gnas kyi steng bzhugs te //
NK133(po)003:92: yang dag sangs rgyas der sangs rgyas //
NK133(po)003:95: yang theg chen pa kha cig gis bzhed pa lta na /
NK133(po)003:96: ston pa 'di nyid bskal pa bsam gyis mi khyab
NK133(po)003:97: pa'i gong nas mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas nas
NK133(po)003:98: / slar mi mjed 'jig rten gyi khams gling bzhi
NK133(po)003:99: bye ba phrag brgya 'di nyid kyis mtshon pa'i phyogs
NK133(po)003:100: bcu'i zhing khams rgya mtsho bsam gyis mi khyab par
NK133(po)003:101: / / sems can gyi khams rgya mtsho smin par
NK133(po)003:102: bgyi ba'i phyir la lar byang chub tu thugs bskyed
NK133(po)003:103: / / pa dang / la lar lam sbyangs pa dang /
NK133(po)003:104: la lar sa nas sar 'phar ba dang /
NK133(po)003:105: la lar mngon par byang chub pa dang /
NK133(po)003:106: la lar chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba sogs sangs
NK133(po)003:107: rgyas kyi rnam par rol pa tshad med pa'i bkod
NK133(po)003:108: pa rgya mtsho sngon dang phyi ma'i mtha' mi mngon
NK133(po)003:110: yab sras mjal ba'i mdo las /
NK133(po)003:111: dpa' bo chen po thabs mkhas te //
NK133(po)003:112: sems can yongs su smin mdzad phyir //
NK133(po)003:113: bye ba phrag brgyar rgyal ba nyid //
NK133(po)003:114: sangs rgyas nyid du bstan gyur kyang //
NK133(po)003:115: da dung yang ni 'dren pa khyod //
NK133(po)003:116: sangs rgyas mang po ston par mdzad //
NK133(po)003:118: mdo sde pad+ma dkar po las /
NK133(po)003:119: bskal pa bye stong bsam gyis mi khyab pa //
NK133(po)003:120: de yi tshad ni nam yang med pa nas //
NK133(po)003:121: byang chub mchog rab 'di ni ngas thob ste //
NK133(po)003:122: nga ni rtag tu chos kyang rab 'chad do //
NK133(po)003:124: de rnams kyang gdul bya'i blo stobs che chung gi
NK133(po)003:125: dbang las 'dod tshul tha dad du byung bar snang
NK133(po)003:126: yang / don la sangs rgyas kyi spyod yul ni
NK133(po)003:127: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i phyir mtha' gcig tu tshad
NK133(po)003:128: bzung bar sla ba ma yin te /
NK133(po)003:130: byang chub rgya mtsho rab brnyes gyur nas kyang //
NK133(po)003:131: sems can rgya mtsho rab tu smin bya'i phyir //
NK133(po)003:132: byang chub sems bskyed rgya mtsho ston mdzad cing //
NK133(po)003:133: mi 'grib spyod pa rgya mtsho dus kun ston //
NK133(po)003:134: bde gshegs rnams kyi rnam 'phrul de 'dra'o //
NK133(po)003:137: dpal gsang ba'i snying po las /
NK133(po)003:138: chos sku dpag med brjod du med //
NK133(po)003:139: longs sku zad med yid bzhin gter //
NK133(po)003:140: sprul pa bye ba bsam mi khyab //
NK133(po)003:142: gang gi tshe ston pa sku gsum gyi mnga' bdag
NK133(po)003:143: 'di nyid srid zhi gang du'ang dbyer mi phyed pa'i
NK133(po)003:144: snga rol du / ye thog dang po'i gzhi la
NK133(po)003:145: rig pa'i ye shes gzung 'dzin gyi sbub rgya las
NK133(po)003:146: grol te khyad chos drug gi tshul gyis mngon par
NK133(po)003:147: snga rol du / byang chub nas / nang dbyings
NK133(po)003:148: gzhon nu bum pa sku'i zhing khams chen por dbyings
NK133(po)003:149: dang ye shes 'du 'bral med pa'i dgongs pa 'od
NK133(po)003:150: gsal ba'i ngang la dus gsum 'pho 'gyur med par
NK133(po)003:151: snga rol du / byang chub nas / bzhugs pa
NK133(po)003:152: la / dpal chos sku'i ston pa kun tu bzang
NK133(po)003:155: rab tu dag pa kun gyi mchog /
NK133(po)003:156: gdod nas grol ba de bzhin gshegs //
NK133(po)003:157: kun tu bzang po kun gyi bdag /
NK133(po)003:158: byang chub sems nyid nges pa'o //
NK133(po)003:160: de lta bu'i dgongs pa chos nyid kyi ngang na /
NK133(po)003:161: dus gsum gyi rgyal ba thams cad gcig dang tha
NK133(po)003:162: dad bral ba'i rang bzhin du dbyer mi phyed cing
NK133(po)003:163: yul yul can gyi dngos por ma grub pas /
NK133(po)003:164: phan tshun gzigs bya gzigs byed las 'das pa'i rang
NK133(po)003:165: byung gi ye shes kyi rol pa 'ba' zhig tu
NK133(po)003:166: snang ba ste / gsang snying las /
NK133(po)003:167: gcig dang tha dad bral ba yi //
NK133(po)003:168: mtha' dang dbus med de bzhin nyid //
NK133(po)003:169: sangs rgyas kyis kyang mi gzigs te //
NK133(po)003:170: rang byung ye shes gnas med snang //
NK133(po)003:172: de ltar gnyis su med pa'i ston pa kun tu
NK133(po)003:173: bzang po de nyid kyis 'khor ye shes rgya mtsho
NK133(po)003:174: la / dus bsam gyis mi khyab par /
NK133(po)003:175: chos 'od gsal 'dus ma byas pa'i dgongs pa rang snang bar mdzad do //
NK133(po)003:177: de las yi ge med dang rig pa'i gsung //
NK133(po)003:178: ljags kyi rtse mor ma byung yang //
NK133(po)003:179: thugs rje gsung gi byin rlabs kyis //
NK133(po)003:180: 'gro don sna tshogs so sor gsal //
NK133(po)003:182: de'i ngang las nang gsal thim la ma rmugs phra ba'i ye shes mched pa'i cha las /
NK133(po)003:183: lhun grub stug po bkod pa'i zhing khams longs spyod
NK133(po)003:184: chen po'i rgyan dang bkod pa tshad med par rang
NK133(po)003:185: snang ba ni / snga ma las /
NK133(po)003:186: phyogs bcu dus bzhi mngon rdzogs pa'i //
NK133(po)003:187: zhing khams rnam dag bsam yas dang //
NK133(po)003:188: rgya dang bral ba'i gzhal yas khang //
NK133(po)003:189: 'khor lo'i rgyan dang rol mo'i tshogs //
NK133(po)003:190: dkyil 'khor ma lus bsam yas kun //
NK133(po)003:191: mthong nas nye bar mnyes pa dang //
NK133(po)003:192: rgya chen gsung la don byung ba'ang //
NK133(po)003:193: mthun pa'i ye shes rang snang ba'o //
NK133(po)003:195: der mnga' dbang rdzogs pa'i ston pa kun tu bzang
NK133(po)003:196: po nyid mtshan dang dpe byad yongs su rdzogs pa
NK133(po)003:197: rigs bdag drug pa'i phyag rgyar bzhengs nas nyid las
NK133(po)003:198: mi gzhan pa'i 'khor bka' sdod skyes bu /
NK133(po)003:201: 'joms byed khro bo dang bcas pa snang bar mdzad pa yang /
NK133(po)003:202: rgyal ba'i ye shes kyi rang snang kho na ste /
NK133(po)003:204: zag pa med pa'i bsod nams kyi //
NK133(po)003:205: ye shes sgyu ma rang snang ba //
NK133(po)003:206: rol mo'i dkyil 'khor mtha' yas mchog /
NK133(po)003:207: gsang ba'i thig le nyid kyi dbyings //
NK133(po)003:209: de lta bu'i gnas dang ston 'khor thams cad skye
NK133(po)003:210: 'jigs mtshan ma'i yul las ring du song ba'i dus
NK133(po)003:211: bzhi mnyam pa nyid kyi 'khor lor rdzogs pa na
NK133(po)003:212: / chos zab gsang rdo rje'i theg pa nang pa
NK133(po)003:213: bskyed rdzogs gsum gyi 'khor lo sgra tshig rang mtshan
NK133(po)003:214: las 'das pa'i gsung gis rgyun mi chad par bgro
NK133(po)003:216: e ma ho ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK133(po)003:217: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsung //
NK133(po)003:218: sgra dang ming tshig kun las 'das //
NK133(po)003:219: sna tshogs sgra rnams gsal bar 'byung //
NK133(po)003:221: theg pa mtho dman bsam yas kyang //
NK133(po)003:222: de bzhin nyid las ma gsung ste //
NK133(po)003:223: gdul bya'i thabs su so sor thos //
NK133(po)003:225: ston pa longs spyod rdzogs sku'i zhing khams chen po 'di nyid ni /
NK133(po)003:226: de bzhin gshegs pa 'ba' zhig gi spyod yul las
NK133(po)003:227: sa bcu pa'i sems dpa' rnams la'ang snang ba ma
NK133(po)003:228: yin te / rgyud bla ma las /
NK133(po)003:229: sangs rgyas khams dang sangs rgyas byang chub dang //
NK133(po)003:230: sangs rgyas yon tan sangs rgyas phrin las te //
NK133(po)003:231: dag pa'i sems can gyis kyang bsam bya min //
NK133(po)003:232: 'di ni 'dren pa rnams kyi spyod yul yin //
NK133(po)003:234: de ltar sangs rgyas rang snang gi bsdus pa'i sa
NK133(po)003:235: na gnyis snang gi rtog pa shin tu phra ba'ang
NK133(po)003:236: dbyings su nub pas byed rtsol gyi spros pa mi
NK133(po)003:237: mnga' yang / sngon gyi thugs rje chen po'i dbang
NK133(po)003:238: gis gdul bya'i khams la gzugs sku'i rnam rol sna
NK133(po)003:241: de bzhin nyid las ma g.yos kyang //
NK133(po)003:242: yang dag thar pa'i gzugs sku dang //
NK133(po)003:244: mthun byas sku ni sna tshogs ston //
NK133(po)003:246: rang snang longs spyod rdzogs pa'i ngang las mkha' zla chu mtshor shar ba ltar /
NK133(po)003:247: gdul bya sa bcu'i sems dpa' rnams kyi ngor /
NK133(po)003:248: gnas 'og min khang bu brtsegs pa la sogs par /
NK133(po)003:249: ston pa rnam par snang mdzad sogs rigs lnga'i sangs
NK133(po)003:250: rgyas mtshan dang dpe byad rgya mtshos brgyan pa'i skur
NK133(po)003:251: snang bas chos bya spyod rnal 'byor gyi rgyud gsum
NK133(po)003:252: gtso bor gyur pa'i gsang sngags kyi rgyud sde mtha'
NK133(po)003:253: dag dgongs pa brda' yi gsung gis /
NK133(po)003:254: dus rtag pa rgyun gyi 'khor lor ston par mdzad pa ste /
NK133(po)003:256: 'og min bla med gnas mchog tu //
NK133(po)003:257: sku ni rnam par snang mdzad tshul //
NK133(po)003:258: byang chub sems dpa' 'khor rnams la //
NK133(po)003:259: de bzhin gsung mchog ni smra ste //
NK133(po)003:260: sku yi chos rnams mjal bar ston //
NK133(po)003:262: de'i tshe 'jig rten gyi khams ma dag pa rnams
NK133(po)003:263: su gdul bya'i bsod nams dang rgyal ba'i thugs rje'i
NK133(po)003:265: gang zag so so'i khams dbang dang 'tshams par zhi
NK133(po)003:266: dang khro bo'i sprul pa'i rol gar chags can dang
NK133(po)003:267: / chags bral gyi tshul bsam gyis mi khyab par snang ba yang /
NK133(po)003:269: de tshe mi mthun sna tshogs la //
NK133(po)003:270: so sor 'dra bar snang ba ni //
NK133(po)003:271: de bzhin nyid las ma g.yos kyang //
NK133(po)003:272: las 'phro'i dbang gis so sor snang //
NK133(po)003:273: dper na me long chu zla bzhin //
NK133(po)003:274: zhes pas steng 'og dang s+n+rel gzhi 'i 'jig rten
NK133(po)003:275: 'gro ba drug gi gnas ris so sor rig pa'i
NK133(po)003:276: skyes bu thub pa drug grangs med par sprul nas
NK133(po)003:277: sems can gyi don mdzad pa ste /
NK133(po)003:279: lha yi gnas na brgya byin mgon //
NK133(po)003:280: lha ma yin la thag bzang ris //
NK133(po)003:282: yi dwags rnams la kha 'bar te //
NK133(po)003:283: dmyal bar las kyi gshin rje mgon //
NK133(po)003:286: de tshe 'gro drug thams cad la //
NK133(po)003:287: sdig spong gzugs su snang bar bstan //
NK133(po)003:289: de ltar sprul pa'i rol pa tshad med par bkod pa las /
NK133(po)003:290: gtso bor mchog gi sprul pa'i sku'i 'gro ba 'dul ba'i phrin las ji ltar mdzad pa'i tshul yang /
NK133(po)003:292: s+n+rel gzhi dang yan man gyi 'jig rten drug gi
NK133(po)003:293: phyogs bcu mtha' yas mu med pa'i stong gsum gyi
NK133(po)003:295: thub pa chen po bcom ldan 'das re res gdul
NK133(po)003:296: ba rnam pa bzhis 'gro ba'i don mdzad de zhes
NK133(po)003:298: sku bsod nams chen po'i 'dul ba ni /
NK133(po)003:299: mdzad pa bcu gnyis kyi sgo nas sems can gyi don mdzad pa ste /
NK133(po)003:300: de yang rgyud bla ma las /
NK133(po)003:301: thugs rje chen po 'jig rten mkhyen //
NK133(po)003:302: 'jig rten kun la gzigs nas ni //
NK133(po)003:303: chos kyi sku las ma g.yos par //
NK133(po)003:304: sprul pa'i rang bzhin sna tshogs kyis //
NK133(po)003:305: skye ba mngon par skye ba dang //
NK133(po)003:306: dga' ldan gnas nas 'pho ba dang //
NK133(po)003:307: lhums su 'jug dang bltams pa dang //
NK133(po)003:308: bzo yi gnas la mkhas pa dang //
NK133(po)003:309: btsun mo'i 'khor dgyes rol ba dang //
NK133(po)003:310: nges 'byung dka' ba spyod pa dang //
NK133(po)003:311: byang chub snying por gshegs pa dang //
NK133(po)003:312: bdud sde 'joms dang rdzogs par ni //
NK133(po)003:313: byang chub chos kyi 'khor lo dang //
NK133(po)003:314: mya ngan 'da' bar ston mdzad rnams //
NK133(po)003:315: yongs su ma dag zhing rnams su //
NK133(po)003:316: srid pa ji srid gnas par ston //
NK133(po)003:319: 'khor rnam pa bzhi la theg pa lnga las brtsams
NK133(po)003:320: pa'i chos kyi tshul dpag tu med pa snang bar
NK133(po)003:323: 'dul ba'i dbang gis lha dang mi'i theg pa dang /
NK133(po)003:324: nyan thos kyi theg pa dang /
NK133(po)003:325: rang byang chub kyi theg pa dang /
NK133(po)003:326: byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa dang /
NK133(po)003:327: bla na med pa'ii theg pas /
NK133(po)003:328: ma rig pa'i rnam par rtog pa nyon mongs pa
NK133(po)003:329: stong phrag brgyad cu rtsa bzhi'i gnyen por chos stong
NK133(po)003:330: phrag brgyad cu rtsa bzhi gsungs so //
NK133(po)003:334: thugs mngon sum pas 'dul ba ni /
NK133(po)003:335: mngon shes drug gi sgo nas gdul bya'i rgyud smin par mdzad pa ste /
NK133(po)003:337: dus bzhi kun tu mkhyen pa dang /
NK133(po)003:338: thams cad kyi sems kyi rgyud kun tu mkhyen pa dang /
NK133(po)003:339: rdzu 'phrul gyi spyan gyis thams cad kun tu gzigs pa dang /
NK133(po)003:340: rdzu 'phrul gyi snyan gyis kun tu gsan pa dang /
NK133(po)003:341: rdzu 'phrul gyi tshogs kun tu don spyod pa dang /
NK133(po)003:342: zag pa med pa kun tu bzang po'i spyod pa
NK133(po)003:343: yongs su rdzogs pa'i mngon par shes pa chen po
NK133(po)003:345: rdzu 'phrul bsam gyis mi khyab pas 'dul ba ni /
NK133(po)003:346: de las kun tu sku bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK133(po)003:347: kun tu thugs bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK133(po)003:348: kun tu zhal bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK133(po)003:349: kun tu gsung bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK133(po)003:350: bsam gyis mi khyab pa grangs med pa phyogs bcur snang bar gyur to //
NK133(po)003:352: mdor na rgyal ba'i sku gsung thugs mi zad pa
NK133(po)003:353: rgyan gyi 'khor lo bsam gyis mi khyab pa las
NK133(po)003:354: gang 'dul gzugs sku'i rol pa ni gdul bya'i 'gro
NK133(po)003:355: ba mtha' dag gi khams dang dbang po bsam pa'i
NK133(po)003:356: bye brag ji ltar mos pa bzhin du ma'atha yas
NK133(po)003:358: de lta bu'i ston pa sku gsum gyi bdag nyid
NK133(po)003:359: can de'i bstan pa dam pa'i chos kyi tshul 'god
NK133(po)003:360: pa la spyir chos zhes bya ba ni /
NK133(po)003:362: chos ni shes bya'i lam dang ni //
NK133(po)003:363: mya ngan 'das dang yid kyi yul //
NK133(po)003:364: bsod nams tshe dang gsung rab dang //
NK133(po)003:371: khyad par du 'phags pa'i don gyis /
NK133(po)003:372: sdug kun phyogs kyi gnyen por gyur pa rnam byang gis bsdus pa'i chos la 'jug ste /
NK133(po)003:373: sdug bsngal dag ni thams cad dang //
NK133(po)003:374: sgrib kun sel byed dam pa'i chos //
NK133(po)003:376: de la dbye na brjod bya don gyi ngo bor gyur pa rtogs pa'i chos dang /
NK133(po)003:377: rjod byed tshig gi rigs su gnas pa lung gi chos gnyis te /
NK133(po)003:379: ston pa'i dam chos rnam gnyis te //
NK133(po)003:380: lung dang rtogs pa'i bdag nyid do //
NK133(po)003:382: de ltar rtogs pa'i chos ni 'gog pa dang lam gyi bden pa dag gis bsdus pa ste /
NK133(po)003:384: gang zhig gang gis chags bral ba //
NK133(po)003:385: bden gnyis mtshan nyid can de chos //
NK133(po)003:386: chags bral nyid ni 'gog pa dang //
NK133(po)003:387: lam gyi bden pa dag gis bsdus //
NK133(po)003:390: lam bden gyi dmigs par gyur pa gsung rab ming
NK133(po)003:391: tshig gi rnam par gnas pa gang zhig ngo bo'i
NK133(po)003:393: legs par gsungs pa'i bka' dang /
NK133(po)003:394: de'i dgongs 'grel gyi bstan bcos gnyis te /
NK133(po)003:395: lha'i bus zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK133(po)003:396: chos rnams thams cad bka' dang bstan bcos gnyis su 'dus //
NK133(po)003:397: legs par gsung dang de yi dgongs 'grel pa //
NK133(po)003:401: gang zhig don ldan chos dang nyer 'brel zhing //
NK133(po)003:402: khams gsum kun nas nyon mongs spang byed gsung //
NK133(po)003:403: zhi ba'i phan yon ston par mdzad pa gang //
NK133(po)003:404: de ni drang srong gsung yin bzlog pa gzhan //
NK133(po)003:405: zhes pa bzhin brjod bya don ldan gyi chos lhag pa'i bslab pa gsum dang nye bar 'brel zhing /
NK133(po)003:406: byed las khams gsum gyi nyon mongs pa mthong sgom
NK133(po)003:407: lam gyis spang bya thams cad spong bar byed pa
NK133(po)003:408: dang / 'bras bu zhi ba mya ngan las 'das pa'i phan yon ston par byed pa gang zhig /
NK133(po)003:409: bdag rkyen rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi rnam rig las byung ba'o //
NK133(po)003:410: gnyis pa ni rgyud bla ma las /
NK133(po)003:411: gang zhig rgyal ba'i bstan pa 'ba' zhig gi //
NK133(po)003:412: dbang byas rnam g.yeng med yid can gyis bshad //
NK133(po)003:413: thar pa thob pa'i lam dang rjes mthun pa //
NK133(po)003:414: de yang drang srong gsung bzhin spyi bos blang //
NK133(po)003:416: rtsom pa po rnam g.yeng med pa'i yid can zab mo'i blo dang ldan pa dag gis /
NK133(po)003:417: rgyal ba'i bstan pa kho na'i dbang du byas nas
NK133(po)003:418: thar pa'i lam mtshon pa'i ngag 'chos skyob kyi yon
NK133(po)003:419: tan gnyis dang ldan par bkod pa la bstan bcos
NK133(po)003:420: zhes brjod de / rnam bshad rig par /
NK133(po)003:421: nyon mongs dgra rnams ma lus 'chos pa dang //
NK133(po)003:422: 'khor ba'i 'jigs las skyob pa gang yin pa //
NK133(po)003:423: 'chos skyob yon tan phyir na bstan bcos te //
NK133(po)003:424: gnyis po 'di dag gzhan gyi lugs na med //
NK133(po)003:426: de ltar lung dang rtogs pa'i rnam 'byed spyir bkod nas /
NK133(po)003:427: bye brag chos kyi 'khor lo ji ltar bskor ba'i tshul dngos la /
NK133(po)003:428: rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa rnams ni rgyal ba
NK133(po)003:429: thabs la mkhas pa'i bdag nyid can des gdul bya'i
NK133(po)003:430: gang zag gi blo nus kyi rim pa dang mthun
NK133(po)003:431: par / 'o ma'i sman gyi dpe dang /
NK133(po)003:432: nor bu sbyong ba'i dpe sogs kyis bstan pa ltar
NK133(po)003:433: dang po 'khor ba las nges par 'byung ba'i gtam
NK133(po)003:434: dang / bar du rnam thar sgo gsum gyi gtam dang /
NK133(po)003:435: tha mar phyir mi ldog pa'i 'khor lo'i gtam gyis
NK133(po)003:436: chos kyi 'khor lo rim pa gsum du bskor bar
NK133(po)003:437: mdzad pa yang / gzungs kyi dbang phyug rgyal pos zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK133(po)003:438: rigs kyi bu de bzhin gshegs pas yongs su ma
NK133(po)003:439: dag pa'i sems can gyi khams rig nas mi rtag
NK133(po)003:440: pa dang / sdug bsngal ba dang /
NK133(po)003:442: mi sdug pa yid 'byung bar 'gyur ba'i gtam gyis
NK133(po)003:443: 'khor ba la mngon par dga' ba'i sems can rnams
NK133(po)003:445: 'phags pa'i chos 'dul ba la 'jug par byed de /
NK133(po)003:446: de tsam gyis de bzhin gshegs pa brtson 'grus rgyun mi gcod cing /
NK133(po)003:447: de'i 'og tu stong pa nyid dang /
NK133(po)003:449: smon pa med pa'i gtam gyis de bzhin gshegs pa'i tshul khong du chud par byed do //
NK133(po)003:450: de tsam gyis kyang de bzhin gshegs pa brtson 'grus rgyun mi gcod kyi /
NK133(po)003:451: de'i 'og tu phyir mi ldog pa'i 'khor lo'i gtam dang /
NK133(po)003:452: 'khor gsum yongs su dag pa'i gtam gyis sems can
NK133(po)003:453: de dag de bzhin gshegs pa'i yul la 'dzud do
NK133(po)003:455: dang po bden bzhi'i chos 'khor ni /
NK133(po)003:456: ston pa sangs rgyas nas zhag bdun phrag bdun gyi mthar shing sgrol rgyu'i tshal du bzhugs nas /
NK133(po)003:457: zab zhi spros bral 'od gsal 'dus ma byas //
NK133(po)003:458: bdud rtsi'i lta bu'i chos shig bdag gis rnyed //
NK133(po)003:459: su la bstan kyang go bar mi nus pas //
NK133(po)003:460: mi smra nags 'dabs nyid du gnas par bya //
NK133(po)003:461: zhes chos mi gsung par thugs las chung ngu la gzhol ba'i tshe /
NK133(po)003:462: sngon gyi smon lam chen pos rgyud bskul nas lha'i dbang po tshangs pa dang /
NK133(po)003:463: brgya byin gnyis kyis gser gyi 'khor lo rtsibs stong pa dang /
NK133(po)003:464: yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po phul nas chos
NK133(po)003:465: kyi 'khor lo bskor bar gsol ba btab pa la
NK133(po)003:466: brten nas / yul w+aa r+aa na si drang srong lhung ba ri dwags kyi nags su /
NK133(po)003:467: 'khor lnga sde bzang po lha brgyad khri dang bcas pa la /
NK133(po)003:468: bden pa bzhi lan gsum du bzlas pa'i chos kyi
NK133(po)003:469: 'khor lo rnam pa bcu gnyis su bskor ba ste
NK133(po)003:470: 'dul ba lung la sogs pa rnams so //
NK133(po)003:471: bar pa mtshan nyid med pa'i chos kyi 'khor lo ni /
NK133(po)003:472: gnas bya rgod spung pa'i ri bo la sogs par /
NK133(po)003:473: 'khor nyan thos dang byang chub sems dpa'i tshogs la /
NK133(po)003:474: zab mo stong pa nyid kyi tshul las brtsams te /
NK133(po)003:475: gzugs nas rnam mkhyen gyi bar gyi chos thams cad
NK133(po)003:476: rang rang gi ngo bos stong par gtan la phab
NK133(po)003:477: nas bstan pa sher phyin stong phrag brgya pa sogs
NK133(po)003:478: yum sras bcu bdun gyi sder gtogs pa thams cad
NK133(po)003:479: do // tha ma legs par rnam par phye ba'i chos 'khor ni gnas yangs pa can dang /
NK133(po)003:481: ma la ya sogs gnas ma nges pa rnams su /
NK133(po)003:482: 'khor byang chub sems dpa' blo gros chen po dang /
NK133(po)003:483: dpal phreng seng ge'i nga ro sogs sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa'i tshul la mkhas pa sha stag la /
NK133(po)003:484: drang ba dang nges pa'i don dag so sor rnam
NK133(po)003:485: par phye ste legs par gtan la phab nas bshad
NK133(po)003:486: pa lang kar gshegs pa dang /
NK133(po)003:488: mdo dgongs pa nges 'grel mya ngan las 'das pa chen po'i mdo la sogs pa rnams dang /
NK133(po)003:489: gzhan yang phal po che dang /
NK133(po)003:490: dkon mchog brtsegs pa sogs shin tu rgyas pa'i sde snod ji snyed pa rnams so //
NK133(po)003:491: de ltar chos kyi 'khor lo rim pa gsum du bskor ba yang /
NK133(po)003:492: spang bya dang gnyen po'i sgo nas chos kyi phung po brgyad khri bzhi stong du nges te /
NK133(po)003:494: spyod pa rnams kyi gnyen por ni //
NK133(po)003:495: chos kyi phung po mthun par gsung //
NK133(po)003:498: nyon mongs 'dod chags 'dul ba'i gnyen po ru //
NK133(po)003:499: 'dul ba'i sde snod nyi khri chig stong gsungs //
NK133(po)003:500: zhe sdang 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsung pa ni //
NK133(po)003:501: mdo sde'i sde snod nyi khri chig stong gsungs //
NK133(po)003:502: gti mug 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsung pa ni //
NK133(po)003:503: mngon pa'i sde snod nyi khri chig stong gsungs //
NK133(po)003:504: cha mnyam 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsung pa ni //
NK133(po)003:505: sde snod bzhi pa nyi khri chig stong gsungs //
NK133(po)003:507: bdag rkyen ston pas gsungs tshul gyi sgo nas gsum du bzhag ste /
NK133(po)003:508: zhal nas gsungs pa'i bka' dang /
NK133(po)003:509: byin gyis rlabs pa'i bka' dang /
NK133(po)003:511: brjod bya bslab pa gsum du ston pa'i sgo nas
NK133(po)003:512: kyang gsum ste lhag pa'i tshul khrims kyi bslab pa
NK133(po)003:514: lhag pa'i sems kyi bslab pa gtso bor ston pa mdo sde /
NK133(po)003:515: lhag pa'i shes rab kyi bslab pa gtso bor ston pa mngon pa rnams so //
NK133(po)003:516: rjod byed gsung rab kyi sgo nas rnam grangs bcu gnyis su 'gyur te /
NK133(po)003:518: mdo sde dbyangs bsnyan lung du bstan //
NK133(po)003:519: tshigs bcad ched brjod gleng gzhi dang //
NK133(po)003:520: rtogs brjod de lta bu byung dang //
NK133(po)003:521: skyes rab shin tu rgyas pa dang //
NK133(po)003:522: rmad byung gtan la dbab pa'i sde //
NK133(po)003:523: gsung rab yan lag bcu gnyis so //
NK133(po)003:525: gdul bya'i gang zag gi dbang las /
NK133(po)003:526: theg pa'i rim pa gnyis su yang bzhag ste /
NK133(po)003:530: theg pa mchog gi bye brag gis gnyis su 'gyur te /
NK133(po)003:531: nyan thos kyi sde snod dang /
NK133(po)003:532: byang chub sems dpa'i sde snod do //
NK133(po)003:534: theg dman la nyan rang gnyis su dbye bas theg pa gsum dang /
NK133(po)003:536: rgyu 'bras kyi theg pa so sor phye bas bzhi dang /
NK133(po)003:537: lam stegs lha mi'i theg pa dang bcas pa lngar
NK133(po)003:538: bzhag pa sogs nas gnas skabs lam gyi dbye bas
NK133(po)003:539: grangs med pa'i bar du gsungs kyang mthar thug gi
NK133(po)003:540: don la theg pa tha dad kyi rnam par bzhag
NK133(po)003:543: ji srid sems kyi 'jug pa'i bar //
NK133(po)003:544: theg pa'i mtha' la thug pa med //
NK133(po)003:545: sems ni rab zad gyur pa na //
NK133(po)003:546: theg pa med cing 'gro ba'ang med //
NK133(po)003:548: grub matha'i sgo nas bzhag na /
NK133(po)003:549: 'khor lo dang po'i rjes su 'brang ba theg dman bye mdo gnyis dang /
NK133(po)003:550: 'khor lo bar tha gnyis kyi rjes su 'brang ba theg chen dbu sems gnyis te bzhi'o //
NK133(po)003:551: de dag la'ang nang gses kyi dbye ba dang 'dod
NK133(po)003:552: tshul gyi bye brag rgya cher yod kyang 'dir yi
NK133(po)003:554: de dag las khyad par du 'phags pa 'bras bu
NK133(po)003:555: gsang chen rdo rje theg pa'i chos kyi 'khor lo
NK133(po)003:557: gnas rang snang shin tu rnam par dag pa 'og min chen po'i zhing khams su /
NK133(po)003:558: ston pa rigs drug pa kun tu bzang po'am khyab bdag rdo rje 'chang chen pos /
NK133(po)003:559: nyid las mi gzhan pa'i bde bar gshegs pa'i tshogs tshad med pa la /
NK133(po)003:560: chos nyid brjod bral chen po'i dgongs pa sgra tshig
NK133(po)003:561: rang mtshan las 'das pa'i gsung gis snang bar mdzad
NK133(po)003:563: 'og min rnam mdzes chen po dang /
NK133(po)003:565: 'dzam bu'i gling rnams su longs spyod rdzogs pa dang /
NK133(po)003:566: sprul pa'i rnam pa tha dad pas gdul bya sa la gnas pa /
NK133(po)003:567: rigs pa khyad par can gyi 'khor dpa' bo dang
NK133(po)003:568: rnal 'byor ma'i tshogs bsam gyis mi khyab pa rnams
NK133(po)003:569: la / gsang sngags kyi rgyud sde mtha' dag brda
NK133(po)003:570: dang tshig gi sgo nas dus ci rigs par gsungs
NK133(po)003:571: la / te / 'jam dpal sgyu 'phrul dra'i bshad rgyud las //
NK133(po)003:572: gling bzhi rnam pa gsum yin te //
NK133(po)003:573: 'og min gnas dang ri rab rtse //
NK133(po)003:575: byang chub sems dpa' lha rnams dang //
NK133(po)003:576: mi rnams kyi ni don du gsungs //
NK133(po)003:577: ston pa yang ni rnam gsum ste //
NK133(po)003:578: sangs rgyas rdo rje 'chang chen dang //
NK133(po)003:579: sprul sku 'khor los bsgyur ba dang //
NK133(po)003:580: sh+aakya thub pa nyid kyis gsungs //
NK133(po)003:581: dus ni gdul bya 'dul ba'i tshe //
NK133(po)003:587: dpal ldan sham b+ha la sogs su /
NK133(po)003:588: ston pa nyid dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo'i rnam par
NK133(po)003:589: bzhengs pa'am ma bzhengs par ci rigs pas sngags kyi
NK133(po)003:590: rgyud sde bsam gyis mi khyab pa gsungs so //
NK133(po)003:591: theg pa'i rim pa gzhan ji snyed pa rnams kyang
NK133(po)003:592: dus de'i tshe gsang chen bla na med pa'i chos
NK133(po)003:593: kyi 'khor lo 'di nyid las 'phros te gsungs pa'ang
NK133(po)003:595: 'dul ba mdo sde chos mngon dang //
NK133(po)003:596: dam tshig sgrub dang grub pa dang //
NK133(po)003:597: sku dang gsung dang thugs kyi rgyud //
NK133(po)003:598: phyogs bcu rnams su rab grags pa //
NK133(po)003:599: gsang ba'i snying po las 'phros te //
NK133(po)003:600: rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po 'di //
NK133(po)003:601: sde snod kun dang rgyud kun gyi //
NK133(po)003:604: de ltar rgyu dang 'bras bu'i theg pa ji ltar
NK133(po)003:605: gsungs pa rnams so sor bka' yi bsdu ba mdzad
NK133(po)003:606: pa'i tshul la / theg dman nyan rang dang thun mong ba'i sde snod rnams ni /
NK133(po)003:607: ston pa mya ngan las 'das pa'i 'og tu /
NK133(po)003:608: lha rnams kyis 'phya ba bsal ba'i phyir /
NK133(po)003:609: rgyal po'i khab kyi nya gro d+ha'i phug par dgra bcom pa lnga brgya 'dus nas /
NK133(po)003:612: 'od srung chen pos mngon pa ste /
NK133(po)003:613: sde snod gsum ka legs par bsdus te bka' bsdu dang po'o /
NK133(po)003:614: slad nas kyang mi rung ba'i gzhi bcu dang /
NK133(po)003:615: rtsod pa'i gzhi lnga rnams byung ba la brten nas /
NK133(po)003:616: de dag bsal ba'i phyir bka' bsdu gnyis pa dang /
NK133(po)003:617: gsum pa dag kyang rim bzhin mdzad do //
NK133(po)003:618: theg chen pha rol tu phyin pa'i sde snod rnams ni /
NK133(po)003:619: rgyal po'i khab kyi lho phyogs bi ma sam b+ha'i ri la rgyal sras 'bum phrag bcu 'dus te /
NK133(po)003:620: phyag na rdo rjes mdo sde /
NK133(po)003:622: 'jam dpal gyis mngon pa rnams bsdus zhes grags so //
NK133(po)003:623: thun mong ma yin pa gsang ba sngags kyi rgyud sde rnams ni /
NK133(po)003:624: lcang lo can du byang chub sems dpa'i tshogs bye
NK133(po)003:625: ba phrag dgu cu rtsa drug gi dbus su gsang
NK133(po)003:626: ba'i bdag po phyag na rdo rje nyid kyis bsdu
NK133(po)003:627: ba mdzad de / in+d+ra b+hu ti'i bde mchog gi 'grel pa las /
NK133(po)003:628: phyi dus rim par lung bstan sdud pa pos //
NK133(po)003:629: ri bo mchog rab byang shar lha gnas mchog /
NK133(po)003:630: lcang lo can gyi pho brang chen por ni //
NK133(po)003:631: rgyud rnams ma lus sems dpa' chen po'i tshogs //
NK133(po)003:632: bye ba phrag ni dgu bcu rtsa drug sogs //
NK133(po)003:633: 'dus te rje btsun gsang ba'i bdag po la //
NK133(po)003:634: gsol ba btab tshe 'di skad bdag thos zhes //
NK133(po)003:635: rab tu gsungs pa gser gyi glegs bu la //
NK133(po)003:636: beed+aur+ya yi zhun mas yi ger bkod //
NK133(po)003:639: ma 'ongs pa'i dus su gsang ba'i rgyud skal ba
NK133(po)003:640: dang ldan pa'i sems can la sus 'chad par byed
NK133(po)003:642: phyag na rdo rje mgon pos bshad par byed do //
NK133(po)003:644: de ltar na dus 'khor zla ba bzang po dang brtags gnyis rdo rje snying po /
NK133(po)003:645: rdo rje mkha' 'gro phag mo sogs kyis bsdus pa ma yin nam zhe na /
NK133(po)003:646: de dag rnams kyang ston pa nyid kyi thugs rdo
NK133(po)003:647: rje sdud po dang 'khor gyi tshul du snang ba
NK133(po)003:648: las / rgyud tha dad pa ma yin pa'i phyir skyon med de /
NK133(po)003:649: gsang ba grub pa'i rgyud las /
NK133(po)003:650: 'di yi sdud par byed pa po //
NK133(po)003:651: gzhan dag yod pa ma yin zhes //
NK133(po)003:652: bdag nyid 'ba' zhig smra bar byed //
NK133(po)003:653: rgyud mdzad pa de thugs rdo rje //
NK133(po)003:655: rgyud 'chad pa de thugs rdo rje /
NK133(po)003:656: 'chad pa po de sdud pa'ang de /
NK133(po)003:658: de nas rdo rje chos dang /
NK133(po)003:660: rdo rje snying po sogs mtshan gyi rnam grangs tha dad pa dang /
NK133(po)003:663: sh+aakya thub pa sogs ston pa dang /
NK133(po)003:666: kun dga' bo sogs 'khor gyi sku'i snang tshul tha
NK133(po)003:667: dad pa rnams kyang don la dgongs pa dbyer mi
NK133(po)003:668: phyed par shes par bya ste /
NK133(po)003:669: ye shes thig le'i rgyud las /
NK133(po)003:670: lta ba kun ni srung don du //
NK133(po)003:671: sna tshogs pa yi gzugs su spyod //
NK133(po)003:672: la lar rdo rje 'dzin pa dang //
NK133(po)003:673: la lar sangs rgyas kyi ni gzugs //
NK133(po)003:674: la lar he ru ka yi gzugs //
NK133(po)003:675: la lar de bzhin gshegs pa dang //
NK133(po)003:676: la lar byang chub sems dpa'i gzugs //
NK133(po)003:677: la lar nyan pa lta bur bzhugs //
NK133(po)003:678: la lar mchod do dgyes pad+ma //
NK133(po)003:679: la lar klog pa'i tshul du bzhugs //
NK133(po)003:680: la lar rgyud dang bstan bcos ni //
NK133(po)003:681: mdzad pa dang ni la lar 'dzin //
NK133(po)003:682: mang du brjod lta ci zhig dgos //
NK133(po)003:683: de ston phyag na rdo rje rgyal //
NK133(po)003:685: de ltar ston pa sku gsum gyi rnam bzhag chos
NK133(po)003:686: kyi 'khor lo bskor tshul bka' yi bsdu ba mdzad
NK133(po)003:687: pa dang bcas pa mdor bsdus tsam brjod grub nas
NK133(po)003:688: / don gnyis pa rgya gar 'phags pa'i yul du
NK133(po)003:689: rgyu 'bras kyi theg pa bshad sgrub kyi sgo nas
NK133(po)003:690: rim pa bzhin ji ltar bskyangs pa'i tshul la /
NK133(po)003:691: thog mar nyan thos kyi theg pa gtso bor gyur pa'i sde snod rnams ni /
NK133(po)003:692: ston pa mya ngan las 'das pa'i tshe nyan thos 'od srung chen po la bstan pa gtad /
NK133(po)003:693: des kyang sngar bshad pa ltar bka' yi bsdu ba sogs mdzad nas bstan pa dar bar byas te /
NK133(po)003:694: kun dga' bo la gtad nas ri bo bya rkang
NK133(po)003:695: can du sku gdung mi 'jigs par byin gyis rlabs
NK133(po)003:697: kun dga' bos rgyal po'i khab tu gzhon nu gser
NK133(po)003:698: mdog gi skyabs mdzad nas dgra bcom pa la bkod
NK133(po)003:699: pa dang / lho phyogs kyi bram ze ba ra
NK133(po)003:700: dza gnod can dang rus gcig pa cho 'phrul gyi
NK133(po)003:701: tshar bcad pa sogs lha dang mi'i don rgya chen
NK133(po)003:702: po mdzad nas sha na'i gos can bsnyen par rdzogs
NK133(po)003:704: de nas chu bo gang+ga'i dbus su drang srong nyi
NK133(po)003:705: ma'i gung pa rab tu phyungs nas bsnyen par rdzogs
NK133(po)003:706: shing / spyir sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa skyong ba dang /
NK133(po)003:707: khyad par kha che'i yul du bstan pa spel bar gdam nas mya ngan las 'das so //
NK133(po)003:708: sha na'i gos can gyis rgyal po gzhu bzang gi
NK133(po)003:709: 'khor nyis stong rab tu phyungs nas 'bras bu la
NK133(po)003:710: bkod pa sogs dgra bcom pa khri dang bden pa
NK133(po)003:711: mthong ba'ang 'bum tsam du byung bar grags shing /
NK133(po)003:712: de nas mtshan med pa'i sangs rgyas su lung bstan
NK133(po)003:713: pa spos tshong gi bu nyer sbas rab tu byung
NK133(po)003:714: nas bstan pa gtad de yul tsam par mya ngan
NK133(po)003:715: las 'das so // 'phags pa nyer sbas kyis lus 'phags dang /
NK133(po)003:717: gar mkhan dpa' bo'i gtsug lag rnams su rim par
NK133(po)003:718: byon nas chos bstan pas dgra bcom pa thob pa
NK133(po)003:719: yang bgrang gis mi lang ba byung ngo //
NK133(po)003:720: gzhan yang bdud sdig to can rdzu 'phrul gyis btul
NK133(po)003:721: ba sogs rgyal ba'i bstan pa la rmad du byung
NK133(po)003:722: ba'i mdzad pa du ma bsgrub nas /
NK133(po)003:723: grong khyer ma thu rar bram ze h+ai ti ka
NK133(po)003:724: rab tu phyung nas zhag bdun na dgra bcom par
NK133(po)003:725: gyur pa de la bstan pa gtad nas mya ngan
NK133(po)003:726: las 'das so // 'di'i dus su nyan thos bye
NK133(po)003:727: brag smra ba dag gi gzhung phyi mor gyur pa
NK133(po)003:728: bye brag bshad mdzod chen mo'ang dgra bcom pa rnams
NK133(po)003:729: kyi spyi mthun du mdzad par grags so //
NK133(po)003:730: h+ai ti kas tho gar gyi rgyal po nam mkha' la mchod pa dang /
NK133(po)003:731: shar phyogs k+aa ma ru pa'i bram ze seng+ha zhes
NK133(po)003:732: pa 'khor stong phrag mang po dang bcas pa nyi
NK133(po)003:734: mal+la war bram ze dregs byed ces pa ra skyes
NK133(po)003:735: kyi mchod sbyin byed pa rnams rdzu 'phrul gyis dad
NK133(po)003:736: par byas nas skye bo mang po dgra bcom pa
NK133(po)003:739: de nas shar phyogs ang+ga'i yul gyi tshong dpon nag
NK133(po)003:740: po zhes pa rgya mtsho'i gling du srin mo'i 'jigs
NK133(po)003:741: pa las bskyabs nas mthar rab tu phyungs nas dgra
NK133(po)003:742: bcom par gyur pa la bstan pa gtad de grong
NK133(po)003:743: khyer 'phags rgyal du mya ngan las 'das so //
NK133(po)003:744: 'di'i ring la dgra bcom pa grags pa dang /
NK133(po)003:745: thams cad 'dod sogs kyis bka' bsdu bar pa mdzad pa'i skabs yin no //
NK133(po)003:747: kha che'i yul du bstan pa la skyon byung ba bsal ba dang /
NK133(po)003:748: sing+g+ha la'i yul du byon nas rgyal po sing+ha ko
NK133(po)003:749: sha 'khor bcas 'bras bu la bkod nas yul phyogs
NK133(po)003:750: der gtsug lag khang dang dge 'dun gyis khyab par
NK133(po)003:751: mdzad do // nub phyogs b+ha ru ka tsar skya
NK133(po)003:752: bseng gi rigs mthong ba'i bu legs mthong zhes pa
NK133(po)003:753: dgra bcom pa su k+aa ya na'i slob mar gyur
NK133(po)003:754: pa de la bstan pa gtad nas byang phyogs ku
NK133(po)003:755: sha'i tshal du mya ngan las 'das so //
NK133(po)003:757: nub phyogs sin+d+hu'i yul du gnod sbyin mo sing+g+ha l+ai
NK133(po)003:758: c+ai sogs bstan pa la ma dad pa'i klu dang
NK133(po)003:759: gnod sbyin lnga brgya tsam btul nas sangs rgyas kyi
NK133(po)003:760: bstan pa rgya cher spel bar mdzad do //
NK133(po)003:761: skabs 'di tsam na rgya nag gi yul du'ang bstan
NK133(po)003:762: pa'i mgo tshugs par grags te de yan chad la
NK133(po)003:763: bstan pa'i gtad rab bdun zhes bshad do //
NK133(po)003:764: 'di'i tshe rgyal po d+harma a shwa ka rgyal srid byed pa las /
NK133(po)003:765: de'i bu ku na la'i mig /
NK133(po)003:768: de nas bzung ste ka nish+ka'i bar gyi rgyal rab
NK133(po)003:769: bzhi la dge slong lha chen sogs kyis rtsod pa
NK133(po)003:770: spel ba'i rgyus dge 'dun rnams che thang du 'khrugs
NK133(po)003:771: nas / nyan thos rtsa ba'i sde bzhi nas rim par bco brgyad kyi bar du gyes so //
NK133(po)003:772: de'i tshe dgra bcom pa rtsibs log dang /
NK133(po)003:773: ba su mi tra sogs kyis gyes pa bco brgyad
NK133(po)003:774: sangs rgyas kyi bkar bsgrub te bka' bsdu gsum pa'i
NK133(po)003:775: dus so // theg chen pha rol tu phyin pa'i
NK133(po)003:776: sde snod rnams ni lha klu gnod sbyin sogs kyi
NK133(po)003:777: yul du rgya cher 'phel zhing mi yul gzhan du
NK133(po)003:778: khol bur spyod pa las yul dbus su cher ma
NK133(po)003:779: dus so // dar kyang / dus 'di tsam na
NK133(po)003:780: yul o di bi shar rgyal po zla bsrung zhes
NK133(po)003:781: pa'i khyim du 'phags pa 'jam dpal gyi sprul pa'i
NK133(po)003:782: dge slong zhig gis brgyad stong pa'i glegs bam zhig
NK133(po)003:783: bzhag ste song ba nas bzung theg chen dar ba'i
NK133(po)003:785: rim bzhin byang chub sems dpa'i byams pa dang /
NK133(po)003:786: 'jam dpal sogs las dngos su chos gsan pa'i pan+di ta mang du byon nas /
NK133(po)003:788: lang+kara gshegs pa sogs theg chen gyi sde snod phal che ba mi yul du dar bar mdzad do //
NK133(po)003:789: de nas ring por ma lon par sangs rgyas nyid
NK133(po)003:790: kyis bka'i dgongs 'grel mdzad pa por lung bstan pa'i
NK133(po)003:791: shing rta chen po rnam gnyis byon nas theg pa
NK133(po)003:792: chen po dar rgyas su mdzad tshul ni /
NK133(po)003:794: lho phyogs be da'i yul du ni //
NK133(po)003:795: dge slong dpal ldan cher grags pa //
NK133(po)003:796: de ming klu zhes 'bod pa ste //
NK133(po)003:797: yod dang med pa'i phyogs 'jig pa //
NK133(po)003:798: nga yi theg pa 'jig rten du //
NK133(po)003:799: bla med theg par rab bshad nas //
NK133(po)003:800: rab tu dga' ba'i sa bsgrubs te //
NK133(po)003:803: sangs rgyas mya ngan las 'das nas lo bzhi brgya
NK133(po)003:804: lon pa na dpal mgon 'phags pa klu sgrub zhabs
NK133(po)003:805: kyis / rgyas pa 'bum klu yul nas spyan 'dren pa dang /
NK133(po)003:806: bka' dang po'i dgongs 'grel du gtam tshogs /
NK133(po)003:807: bar pa'i dgongs 'grel du rig tshogs /
NK133(po)003:808: tha ma'i dgongs 'grel du bstod tshogs sogs mdzad nas
NK133(po)003:809: zab mo dbu ma'i lam gyi srol phye bar mdzad
NK133(po)003:810: do // slob dpon thogs med ni /
NK133(po)003:812: thogs med ces bya'i dge slong ni //
NK133(po)003:813: bstan bcos de ni don la mkhas //
NK133(po)003:814: mdo sde nges don drang ba'i don //
NK133(po)003:815: rnam pa mang po'i rab tu 'byed //
NK133(po)003:817: thogs med sku mched byon te /
NK133(po)003:818: thogs med zhabs kyis rje btsun ma pham pa las byams chos lnga dngos su gsan zhing /
NK133(po)003:821: gcung dbyig gnyen gyis rab tu byed pa brgyad sogs
NK133(po)003:822: brtsam pa rnams byams pa dang 'brel ba'i chos nyi
NK133(po)003:823: shur grags te / rnal 'byor spyod pa sems tsam pa'i gzhung 'byed par mdzad do //
NK133(po)003:824: gzhan yang slob dpon klu sgrub kyi rjes su 'brangs nas zab mo dbu ma'i srol 'dzin /
NK133(po)003:827: zla ba grags pa sogs dang /
NK133(po)003:828: thogs med yab sras kyi rjes su 'brangs nas /
NK133(po)003:829: rnal 'byor spyod pa'i srol 'dzin pa phyogs kyi glang po /
NK133(po)003:830: chos kyi grags pa tsan+d+ra go mi sogs mkhas shing
NK133(po)003:831: grub pa'i khyu mchog chen po rtsod pa dang bral
NK133(po)003:832: ba rnams kyis bshad sgrub las kyi 'khor lo gsum
NK133(po)003:833: gyis rgyal ba'i bstan pa la mdzad pa ji ltar
NK133(po)003:834: bgyis pa rnams rgya cher gzhan las shes par bya'o
NK133(po)003:835: // gsang chen bla na med pa'i rgyud sde gtso
NK133(po)003:836: bor gyur pa'i rig pa 'dzin pa sngags kyi sde
NK133(po)003:837: // snod rnams ni / ston pas 'og min du
NK133(po)003:838: gsungs nas nyid las mi gzhan pa'i rgyal sras rigs
NK133(po)003:841: phyi rab kyi gang zag chos kyi spyan ldan rnams
NK133(po)003:842: dang bcas pa la bstan pa mi nub pa'i btsas
NK133(po)003:843: su rgyud gtad par mdzad pa yin te /
NK133(po)003:844: glang chen rab 'bog gi rtogs pa dum bu'i rgyud las /
NK133(po)003:845: sku gsung thugs kyi sprul pa rigs gsum mgon //
NK133(po)003:846: de la gtad pas khams su sgron me yin //
NK133(po)003:847: rigs lnga 'khor gyi mkha' 'gro sde bzhi rnams //
NK133(po)003:848: de la gtad pas gsang sngags srung ma yin //
NK133(po)003:849: sngon sbyangs gang zag chos kyi spyan ldan rnams //
NK133(po)003:850: de la gtad pas bstan pa dar ba yin //
NK133(po)003:852: de las rgyal sras rigs gsum sems dpas thog mar
NK133(po)003:853: lha klu gnod sbyin gyi gnas so sor gsang sngags
NK133(po)003:854: kyi bstan pa ji ltar spel tshul ni /
NK133(po)003:855: mkhyen rab kyi dbang phyug 'jam dpal gzhon nu mdzes
NK133(po)003:856: pa'i sku dang ldan pa de nyid kyis lha rnams
NK133(po)003:857: kyi lus dang bsam pa dang mthun par lha grags
NK133(po)003:861: tshangs pa skye gu'i bdag po /
NK133(po)003:863: tshangs pa gtsug phud 'dzin lha'i dbang po brgya byin rnams la brgyud nas /
NK133(po)003:864: tshom bu 'bum dang bcas pas mchog gi dngos grub
NK133(po)003:865: brnyes te lha yul du bstan pa dar bar gyur
NK133(po)003:866: to // byams brtse'i mnga' bdag spyan ras gzigs bdud rtsi sman gyi sku dang ldan pa des /
NK133(po)003:867: klu rnams kyi lus dang bsam pa dang mthun par klu rgyal mgrin pa nag po la bshad /
NK133(po)003:872: klu rgyal 'jog po rnams la bshad de tshom bu
NK133(po)003:873: 'bum dang bcas pa rig pa 'dzin pa'i sar bkod
NK133(po)003:874: nas klu'i yul du bstan pa dar bar mdzad do
NK133(po)003:875: // mthu stobs kyi bdag po phyag na rdo rje 'jigs tshul bsdig pa'i sku dang ldan pa des /
NK133(po)003:876: gnod sbyin rnams kyi lus dang bsam pa dang mthun par gnod sbyin kun tu bzang po la bshad /
NK133(po)003:878: gnod sbyin lag na rdo rje dang /
NK133(po)003:879: skar mda' gdong sogs las brgyud nas tshom bu 'bum
NK133(po)003:880: dang bcas pa rdo rje 'chang gi sar gshegs te
NK133(po)003:881: / gnod sbyin gyi yul du bstan pa rgyas par mdzad do //
NK133(po)003:882: de nas bstan pa de nyid mi'i yul du yongs su grags pa ji ltar byung tshul ni /
NK133(po)003:883: mdo dgongs pa lung ston las /
NK133(po)003:884: rgyu la mos pa rgyu'i chos kyi //
NK133(po)003:885: 'khor lo rab tu bskor byas nas //
NK133(po)003:886: rdo rje theg pa'i nye lam zhig /
NK133(po)003:888: zhes ma 'ongs pa'i dus na 'bras bu rdo rje'i theg pa 'byung ba spyir lung bstan cing /
NK133(po)003:889: bye brag tu dus ci tsam na gang zag gang
NK133(po)003:890: la gnas gang du tshul ji ltar snang ba yang
NK133(po)003:892: nga ni 'di nas mi snang nas //
NK133(po)003:893: lo ni brgyad dang bcu gnyis na //
NK133(po)003:894: lha gnas gsum du grags pa yi //
NK133(po)003:895: bstan pa'i snying po dam pa zhig /'dzam gling shar gyi phyogs mtshams kyi //
NK133(po)003:896: mi las rigs can skal ldan de //
NK133(po)003:897: rgyal po dza zhes bya ba la //
NK133(po)003:898: sngon du ltas snang snang 'gyur te //
NK133(po)003:899: drag shul can zhes bya ba'i rtser //
NK133(po)003:900: grogs kyi sems dpa' dman pa'i lus //
NK133(po)003:901: lang+ka'i bdag po la sogs la //
NK133(po)003:902: lag na rdo rjes snang bar 'gyur //
NK133(po)003:904: ston pa mchog gi sprul pa'i sku mya ngan las 'das nas lo nyi shu rtsa brgyad na /
NK133(po)003:908: srin po blo gros thabs ldan /
NK133(po)003:909: mi'i rig 'dzin li tsa b+ai dri med grags pa ste /
NK133(po)003:910: dam pa'i rigs can dra ma lnga rang rang gi
NK133(po)003:911: gnas su nang du yang dag 'jog pa la zhugs
NK133(po)003:913: 'jig rten mun pa lta bur gyur pa mthong nas ston pa mya ngan las 'das pa shes te /
NK133(po)003:914: gang du 'du ba'i gnas ni ji skad du /
NK133(po)003:915: rtse na rtsal gyi rgyal po gnas //
NK133(po)003:916: ngos la brag dkar khyi tshug pa //
NK133(po)003:918: rtsi sman rtsa brgyad rtsa bar 'khrungs //
NK133(po)003:919: 'du ba'i nad kyis yongs mi tshug /
NK133(po)003:920: spyi bor ka lan+ta ka ni //
NK133(po)003:921: mi gnyis gcig pur gnas pa yi //
NK133(po)003:922: mdzod ldan de yi tshang bcas pa //
NK133(po)003:923: skal ldan rnams kyis bgrod par sla //
NK133(po)003:924: skal med rnams kyis yongs mi thar //
NK133(po)003:925: zhes pa'i mtshan nyid rnams dang ldan pa'i lang+ka'i yul
NK133(po)003:926: gyi ri bo drag shul can nam gnam lcags yod
NK133(po)003:927: pa'i rtse mor rang rang gi rdzu 'phrul gyi bya
NK133(po)003:928: bas gshegs te / kye ma'o kyi hud kye ma klong //
NK133(po)003:929: ston pa sgron me'i 'od nub na //
NK133(po)003:930: 'jig rten mun pa gang gis sel //
NK133(po)003:931: zhes pa la sogs pa'i gdung tshig nyer gsum bton pas /
NK133(po)003:932: gsang ba'i bdag po dngos su byon nas /
NK133(po)003:933: dam pa'i rigs can dra ma lnga sogs rig 'dzin 'dus pa phal mo che la /
NK133(po)003:934: sngar 'og min sogs su bstan pa'i gsang sngags kyi rgyud sde rnams slar yang bzlas te gsungs so //
NK133(po)003:935: de rnams srin po blo gros thabs ldan gyis rin
NK133(po)003:936: po gser gyi shog bu la beed+aur+ya'i zhun mas yi
NK133(po)003:937: ger bris nas dgongs pa ting 'dzin ni gyi rtsal
NK133(po)003:938: gyis mi zad pa'i gter nam mkha'i mdzod du rgya
NK133(po)003:940: de'i tshe de'i byin rlabs kyis sa ho ra'i rgyal
NK133(po)003:941: po dza la rmi ltas ngo mtshar ba bdun byung
NK133(po)003:942: ba ni / sku gsung thugs rtags thim pa dang //
NK133(po)003:943: rin chen glegs bam babs pa dang //
NK133(po)003:944: chos kyi bgro ba byed pa dang //
NK133(po)003:945: kun gyi dam par bsgrags pa dang //
NK133(po)003:946: mchod pa chen po byas pa dang //
NK133(po)003:947: rin chen char du babs pa dang //
NK133(po)003:948: sangs rgyas sa la lung bstan pa'o //
NK133(po)003:950: rmi ltas dang mthun par rgyal po'i khang steng du badz+ra p+aa ni'i sku khru gang ba zhig dang /
NK133(po)003:951: sarba bud+d+ha sa ma yo ga sogs rgyud sde chen
NK133(po)003:952: po rnams kyi glegs bam mang po babs par gyur
NK133(po)003:953: to // de nas glegs bam rnams la rgyal pos
NK133(po)003:954: brtags pas don ma shes nas 'jig rten na 'di'i
NK133(po)003:955: brda' mjal ba su yod ces bsgrags pa na za
NK133(po)003:956: hor gyi rgyal po u pa r+aa dza zhes bya
NK133(po)003:957: ba mkhyen rab che bar gsan nas de la bstan
NK133(po)003:958: pas kyang don dang brda' ma mjal /
NK133(po)003:959: de nas slob dpon ku ku r+aa dza la bstan pas /
NK133(po)003:960: de'i rdor sems zhal mthong gi le'u rtogs te sgrub
NK133(po)003:961: pas rdo rje sems dpas zhal bstan rgyud kyi don
NK133(po)003:962: rnams rgyal po nyid la gsang ba'i bdag pos ston
NK133(po)003:963: par 'gyur ro zhes lung bstan pa ltar /
NK133(po)003:965: de nas rgyal po nyid kyis rdo rje sems dpa'
NK133(po)003:966: zhal mthong gi le'u dang badz+ra pa ni'i sku la
NK133(po)003:967: brten nas sgrub pa mdzad cing gsol ba btab pas
NK133(po)003:968: rdo rje sems dpa'i zhal gzigs nas /
NK133(po)003:969: khyod kyi ston pa ni gsang ba'i bdag po yin
NK133(po)003:970: gyi des ston par 'gyur ro zhes gsungs thos nas
NK133(po)003:971: dga' ba cher skyes te sgrub pa la brtson pas
NK133(po)003:972: / re zhig nas gsang ba'i bdag po mngon sum du byon nas /
NK133(po)003:973: theg pa thams cad rdzogs pa'i dbang bskur zhing rgyud kyi don rnams bstan pa /
NK133(po)003:974: tshig gi bstan pa li tsa bi dri med grags
NK133(po)003:975: pa la zhus shig ces lung bstan pa ltar gsan
NK133(po)003:976: zhing / gsang bdag gi bka' ltar rgyud sde chen
NK133(po)003:977: po bco brgyad du so sor phyes nas slob dpon
NK133(po)003:978: ku ku r+aa dza la bshad /
NK133(po)003:979: des in+d+ra bo ti la bshad /
NK133(po)003:981: des u pa r+aa dza la /
NK133(po)003:982: des sras mo go ma de w+ai la bshad cing
NK133(po)003:983: so so'i tshom bu dang bcas pa rdo rje 'chang
NK133(po)003:986: sangs rgyas gsang ba'i lam rim las /
NK133(po)003:987: gsang ba'i bdag po mngon gshegs nas //
NK133(po)003:988: lha klu gnod sbyin srun po dang //
NK133(po)003:989: mi las skal ldan 'dus pa la //
NK133(po)003:990: dbang pos ji ltar lung bstan dus //
NK133(po)003:991: rgyal bu rigs can ltas shar ba //
NK133(po)003:992: 'brel bas snang ba mngon brtags pas //
NK133(po)003:993: thugs kyi sgrub pa mngon rtogs te //
NK133(po)003:994: de nyid sgo nas de nyid bsgrubs //
NK133(po)003:995: bstan pa'i dngos grub de nas thob //
NK133(po)003:996: don dam bcud kyis de nas rgyas //
NK133(po)003:998: smon pa'i lha dang de ru mjal //
NK133(po)003:999: de nas rdo rje gdan steng gi //
NK133(po)003:1000: 'dzam gling shar gyi phyogs mtshams su //
NK133(po)003:1001: pho brang rin chen dam pa der //
NK133(po)003:1002: bkra shis pa yi khang bu ru //
NK133(po)003:1003: ku ku r+aa dza in+d+ra bo d+hi dang //
NK133(po)003:1004: sing ha u pa r+aa dza dang //
NK133(po)003:1005: sras mo go ma sa la sogs //
NK133(po)003:1006: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i dbang thob nas //
NK133(po)003:1007: tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor mngon bsgrubs te /
NK133(po)003:1008: rdo rje 'chang sar mngon du gshegs //
NK133(po)003:1012: sprul pa'i sku 'das phyi ma'i dus kyi tshe //
NK133(po)003:1013: rgyal ba'i bka' gsang 'dzam gling gnas su shar //
NK133(po)003:1014: rgyal po'i khab tu spyan drangs mchod byas te //
NK133(po)003:1015: dga' zhing gus bstod legs bltas brda' ma mjal //
NK133(po)003:1016: thugs rje'i 'brel shugs gsang sngags 'dzin par grags //
NK133(po)003:1017: dam par bzung nas glegs bam gzigs par zhus //
NK133(po)003:1018: sgyu 'phrul thig le stong pa'i dkyil 'khor gzhung //
NK133(po)003:1019: grub thob lhag pa'i lha yis lung bstan mdzad //
NK133(po)003:1020: rdo rje theg pa'i gzhung lugs sna tshogs mtha' //
NK133(po)003:1021: dam pa rnams kyis gdams pa ji bzhin pa //
NK133(po)003:1022: mi 'gal legs par bsdus shing rab bkrol te //
NK133(po)003:1023: 'grel dang bsdus don sgrub thabs mang du bstan //
NK133(po)003:1025: de nas sras mo go ma de w+ais ku ku r+aa dza phyi ma la bshad /
NK133(po)003:1028: sangs rgyas gsang ba gsum sogs la bshad pa nas rgya cher 'phel lo //
NK133(po)003:1029: 'di dang dus mnyam du a nu yo ga'i rgyud rnams sing+ga la'i nags tshal du babs pa dang /
NK133(po)003:1030: kri ya'i rgyud rnams w+aa r+aa na sir /
NK133(po)003:1031: yo ga rnams me ri 'bar ba'i rtse mor babs par bshad /
NK133(po)003:1032: gsang chen a ti yo ga'i rgyud sde rnams ni /
NK133(po)003:1033: lha'i bu kun dga' snying po zhes bya ba de
NK133(po)003:1034: nyid nub phyogs o rgyan gyi yul du rgyal po
NK133(po)003:1035: u pa r+aa dza'i sras mo su d+harma zhes bya
NK133(po)003:1036: ba'i sras su 'khrungs pa sprul pa'i sku dga' rab
NK133(po)003:1037: rdo rjes 'og min du rdo rje sems dpa' las
NK133(po)003:1038: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i chos rnams mngon sum
NK133(po)003:1039: du gsan nas slob dpon 'jam dpal bshes gnyen sogs
NK133(po)003:1040: la bstan nas bzung rim par dar ro //
NK133(po)003:1041: 'di dag ni gtso bor snga 'gyur gyi phyogs su grags che ba tsam zhig brjod pa yin gyis /
NK133(po)003:1042: gzhan du o rgyan gyi yul dang sham b+ha la sogs nas grub pa brnyes pa'i skyes bu /
NK133(po)003:1045: mtsho skyes zhabs sogs kyis blang nas dar ba sogs
NK133(po)003:1046: gsang sngags kyi byung tshul ni mtha' yas par yod
NK133(po)003:1047: pas mtha' gcig tu 'chad par mi nus so //
NK133(po)003:1048: gsum pa bod gangs can gyi ljongs 'dir mdo sngags kyi bstan pa dar tshul ni /
NK133(po)003:1049: bod kyi rgyal po'i thog ma gnya' khri btsan po
NK133(po)003:1050: nas bzung rgyal rab nyer drug 'das pa lha tho
NK133(po)003:1051: tho ri snyan shal gyi sku ring la bod du
NK133(po)003:1052: dam chos dar ba'i snga ltas su dpang skong phyag
NK133(po)003:1053: rgya pa / mdo sde za ma tog sogs babs pa nas dam pa chos kyi dbu brnyes /
NK133(po)003:1054: chos rgyal srong btsan sgam po'i sku ring la ra
NK133(po)003:1055: sa 'phrul snang sogs mtha' 'dul yang 'dul gyi gtsug
NK133(po)003:1057: rten gyi gtso bo jo sh+aaka rnam gnyis spyan drangs /
NK133(po)003:1058: lo ts+aa ba thu mi sam b+ho ta rgya gar
NK133(po)003:1059: du bardzangasa nas yig rigs dang sgra sbyor la phul
NK133(po)003:1060: du phyin par bslabs te bod yig gi srol btod
NK133(po)003:1061: cing sum cu pa dang rtags kyi 'jug pa sogs
NK133(po)003:1062: brda' sprod kyi bstan bcos kyang mdzad /
NK133(po)003:1063: mdo sde dkon mchog sprin dang /
NK133(po)003:1064: za ma tog sogs theg pa chen po'i sde snod
NK133(po)003:1065: mang du bsgyur nas dam pa'i chos kyi srol btod
NK133(po)003:1066: do // khyad par du 'phags pa 'jam dpal dbyangs
NK133(po)003:1067: kyi sprul pa chos skyong ba'i rgyal po lha btsad
NK133(po)003:1068: po khri srong lde'u btsan gyi ring la'ang 'phags yul
NK133(po)003:1069: nas za hor mkhan po zhi ba 'tsho dang /
NK133(po)003:1070: o rgyan gyi slob dpon sangs rgyas gnyis pa pad+ma sam b+ha wa spyan drangs /
NK133(po)003:1071: slob dpon chen pos bod kyi lha 'dre mthu bo
NK133(po)003:1072: che rnams dam 'og tu bcug nas sa gzhi byin
NK133(po)003:1073: gyis brlabs / zan yang mi 'gyur lhun gyi grub
NK133(po)003:1074: pa'i gtsug lag bzhengs nas rab tu gnas par mdzad
NK133(po)003:1075: gyis brlabs / / rgya gar 'phags yul nas yod smra'i dge slong bcu gnyis spyan drangs /
NK133(po)003:1076: mkhan po bo d+hi sa t+wa sh+aan+ta rak+shi tas mkhan po dang /
NK133(po)003:1078: dzi na mi tra gnyis kyis las slob dang gsang ston /
NK133(po)003:1079: pan+di ta bcu po kha skong mdzad nas bod kyi
NK133(po)003:1080: mi la rab tu byung gtub bam mi gtub sad
NK133(po)003:1081: pa'i phyir rba khri gzigs rab tu byung zhing bsnyen
NK133(po)003:1082: par rdzogs te mtshan dpal dbyangs dang /
NK133(po)003:1083: btsan pos bod kyi dkon mchog zhes basngagasa pas rba rat+nara grags /
NK133(po)003:1084: sgom pas mngon shes lnga dang ldan /
NK133(po)003:1085: de nas rim par rba gsal snang /
NK133(po)003:1086: pa gor bee ro tsa na /
NK133(po)003:1087: ngan lam rgyal ba mchog dbyangs /
NK133(po)003:1088: rma rin chen mchog mkhon klu'i dbang po /
NK133(po)003:1089: la sum rgyal ba byang chub rnams rab tu byung
NK133(po)003:1090: zhing bsnyen par rdzogs te mtshan ye shes dbang po
NK133(po)003:1091: sogs su btags pa la 'dul 'dzin sad mi bdun
NK133(po)003:1092: zhes grags te bod kyi rab byung thog ma bstan
NK133(po)003:1093: pa'i gzhi btsugs pa yin la /
NK133(po)003:1094: sad mi bdun las blo sbyangs pa ska ba dpal brtsegs sogs lo ts+aa ba brgya /
NK133(po)003:1095: de dag las sbyangs ba cog ro klu'i rgyal mtshan
NK133(po)003:1096: sogs mchan bu stong rtsa ste sprul pa'i lo ts+aa
NK133(po)003:1097: ba dang btsun pa'i sde grangs las 'das pa byon
NK133(po)003:1098: / 'dul ba lung sde bzhi dgongs 'grel dang bcas slob dpon d+aa na sh+ai la dang /
NK133(po)003:1099: dzi na mi tra gnyis las lo ts+aa ba cog
NK133(po)003:1100: ro klu'i rgyal mtshan sogs kyis bsgyur cing zhus te
NK133(po)003:1101: gtan la phab / gzhan yang 'phags yul nas slob dpon chen po shin+tam gar+b+ha /
NK133(po)003:1106: bi ma mi tra sogs pan chen brgya dang rtsa brgyad spyan drangs /
NK133(po)003:1107: lo ts+aa ba bee ro ka cog zhang gsum /
NK133(po)003:1109: gnyags dz+ny+aa na ku ma ra /
NK133(po)003:1110: brang ti dza ya badz+ra sogs mdo sngags gzhung lugs
NK133(po)003:1111: rab 'byams la thogs pa med par mkhyen pa rgyas
NK133(po)003:1112: pa'i 'phags yul gyi pan grub chen po rnams dang
NK133(po)003:1113: khyad par mi mnga' ba dpag tu med pa byon
NK133(po)003:1114: / sam kri ta sogs skad rigs bzhi mkha' 'gro'i
NK133(po)003:1115: brda' skad sogs la dbang 'byor ba shin tu mang
NK133(po)003:1116: bas gsung rab gzhung tshan re'ang mkhas pa mang pos
NK133(po)003:1117: dum bu dum bur mdzad de bsgyur ba bsgyur byang
NK133(po)003:1119: deng sang bka' 'gyur gyi khrod du bzhugs pa thar
NK133(po)003:1120: lo'i mdo phran bcu gsum tsam ma gtogs snga 'gyur
NK133(po)003:1121: kho na yin / dus de tsam na dpal gyi
NK133(po)003:1122: bsam yas sogs chos 'khor gsum du klog pa thos
NK133(po)003:1123: bsam gyi 'khor lo gtso bor bzung nas sde snod
NK133(po)003:1124: gsum dang rgyud sde drug bcas lung gi bstan pa
NK133(po)003:1125: mtha' dag bshad nyan gyi sgo nas 'dzin skyong spel
NK133(po)003:1126: kho na yin / bar mdzad cing / mchims phu /
NK133(po)003:1128: shel brag gsum sogs su spong ba bsam gtan gyi
NK133(po)003:1129: 'khor lor gtso bor bzung nas rtogs pa'i bstan pa
NK133(po)003:1130: sgrub pa'i sgo nas 'dzin par mdzad pas gangs can
NK133(po)003:1131: gyi ljongs 'dir rgyal ba'i lung rtogs kyi bstan pa
NK133(po)003:1132: rin chen po nyin mor byed pa'i dpal ltar 'bar
NK133(po)003:1133: zhing mkhas shing grub pa brnyes pa'i bstan 'dzin gyi
NK133(po)003:1134: skyes bu rnams kyis kyang sa chen po'i phyogs kun
NK133(po)003:1136: de nas lha sras mu tig btsan pos ka chu'i lha khang bzhengs /
NK133(po)003:1137: mnga' bdag ral pa can gyis 'un shang rdo dpe
NK133(po)003:1138: med bkra shis dge 'phel gyi lha khang bzhengs pa
NK133(po)003:1139: sogs chos rgyal 'di gnyis kyi ring la yab mes
NK133(po)003:1140: kyi srol bzung nas sngar gyi 'gyur 'phro rnams bsgyur
NK133(po)003:1141: ba dang / bsgyur zin pa rnams zhus dag bgyis
NK133(po)003:1142: nas skad gsar bcad gyis gtan la phab pa sogs
NK133(po)003:1143: rgyal ba'i bstan pa la rma med pa'i mdzad pa
NK133(po)003:1145: de ltar rgyal po tho ri snyan shal nas bzung
NK133(po)003:1146: mnga' bdag ral pa can gyi bar la skyid pa'i
NK133(po)003:1147: gdung rab bcu gsum zhes grags te /
NK133(po)003:1148: de dag gi ring la pan+di ta lha rig pa'i seng ge ste ku sa ra /
NK133(po)003:1149: bram ze shang+ka ra kha che t+aa nu /
NK133(po)003:1156: yo ga'i slob dpon d+harma k+airti /
NK133(po)003:1168: di nya pra b+ha sogs dang /
NK133(po)003:1169: rgya'i slob dpon hwa shang ma h+aa de ba tshe /
NK133(po)003:1170: hwa shang ma ko se hwa shang ma h+aa ya na /
NK133(po)003:1171: pan chen smri ti sogs dang /
NK133(po)003:1172: de bzhin du lo ts+aa ba yang thon mi sam b+ho ta /
NK133(po)003:1175: bran ka m+au la ko sha /
NK133(po)003:1177: khri gzhir sam sh+ai ta s+n+rang rgyal legs gzigs /
NK133(po)003:1180: ngan lam rgyal ba mchog byangs /
NK133(po)003:1182: pa gor bee ro tsa na /
NK133(po)003:1184: rba mang rje gsal snang sna nam rdo rje bdud 'joms /
NK133(po)003:1185: gnyags dz+ny+aa na ku m+aa ra /
NK133(po)003:1188: brang ti dza ya rak+shi ta /
NK133(po)003:1189: shud bu dpal gyi seng ge /
NK133(po)003:1194: la sum rgyal ba byang chub /
NK133(po)003:1195: rtsang bu rin chen legs grub /
NK133(po)003:1199: rma rnam par mi rtog pa /
NK133(po)003:1208: ska ba dpal brtsegs srung ba /
NK133(po)003:1223: yi ge pa dgon gling rma /
NK133(po)003:1224: gzhon nu srung ba nam mkha' skyong sogs nas pan+di ta smri ti dz+ny+aa na dang /
NK133(po)003:1225: lo ts+aa ba rong zom chos kyi bzang po'i bar
NK133(po)003:1226: du byon pa rnams kyis bsgyur ro cog cog bshad
NK133(po)003:1227: pa rnams snga 'gyur rnying ma zhes grags te 'di
NK133(po)003:1228: nas grub pa'i rig 'dzin chen po rnams ni /
NK133(po)003:1230: gnyan grogs dang srid sde'i kha la mi nyan /
NK133(po)003:1233: chos la blo thag bcad de /
NK133(po)003:1234: gangs brag g.ya' ri sogs su ri yi bu byas /
NK133(po)003:1236: rtsa ba dang myu gu sngo dang ldum bu sogs
NK133(po)003:1237: mi zhim pa'i zas gsol nas snying po'i sgrub pa
NK133(po)003:1238: la rtse gcig tu gzhol bas /
NK133(po)003:1239: bden gnyis byang chub kyi sems 'byangs /
NK133(po)003:1240: bskyed rdzogs kyi drod rtags thon /
NK133(po)003:1241: yi dam gyi lha rab 'byams zhal gzigs shing rjes su bzungs /
NK133(po)003:1242: snang srid 'dod rgur bsgyur ba'i rdzu 'phrul la dbang thob /
NK133(po)003:1244: rig 'dzin bzhi dang rnal 'byor chen po lnga 'od
NK133(po)003:1245: gsal snang ba rnam bzhi rnams kyi grub mtha' sa
NK133(po)003:1246: lam spangs rtogs yon tan sgra ji bzhin pa brnyes
NK133(po)003:1247: / skal ldan gyi slob ma 'ga' dang 'ga' zhig
NK133(po)003:1248: rjes su bzung ba tsam las mgo nag mi dang
NK133(po)003:1249: mi 'phrad 'tsho ba dpa' bo mkha' 'gros phul te
NK133(po)003:1250: / / sku tshe lo brgya phrag du ma sogs
NK133(po)003:1251: ring por bzhugs te mthar tshogs kyi spyod pa la
NK133(po)003:1252: brten te 'khor tshom bu bcas sangs rgyas kyi sar
NK133(po)003:1253: / / gshegs pa dang / snang bzhi'i lam nas
NK133(po)003:1254: sku lus 'od phung du yal te tshe gcig gis
NK133(po)003:1255: mngon par rdzogs pa sangs rgyas kyi sa brnyes pa
NK133(po)003:1256: grangs med pa byung ba yin no //
NK133(po)003:1257: rgyal po dar mas lcags bya la bstan par tho brtsams pa na /
NK133(po)003:1258: 'dul 'dzin mkhas pa dmar sh+aakya mu ne /
NK133(po)003:1260: gtsang pa rab gsal rnams khams phyogs byon nas rang
NK133(po)003:1261: gis sgrub pa mdzad pa dang 'chad nyan gyis rgyun
NK133(po)003:1262: bskyangs / dbus gtsang du rab byung gi sdom pa 'bog pa dang 'chad nyan sogs med kyang /
NK133(po)003:1263: khyim pa'i sngags 'chang sbas tshul can rnams kyis sgrub pa snying por byas shing /
NK133(po)003:1264: mdo sngags gsung rab 'gyur ro cog gi glegs bam thams cad sbas te phyag tu bzung /
NK133(po)003:1265: lha sa bsam yas sogs gtsug lag khang rnams ma nyams par bskyangs /
NK133(po)003:1266: 'di skor rgya gar nas pan+di ta sham thabs sngon po dang /
NK133(po)003:1267: a tsar dmar po sogs byon nas chags lam cher spel ba dang /
NK133(po)003:1268: slob dpon gyis ma zin pa'i sngags rlom dag gis
NK133(po)003:1269: kyang dpe tsam la bltas nas sbyor sgrol 'chol bar
NK133(po)003:1271: lha sras 'od srung mnga' ris su byon /
NK133(po)003:1272: yum brten dbus su bzhugs te /
NK133(po)003:1273: bod kyi chab srid phyogs gnyis su gyes pa'i skabs
NK133(po)003:1274: klu mes tshul khrims shes rab sogs dbus gtsang mi
NK133(po)003:1276: dmar g.yor gtsang gsum dang dge ba rab gsal sogs las 'dul ba'i sdom rgyun dang /
NK133(po)003:1277: 'dul mngon sher phyin byang sa sogs kyi bshad rgyun gsan /
NK133(po)003:1278: kun byed rgyal po sogs rdzogs chen sems phyogs rnams kyang mkhyen par mdzad de slar dbus su byon /
NK133(po)003:1279: btsan pos kyang sna len byas te 'dir lcags bya
NK133(po)003:1280: nas lo don gsum chu bya la bstan pa byung
NK133(po)003:1281: gsungs pa dang / don brgyad sa stag la gsungs
NK133(po)003:1282: pa sogs lo rgyus 'dra min 'ga' re byung yang
NK133(po)003:1283: don du dbus gtsang mi bcus bsam yas dbu rtse
NK133(po)003:1284: gsungs pa dang / gsos / dad pa can nyin
NK133(po)003:1285: re bzhin rab tu byung ba'i dge 'dun gyi sde
NK133(po)003:1286: gsungs pa dang / gsos / mang po 'phel / la mo chags de'u /
NK133(po)003:1288: tshongs 'dus gnas gzhi sogs gtsug lag mtha' yas pa brtsigs /
NK133(po)003:1289: sngags 'chang jo sras rnams kyis bka' bstan gyi glegs
NK133(po)003:1290: bam sbas te bzung ba rnams de dag tu phul
NK133(po)003:1292: slob ma ka bzhi gdung brgyad /
NK133(po)003:1294: dral ma grangs las brgal ba sogs byung ba yin no //
NK133(po)003:1295: mnga' ris rgyal po khu dbon sogs kyis sngon du
NK133(po)003:1296: lo chen rin bzang sogs rgya gar du chos nyan
NK133(po)003:1297: btang / rjes su gu ru pad+ma'i rnam 'phrul jo bo di pam ka ra spyan drangs /
NK133(po)003:1298: slob ma khu rngog 'brom sogs las bka' gdams gsar
NK133(po)003:1299: rnying gi bstan pa dar rgyas su byung ba dang
NK133(po)003:1300: / 'brog mi sh+aakya ye shes kyi pan+di ta ga
NK133(po)003:1301: ya d+ha ra sogs brten nas slob ma sa skya
NK133(po)003:1302: pa sogs la gsung ngag rin po che lam 'bras
NK133(po)003:1303: bu dang bcas pa stsal ba rgya bod hor gsum
NK133(po)003:1304: / du cher dar / lho brag mar pa lo
NK133(po)003:1305: ts+aas dpal na ro pa sogs bka' bzhi brgyud pa'i
NK133(po)003:1306: gdams ngag gsan nas slob ma ka chen bzhi sogs
NK133(po)003:1307: las bka' brgyud che bzhi chung brgyad sogs grub thob
NK133(po)003:1308: / du cher dar / kyi tshang brdol / khyung
NK133(po)003:1309: po rnal 'byor pas ni gum sogs grub thob pho
NK133(po)003:1310: mo lnga bcu'i gdams ngag blang ste shang pa'i slob
NK133(po)003:1311: ma khri phrag bco brgyad sogs phrin las rgyas /
NK133(po)003:1312: slob dpon ka ma sh+ai la'i mtshan gyi bye brag dam pa sangs rgyas kyis zhi byed dang /
NK133(po)003:1313: grub thob o rgyan pas rdo rje'i bsnyen bsgrub dang /
NK133(po)003:1314: ra 'bro tsa mi sogs las dus 'khor sbyor drug
NK133(po)003:1315: sogs gsar 'gyur gyi mkhas grub dpag tu med pa
NK133(po)003:1316: byon nas bod 'dir rgyal bstan dar rgyas su byung
NK133(po)003:1317: ba mdo tsam smros pa ste zhib par deb sngon
NK133(po)003:1318: sogs chos 'byung rnams las rtogs par bya ste dag
NK133(po)003:1319: snang phyogs med du 'byung ba'i rgyur 'gyur bas zhar
NK133(po)003:1320: la smros pa'o // dkon mchog t+aa la'i mdo las /
NK133(po)003:1321: phyogs rnams gang na chos ni med gyur na //
NK133(po)003:1322: phyogs der chos kyi gter ni ston par byed //
NK133(po)003:1324: da ltar gyi sangs rgyas mngon sum du bzhugs pa'i ting 'dzin gyi mdo las /
NK133(po)003:1325: byang chub sems dpa' dad pa phun sum tshogs pa
NK133(po)003:1326: la la ni sangs rgyas mi bzhugs kyang nam mkha'i
NK133(po)003:1327: dkyil dang rtsig pa dang shing las kyang chos 'byung
NK133(po)003:1328: ngo // zhes gsungs ba ltar rnying ma'i gter rnams
NK133(po)003:1329: kyang rim gyis byon nas bla rdzogs thugs gsum sgrub
NK133(po)003:1330: sde brgyad spyi dang bye brag gi bka' srol mtha'
NK133(po)003:1331: yas pa byung ba yin no //
NK133(po)003:1332: de ltar snga 'gyur lo pan rnams kyis rgyal bstan
NK133(po)003:1333: gangs can du drangs pa'i mdo 'dul sher phyin sngags
NK133(po)003:1334: bya spyod sogs ni gangs can pa'i grub mtha' thams
NK133(po)003:1335: cad kyi gzhi rtsa ba lus kyi zung srog rtsa
NK133(po)003:1337: sngags nang rgyud rnams kyang sa skya'i yab chos yang
NK133(po)003:1338: phur sogs las grub brnyes rgyun ma chad pa dang
NK133(po)003:1339: / bka' brgyud phyogs rnams bka' rnying zung 'brel 'ba' zhig dang /
NK133(po)003:1340: rje tsong kha pas thugs dam rtsa ba lho brag
NK133(po)003:1341: snyan brgyud sogs rnying rgyud mang po gsan pa dang
NK133(po)003:1342: / gong sa rgyal ba'i dbang po na rim dang
NK133(po)003:1343: pan chen sku phreng sogs dge phyogs bstan 'dzin gtso
NK133(po)003:1344: bo phal mo ches kyang bstan pa'i snying po'i zab
NK133(po)003:1345: gnad gzigs nas thugs dam mdzad pa dang /
NK133(po)003:1346: 'gal rkyen bsal nas bstan pa 'phel rgyas kyi rgyur snying la 'chang bar mdzad pa yin no //
NK133(po)003:1347: lugs de la mdo phyogs sde snod gsum dang sngags la'ang zhal nas gsungs pa'i bka' ma /
NK133(po)003:1348: rjes su gnang ba'i gter ma /
NK133(po)003:1349: byin gyis brlabs pa'i dag snang zhes brgyud pa'i srol ka chen po gsum du yod pa las /
NK133(po)003:1350: dang po'i phyogs la'ang rgyud sde dang sgrub sde bsam
NK133(po)003:1351: gyis mi khyab pa zhig mchis pa'i nang nas gtso
NK133(po)003:1352: bor gyur pa ni mdo sgyu sems gsum yin zhing
NK133(po)003:1353: / de dag gi brgyud pa'i babs lugs kyang sgyu 'phrul sogs ma h+aa yo ga'i skor rnams ni /
NK133(po)003:1356: sangs rgyas gsang ba sogs nas /
NK133(po)003:1357: gnyags dz+ny+aa na ku ma ra dang /
NK133(po)003:1358: sog po dpal gyi ye shes sogs las brgyud nas gnubs chen sangs rgyas ye shes la babs so //
NK133(po)003:1359: rdzogs pa chen po a ti yo ga sems phyogs kyi skor rnams kyang /
NK133(po)003:1360: slob dpon sh+r+ai seng+ha las lo ts+aa ba bee ro
NK133(po)003:1361: tsa nas gsan te chos rgyal khri srong lde'u btsan
NK133(po)003:1362: dang / rgyal mo g.yu sgra snying po /
NK133(po)003:1363: spang mi pham mgon po gsum la bshad /
NK133(po)003:1364: bee ro dang g.yu sgra gnyis las gnyags kyis gsan nas rim par gnubs la babs so //
NK133(po)003:1365: mdo dgongs pa 'dus pa sogs a nu yo ga'i skor rnams ni /
NK133(po)003:1366: bal po'i slob dpon ba su d+h+aa ra dang gru
NK133(po)003:1367: sha'i slob dpon che btsan skyes sogs las gnubs chen
NK133(po)003:1369: de ltar na bskyed rdzogs rdzogs chen gsum gyi bka'i
NK133(po)003:1370: chu bo gnubs chen sangs rgyas ye shes rin po
NK133(po)003:1372: gnubs chen 'di sa gsum pa 'od byed brnyes sku
NK133(po)003:1373: tshe khri srong dus nas dpal 'khor btsan gyi bar
NK133(po)003:1374: bzhugs pa'o // de la so ye shes dbang phyug /
NK133(po)003:1377: sru legs pa'i sgron ma ste thugs kyi sras bzhi /
NK133(po)003:1378: thugs sras kyi dam pa khu lung pa yon tan rgya mtsho dang lnga sogs yod pa las /
NK133(po)003:1380: so ye shes dbang phyug gnyis ka'i slob ma nyang shes rab mchog /
NK133(po)003:1381: de'i slob ma nyang ye shes 'byung gnas /
NK133(po)003:1382: de'i slob ma zur po che ste 'di ni gnubs
NK133(po)003:1383: chen dngos slob stod tshab 'phags pa rin po che
NK133(po)003:1384: la'ang thug / bde gshegs zur po che sh+aakya 'byung
NK133(po)003:1385: gnas ni 'od gsal lha rigs zur gyi gdung las
NK133(po)003:1386: mdo khams g.yer mor 'khrungs bla chen dgongs pa rab
NK133(po)003:1388: zur rin rgyal las sde snod gsum dang sngags phyi nang kun mkhyen par mdzad /
NK133(po)003:1389: dbus su byon nas yar lung na kri ya'i sgrub pa mdzad pas sngags kyi rig sad /
NK133(po)003:1390: nyang ye shes 'byung gnas lce sh+aakya mchog sogs grub
NK133(po)003:1391: brnyes bla ma mang po las sgyu 'phrul dang sems
NK133(po)003:1392: phyogs sogs rgyud lung man ngag thams cad gsan /
NK133(po)003:1393: sgrub pas bskyed rdzogs gdengs thob /
NK133(po)003:1394: shes rab phyogs med du rgyas /
NK133(po)003:1395: mkhas dang grub pa'i rnam thar nam mkha' dang mnyam /
NK133(po)003:1396: gtsang 'ug pa lung du bshad sgrub kyi chos sde btab /
NK133(po)003:1397: slob ma rtse mo bzhi ni /
NK133(po)003:1398: lta sgom gyi rtse mo zur chung ba /
NK133(po)003:1399: sgyu 'phrul bshad pa'i rtse mo me nyag khyung grags /
NK133(po)003:1400: mkhyen rgya'i rtse mo zhang 'gos chung /
NK133(po)003:1401: sgom sgrub kyi rtse mo bzang sgom shes rab rgyal po dang /
NK133(po)003:1402: rtse lkog tsag tsha bla ma dang lnga /
NK133(po)003:1403: sgom chen brgya rtsa brgyad sogs grub thob dpag tu med pa byon /
NK133(po)003:1404: yi dam lha thams cad zhal gzigs mkha' 'gro dam can gzhi bdag thams cad bran du khol /
NK133(po)003:1405: shang mad'i lha khang rten dang brten par bcas pa rdzu 'phrul gyis bzhengs /
NK133(po)003:1406: gzhi bdag gis gser phul ba /
NK133(po)003:1407: chu mig mar khur bsgyur ba /
NK133(po)003:1408: bsad gso sogs rdzu 'phrul gyi bkod pa zad mi shes pa bstan /
NK133(po)003:1409: mthar nga ni 'di nas bde ba can du 'gro
NK133(po)003:1410: sogs gsungs nas sku 'od phung du gyur te dpal
NK133(po)003:1411: chen po'i thugs dang gnyis su med par thim /
NK133(po)003:1412: slob ma lta sgom gyi rtse mo zur chung pa shes rab grags pa ni /
NK133(po)003:1413: zur a tsa ra'i sras te bla mas rus gcig gsungs rjes su bzung /
NK133(po)003:1414: dbang dang gdams ngag rdzogs par mdzad /
NK133(po)003:1415: thos bsam sgom gsum la brtson pas shes rab klong brdol /
NK133(po)003:1416: rtogs pa bsam gyis mi khyab /
NK133(po)003:1417: brag rgya bo sogs gang du bzhugs kyang mi ma yin gyis gsol 'dren pa /
NK133(po)003:1418: sa rdo ri brag la thogs pa med pa nyi zer la gshegs bzhugs kyis /
NK133(po)003:1419: 'ug pa lung du snga chos sgro phug tu gung chos brag rgya bor dgong chos te /
NK133(po)003:1420: nyin bzhin gdan sa gsum kar chos thun gsung pa
NK133(po)003:1421: sogs bshad sgrub las gsum gyi phrin las nam mkha'
NK133(po)003:1422: dang mnyam / slob ma ka ba bzhi ni /
NK133(po)003:1423: sems phyogs kyi ka ba skyo ston sh+aakya ye shes /
NK133(po)003:1424: mdo'i ka ba stod lung yang khyed bla ma /
NK133(po)003:1425: sgyu 'phrul ka ba glan sh+aakya bzang po /
NK133(po)003:1426: phrin sgrub kyi ka ba mda' tig jo sh+aag bcas bzhi dang /
NK133(po)003:1427: gdung ma brgyad phyam bcu drug dral ma sum cu rtsa gnyis sogs bsam gyis mi khyab pa las /
NK133(po)003:1428: khyad par sku'i sras sgro phug pa sh+aakya seng ge
NK133(po)003:1429: ni shing pho stag la 'khrungs gsan bsam rdzogs par
NK133(po)003:1430: mdzad / bsgrubs pas bskyed rdzogs kyi gnas la rgyud nas gsungs pa'i gzer bzhi thebs /
NK133(po)003:1432: phyag rdor gyi skur ston pa dang /
NK133(po)003:1433: slob ma'i dbus su zhal phyogs thams cad du thal
NK133(po)003:1434: le snang ba sogs dkyil 'khor bdag po rtsod med
NK133(po)003:1435: du grags / slob ma dge ba'i bshes gnyen gra
NK133(po)003:1436: sa 'dzin cing bstan pa skyong nus pa'i gdugs thog
NK133(po)003:1437: stong phrag brgal bas mtshon slob ma khri phrag thal
NK133(po)003:1438: du grags / ba byung / dpal gsang ba'i snying
NK133(po)003:1439: po sogs bshad sgrub gnyis kyi gsang chen snga 'gyur
NK133(po)003:1440: ba'i bstan pa gangs can mtha' dbus kun tu rgyas
NK133(po)003:1441: du grags / ba byung / par mdzad / sgro phug pa'i slob ma'i gtso bo nag bzhi /
NK133(po)003:1447: bla chen lha khang pa yon tan gzungs /
NK133(po)003:1448: de'i slob ma zhig po bdud rtsi /
NK133(po)003:1451: 'dzam ston 'gro ba'i mgon po sogs mkhas dang grub pa'i rnam thar bsam gyis mi khyab /
NK133(po)003:1452: sgro phug pa'i slob ma sangs rgyas grags de'i slob
NK133(po)003:1453: ma skyid chos seng ging yar lung rdo thog thel
NK133(po)003:1454: bar dar rgyas cher byung ba dang /
NK133(po)003:1455: de'i slob ma sman lung sh+aakya 'od kyi phrin las rgyas shing /
NK133(po)003:1456: de'i slob ma dag po bla ma gnyan gon 'jo
NK133(po)003:1457: ba dag po'i bla mar gyur te khams phyogs su
NK133(po)003:1458: rgyas pa dang / zla med pa'i mkhas grub chen
NK133(po)003:1459: po rang zom chos kyi bzang pos 'chad rtsod rtsom
NK133(po)003:1460: pa'i phrin las rgya chen po mdzad pa dang /
NK133(po)003:1461: 'dzam ston slob ma kahthoga dam pa bde gshegs las
NK133(po)003:1462: cher rgyas pa sogs zur pa mes dbon gsum dang
NK133(po)003:1463: / khyad par sgro phug pa'i slob rgyud kyis dbus
NK133(po)003:1464: gtsang lho mon khams a mdo me nyag sog yul
NK133(po)003:1465: sogs phyogs kun tu gsang chen snga 'gyur ba'i chos
NK133(po)003:1466: sde bshad sgrub kyi phrin las rgyas par byung yang
NK133(po)003:1467: thog snga bas dus dbang gis bstan pa 'phel 'grib
NK133(po)003:1468: ci ring byung bas deng song phal cher dbyings su
NK133(po)003:1469: zhi la sngags 'chang rnams kyi gdung rgyud las sa
NK133(po)003:1470: skya pa rngog lo khu dbon khro lo sogs gsar
NK133(po)003:1471: ma'i mkhas grub mang po byon pa'ang thugs bskyed smon
NK133(po)003:1472: lam mthu las byung bar mngon /
NK133(po)003:1473: de dag gi tshul zhib par yi ge ltos che
NK133(po)003:1474: bar zhad nas ma smos pas rang rang gi rnam
NK133(po)003:1475: thar dang chos 'byung rgyud 'bum dkar chag snga phyi
NK133(po)003:1477: bar skabs su kun mkhyen chos kyi rgyal po klong
NK133(po)003:1478: chen rab 'byams ni gdod ma'i mgon po kun tu
NK133(po)003:1479: bzang po dang rje btsun 'jam pa'i dbyangs mi yi
NK133(po)003:1481: seng ge dpral bar nyi dkyil gsal ba'i rnam pas
NK133(po)003:1482: lhums su zhugs te rab byung lnga pa'i sa sprel
NK133(po)003:1483: zla tshes la sku ltam ma thag nas nam gru
NK133(po)003:1484: re ma t+ais gzugs dngos su bstan nas bsrung ba
NK133(po)003:1485: dang / gsung bye tshe dad pa dang snying rje
NK133(po)003:1486: blo gros kyi mthu rnams skye bas thob pa'i rtags
NK133(po)003:1487: dang / shin tu gsal / lo lnga nas bris
NK133(po)003:1488: klog brda' bstan pa tsam gyis tshegs med par mkhyen
NK133(po)003:1489: dang / shin tu gsal / / bdun pa nas bzung yab las bka' brgyad bder gshegs 'dus pa /
NK133(po)003:1492: gu ru zhi drag rnams kyi dbang lung man ngag
NK133(po)003:1493: phyag bzhes dang bcas pa dang sman rtsis la sogs
NK133(po)003:1494: pa'ang gsan cing kun chub par mdzad /
NK133(po)003:1495: dgu pa la gra phyi'i tshong 'dus su nyi khri
