NK133(po)003:1496: dang brgyad stong pa brgya tshar sgrogs pas tshig don
NK133(po)003:1497: thugs su chud / bcu gnyis pa la bsam yas su mkhan po bsam 'grub rin chen dang /
NK133(po)003:1498: slob dpon kun dga' 'od zer las rab tu byung /
NK133(po)003:1499: mtshan tshul khrims blo gros su gsol /
NK133(po)003:1500: 'dul ba sbyangs pa bcu bzhi nas bshad pas mkhas pa'i grags pa thob /
NK133(po)003:1501: bcu dgu nas gsang phur byin byams chos dbu tshad sogs gzhung lugs rab 'byams dpyis phyin par mdzad /
NK133(po)003:1502: dpang lo blo brtan las mngon pa gong 'og sgra
NK133(po)003:1503: rtsis bzo gso snyan ngag sogs rig gnas rnams gsan
NK133(po)003:1504: / slob dpon gzhon nu rdo rje /
NK133(po)003:1505: karma pa rang byung rdo rje /
NK133(po)003:1506: sa skya pa bsod nams rgyal mtshan sogs las bka' gdams /
NK133(po)003:1515: rdo rje phreng ba sogs dang /
NK133(po)003:1516: dan 'bag pa gzhon nu don 'grub las mdo sgyu
NK133(po)003:1517: sems gsum sogs te mdor na gangs can na mdo
NK133(po)003:1518: sngags rig gnas bcas rgyun mchis so 'tshal gsan sbyong
NK133(po)003:1519: dang nyams bzhes mthar phyin par mdzad /
NK133(po)003:1520: gsang bde gung gsum sogs rigs gra rnams su gra
NK133(po)003:1521: skor mdzad pas mkhas pa'i grags pas sa tshon khyab
NK133(po)003:1522: par gyur / 'jam dbyangs mi g.yo ba sogs sgrub pas zhal gzigs shing lung bstan /
NK133(po)003:1523: dbyangs can mas phyag mthil du bzhag nas gling bzhi ri rab bcas zhag bdun du gzigs /
NK133(po)003:1524: blo gros phyogs med du rgyas shing spobs pa'i gter
NK133(po)003:1525: kha grol khyad par yi dam lhas lung bstan pa
NK133(po)003:1526: bzhin rig 'dzin chen po gzhon nu rgyal po'i spyan
NK133(po)003:1527: sngar byon te snying thig chen mo'i dbang dang rgyud
NK133(po)003:1529: bya bral kun spang kho na'i tshul gyis dben ri
NK133(po)003:1530: rnams su sgrub pa nyams bzhes snying por mdzad pas
NK133(po)003:1531: rig pa tshad phebs chen po'i sa la gshegs shing
NK133(po)003:1532: longs sku'i zhing khams nyul bar mdzad /
NK133(po)003:1533: bi ma'i lung bstan bzhin dbu ru zhwa'i lha khang
NK133(po)003:1534: nyams gsos mdzad tshe rtags dang cho 'phrul dpag tu
NK133(po)003:1535: med pa bstan / dus kun rtsa gsum lha tshogs sangs rgyas byang sems til gong bzhin gzigs /
NK133(po)003:1536: khyad par rje btsun byams pas khyod kyi skye ba'i mthar pad+ma brtsegs pa'i zhing du /
NK133(po)003:1537: de bzhin gshegs pa ri rab mar me'i rgyal mtshan du sangs rgyas par lung bstan /
NK133(po)003:1538: gangs can gyi bstan 'dzin rnams dang sa skyong rnams gtsos slob tshogs dpag tu med pa 'dus /
NK133(po)003:1539: rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi dgongs don 'khrul
NK133(po)003:1540: pa med pa snga 'gyur lo pan rnams kyis legs
NK133(po)003:1541: par bkral ba tshul bzhin gtan la phabs pa'i legs
NK133(po)003:1542: bshad bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang khyad par snying
NK133(po)003:1543: thig bka' gter gyi bka' bsdu mdzad de /
NK133(po)003:1544: yang tiig gsum dang rgyab chos mdzod chen bdun dang
NK133(po)003:1545: ngal bso gsum sogs rtsal te sde snod spyi dang
NK133(po)003:1547: khyad par man ngag sde'i chos kyi 'khor lo seng
NK133(po)003:1548: ge'i sgra chen po bsgrags pas kun bzang thugs kyi
NK133(po)003:1549: bstan pa mi nub pa'i rgyal mtshan gyi srog shing
NK133(po)003:1550: brtan par tshug par mdzad pa sogs rgyal ba rdzogs
NK133(po)003:1551: pa'i sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa nges pa'i don la
NK133(po)003:1552: phyag rjes gangs ri'i khrod na 'gran zla kun bral
NK133(po)003:1553: du mdzad pa shes dgos la /
NK133(po)003:1554: gter ston chen po rat+na gling pas kyang rnying bstan
NK133(po)003:1555: la bya ba chen po mdzad pa ste 'di nyid
NK133(po)003:1556: rab byung bdun pa'i chu lug la lho brag gru
NK133(po)003:1558: gzhon dus nas nges 'byung snying rje shes rab tshad med pa mnga'/
NK133(po)003:1559: ye shes dpal bzang rgyal sras zla ba grags pa /
NK133(po)003:1560: karma pa sogs mkhas grub mang po brten nas mdo
NK133(po)003:1561: sngags gsar rnying bka' gter gyi chos mang po dang
NK133(po)003:1562: / khyad par byams dgon bsam gtan bzang po las snga 'gyur rgyud sde thams cad gsan /
NK133(po)003:1563: bskyed rdzogs nyams bzhes kyis dbang bzhi'i ye shes mthar phyin brnyes /
NK133(po)003:1564: o rgyan rin po che'i dngos zhal nyer lnga mjal /
NK133(po)003:1565: bi ma las rjes su bzung zhing gdams ngag stsal
NK133(po)003:1566: ba sogs rtsa gsum lha tshogs dpag tu med pa
NK133(po)003:1568: thugs gter nyer lnga bton cing grub 'bras thob par
NK133(po)003:1569: mdzad pa la nyer 'tshe phra mo tsam yang ma
NK133(po)003:1570: byung / dbus gtsang khams gsum gyi slob tshogs dpag
NK133(po)003:1571: tu med pa la sems klong man ngag sde gsum
NK133(po)003:1572: gtso bor gyur pa'i ris med bka' gter gyi chos
NK133(po)003:1574: rnying rgyud rnams dkar chag ldan dkar mar gsang sngags
NK133(po)003:1575: nang rgyud rnams bka' gnyen pas 'dir ma bkod ces
NK133(po)003:1576: / bka' 'gyur ldebs su ma bzhugs pas dpe lung gnyis ka'i rgyun dkon pas /
NK133(po)003:1577: 'di yab sras kyis zur 'ug bya lung du rgyud
NK133(po)003:1578: rag rim bzhugs pas mtshon phyogs mtha' dag nas dpe
NK133(po)003:1579: lung gi rgyun thugs rtsol chen pos btsal /
NK133(po)003:1580: rgyud 'bum dkyus gcig tu bsgrigs te sngon du snag
NK133(po)003:1581: bris dang rjes su gser chos bzhengs shing 'chad spel
NK133(po)003:1582: mang po mdzad pas rnying bstan la phan pa rgya
NK133(po)003:1583: che / sa gnad mkho mthing lha khang rnying gso dang gsar bzhengs mang po dang /
NK133(po)003:1584: jo bor gser rkang 'bul ba sogs rten bzhengs mchod 'bul rgya chen po mdzad /
NK133(po)003:1585: de rjes gangs ra lo chen gyis rnying rgyud tshar
NK133(po)003:1586: gsum bzhengs nas khams dbus gtsang gsum du bskur ba
NK133(po)003:1587: sogs bstan pa la bka' drin che /
NK133(po)003:1588: gzhan yang mnga' ris pan chen rin po che sogs
NK133(po)003:1589: kyis bstan pa'i srog mthud de dam pa de dag
NK133(po)003:1590: gi bka' drin gyis deng sang snga 'gyur ba'i rgyud
NK133(po)003:1591: lung man ngag la cung zad longs spyod du yod
NK133(po)003:1592: pa 'di nyid byung ba yin no //
NK133(po)003:1593: snga 'gyur bka' ma theg rim dgu'i phrin chog gzhung
NK133(po)003:1594: phyi mo rnams dang bcas pa'i dkar chag bstan pa
NK133(po)003:1595: rgya mtsho'i gru gzings bkra shis dpal brgya'i 'byung gnas
NK133(po)003:1596: las bstan pa rin po che'i babs tshul mdo tsam
NK133(po)003:1597: brjod pa'i skabs te dang po'o ////
NK133(po)003:1598: de nas rnam thar zhal skor tshul du deng sang
NK133(po)003:1599: gi rnying ma'i gdan sa rnams kyi lo rgyus cung
NK133(po)003:1601: phyis kyi dus 'dir rnying ma'i bstan pa gtsang na gsang sngags gling dang /
NK133(po)003:1602: 'ug pa lung sogs zur pa'i gdung rgyud dang rnying chos 'dzin pa'i sngags grong ni shin tu mang /
NK133(po)003:1608: zhe chen rnams bstan pa'i rtsa ba rming rdo lta
NK133(po)003:1609: bur 'dug pa de dag gi byung tshul rnam thar
NK133(po)003:1611: o rgyan smin grol gling pa ni /
NK133(po)003:1612: gdan sa rnying pa dar rgyas chos gling ni thog
NK133(po)003:1613: mar gter chen rat+na gling pa'i sku skye de ma
NK133(po)003:1614: thag pa sprul sku sna tshogs rang grol gyis btab
NK133(po)003:1615: pa de nas rim bzhin pad gling sprul pa bstan
NK133(po)003:1616: 'dzin grags pa / sna tshogs rang grol yang srid
NK133(po)003:1617: 'od gsal lha'i gdung rgyud myos rigs mkhas grub mdo
NK133(po)003:1618: 'dzin grags pa / sngags bstan 'dzin / de'i sras
NK133(po)003:1619: phrin las lhun grub sogs myos rigs rdo rje 'dzin
NK133(po)003:1620: pa rnams kyis bskyangs pa ste /
NK133(po)003:1621: phrin las lhun grub sras rig 'dzin gter bdag gling
NK133(po)003:1622: pa 'gyur med rdo rje ni rab byung bcu gnyis
NK133(po)003:1624: rje lnga pa chen por gtsug phud phul bas mtshan ngag dbang pad+ma bstan 'dzin gsol /
NK133(po)003:1627: rgyal mchog lnga pa chen po sogs mkhas grub kyi
NK133(po)003:1628: yongs 'dzin lnga bcu las sde snod gsum dang rgyud
NK133(po)003:1629: sde yongs grags ji snyed dang /
NK133(po)003:1634: gshed skor sogs snga 'gyur bka' ma deng sang rgyun yod do cog dang /
NK133(po)003:1635: gter ma bla rdzogs thugs gsum /
NK133(po)003:1636: sgrub sde spyi bye brag dgos bka' yongs grags ji snyed dang /
NK133(po)003:1640: phyag chen na ro chos drug /
NK133(po)003:1641: shang chos sogs sngags gsar rnying gi smin grol rgyun bzhugs phal mo che dang /
NK133(po)003:1642: de dag gi rtsa ba bka' 'gyur ro cog gi lung sogs mtha' yas pa gsan /
NK133(po)003:1646: zab mo nang don rnams thugs la bzung zhing /
NK133(po)003:1647: khyad par kun mkhyen chos rje'i gsung rab las blo
NK133(po)003:1648: gros kyi mthu thogs pa med pa brnyes te ji
NK133(po)003:1649: snyed pa'i chos la sgro 'dog chod /
NK133(po)003:1650: dben gnas du mar sgrub pa snying por mdzad pas
NK133(po)003:1651: bskyed rdzogs rdzogs chen rnams kyi lam rtags sgra ji
NK133(po)003:1652: bzhin brnyes / bla ma brgyud pa yi dam dkyil
NK133(po)003:1653: 'khor lha tshogs bsam gyis mi khyab pa zhal gzigs
NK133(po)003:1655: khyad par zab mo gter gyi bka' babs /
NK133(po)003:1656: bde ba can dang pad+ma 'od sogs zhing yongs su sbyong ba'i ting 'dzin 'byangs /
NK133(po)003:1657: dbang bzhi'i nyams myong gtan la phebs pas sku gzugs
NK133(po)003:1658: kyi 'gro don rim bzhin zab pa dang rgya che
NK133(po)003:1660: bshad sgrub las gsum gyi phrin las mtha' klas pa
NK133(po)003:1661: las gtso bor bstan pa yun ring gnas phyir snga
NK133(po)003:1662: 'gyur bka' gter gyi sgrub dkyil dbang chog khrid yig
NK133(po)003:1663: gtso bor gyur pa'i rgyud gzhung gi dgongs don gnad
NK133(po)003:1664: du phig pa'i bka' rtsom ches mang bar mdzad /
NK133(po)003:1665: deng sang gangs can gyi grub mtha' gzhan rnams rang
NK133(po)003:1666: rang nas dar ba re snang yang rnying ma'i dgon
NK133(po)003:1667: rnying phal cher ni grong nag tu song nas ming
NK133(po)003:1668: ma stong tsam gyur pas bstan pa'i gzhi ma grwa
NK133(po)003:1669: gtsang re ma tshug na gang yang mi 'byung bar
NK133(po)003:1670: dgongs nas sdom pa gsum gyis rgyud sdom zhing bshad
NK133(po)003:1671: sgrub kyis bya bas dus 'da' ba'i grwa phyi o
NK133(po)003:1672: rgyan smin grol gling rten dang brten par bcas pa
NK133(po)003:1674: dus bzhi'i sgrub mchod spyi dang /
NK133(po)003:1675: khyad par sa zla'i snga 'gyur mdo sgyu gnyis phreng
NK133(po)003:1676: chad yod snyam la mkha' spyod dpa' bo mkha' 'gro
NK133(po)003:1677: grong du gshegs / gong sa lnga pas rnying ma'i
NK133(po)003:1678: dgon rnying nyams rgud du gyur pa 'ga' smin grol
NK133(po)003:1679: gling nas nyams gso 'dzin skyong mdzad phyir dgon lag
NK133(po)003:1680: nyer lnga tsam sbyor 'jag mdzad pa dang /
NK133(po)003:1681: chos rgyud kyis ni rnying ma phal mo che khyab pa'o //
NK133(po)003:1682: 'di nyid kyi gcung rgyal sras bstan pa'i nyi ma
NK133(po)003:1683: dang kun dga' tshul khrims rnams dam pa'i rnam thar
NK133(po)003:1684: can dang / khyad par lo ts+aa ba g.yu sgra
NK133(po)003:1685: snying po'i rnam 'phrul mkhan chen chos dpal rgya mtsho
NK133(po)003:1687: zhi 'tsho'i sdom rgyun las bsnyen par rdzogs /
NK133(po)003:1688: gter chen bla ma rdor brag pad phrin /
NK133(po)003:1691: mkhas grub chos skyong rnam rgyal /
NK133(po)003:1692: mkhas dbang sangs rgyas chos dang /
NK133(po)003:1693: sku zhang zlum po ba sogs yongs 'dzin bcu phrag las sgra ka tsan dbyangs gsum /
NK133(po)003:1694: sum rtags sdeb sbyor snyan ngag skar rtsis lha ris sogs thun mong rig gnas dang /
NK133(po)003:1695: dbu ma phar phyin 'dul ba mngon pa /
NK133(po)003:1696: dus 'khor sogs gsan cing bzung ba tsam gyis don thog med du thugs ma shar /
NK133(po)003:1699: rgyud sde dang sgrub sde'i dbang bka' bshad bka' lung man ngag ji snyed dang /
NK133(po)003:1700: gter chos phal mo che dang gsar rnying ris med kyi gdams ngag rgya mtsho lta bu gsan /
NK133(po)003:1701: khyad par gter chen las snying 'grel spar khab g.yung tika sbyar ba gsan pas don gyi gting sleb /
NK133(po)003:1702: de dag bsam byung gis gtan la phab cing sgom
NK133(po)003:1703: byung gis chos nyid yid dpyod la rag ma lus
NK133(po)003:1704: par zab mo'i don gyi ye shes mngon du gyur
NK133(po)003:1706: phar phyin 'dul ba sogs gzhung chen mang po'i bshad pa dang /
NK133(po)003:1707: khyad par gsang ba snying po lo bstar chags su gsung /
NK133(po)003:1708: sgyu 'phrul zhi khro'i dbang tshar brgyad /
NK133(po)003:1709: mdo dbang tshar gsum sogs gsar rnying bka' gter gyi smin grol tshar mang /
NK133(po)003:1710: sa skya kun bkra gter gsar yongs rdzogs /
NK133(po)003:1711: mdo khams chab mdor phebs te der sku ngo rnams
NK133(po)003:1712: dang mdo smad kyi bstan 'dzin phal mo che 'dus
NK133(po)003:1713: par gsar rnying ris med kyi chos 'khor bskor /
NK133(po)003:1714: chab mdor tshes bcu spros bcas tshugs /
NK133(po)003:1715: gsung rtsom legs bshad ngo mtshar bsam gyis mi khyab pa rnam thar du gsal ba rnams dang /
NK133(po)003:1716: der ma 'khod pa snyan ngag gi dpe brjod /
NK133(po)003:1717: 'byung rtsis zla ba'i 'od zer gshin rje dreg 'jom mchan 'grel /
NK133(po)003:1718: bde kun gyi rtsa khrid ri chos /
NK133(po)003:1719: gter chen 'das byung rnam thar bstod tshogs smon lam rim pa /
NK133(po)003:1722: dris len skor sogs mang du bzhugs /
NK133(po)003:1723: rje gter chen 'gyur med rdo rje'i sras pad ma
NK133(po)003:1724: 'gyur med rgya mtsho shes rab rnam rgyal rdo rje
NK133(po)003:1725: 'bum ni / khri lcam gu na ta rar shing glang zla 11tshes 9la 'khrungs /
NK133(po)003:1726: chos rje gzhan phan dbang po las 'dul mdzod dbu
NK133(po)003:1727: phar sogs rig lam nas drang pa'i bshad pa dang
NK133(po)003:1728: / bla ma sku mched kyi gsan pa bum pa gang 'byo'i steng /
NK133(po)003:1729: gang dkar chos sde'i slob dpon dbang phyugs pa las
NK133(po)003:1730: rdo rje phreng ba sogs gsar ma'i chos rgyun ji
NK133(po)003:1736: 'da' ka smon 'grel bde kun dbang bshad /
NK133(po)003:1738: sgyu 'phrul dbang chog sogs mang du mdzad pa yod /
NK133(po)003:1739: sras yid bzhin legs grub ni /
NK133(po)003:1740: phun rab lcam las rab nyi lcags lug la 'khrungs /
NK133(po)003:1741: sdom brtson mkhas pa chen po ste 'dus sde'i byang 'dren mdzad pa dang /
NK133(po)003:1742: stag bla sku mched la rnying rgyud klag lung spel ba sogs phyag rjes yod /
NK133(po)003:1743: rje btsun mi 'gyur dpal sgron ni yos la 'khrungs /
NK133(po)003:1745: sku btsun zhing mkhyen rab che /
NK133(po)003:1747: me bya dus 'gyur skabs 'bras ljongs phyogs phebs /
NK133(po)003:1748: rjes su gdan sar phebs nas rdzogs chen gtso bor gyur pa'i chos 'khor rgya che /
NK133(po)003:1750: sgom chen don 'grub sh+r+ai n+aa tha /
NK133(po)003:1751: khyung ras sogs slob tshogs mang du mchis so //
NK133(po)003:1752: bi ma'i rnam 'phrul rgyal sras rin chen rnam rgyal ni /
NK133(po)003:1754: rje khu dbon gsum las gsan bsam rdzogs par mdzad /
NK133(po)003:1755: me bya'i dus 'gyur skabs khams phyogs su cung phyag mdzod u pa n+aa tha'am nye mgon bcas phebs /
NK133(po)003:1756: khams phyogs su smin grol gyi 'gro don rgya chen po mdzad /
NK133(po)003:1757: rje bdun pa khrir 'khod nas slar gdan sar phebs nas bstan dgon nyams gsos /
NK133(po)003:1758: mdo sngags bshad sgrub smin grol rgyun sogs sngar rgyun
NK133(po)003:1759: bzhin sor chud par mdzad de dgung grangs re lnga
NK133(po)003:1760: bzhugs / de sras khri sngags 'chang pad ma bstan 'dzin ni /
NK133(po)003:1761: pad ma 'gyur med rgya mtsho'i yang srid de me sbrul la 'khrungs /
NK133(po)003:1762: gcung mkhan chen o rgyan bstan 'dzin rdo rje ni lo chen sprul pa ste chu khyi la 'khrungs /
NK133(po)003:1763: sku btsun 'dul mngon dbu tshad phar phyin sdom gsum
NK133(po)003:1764: gsang 'grel ste gzhung pod chen bdun thugs la btsud
NK133(po)003:1765: / rigs lam nas drangs pa'i bshad sbyang mthar phyin /
NK133(po)003:1766: mdo sngags smin grol 'chad spel rten gsum bzhengs pa /
NK133(po)003:1767: lha ldan du chu gnod mngon sum bzlog pa sogs bstan 'gro'i don rgya chen po mdzad /
NK133(po)003:1769: pad ma bstan 'dzin sras khri sngags 'chang phrin las
NK133(po)003:1770: rnam rgyal ni phrin las lhun grub rnam sprul te
NK133(po)003:1771: rab 'dod shing byal ba ltams dgung lo zhe brgyad
NK133(po)003:1772: bzhugs / gcung mkhan chen gsang sngags bstan 'dzin 'dul ba'i kun spyod gtsang /
NK133(po)003:1773: dam pa'i tshul dgu'i yon tan phyug pa ste /
NK133(po)003:1774: 'di khu dbon rnams kyi skabs dge 'dun khrims gtsang sum brgya lnga bcu skor yod /
NK133(po)003:1775: karma bi dza'i sras mo rje btsun phrin las chos sgron chu khyi la 'khrungs /
NK133(po)003:1776: mdo sngags rig gnas dang bcas par mkhas shing gsar rnying gi gsan rgya che /
NK133(po)003:1777: bsnyen sgrub dang 'chad spel gyi dus 'da'/
NK133(po)003:1778: khri chen pad ma dbang rgyal gter chen sprul pa ste me 'brug la 'khrungs /
NK133(po)003:1779: gsan sbyang la ma ltos pa'i mkhyen rab rgyas dgung grangs nyer brgyad bzhugs /
NK133(po)003:1780: de sras sangs rgyas kun dga' rab yid me glang la 'khrungs /
NK133(po)003:1781: skyes thob kyi grub rtags brnyes /
NK133(po)003:1782: rje btsun mchog dang lcang phug rnam grol dbang po /
NK133(po)003:1783: rdzogs chen gzhan phan mtha' yas /
NK133(po)003:1785: dpal ri pad dbang sogs las chos kyi bdud rtsi 'bul res mdzad /
NK133(po)003:1786: phyis rab tu byung mkhan khrir bzhugs /
NK133(po)003:1787: so dgu shing yos la gshegs /
NK133(po)003:1788: de'i sras gnubs chen sprul pa yid bzhin dbang rgyal lcags glang la 'khrungs /
NK133(po)003:1789: gshin rje gshed kyi grub rtags brnyes /
NK133(po)003:1790: gtsang pan chen bstan pa'i nyi mar rnying ma'i dbang chos mang po 'bul ba sogs phrin las rgyas /
NK133(po)003:1791: bshad sgrub las gsum gyis gdan sa bskyang nas dgung grangs bzhi bcu la gshegs /
NK133(po)003:1792: gcung kun dga' tshul khrims rdo rje 'am bden don mchog grub shing 'brug la ba ltams /
NK133(po)003:1793: kong po tsa khang gdan sar yang phebs gcen gshegs rjes gdan sa bskyangs /
NK133(po)003:1794: zhe gsum bzhugs pa rnams mkhas shing dngos grub brnyes
NK133(po)003:1795: pa rgyal bstan skyong ba'i phrin las zla bral can
NK133(po)003:1797: da lta'ang gdung tshab yab sras dang 'dus sde'i mkhan
NK133(po)003:1798: sku mched rnams kyi mkhyen brtse nus pas rang lugs
NK133(po)003:1799: gsang chen bstan pa'i gzi byin mi nyams gong 'phel
NK133(po)003:1800: du bzhugs pa'o // thub bstan rdo rje brag rig
NK133(po)003:1801: 'dzin 'dus pa'i sde'i gzhi ni mnga' ris pan chen
NK133(po)003:1802: rin po che sku mched kyis e wam lcog sgar
NK133(po)003:1803: zhes pa'i grwa gtsang zhig 'dzug par mdzad pa rig
NK133(po)003:1804: 'dzin rgod ldem gnyis pa rig 'dzin legs ldan rje
NK133(po)003:1805: dang pan chen yang srid byang bdag bkra shis stobs
NK133(po)003:1806: rgyal gyis bskyangs te gsang sngags theg mchog gling sdom
NK133(po)003:1807: pa sum ldan gyi dge 'dun rnam par dag pas
NK133(po)003:1808: snga 'gyur bshad sgrub kyi bstan pa gong 'phel skabs
NK133(po)003:1809: du bzhugs pa'o // / dus 'gyur dang mdo khams
NK133(po)003:1810: phyogs 'gro don dus babs kyis byang bdag lan gnyis
NK133(po)003:1811: phebs pa'i snga mar khams sbu bor sde pa ka
NK133(po)003:1812: gnam pa'i chos mdzad ma zhig gis ban chas phul
NK133(po)003:1813: du bzhugs pa'o // / bas / zhabs phyir 'brengs
NK133(po)003:1814: pa'i drung 'khor 'ga' dang chos zhu sngags 'chang sogs
NK133(po)003:1815: thams cad grwa gtsang du bsgyur bas 'dus sde'i gzhi
NK133(po)003:1817: barjesa nas ring sras rig 'dzin gsum pa ngag gi dbang pos rdo rje brag gdan sa bskyang /
NK133(po)003:1818: de rjes rig 'dzin yol mo pa bstan 'dzin nor bus bskyang /
NK133(po)003:1819: de rjes ngag gi dbang po'i sprul sku bzhi pa
NK133(po)003:1820: rig 'dzin pad+ma phrin las mon khar rnam sras gling
NK133(po)003:1822: kun mkhyen lnga pa chen por gtsug phud phul ba'i
NK133(po)003:1823: mtshan blo bzang pad ma phrin las su rtsal zhing
NK133(po)003:1824: bsnyen par rdzogs zab chos mang du gsan /
NK133(po)003:1825: gzhan yang zur chos dbyings rang grol /
NK133(po)003:1826: bka' 'gyur pa bsod nams mchog ldan /
NK133(po)003:1827: khra tshang pa blo mchog rdo rje la sogs mkhas
NK133(po)003:1828: grub kyi bla ma mang po las gsar rnying gi
NK133(po)003:1829: dbang lung man ngag bshad pa sogs chos bka' mtha'
NK133(po)003:1831: bsam byung gis gtan la phabs pas thogs pa med pa'i mkhyen rab rgyas /
NK133(po)003:1832: sgrags yang rdzogs chu bo ri gdan sa la sogs
NK133(po)003:1833: par sgom pa'i shes rab kyis nyams su bzhes pas
NK133(po)003:1834: bskyed rim la brtan pa thob rdzogs rim gyi ye
NK133(po)003:1835: shes la dbang 'byor bas mkhas grub chen por gyur
NK133(po)003:1836: / sdom pa gsum ldan gyi dge 'dun spang klog las gsum gyi bgyi ba la bkod /
NK133(po)003:1837: mdo dbang chen mo sogs legs bshad kyi bstan bcos
NK133(po)003:1838: mang du mdzad dgung grangs don bdun par snang tshul
NK133(po)003:1839: sna tshogs kyang 'ga' zhig gis mthong bar mkha' lding
NK133(po)003:1840: gi rtsal gyis mkha' spyod du gshegs /
NK133(po)003:1841: de nyid kyi sprul pa'i sku rig 'dzin lnga pa skal bzang pad+ma dbang phyug /
NK133(po)003:1842: rig 'dzin drug pa kun bzang 'gyur med /
NK133(po)003:1843: bdun pa ngag dbang 'jam dpal mi 'gyur lhun grub rdo rje /
NK133(po)003:1844: brgyad pa pad+ma dbang rgyal nas /
NK133(po)003:1845: da lta'i mchog sprul dgu pa thub bstan mnyam nyid
NK133(po)003:1846: bar mkhas btsun grub pa'i rnam thar can gyis gsang
NK133(po)003:1847: chen bka' gter gyi phrin las stod mnga' ris nas
NK133(po)003:1848: smad rgya nag yan gyi phyogs mthar dar zhing rgyas
NK133(po)003:1850: mchong rgyas dpal ri theg pa mchog gi sde ni /
NK133(po)003:1851: 'phreng po gter chen shes rab 'od zer gyis mchong
NK133(po)003:1852: rgyas sde pa'i mthun rkyen bcas pas phyag btab mdzad
NK133(po)003:1853: pa nas snga 'gyur bshad sgrub kyi phrin las rgyas
NK133(po)003:1854: pa dpal ri chos 'byor rgya mtsho sogs kyis bskyang
NK133(po)003:1855: ba rig 'dzin 'jigs med gling pa'ang dge 'dun 'di
NK133(po)003:1856: las byon te / rje 'dis rdzogs chen man ngag
NK133(po)003:1857: sde gtso bor gyur pa'i snga 'gyur bka' gter gyi
NK133(po)003:1858: bstan pa la dngos dang brgyud nas sri zhu phyag
NK133(po)003:1859: rjes bla na med pa mdzad pa yin no //
NK133(po)003:1860: lho brag lha lung yang sngon bka' brgyud dpa' bo
NK133(po)003:1861: gtsug lag phreng bas bzhengs pa phyis dar lding pad
NK133(po)003:1862: gling gnyis pa bstan 'dzin grags pa'i yang srid gsung
NK133(po)003:1863: sprul tshul khrims rdo rje sku phreng dang thugs sras
NK133(po)003:1864: zla ba sku phreng kyis bskyang ba pad gling chos
NK133(po)003:1866: mnga' bdag nyang rin po che'i gdan sa lho brag shar smra bo cog /
NK133(po)003:1867: chos dbang gdan sa lho brag nub la yag gu ru lha khang /
NK133(po)003:1868: shar btsan 'gro gnas gzhi dgon rat+na gling pa'i gdan sa lho mdo mkhar lhun grub pho brang /
NK133(po)003:1869: yang de phyogs dge ye dgon /
NK133(po)003:1870: lho brag ban pa'i phur bsam 'grub gling /
NK133(po)003:1873: mon phyogs pad gling chos brgyud dgon che phra du ma dang /
NK133(po)003:1874: lho 'brug gdan sa gsar rnying zung 'brel mang /
NK133(po)003:1875: rgya gar sa mtshams su gdung bsam ri bo bstan rgyas gling yar 'brog yon po do /
NK133(po)003:1876: gtsang la stod zang zang lha brag tu byang pa'i srid gsum rnam rgyal dgon /
NK133(po)003:1878: mtsho skya bo kha gdang phyogs rig 'dzin rgod ldem phyag btab se ston brgyud pa'i gdan sa /
NK133(po)003:1880: rgya mkhar gsang sngags chos gling /
NK133(po)003:1881: zam bu lung zab lung dbang rgyas sogs kyi gdan sa dang /
NK133(po)003:1882: gangs ra lo chen gdan sa gangs ra nges gsang rdo rje gling /
NK133(po)003:1884: phung po ri bo cher bdud dpung zil gnon gling /
NK133(po)003:1888: rgyal rtse'i phyogs o rgyan 'gro 'dren gling /
NK133(po)003:1889: lha btsun gdan sa smin grol rab brtan gling /
NK133(po)003:1891: dbus phyogs thang rgyal phyag btab lcags zam bo ri
NK133(po)003:1892: dang tshe chu sgrub sde chu shul byang chub gling
NK133(po)003:1894: lho rgyud gnyal dang lo ro'i phyogs su 'brug smyon gdan sa dre'u lhas dang /
NK133(po)003:1895: sha gzugs bkra shis rnam rgyal sku phreng dang sbyor
NK133(po)003:1896: ra thams cad mkhyen pa rim byon sogs rnying ma'i
NK133(po)003:1898: e rong phyogs rdzogs chen pa 'brug sgra bzang po'i rtsa sgrub sde e spe cog /
NK133(po)003:1900: dag kong phyogs rtse le gdan sa gong 'og gsum /
NK133(po)003:1901: sangs rgyas gling pa'i snyi phu /
NK133(po)003:1903: rtsa nang dri med lhun po'i gdan sa /
NK133(po)003:1904: 'ja' tshon bang ri bkra shis 'od 'bar sogs dang /
NK133(po)003:1905: spu bo'i phyogs rig 'dzin chos kyi rgya mtsho'i gdan sa spa kha gsang sngags gling /
NK133(po)003:1907: stag sham pa'i dga' ba lung /
NK133(po)003:1908: ye gang khrom gzigs dgon sogs rag rim 'ga' zhig
NK133(po)003:1909: brjod pa las stod mnga' ris nas lho mon tshun
NK133(po)003:1910: mtha' dbus kun tu dgon che phra shin tu mang
NK133(po)003:1911: yang deng sang mnga' thang dang bshad sgrub dar rgyas
NK133(po)003:1913: lar yang rnying ma tsam du ma zad /
NK133(po)003:1914: gsar phyogs dgon sde mnga' thang rgyas pa ltar snang
NK133(po)003:1915: ba phal cher yang dam chos nyams len bshad sgrub
NK133(po)003:1916: kyi phrin las rgud cing nyag phra bar gyur pa
NK133(po)003:1917: ni dus dbang gis gsar rnying thams cad phyogs mtshungs
NK133(po)003:1918: la skyo ba skye ba'i gnas su'o //
NK133(po)003:1919: mdo khams phyogs ngom gnas mdo ba ni /
NK133(po)003:1920: cog ro klu'i rgyal mtshan dang lha sras sad na
NK133(po)003:1921: legs zung gi sprul pa mkhas grub karma chags med
NK133(po)003:1922: nyid / ngom yul du chos rgyal gdung brgyud gdong
NK133(po)003:1923: mkha' spyod pa nam mkha' rgyal mtshan gyi dbon rigs
NK133(po)003:1924: nyid / las 'khrungs / yab sngags 'chang a nu
NK133(po)003:1925: pad ma dbang drag las rnying chos mang po gsan
NK133(po)003:1927: grwa sar tshad ma 'dul mdzod dbu phar thar rgyan
NK133(po)003:1929: don sogs sngags kyi gzhung rnams sbyangs pa mthar phyin
NK133(po)003:1931: shin tu dul bas grwa tshang du lo lngar bzhugs
NK133(po)003:1932: ring spyi mi chos khrims sogs kyis mig log tsam
NK133(po)003:1934: ma byung / zhwa dmar drug pa chos kyi dbang
NK133(po)003:1935: phyug las phyag chen chos drug sogs bka' chos mang
NK133(po)003:1936: du zhus nas rtsa ba'i bla mar bzung rje brgyad
NK133(po)003:1938: ma byung / pas / gdong mkha' spyod arga'i dug
NK133(po)003:1940: ma byung / pas / po la // nga ma
NK133(po)003:1941: chags mi chags chags pa med //
NK133(po)003:1942: zhes karma pa'i sprul par nges la /
NK133(po)003:1943: b+ha kha chos kyi rgyal mtshan las snying tig /'bri
NK133(po)003:1944: gung dkon mchog phrin las las rngog dkyil dang rdor
NK133(po)003:1945: phreng sogs / yongs 'dzin mang po las dbang lung man ngag mang po gsan /
NK133(po)003:1946: gnas mdo dpal ri rtser gdan sa mdzad nas skabs
NK133(po)003:1947: 'ga' zhig tu 'gro don chos sgo skyel phebs bzhud
NK133(po)003:1948: ma gtogs sku mtshams kho nar bzhugs te byang chub
NK133(po)003:1950: dkyil 'khor brgya lhag gi bsnyen sgrub rtags thon mdzad /
NK133(po)003:1951: ro gcig gi rtogs pa mngon du gyur /
NK133(po)003:1952: bla ma dang lhag pa'i lhas byin gyis rlabs pa'i ltas shin tu mang /
NK133(po)003:1953: byang chub sems kyi nus pa mngon du gyur pas
NK133(po)003:1954: gang du bzhugs pa'i sa phyogs kun tu nad mug
NK133(po)003:1956: btang len dmigs pas gzhan gyi nad yams sogs dngos su len pa dang /
NK133(po)003:1958: dbang bskur ba tsam gyis gnas lugs ngo 'phrod pa sogs thugs rje phrin las tshad med /
NK133(po)003:1959: thugs rje chen po'i dmar khrid 'dis dung phyur bco
NK133(po)003:1960: brgyad bde ba can du 'gro zhes lung bstan thob
NK133(po)003:1961: pa sogs gsung chos rnams lhag pa'i lhas rjes su
NK133(po)003:1962: gnang bas byin rlabs 'gro phan rgya che /
NK133(po)003:1963: dgung lo re bzhi bar nga bde ba can du nges par 'gro gsungs pa dang /
NK133(po)003:1964: nga yi rnam shes 'di gsum du gyur nas bde
NK133(po)003:1965: ba can du byang chub sems dpa' chu skyes pad
NK133(po)003:1966: ma dri med / rnga yab gling na rig 'dzin rma bya'i mgrin pa'i rgyal mtshan /
NK133(po)003:1967: sangs rgyas sman bla'i drung du byang chub sems dpa'
NK133(po)003:1968: 'gro la rtag tu gzigs bya bar 'gyur tshul sogs
NK133(po)003:1969: lung bstan stsal / zhal slob kyang rdzogs chen pad ma rig 'dzin /
NK133(po)003:1970: dpal yul kun mtshan shes rab /
NK133(po)003:1971: rig 'dzin mi 'gyur rdo rje rnams gtso bor gyur
NK133(po)003:1972: pa'i slob tshogs chos rgyud 'phel bas snga 'gyur rnying
NK133(po)003:1973: ma'i bstan pa 'phel rgyas su bka' drin che ba
NK133(po)003:1975: mdo khams grub dbang rdzogs chen pa pad+ma rig 'dzin ni /
NK133(po)003:1976: sangs rgyas rin chen gtsug tor can /
NK133(po)003:1977: slob dpon ku ku r+aa dza /
NK133(po)003:1978: bi ma la sa ra ha /
NK133(po)003:1986: rje tsong kha pa rnams kyi sprul pa ste rab
NK133(po)003:1987: drag shing glang la 'khrungs sku chung ngu nas grub
NK133(po)003:1988: dbang karma chags med rigs bdag tu brten nas smin
NK133(po)003:1989: grol gdams pa mtha' yas gsan /
NK133(po)003:1990: lo drug stan thog gcig tu rat+na'i thugs sgrub gtsor
NK133(po)003:1991: gyur bsnyen sgrub dang rtsa rlung gtum mo mun pa'i
NK133(po)003:1992: rnal 'byor sogs bskyed rdzogs la brtan pa thob par
NK133(po)003:1993: mdzad / bdud 'dul rdo rje las sprul sku snying thig gsan /
NK133(po)003:1994: spu bo b+ha kha ri khrod du rig 'dzin chos
NK133(po)003:1995: kyi rgyal mtshan las rdzogs chen mkha' 'gro snying thig
NK133(po)003:1996: gsan pas chos nyid mngon sum gyi snang ba shar
NK133(po)003:1997: / ye shes mkha' 'gros rdzogs chen pa'i mtshan dang rgyal tshabs su mnga' gsol /
NK133(po)003:1998: 'ja' tshon slob ma kun mkhyen pa las 'ja' tshon gter chos zhus /
NK133(po)003:1999: dgung lo so dgu nas dbus phyogs sgrub gnas bsam
NK133(po)003:2000: yas mchims phur lo gsum bcad rgya mdzad pas nyams
NK133(po)003:2003: smra bo cog chos kyi dbang po /
NK133(po)003:2004: chos dbang gdung rgyud dpal 'byor rgyal po /
NK133(po)003:2005: rdzogs chen klong rdzogs mtha' bral /
NK133(po)003:2007: dpal ri phrin las rnam rgyal /
NK133(po)003:2009: sgam po bzang po rdo rje /
NK133(po)003:2010: ras chung sprul sku sogs yongs 'dzin sum cu las gsar rnying gi chos bka' mang po gsan /
NK133(po)003:2011: sgrub gnas mkhar chu zam bu lung /
NK133(po)003:2014: lha mo mkhar sogs su snying po'i sgrub pa rtse gcig tu gzhol /
NK133(po)003:2015: mkhar chu'i dur khrod la khar bsgom dus kun gyis
NK133(po)003:2016: mthong bar lha lcam man+da ra ba byon nas mkha'
NK133(po)003:2017: spyod du byon par bskul kyang bstan pa rin po
NK133(po)003:2019: ts+aa rir sgom pa'i tshe bka' brgyad lha tshogs zhal gzigs /
NK133(po)003:2020: thod rgal rig pa tshad phebs kyi dgongs pa mngon du gyur /
NK133(po)003:2021: che rgu rnams kyis zhabs nas btud cing srid pa'i lha gnyen rnams kyis phrin las sgrub /
NK133(po)003:2022: chos sde mang por 'gyed dang sgrub gnas rnams la bsnyen bskur mchod 'bul rgya chen dang /
NK133(po)003:2023: chos 'khor bsam yas la nyams gsos mchod 'bul rgya cher mdzad /
NK133(po)003:2024: gcig tu sgrub na rang don mthar phyin 'od lus 'grub pa yin kyang /
NK133(po)003:2025: bstan pa rin po che thugs la brnag pa dang
NK133(po)003:2026: rgyal mchog lnga pa chen pos bskul bzhin dgung lo
NK133(po)003:2027: drug cu nas mdo khams su chibs ba skyod de
NK133(po)003:2028: / zab gsang chos kyi 'khor los bstan 'gro'i don dpag tu med pa mdzad /
NK133(po)003:2029: re gcig shing glang la o rgyan chen pos zhabs
NK133(po)003:2030: kyis bcags shing dpa' bo mkha' 'gro sprin ltar 'du
NK133(po)003:2031: ba'i gnas ru dam skyid khram lung bar 'od gsal
NK133(po)003:2032: bsgom pa'i sgrub sde bsam gtan chos gling btab ste
NK133(po)003:2033: phyogs kyi slob tshogs mtha' yas pa'i gdul bya smin
NK133(po)003:2034: grol la bkod / mthar dgung grangs don gsum me
NK133(po)003:2035: glang mchu zla'i tshes lnga la ngo mtshar ba'i ltas
NK133(po)003:2036: dang bcas te sprul pa'i dkyil 'khor bsdus /
NK133(po)003:2037: zhal slob mkhon na gen+d+ra'i sprul pa gter chen nyi
NK133(po)003:2038: ma grags pa'i phrin las khams dbus gtsang gsum du
NK133(po)003:2039: rgyas pa dang / grub chen me long rnam 'phrul
NK133(po)003:2040: tshad phebs chung ngu'i rtogs pa brnyes pa dpon slob
NK133(po)003:2042: zhal chen rab 'byams gsum pa rnams gtso bo yin la /
NK133(po)003:2043: rje de'i yang srid sku phreng gnyis pa 'gyur med pad+ma theg mchog bstan 'dzin ni /
NK133(po)003:2044: byang o rod tsho ba bzhi bcu'i nang tshan dar khan u lug tu grags par /
NK133(po)003:2046: gong ma'i slob chen gsum dang /
NK133(po)003:2047: smin gling sku mched sras lcam sku ngo drug rdor
NK133(po)003:2048: brag pad+ma phrin las rnams las sdom pa gsum gyi
NK133(po)003:2053: lho brag gsung sprul dang thugs sprul /
NK133(po)003:2054: sa skya dpal ldan chos skyong /
NK133(po)003:2055: khams sprul gong 'og /'bri gung sprul sku /
NK133(po)003:2056: zhwa dmar chos kyi don 'grub sogs ris med kyi
NK133(po)003:2057: yongs 'dzin bzhi bcu las gsan sbyang rdzogs par mdzad
NK133(po)003:2058: / dkyil 'khor rab 'byams kyi bsnyen sgrub mthar phyin /
NK133(po)003:2059: rdzogs chen gong 'phel gyi rtogs pa brnyes /
NK133(po)003:2060: mdzod bdun spar du 'khod par mdzad pa /
NK133(po)003:2061: gtsug lag khang dang rten gsum bzhengs pa /
NK133(po)003:2062: khams dbus gtsang gsum gyi dge 'dun la bsnyen bskur rten gsum la mchod 'bul rgya chen dang /
NK133(po)003:2063: lo hril po la bka' chos gsung pa slob ma
NK133(po)003:2064: khyad par can mang du byung ba sogs dam pa'i
NK133(po)003:2065: rnam thar phyogs sgor mo nas lhun gyis grub pa'o
NK133(po)003:2066: // de nyid kyi yang srid sku phreng gsum pa nges don bstan 'dzin bzang po ni /
NK133(po)003:2067: zla rgyud ho sa zhes pa'i char 'khrungs /
NK133(po)003:2068: gong ma'i bu chen rnams dang kun mkhyen 'jigs med
NK133(po)003:2069: gling pa sogs bshes gnyen du ma'i zhabs pad brten
NK133(po)003:2070: nas gsan bsam sgom pa'i yon tan mthar phyin /
NK133(po)003:2071: smin gling phyag bzhes bzhin snga 'gyur mdo sgyu sogs rgyud sde'i chog grwa bcu gsum /
NK133(po)003:2073: chu 'khor bcu gsum 'dzug pa sogs bstan pa la phyag rjes che /
NK133(po)003:2074: zhal slob kyang rdo grub kun bzang gzhan phan 'jigs med go cha /
NK133(po)003:2076: pad+ma bkra shis sogs rnying ma'i bstan 'dzin mang du byon /
NK133(po)003:2078: de'i yang srid bzhi pa mi 'gyur nam mkha'i rdo
NK133(po)003:2079: rje tshe dbang grub pa rtsal rab 'dod chu glang
NK133(po)003:2080: la ldan yul du ba ltams rigs bdag rdo grub
NK133(po)003:2083: rgya rong nam mkha' tshe dbang mchog grub /
NK133(po)003:2084: 'jigs med rgyal ba'i myu gu sogs gsar rnying mkhas
NK133(po)003:2085: grub du ma brten nas gsan bsam mtha' yas pa
NK133(po)003:2086: mdzad / phyi 'dul ba'i kun spyod mchog tu btsun /
NK133(po)003:2087: nang du skye ba du mar byang chub sems la
NK133(po)003:2088: gom pas gzhan gyi log sgrub sogs kyis thugs nam
NK133(po)003:2090: gsang ba bskyed rdzogs gsum gyis grub pa'i sa mthor gshegs /
NK133(po)003:2091: snang srid dag pa rab 'byams su shar zhing bla ma dang lhag pa'i lhas gdams ngag bstsal /
NK133(po)003:2094: grub matha'i phyogs ris med cing dus gsum sgrib med du gzigs /
NK133(po)003:2095: dgung grangs don brgyad bzhugs pa sogs mdzad phrin mthar phyin /
NK133(po)003:2096: de dang dus mnyam mkhan chen b+ho d+hi sa t+wa /
NK133(po)003:2097: lo chen bee ro tsa na dang chos rgyal gter
NK133(po)003:2098: bdag gling pa rnams kyi rnam 'phrul rgyal sras gzhan
NK133(po)003:2099: phan mtha' yas 'od zer rab 'dod lcags sprel la
NK133(po)003:2100: 'khrungs / mkhas btsun grub pa'i yon tan nam mkha'
NK133(po)003:2101: dang mnyam pa de dang zhal bgros kyii sgo nas
NK133(po)003:2102: ru dam dpal seng ge ri'i rigs grwa tshug ste
NK133(po)003:2103: mdo sngags 'chad nyan gyis bstan pa spel /
NK133(po)003:2104: spyir yang sku zhabs rgyal sras rin po che 'dis
NK133(po)003:2105: seng ge rir 'dul ba gzhi gsum gyi phyag len
NK133(po)003:2106: dang mdo sngags gzhung bshad mang po'i rgyun btsugs pas
NK133(po)003:2107: mdo khams phyogs 'dir bshad sgrub kyi rgyun la bka'
NK133(po)003:2108: drin 'gran zla dang bral bar gyur /
NK133(po)003:2109: khyad par snga 'gyur bka' ma'i phyogs la thugs rtsol
NK133(po)003:2110: chen pos dpe dang dbang lung gi rgyun btsal zhing
NK133(po)003:2111: 'chad nyan spel ba sogs phyi ma'i dus 'dir rnying
NK133(po)003:2112: bstan la 'di kho na bka' drin dang phyag rjes
NK133(po)003:2114: de las kyang smin gling sangs rgyas kun dga'/
NK133(po)003:2115: lha lung sprul sku pad+ma dbang rgyal rnams kyis dngos su dang /
NK133(po)003:2116: ma dang mkha' 'gros brda' thabs kyis bskul bar brten /
NK133(po)003:2117: bka' ma'i chog khrigs glegs bam bcu spar du bkod
NK133(po)003:2118: pas bstan rgyun la phan pa tshad med pa byung
NK133(po)003:2119: ba yin no // da lta rdzogs sprul lnga pa
NK133(po)003:2120: rin po che thub bstan chos kyi rdo rje nyid
NK133(po)003:2121: kyis bshad sgrub kyi sde rnams gong 'phel du btang
NK133(po)003:2122: ba sogs spang klog las gsum gyis rgyal bstan spel
NK133(po)003:2123: ba'i phrin las rlab po cher dbang bsgyur ba bcas
NK133(po)003:2124: ba yin no // so // rdzogs chen pa'i thugs
NK133(po)003:2125: sras dpon slob nam mkha' 'od gsal gyi sku rab
NK133(po)003:2126: gnyis pa pad+ma gsang sngags bstan 'dzin dang /
NK133(po)003:2127: gsum pa nam mkha' chos kyi rgya mtsho /
NK133(po)003:2128: bzhi pa 'jigs med chos dbyings 'od gsal rnams dam pa'i rnam thar tshad med pa kho na'o //
NK133(po)003:2129: grub dbang rdzogs chen pa'i thugs sras ze chen rab
NK133(po)003:2130: 'byams pa bstan pa'i rgyal mtshan ni 'phan yul du
NK133(po)003:2132: 'bras spungs su bka' pod bzhi sogs gzhung chen rnams byang chub pas /
NK133(po)003:2136: sa ngor rnams su gra skor mdzad pas rnam par rgyal ba'i grags pa thob /
NK133(po)003:2139: rgyal ma chog lnga pa sogs las gsar rnying gi gsan pa rgya che /
NK133(po)003:2140: tshe rabs kyi bla ma grub dbang rdzogs chen pa
NK133(po)003:2141: las snying thig ya bzhi sogs rdzogs chen gyi gdams
NK133(po)003:2142: pa mthar phyin par gsan pas /
NK133(po)003:2143: gtad med snang ba rgya yan chos sku khyab brdal gyi dgongs pa'i gdeng thob /
NK133(po)003:2144: yab sras lhan cig phebs te ru dam gdan sa pa'ang mdzad /
NK133(po)003:2145: slar ze chen o rgyan chos rdzong btab /
NK133(po)003:2146: de nyid kyi yang sprul rab 'byams gnyis pa 'gyur
NK133(po)003:2147: med kun bzang rnam rgyal blo gsal rgya mtsho'i sde
NK133(po)003:2148: ni / rdzogs chen gnyis pa'i gcung du 'khrungs /
NK133(po)003:2149: smin gling rin chen rnam rgyal /
NK133(po)003:2152: sa skya dpal ldan chos skyong /
NK133(po)003:2153: mdo khams pa kun dga' bstan 'dzin /
NK133(po)003:2154: kahthoga zhing skyong sogs brten nas mkhas dang grub pa'i dbang phyug chen por gyur /
NK133(po)003:2155: rgyal mchog bdun pa'i lung bstan bzhin /
NK133(po)003:2156: ze chen bstan gnyis dar rgyas gling btab /
NK133(po)003:2157: 'khor lo gsum gyi phrin las rgyas /
NK133(po)003:2158: gsung rtsom pod dgu tsam yod /
NK133(po)003:2159: de nyid kyi yang srid rab 'byams gsum pa rig 'dzin dpal 'byor rgya mtsho thub bstan nyin byed /
NK133(po)003:2160: rab 'byams bzhi pa gar dbang chos kyi rgyal mtshan zhes grub spyod can de dang /
NK133(po)003:2161: rab 'byams lnga pa 'gyur med kun bzang bstan pa'i nyi ma dang /
NK133(po)003:2162: da lta'i drug pa rnams bstan 'dzin dam pa'i rnam thar phul du byung ba byon pa yin no //
NK133(po)003:2163: ze chen rgyal tshab sku phreng dang po grub dbang pad+ma rgyal mtshan /
NK133(po)003:2164: gnyis pa pad+ma gsang sngags bstan 'dzin chos rgyal /
NK133(po)003:2165: gsum pa o rgyan rang byung rdo rje /
NK133(po)003:2166: bzhi pa pad+ma rnam rgyal rnams mkhas dang grub pa'i
NK133(po)003:2167: rnam thar rgya mtsho lta bu mnga' ba 'ba' zhig
NK133(po)003:2168: yin / pad+ma rgyal mtshan gyi rigs dbon rtogs ldan
NK133(po)003:2169: sangs rgyas rab brtan zhes pa'i sprul pa dbon sprul
NK133(po)003:2170: mthu stobs rnam rgyal lam 'jam mgon bstan 'dzin 'phel
NK133(po)003:2171: yin / rgyas dang / rgyal tshab slob ma mkhas grub chen po shes rab yar 'phel dang /
NK133(po)003:2172: 'jam pa'i dbyangs dngos mi pham 'jam dbyangs rnam rgyal
NK133(po)003:2173: rgya matsho'ang chos brgyud 'di las byon pa yin te
NK133(po)003:2174: 'di ni rab byung bcu bzhi pa'i me rta lor
NK133(po)003:2176: sku chung ngu nas nges gsang snying po'i bstan pa la mos pa brtan /
NK133(po)003:2177: kun mkhyen rdo rje gzi brjid /
NK133(po)003:2179: lab skyabs mgon dbang chen dgyes rab rdo rje /
NK133(po)003:2180: o rgyan 'jigs med chos kyi dbang po /
NK133(po)003:2181: mkhan chen pad+ma dam chos 'od zer rnams las zab
NK133(po)003:2182: rgyas kyi gdams pa'i smin grol gzhung bshad nyams myong
NK133(po)003:2183: dmar khrid bcas mtha' yas pa gsan /
NK133(po)003:2184: gsung rab thams cad kyi dgongs pa'i gting phyin /
NK133(po)003:2185: gsan sbyang dang 'chad spel gyi skabs phran bu ma
NK133(po)003:2186: gtogs sku tshe ril por sgrub pa'i rgyal mtshan brtan
NK133(po)003:2187: pos don brgyud kyi rgyal sa zin te 'gran bral
NK133(po)003:2188: gyi mkhas grub chen por gyur /
NK133(po)003:2189: spobs pa'i gter chen brgyad la rang dbang 'byor /
NK133(po)003:2190: so skye'i blo skyon dang rtog ge'i 'khyogs bshad kyi
NK133(po)003:2191: brjod sgros sogs dang ma 'dres par rgyal ba sras
NK133(po)003:2192: dang bcas pa'i dgongs don phyin ci ma log pa'i
NK133(po)003:2193: / legs bshad kyi gter sgo phyes pas bstan pa'i snying po gsal bar mdzad /
NK133(po)003:2194: phas rgol gyi tshang tshing tha dag lung dang rigs pa'i mes gtsang bar mdzad /
NK133(po)003:2195: log rtog gi mun pa thams cad dngos po stobs
NK133(po)003:2196: shugs kyi rig pa'i nyi mas bsal bar mdzad de
NK133(po)003:2197: bstan pa rin po che sri zhu bla na med
NK133(po)003:2198: pa mdzad nas dgung grangs re bdun du bzhugs pa
NK133(po)003:2199: yin no // mdo khams phyogs su snga 'gyur bstan
NK133(po)003:2200: pa'i 'byung gnas lta bu dpal kahthoga pa ni 'phags
NK133(po)003:2202: dga' rab slob ma tog tse ba /
NK133(po)003:2204: bal po pan+ta pa sogs kyi rnam 'phrul kahdama pa bde gshegs spobs pa mtha' yas sam /
NK133(po)003:2205: chos rje shes rab seng ge ni mdo khams bu
NK133(po)003:2206: 'bor dpe war 'bal mo'i yul du rje phag gru'i
NK133(po)003:2207: sku mched de rab byung gnyis pa'i chu stag la
NK133(po)003:2208: ngo mtshar ba'i ltas dang bcas pa bltams /
NK133(po)003:2209: 'khrungs nas sha chang mi gsol zhing snying rje dang ldan /
NK133(po)003:2210: dgung lo drug nas 'bri klog dang bdun nas bzo gso /
NK133(po)003:2211: spor thang rtsis dang brgyad stong thugs la bzung /
NK133(po)003:2212: dgu par skyid chu bu le'i dgon par rje btsun drung sems bskyed dang bde mchog zhus /
NK133(po)003:2217: brgyad stong sogs kyi bshad pa gsan /
NK133(po)003:2218: bcu nas gu ru pad+ma dang /
NK133(po)003:2219: rang byung rgyal mos zhal gzigs /
NK133(po)003:2221: dge bshes phyar bu las don zhags /
NK133(po)003:2222: mngon byang gsan te zhal gzigs /
NK133(po)003:2223: bcu drug par kam po'i gnas su dge bshes byang ston las 'dul mngon /
NK133(po)003:2227: gsang snying dbang dang nyi seng 'grel pa gsan /
NK133(po)003:2228: 'di bee ros 'o du byams pa'i lha khang du
NK133(po)003:2229: gsang tika rgya cher 'grel bsgyur bshad mdzad pa de'i
NK133(po)003:2232: rong zom bstan bcos pod nyi shu sogs gsan /
NK133(po)003:2233: bcu dgu par dbus su byon dge bshes d+ho thog thel ba las byams chos dang /
NK133(po)003:2234: pra ka ra na sde brgyad /
NK133(po)003:2237: sa sde sdom rnam gnyis bshad pa nos so //
NK133(po)003:2242: dus 'khor dbang mdor bstan sogs dang /
NK133(po)003:2243: nyer gcig par ra sgreng du /
NK133(po)003:2244: seng ge bzang po las rig tshogs phal tshad /
NK133(po)003:2245: lam sgron sogs gsan cing chos 'khor bzhir gra bskor mdzad pas thog gcig la mkhas par grags /
NK133(po)003:2246: sa skya bsod nams rtse mo sogs las yang phur brtags gnyis sogs dang /
NK133(po)003:2247: gzhan yang kam chos kyi rdo rje las lam 'bras /
NK133(po)003:2248: ljang ston dang zhang ston las gsang 'dus dgra gdong 'jigs gsum /
NK133(po)003:2249: skyor lung pa las gnubs dang rngog lung chos skor /
NK133(po)003:2250: ka chos ye las thugs bskyed sems tsam lugs gsan /
NK133(po)003:2251: nyer gcig par dga' ldan du byams pa las chos nyan pa'i dag snang shar /
NK133(po)003:2252: skyi 'dul 'dzin las sum brgya pa 'od ldan mdo /
NK133(po)003:2253: kam lo ts+aa las bde mchog /
NK133(po)003:2254: cog ro lo ts+aa las phag mo dang sdom 'byung /
NK133(po)003:2255: nyer gnyis par rat+na seng ge las bde mchog gdan bzhi sogs gsan nas grub rtags thon par mdzad /
NK133(po)003:2256: nyer bzhi par 'phan yul rgyal du byang chub seng
NK133(po)003:2257: ge'i drung rab tu phyung mtshan shes rab seng ge
NK133(po)003:2258: gsol / de nas sgyu 'phrul sems sde /
NK133(po)003:2264: sbrang phur bu mgo las yang phur sogs gsan /
NK133(po)003:2265: nyer lnga par bal yul du byon /
NK133(po)003:2266: ras chung pa las na ro chos drug lus med mkha' 'gro'i chos skor /
NK133(po)003:2267: zhi ba 'od las gtum mo nos so //
NK133(po)003:2268: slar dbus su sde pa nags kyi rin chen las
NK133(po)003:2269: dpal ldan snar thang pa'i smad 'dul las bsnyen par
NK133(po)003:2270: rdzogs te de nas sku mchog tu btsun /
NK133(po)003:2277: kun 'dus rig pa sogs rtsa mdo bzhi'i bshad pa /
NK133(po)003:2278: man ngag phra mo drug cu /
NK133(po)003:2279: sgrub dbang zla ba bdun sogs lo bzhi bzhugs /
NK133(po)003:2280: bla ma dpal chen por mthong /
NK133(po)003:2281: brag rgya bor tshogs pa sum stong mdun spar khab
NK133(po)003:2282: steng nas rtsod pa'i dam bca' bzhag pas bla ma
NK133(po)003:2284: thod smyon dang smyon pa don ldan las dam pa'i man ngag gsan /
NK133(po)003:2285: nyer dgu par 'dzam ston pas khyod kam po'i gnas su sgom na phung po 'od du deng /
NK133(po)003:2286: kahthoga tu song na bstan pa mtha' yas su 'ong
NK133(po)003:2287: gsung mar lam chos rje dag po las lhan cig
NK133(po)003:2289: ts+aa rir zla ba bzhir bsgom pas yon tan khyad par can thob dag snang dpag med shar /
NK133(po)003:2290: sum cu par khams su phebs rje dus mkhyen las chos mang du gsan /
NK133(po)003:2291: mdor na snga phyir bshes gnyen brgya lhag las chos dang gdams ngag nos so //
NK133(po)003:2292: 'jang dang me nyag phyogs gdul bya skyong /
NK133(po)003:2293: bstan pa la thugs brnag pas sa mo yos kyi
NK133(po)003:2294: lor ka'dra ba'i thog tu gtsug lag bzhengs nas chos
NK133(po)003:2298: lho mon tshun gyi slob ma 'dus te dge 'dun sum khri lang ba dang /
NK133(po)003:2299: dbyar khas len pa'i dge slong khri yang byung /
NK133(po)003:2302: mdo sgyu sems gsum gtso bor gyur pa'i mdo sngags kyi chos sgo mtha' yas pa gsungs /
NK133(po)003:2303: bde ba can sogs sangs rgyas kyi zhing rnams rtag par gzigs /
NK133(po)003:2304: bde gshegs rigs lnga sogs las chos gsan /
NK133(po)003:2305: 'jam dpal dbyangs ni gshegs bzhud mi mnga' ba dang /
NK133(po)003:2306: rgyud sde rab 'byams kyi lha rnams nam bzhed du
NK133(po)003:2307: gzigs ma 'ongs skar ma bkram par bde gshegs tshe
NK133(po)003:2308: dpag med par sangs rgyas pa'i lung bstan brnyes /
NK133(po)003:2309: de ltar mdo khams ljongs su snga bstan gzhi bzhengs
NK133(po)003:2310: su btang nas dgung grangs don gcig lo tha skar
NK133(po)003:2311: zla bar bde ba can du gshegs nas byang sems
NK133(po)003:2312: blo gros snying po bya bar bzhugs so //
NK133(po)003:2313: de'i rgyal tshab kun tu 'od kyi sa brnyes pa gtsang ston rdo rje rgyal mtshan dang /
NK133(po)003:2314: grub chen nag po spyod pa'i rnam 'phrul byams pa 'bum dang /
NK133(po)003:2318: tsa sde nam mkha' rdo rje ste lung bstan bu
NK133(po)003:2319: bzhi las 'bru tsha sgang pas chos sde brgya rtsa
NK133(po)003:2320: btab pa dang / bsod nams 'bum pa /
NK133(po)003:2331: byang chub rgyal mtshan te bla rab bcu gsum du grags pa dang /
NK133(po)003:2332: gzhan yang grub thob rmog rab bcu gsum /
NK133(po)003:2334: 'chad nyan mkhan rab bcu gsum sogs gdan sa rab
NK133(po)003:2335: brgyad cu tsam mdo sgyu sems gsum sogs mdo sngags
NK133(po)003:2336: bstan pa'i gsal byed phrin las rgya che rgyun ring
NK133(po)003:2337: gi bstan 'dzin rim par byon pa dang /
NK133(po)003:2338: phyis nas rig 'dzin bdud 'dul rdo rje dang klong gsal snying po gnyis kyi phrin las rgyas shing /
NK133(po)003:2339: bdud 'dul yang srid klong gsal rgyal sras bsod nams
NK133(po)003:2340: lde'u btsan de'i sprul pa gnyis pa dri med zhing
NK133(po)003:2342: de'i yang srid gsum pa rig 'dzin 'jigs med mgon po /
NK133(po)003:2343: bzhi pa 'jigs med yon tan mgon po'am mi 'gyur bstan pa'i rgyal mtshan dang /
NK133(po)003:2344: da lta mchog sprul lnga pa zhal bzhugs pa nyid dang /
NK133(po)003:2345: dri med zhing skyong slob ma gnyag dz+ny+aa na ku ma ra /
NK133(po)003:2346: sgro phug pa ye shes rgyal mtshan /
NK133(po)003:2348: rig 'dzin tshe dbang nor bu sogs kyi rnam 'phrul
NK133(po)003:2349: ma h+aa pan+di ta 'gyur med tshe dbang mchog grub
NK133(po)003:2351: rmog grub nam mkha' chos dbang dang /
NK133(po)003:2352: sbra 'go brtson 'grus rgya mtsho'i sprul rgyud phyag tsha /
NK133(po)003:2353: kam tshang si tu chos kyi 'byung gnas kyi rnam 'phrul 'jigs med chos kyi seng ge /
NK133(po)003:2355: kun mkhyen chos kyi rgya mtsho rnams mkhas shing grub
NK133(po)003:2356: pa'i rnam thar 'khor lo gsum gyi mdzad bzang bstan
NK133(po)003:2357: 'dzin thog mnyam sus kyang 'gran du med pa'i ngo
NK133(po)003:2358: mtshar rmad du byung ba'i phrin las kyis rgyal bstan
NK133(po)003:2359: spyi dang snga 'gyur bka' gter gyi bstan pa nyin
NK133(po)003:2360: mo'i dpal bzhin gsal bar mdzad pa yin no //
NK133(po)003:2361: chos rgyud 'dzin pa'i dgon lag mdo khams shar phyogs kun tu mang zhing /
NK133(po)003:2362: deng sang nyag rong d+ha ki dgon dang /
NK133(po)003:2363: dge rtse gra lag tu dge 'dun stong phrag tsam dang /
NK133(po)003:2364: gzhi chen stag rtse rnams la sum brgya /
NK133(po)003:2365: rag khrom lnga brgya sogs 'gu gser rgya rong 'jang
NK133(po)003:2366: yul sogs su si tu rin po ches dgon ma
NK133(po)003:2367: lag thams cad la phyag 'gyed stsal skabs dge 'dun
NK133(po)003:2368: nyi khri lnga stong byung bar snang ngo //
NK133(po)003:2369: grub dbang dpal yul ba ni chos mdzod 'di bzhengs
NK133(po)003:2370: pa'i rnam thar dang 'brel bas cung zhig gsal bar
NK133(po)003:2371: brjod pa la gdan sa 'di'i thog ma /
NK133(po)003:2372: rje rig 'dzin kun bzang shes rab ni gdod ma
NK133(po)003:2373: nyid nas rgyal kun ye shes rang gzugs dpal ldan
NK133(po)003:2374: rdo rje sems dpa' nyid gang 'dul ye shes kyi
NK133(po)003:2375: rol pa mtha' klas kyang snang tshul phyogs gcig gi
NK133(po)003:2376: dbang du na bdag cag gi ston pa'i spyan sngar
NK133(po)003:2378: mgon po spyi tshogs kyi rnam 'phrul dge bsnyen d+h+aarma t+aa /
NK133(po)003:2379: rdzogs chen ston pa dga' rab rdo rje dang sh+r+ai seng+ha /
NK133(po)003:2381: rgyal po in+d+ra bo d+hi phyi ma /
NK133(po)003:2382: rgya nag gi ha shang grub pa brnyes pa /
NK133(po)003:2383: pad+ma'i spyan sngar bod yul rab byung gi thog ma
NK133(po)003:2384: sad mi mi bdun gyi ya gyal la sum rgyal
NK133(po)003:2385: ba byang chub bam gnas brtan dge 'dun bzang po
NK133(po)003:2386: / +aar+ya sa le'i skye ba phyi ma chos blo mgon /
NK133(po)003:2390: stag lung thang pa bkra shis dpal /
NK133(po)003:2391: grub thob thang stong rgyal po /
NK133(po)003:2393: dol po shes rab rgyal mtshan sogs 'gro ba'i mgon
NK133(po)003:2394: po du ma'i rnam 'phrul rim dang cig char du
NK133(po)003:2395: ston pa las / khyad par dgongs 'dus lung bstan bka' rgya ma las /
NK133(po)003:2396: da lta'i gnas brtan dge 'dun bzang po 'di rje
NK133(po)003:2397: yi thugs rje thugs dam gsang mdzod mnga' dgongs pa
NK133(po)003:2398: klong gcig dgongs 'dus spel don du pradz+ny+aa'i mtshan can
NK133(po)003:2399: zab don bka' la spyod gdul bya'i zhing khams mtha'
NK133(po)003:2400: yas 'khor slob bskyang sbas tshul gdangs gsal thugs rje
NK133(po)003:2401: mkha' ltar khyab dgongs 'dus sgrom 'dzin lha sras che
NK133(po)003:2402: ba 'don bstan pa'i rgyun spel zhal tshab gnyis pa
NK133(po)003:2403: yin phrin las skyong zhing mnga' bdag rgyal po 'di'i
NK133(po)003:2404: lo pan mthar phyung las kyi lhag ma rnams smon
NK133(po)003:2405: lam mthu btsan dge 'dun bzang pos sdud las kyi
NK133(po)003:2406: mtha' stong rje yi thugs kar thim de bzhin thugs
NK133(po)003:2407: rje sprul pa mang po 'gyed zhes pas mtshan dang
NK133(po)003:2408: mdzad spyod gsung gdangs gzeng mtho ba phrin las skyong
NK133(po)003:2409: tshul sogs gsal bar bstan pa dang /
NK133(po)003:2410: gnam chos chos bdag lung bstan du /
NK133(po)003:2411: 'di nas shar ram lho yi phyogs chags med tshul
NK133(po)003:2412: khrims bzang gi ming ltag par sme bas brgyan pa
NK133(po)003:2413: 'byung las can de la chos 'di gtod zhes dang
NK133(po)003:2414: gter chen klong gsal snying po'i rab 'bar lung las
NK133(po)003:2415: / seng ge rnam gsum shes rab rnam gsum dang zhes rtsa ba'i chos bdag du bstan pa dang /
NK133(po)003:2416: pad+ma bde chen gling pa'i klong gsal d+aak+k+ai'i snying thig las /
NK133(po)003:2417: chos blo mgon sprul kahthoga nub phyogs nas kun bzang
NK133(po)003:2418: ming can byang sems zhi dul can sgrub rgyud bstan
NK133(po)003:2419: pa dgung la reg par byed zhes pa sogs gter
NK133(po)003:2420: kha gsar rnying mang po nas gsal bar bstan pa
NK133(po)003:2421: ltar 'khrungs yul mdo khams bu 'bor rgang ngam zal
NK133(po)003:2422: mo sgang las dpal yul a 'phyogs nas gro ltas
NK133(po)003:2423: zhes par sga yi rigs las sngon kahthoga drung ston
NK133(po)003:2424: pa dam pa dbang 'byor sogs dam pa du ma
NK133(po)003:2425: byon pa'i gdung rigs yab rdo rje dang /
NK133(po)003:2426: yum gu ru mtsho las rab byung bcu gcig pa'i
NK133(po)003:2427: me pho byi ba la sku ltams dam pa'i rigs
NK133(po)003:2428: sad cing dpal phyag na rdo rje'i rnam 'phrul sga
NK133(po)003:2429: rje chos skyong rgya mtsho la gtsug phud phul te
NK133(po)003:2430: mtshan tshul khrims rgya mtsho gsol /
NK133(po)003:2431: phyag chen dang mi tra khrid drug sogs zab chos mang du gsan /
NK133(po)003:2432: dpal 'bar re khe dgon du drung pa chos nyid
NK133(po)003:2433: rgya mtsho'i mdun lo lnga bzhugs nas tshe sgrub gsang
NK133(po)003:2434: 'dus / rig 'dzin yongs 'dus smar tshang chos skor
NK133(po)003:2435: dang phyag chen lhan cig skyes sbyor gyi zab khrid
NK133(po)003:2436: 'dus / nos so // chos rje pad+ma blo gros mdun nas dbang bka' tsam dang /
NK133(po)003:2437: khyad par stag bla dang drung pa zung gi slob
NK133(po)003:2438: ma rgya ban dkon mchog bkra shis las rgyud bcu
NK133(po)003:2439: bdun sogs rgyud 'bum phal cher dang /
NK133(po)003:2440: stag bla nas brgyud pa'i gsang snying kun mkhyen 'grel pa dang klong chen mdzod bdun /
NK133(po)003:2442: yang tig yid bzhin nor bu dung mtsho ras pa'i yang ti /
NK133(po)003:2444: bka' brgyad bde gshegs 'dus chen sogs bka' chos shin tu mang ba dang /
NK133(po)003:2445: rong po ba rin chen rdo rje las dgongs 'dus
NK133(po)003:2446: dang khams lugs 'dus pa mdo dbang chen mo tshar
NK133(po)003:2447: gcig sogs kahthoga snga rab pa'i brgyud pa zin nges
NK133(po)003:2448: pa'i dbang lung mang po dang /
NK133(po)003:2449: gter ston so so nas stag bla bar 'phel ba'i
NK133(po)003:2450: smin grol chog phrin phyag bzhes phra zhib nas slob
NK133(po)003:2451: pa'i bla ma 'di gnyis bka' drin che gsung /
NK133(po)003:2452: drung pas bskang gsol sogs kyi dbu mdzad bskos te gsung gdangs shin tu mtho ba'i grags pa'ang byung /
NK133(po)003:2453: thugs nges 'byung gis 'dir snang ba sna btsan thabs su bstung /
NK133(po)003:2454: gdams ngag gi zhun mthar bcad nas nyin mtshan bar
NK133(po)003:2455: med brtson pa las 'tsho chas kyi 'bad rtsol mi
NK133(po)003:2456: mdzad de 'bru khal res lo re'i 'tsho ba 'ong
NK133(po)003:2457: bar mdzad de dus phal cher rdo dang ldum bu'i
NK133(po)003:2459: spyir yang dam pa 'di nyid ma chags 'phags pa'i
NK133(po)003:2460: rigs la gnas pas sku tshe stod la gang byung
NK133(po)003:2461: des chog bcud len sogs dang phyis nas tshe mtshams
NK133(po)003:2462: kyi dam bca' bzhes te 'bul sdud grong chog sogs
NK133(po)003:2463: sku tshe der gtan nas ma mdzad /
NK133(po)003:2464: bar khyim chos 'byung gling du bla ma dam pa
NK133(po)003:2465: dpal mo ba shes rab rgya mtsho las grub brgya'i
NK133(po)003:2466: rjes gnang / rjes gnang brgya rtsa /
NK133(po)003:2467: rat+na'i thugs sgrub sogs chos bka' mang po dang /
NK133(po)003:2469: dgongs 'dus sgrub dbang rgyas pa 'brug pa dkon rgyal sogs las mdo mang dang sher phyin skor /
NK133(po)003:2470: bka' gdams dang 'brug pa'i chos skor dang /
NK133(po)003:2471: rmugs sang nyi ma rgyal mtshan las 'ja' tshon chos skor dang /
NK133(po)003:2473: gzhan yang rma gnyan yon tan rgya mtsho /
NK133(po)003:2475: rgya ra nam mkha' rin chen /
NK133(po)003:2476: sde dge grub thob kun dga' rgya mtsho sogs dge ba'i bshes gnyen mang po las /
NK133(po)003:2480: sbyor drug bsnyen sgrub sogs gsar rnying gi dbang bka'
NK133(po)003:2481: ma gsan pa med pa lta bu gsan yig pusti
NK133(po)003:2482: gnyis yod pa las gsal ba ltar dang /
NK133(po)003:2483: de dag nyams su bzhes pa'i tshe sgrub gnas ri
NK133(po)003:2484: khrod rnams su sgrub pa'i dam bca' ma thel bar
NK133(po)003:2486: bzhugs khri'i mtha' skor tsher ma 'dzug pa dang /
NK133(po)003:2487: dbu skra'i gtsug phud sgrub khang gi klad la 'dogs
NK133(po)003:2488: pa sogs brtson 'grus dang bka' spyad bsam gyis mi
NK133(po)003:2489: khyab pas nyams myong drod tshad thob cing lam rtags
NK133(po)003:2490: kyi yon tan rnams tshul bzhin theb par mdzad /
NK133(po)003:2491: de nas dben gnas shugs 'gags dgon du dpal sa
NK133(po)003:2492: ra ha'i rnam 'phrul 'khrul zhig ston pa rgyal mtshan
NK133(po)003:2494: rje des kyang bla mas lung bstan phyir dgyes pas rjes su bzung /
NK133(po)003:2495: bla ma gong ma rnams kyi bka' 'bum mang zhig dang /
NK133(po)003:2497: kar gling zhi khro sogs dang /
NK133(po)003:2498: khyad par 'dus pa mdo dbang chen mo rtsa ba yan lag dang bcas pa /
NK133(po)003:2500: sems sde dang bcas pa'i smin lam rgyas pa yun
NK133(po)003:2501: ring bar bstsal gsang mtshan thugs mchog drag po rtsal
NK133(po)003:2502: gsol / rdzogs chen dgongs pa zang thal gyi smin khrid rgyas par bstsal /
NK133(po)003:2503: 'di skor 'tsho ba phal cher cong zhi'i bcud len la brten /
NK133(po)003:2504: thugs dgongs chos skur ngo sprod pa'i rigs bdag thun min 'khrul zhig dam pa 'di nyid yin gsungs /
NK133(po)003:2505: slar dbus phyogs phebs bzhed kyis ngom stod du phyin
NK133(po)003:2506: par rig 'dzin mi 'gyur rdo rje'i zhal mjal ba
NK133(po)003:2507: tsam gyis mos gus bsam gyis mi khyab par 'khrungs
NK133(po)003:2508: / rad gling bdud 'dul mkha' 'gro snying thig rnams kyi dbang lung rdzogs par nos so //
NK133(po)003:2509: rje 'di dang slob ma gzhan gcig bcas la shing
NK133(po)003:2510: sgrom stong pa re dam 'byar ba brtsal ba sngas
NK133(po)003:2511: su gsol ba btab pas 'di'i sgam nang man shel
NK133(po)003:2512: rang byung sgo bzhi pa'i dbus su 'od lnga'i thig
NK133(po)003:2513: le gsal ba zhig dngos su babs pas gter ston
NK133(po)003:2514: gyi ngo sprod stsal zhing gnam chos chos bdag tu
NK133(po)003:2515: zhal gyis bzhes nas chos skor yongs rdzogs dang rdzogs
NK133(po)003:2516: chen zab khrid zhib rgyas bstsal /
NK133(po)003:2517: nyid kyis gzim spang ste nyam len dang /
NK133(po)003:2518: gter ston nyid o rgyan rdo rje 'chang dngos kyi thugs 'dun rgyun mi chad pa dang /
NK133(po)003:2519: thugs rgyud la ka dag gi rig pa dmar thag
NK133(po)003:2520: chod cing lhun grub snang bzhi'i ye shes tshad du
NK133(po)003:2521: phyin pa byung / gnas mdo grub brnyes rig 'dzin
NK133(po)003:2522: rgya mtsho'i myes po mkhas grub karma chags med mdun
NK133(po)003:2523: nas dge tshul gyi bslab tshig bzhes shing kar lugs
NK133(po)003:2524: dang rat+na'i chos skor gtso bor gyur pa'i gsar rnying
NK133(po)003:2525: gi smin grol rgya matsho'o lta bu nos so //
NK133(po)003:2526: khyad par gnas chos khrid yig gsar bskrun rnams smin khrid du bstsal /
NK133(po)003:2527: 'di'i ngo sprod mdzad tshe rdzogs pa chen po'i rgyud
NK133(po)003:2528: 'bum phrag drug cu'i don thugs la bkra lam gyis
NK133(po)003:2529: shar / skye phreng gong du bstan pas mtshon skyes
NK133(po)003:2530: rab stong phrag gcig nyis tsam yang skad cig re
NK133(po)003:2531: la gsal bar dran pa sogs sa lam mthon por
NK133(po)003:2532: gshegs pa'i mngon rtogs gsal bar shar /
NK133(po)003:2533: pa bla sangs rgyas rdo rje las gong ra nas brgyud pa'i mdo sde za ma tog /
NK133(po)003:2535: rnying ma rgyud 'bum yongs rdzogs sogs phyogs kyi dge
NK133(po)003:2536: ba'i bshes rnams zhar la brten nas chos bka' mang
NK133(po)003:2537: po gsan / 'di skabs chos rgyal sde dge'i mnga'
NK133(po)003:2538: thang yar 'phel skabs dang 'grigs pas sa skyong byams
NK133(po)003:2539: pa phun tshogs khu dbon nas dam pa mang po'i
NK133(po)003:2540: bka' lung bzhin dpal yul du rgya sdong ston pa
NK133(po)003:2541: seng ge'i gra tshang bar lce sogs 'bri rgyud kyi
NK133(po)003:2542: dge 'dun phal cher bsdus pa'i slob dpon 'khrul zhig
NK133(po)003:2544: rig 'dzin mi 'gyur rdo rje gnyis nas rje 'di
NK133(po)003:2545: phebs dgos pa nan bskyal dang bcas gdam ngag tshang
NK133(po)003:2546: sprugs su stsal zhing bstan pa'i bab gtad rgya dang
NK133(po)003:2547: bcas gdul bya skyong bar nges don gyi rdo rje
NK133(po)003:2548: slob dpon du mnga' gsol zhing bskul te dgung grangs
NK133(po)003:2549: sum cu bzhes pa shing sbrul lor dpal yul gdan
NK133(po)003:2550: sar phebs / der gzhi so thar khrims kyis sdom
NK133(po)003:2551: pa'i lam nyams len snga 'gyur bka' gter bskyed rdzogs
NK133(po)003:2552: spyi dang khyad par rdzogs pa chen po'i nyams len
NK133(po)003:2553: 'ba' zhig la dril ba'i srol btsugs /
NK133(po)003:2554: 'khor lo gsum gyi phrin las dbyar mtsho ltar rgyas /
NK133(po)003:2555: gter ston rig 'dzin chen por phyag rdzas spang dag phul /
NK133(po)003:2556: slar gnas mdo rje chags med rin po che'i mdun phebs /
NK133(po)003:2562: gter bdag gling pa'i thugs thig tshe sgrub rtsal rat+na'i thugs gsang /
NK133(po)003:2563: sku gsum sgrub pa sogs kyi phyag len zhib khrid dang /
NK133(po)003:2564: rat+na'i bka' babs su lung gis zin 'dug pas chos 'di'i 'gro don 'ong ste mchi gsungs /
NK133(po)003:2565: rje nyid kyi gsung chos kyang phal cher nos so //
NK133(po)003:2566: slar la gur drag ye shes rab 'bar dbang lung phul /
NK133(po)003:2567: gter ston bdud 'dul rdo rje mjal bzhed kyis ri
NK133(po)003:2568: bo che dang lho rdzong bar phebs kyang phyogs der
NK133(po)003:2569: 'khrugs zing gis bkag par dngos 'bul bskyal mkhan bardzangasa
NK133(po)003:2570: nas phyir phebs pa'i ngom chu'i rdzing 'di'i phyag gis
NK133(po)003:2571: grwa pa gnyis bzung ste skyil krung bcas sku stod
NK133(po)003:2572: la rlan gyis ma gos par phebs pas phyogs der
NK133(po)003:2573: dad 'dun 'ur / slar rig 'dzin thugs rje'i dbang
NK133(po)003:2574: phyug de nyid kyi drung nas bsnyen par rdzogs sngon
NK133(po)003:2575: dge tshul gyi skabs su mtshan kun bzang shes rab
NK133(po)003:2576: la rig 'dzin dbu brgyan te rig 'dzin kun bzang
NK133(po)003:2578: rgyal mtshan gyis brgyan pa'i khri la bkod de rje
NK133(po)003:2579: karma pa'i dbu zhwa chos gos bcas ston pa'i rgyal
NK133(po)003:2581: rje 'dis sngon rang gi sgrub pa mdzad pa'i dus
NK133(po)003:2582: nas phyis su slob ma bskyang ba'i dus sogs 'dul
NK133(po)003:2583: ba'i srung sdom don thog tu khel ba'i phyag len
NK133(po)003:2584: bstar bas slob tshogs kyang rab byung rdo rje 'dzin
NK133(po)003:2585: pa kho na las btsun ma dang mi nag gi
NK133(po)003:2586: 'khor slob med pas brgyud 'dzin dge 'dun sde 'phel
NK133(po)003:2587: zhing thams cad kyang dgon gtsang kho na byung /
NK133(po)003:2588: dgung grangs so lnga bzhes pa nas ji srid 'tsho'i bar tshe mtshams kyi dam bca' gzhes /
NK133(po)003:2589: bdud 'dul rdo rje'i drung nas grwa pa 'byor bar
NK133(po)003:2590: gter rdzas khyad 'phags 'ga' dang zhal 'don rgyu'i smon
NK133(po)003:2592: gter ston klong gsal snying po slar sgrub sder phebs /
NK133(po)003:2595: gter rdzas shog ser dang gsang ye'i sku sogs brtsal
NK133(po)003:2596: ba da lta gdung rten mchod sdong du bzhugs phyag
NK133(po)003:2597: rtse sprod du gnang zhing bstan pa 'dzin skyong gal
NK133(po)003:2598: che tshul sogs thun min gyi gsung 'phros du ma
NK133(po)003:2599: mdzad / grub dbang rdzogs chen pa pad+ma rig 'dzin
NK133(po)003:2600: phebs nas thugs nang gcig 'dres kyi chos bka' gsan
NK133(po)003:2601: res dang dpal rdzogs gnyis bstan pa gcig dril gyi
NK133(po)003:2602: mdzad / bka' mol gnang / nyid rang tshe mtshams
NK133(po)003:2603: kyi dam bcas gzhan du ma phebs kyang rmugs sangs
NK133(po)003:2604: nas karma bstan 'dzin sogs smin grol gling du dbang
NK133(po)003:2605: lung zhu phyir mngag nas gter chen sku mched kyi
NK133(po)003:2606: bka' ma'i chos skor sogs bzhengs pa'i phyag dpe da
NK133(po)003:2607: lta'ang snang gdul byar gyur pa'i skye bo phal pa
NK133(po)003:2610: yig drug bzlas lung sogs kyis rjes su bzung /
NK133(po)003:2611: yul phyogs thams cad ri klung rngon rgya sdom pa dang /
NK133(po)003:2612: rim gro sogs kyi phyir sems can srog gcod pa'i rgyun bcad pa dang /
NK133(po)003:2613: dge 'dun la chang khrims dam por tshugs pa sogs sa phyogs dkar por btang /
NK133(po)003:2614: rgyun du dge sbyor srang 'jug gis dge sbyor khrigs
NK133(po)003:2615: bcad kyis ma tshan gung thun re tsam las gzim
NK133(po)003:2616: par mi mdzad / 'tsho ba gdan gcig kho na
NK133(po)003:2617: dag bshos 'bul mdo gsungs pa dang snga dgong thod
NK133(po)003:2618: rgal dang gtum mo sogs nyin gcig bzhin /
NK133(po)003:2619: bka' gter gsar rnying gi rtsa gsum rnams res kyis bskor nas gsungs /
NK133(po)003:2620: nya stong gso sbyong dang dus mchod rnams yang chag 'phri med pa dang /
NK133(po)003:2621: myos 'gyur gyi rigs ni nye phyogs su yang khyer du med par bkag /
NK133(po)003:2622: sha yang tshogs rdzas phra mo las mi bzhes /
NK133(po)003:2623: sku shin tu btsun zhing kha na ma tho ba cung zad kyang gos pa med gshis /
NK133(po)003:2624: sku 'khor rnams kyang thugs dul zhing btsun pa dge sbyor 'grub pa sogs kyi khyad chos ldan /
NK133(po)003:2625: mdo khams stod smad nas rgya yul yan gyi slob
NK133(po)003:2626: tshogs bgrangs las 'das pa 'dus pa la dbang khrid
NK133(po)003:2627: lung gsum gyi chos 'khor rgyun mi chad pa dang
NK133(po)003:2628: / khrid rim rnams smin khrid kho nar gnang /
NK133(po)003:2629: rgyun par snga dro gsung ngag sdom zhing dgong mo'i
NK133(po)003:2630: thun mtshams nas yol ba phyi nang gis slob mar
NK133(po)003:2631: khrid dang dog gcod mtshan gung bar mdzad /
NK133(po)003:2632: dad 'bul gang byung de 'phral dge 'dun la bsnyen bskur sogs tshogs gsogs la btang zhing /
NK133(po)003:2633: slob ma sgom sgrub nus kyang 'tsho ba dkon pa rnams la'ang ci rigs stsal /
NK133(po)003:2634: dud 'gro'i rigs ni tshe thar kho na btang ba dang /
NK133(po)003:2635: khyad par mdzo g.yag rnams khal 'gel ba sogs kyi
NK133(po)003:2636: duhkha skyob phyir mgon g.yag la dmigs pas ri la
NK133(po)003:2637: gtod pa grangs mang ba byung /
NK133(po)003:2638: sgrub chen sman sgrub bum sgrub mang po dang /
NK133(po)003:2639: gzhan bskul sogs mchod rten ka ni ka mang po dang /
NK133(po)003:2641: btags grol gyi rigs mang po bsgrub pa sogs mthong thos dran reg smin grol la bkod /
NK133(po)003:2642: gzhan sems mkhyen pa dang 'byung 'gyur gzigs pa la sgrib thogs med /
NK133(po)003:2643: brag ngos la zhabs rjes gsal ba dang chos sder
NK133(po)003:2644: bzhugs nas nye bar ye shes kyi mgon po'i sku
NK133(po)003:2645: gnam sa gang ba gzigs pa dang /
NK133(po)003:2646: dgongs 'dus sman sgrub skabs pad+ma badz+ra sogs dkyil 'khor lha tshogs zhal gzigs pa dang /
NK133(po)003:2647: a ru ra myu gu las gsar du 'khrungs pa'i
NK133(po)003:2648: dri ngad can byung ba dang nyin lam tsam gyi
NK133(po)003:2649: bar sman dri bzang po chang lang ba ltar 'thul
NK133(po)003:2650: ba dang / rten gsum rab gnas mdzad skabs mi
NK133(po)003:2651: 'gyur rdo rje dbyings na bzhugs pas spro nyams kyis
NK133(po)003:2652: sku dang yig 'bru phyag mtshan bsam gyis mi khyab
NK133(po)003:2653: pa rten la thim pa gzigs /
NK133(po)003:2654: rat+na'i thugs sgrub sgo nas sman sgrub mdzad skabs me
NK133(po)003:2655: tog gi char babs pa dang zla zer las 'ja'
NK133(po)003:2656: 'od dkar po sum rim gyis sgrub dkyil bskor ba
NK133(po)003:2658: bdud rtsi chu tshan ltar sgra dang bcas khol zhing lud pa dang /
NK133(po)003:2659: bka' brgyad bder 'dus dbang sgrub skabs bskyed rim gyad
NK133(po)003:2660: du gyur pas sgrub khang du dpal dgu'i lha tshogs
NK133(po)003:2661: bkra lam mer snang ba slob mas mthong ba dang
NK133(po)003:2662: / rat+na'i thugs gsang bum sgrub tshe ril bu 'phel
NK133(po)003:2663: zhing 'phur ba sgrub khang la 'aja'i ka ba zug
NK133(po)003:2664: / pa / gtsug lag chos grwa dang bcas phyi rol tshun dri bzang gis khyab pa dang /
NK133(po)003:2665: gtsug lag khang dang rten gsum bzhengs pa bstan pa
NK133(po)003:2666: spel ba'i bya ba rnams kha na ma tho med
NK133(po)003:2667: cing rnam par dag pa dang /
NK133(po)003:2668: srog chags grogs sbur gyis gser rdog sran chung tsam
NK133(po)003:2669: rten khrod du dor ba sogs ngo mtshar ba mang
NK133(po)003:2670: po yod / der 'du long che bas thugs sun
NK133(po)003:2671: nas 'bros thabs kyis dben pa zhig tu sems par
NK133(po)003:2672: rig 'dzin dga' rab rdo rjes byin gyis rlabs pa'i
NK133(po)003:2673: gnas yin 'dug gsung ste 'od gsal snying po'i nyams
NK133(po)003:2674: len 'ba' zhig la dril ba'i bya btang gi slob
NK133(po)003:2675: tshogs mang du 'dus par lha ri 'od gsal sgang
NK133(po)003:2676: po yod / zhes grags / yongs grags gter kha
NK133(po)003:2677: chen po rnams byin rlabs kyi tshan kha slar la
NK133(po)003:2678: 'bar bas drod rtags gsal ba mngon sum tshad mas
NK133(po)003:2679: po yod / zhes grags / grub pa byung /
NK133(po)003:2680: rje nyid kyi drung nas bsnyen par rdzogs pa stong
NK133(po)003:2682: dge bsnyen dge tshul dang sdom pa phog pa bgrang gis mi chod /
NK133(po)003:2683: zab khrid mnos pa'i slob ma brjod kyis mi lang /
NK133(po)003:2684: de dag phal mo che tshe dang sgrub pa mnyam pa dang /
NK133(po)003:2685: rtogs pa'i rtsal rdzogs shing skye ba snga phyi'i gnas dran pa /
NK133(po)003:2686: dgongs pas gzhan rgyud byin gyis rlabs shing don gnyis
NK133(po)003:2687: spyod pa mkhyen rtogs gnyis ldan gyis bstan pa la
NK133(po)003:2688: bya ba byed nus pa 'gro phan bsam gyis mi
NK133(po)003:2689: khyab pa mang po byung bas sgrub sde ri khrod
NK133(po)003:2690: gsar 'debs mdzad pa brgya phrag tsam byung ba dang
NK133(po)003:2691: / sngon chad chos kyi sgra ma grags pa'i rgya
NK133(po)003:2692: nag gi yul gru 'gar yang mdo sngags kyi bstan
NK133(po)003:2693: pa gtsug lag bcas mang zhig byung /
NK133(po)003:2694: chos brgyud thams cad kyis spyod pa 'dul khrims dang
NK133(po)003:2695: lta ba rdzogs chen la gtso bor byed pa sha
NK133(po)003:2696: stag yin / snga 'gyur rdo rje theg pa'i ring
NK133(po)003:2697: lugs sngon zur pa khu dbon sogs kyis phrin las
NK133(po)003:2698: rgyas pa byung kyang dus dbang gis rim gyis bri
NK133(po)003:2699: nas phyis ser khyim sngags ming ma stong tsam las
NK133(po)003:2701: dam pa rnams kyi thugs rjes ma bzod nas /
NK133(po)003:2702: rdor smin kahrdzogasa gong sa lnga pa sogs kyis rnying bstan spel ba'i phrim las mdzad mod /
NK133(po)003:2703: de las kyang dam pa 'di nyid kyi phrin las
NK133(po)003:2704: 'bad med lhun grub lta bu rgyas shing sku tshe
NK133(po)003:2705: der chos sde gsar 'debs brgya phrag dang /
NK133(po)003:2706: rjes nas je rgyas su gyur te rgya bod hor
NK133(po)003:2707: gsum du je 'phel gyur pa thams cad grangs chod
NK133(po)003:2708: dka' yang dgon sde che phra nyis brgya nye tsam
NK133(po)003:2709: yod par rgyus yod nas bshad /
NK133(po)003:2710: rdor smin dpal gsum sogs snga 'gyur gyi mkhas grub
NK133(po)003:2711: chen po rnams kyis bka' gter zab don legs bshad
NK133(po)003:2712: gter sgo phyes pa rnams kyang rtsig ngos la brten
NK133(po)003:2713: nas ri mo bya ba bzhin phrin las rgyas pa'i
NK133(po)003:2714: yul ni mkhas grub karma chags med dang dam pa
NK133(po)003:2715: 'di nyid kyi thugs bskyed smon lam stobs kyis bstan
NK133(po)003:2716: pa'i gzhi rgya cher tshug pa la brten nas rgyas
NK133(po)003:2717: par 'dug la / mdor na rgyal bstan spyi dang
NK133(po)003:2718: gu ru pad+ma'i ring lugs mdo sgyu sems gsum sogs
NK133(po)003:2720: bka' dgongs sogs gter chos gnad che ba rnams khyab
NK133(po)003:2721: gdal du spel ba la dam pa 'di nyid phyag
NK133(po)003:2722: rjes ches che bar snang ngo //
NK133(po)003:2723: thugs sras kyi gtso bo pad+ma lhun grub rgya mtsho /
NK133(po)003:2724: rdo rje kun bzang rgya mtsho sogs dang /
NK133(po)003:2726: gser pa ye shes seng ge /
NK133(po)003:2729: gtsang mda' rdo rje thal rnams re re las kyang
NK133(po)003:2730: dbon brgyud slob brgyud dzar tshag tu byon pas chos
NK133(po)003:2732: gzhan yang seng ge'i mtshan can gsum sogs phrin las rgya che ba byung /
NK133(po)003:2733: de ltar mdzad mthar phyin nas dus mkhyen pa'i gsung mang po dang /
NK133(po)003:2734: khyad par lan cig kho bo'i rjes 'jug khrod nas
NK133(po)003:2735: bya btang ts+aa ri sogs ri khrod thub pa re
NK133(po)003:2736: gnyis phyin pa las rdzogs chen gyi 'chi lugs rnams
NK133(po)003:2738: 'od lus grub pa'ang 'ga' re byung bar mngon no //
NK133(po)003:2739: pad+ma lhun grub rgya mtsho la khyod kyis kho bo'i dus bzhin bstan pa skyong dang /
NK133(po)003:2740: dga' rab yangs shing ded rang nam yang mjal ba
NK133(po)003:2741: yin da nam mkha' nas shel gyi skas chen po
NK133(po)003:2742: zhig gtsug snang bud med mchod rdzas khyer ba 'ga'
NK133(po)003:2743: dang stag dang seng ge la chibs pa 'gyings bag
NK133(po)003:2745: de nas gsung ci yang ma 'byon par dgung lo
NK133(po)003:2746: drug cu re bzhis yos lo rnam thar spar mar
NK133(po)003:2747: dgung grangs re gsum sa stag gsung kyang /
NK133(po)003:2748: rtsis gzhung yong 'du'i snye mar dgung grangs re bzhi
NK133(po)003:2749: sa yos lor gshegs zhes 'dug pa de nges pa
NK133(po)003:2750: yin pa'i rgyu mtshan sa stag zla 7tshes la gzhi
NK133(po)003:2751: bdag la phrin bcol mdzad pa des gsal /
NK133(po)003:2752: mchan hor zla dang po'i tshes lnga nyin gung la gzugs sku'i bkod pa bsdus /
NK133(po)003:2753: de nas sa gzhi la drod phebs pa dang /
NK133(po)003:2754: myu gu me tog 'ga' yang bkra /
NK133(po)003:2755: thugs sras rnams gtsos dge 'dun sum stong lhag tsam
NK133(po)003:2756: gyis mchod 'bul rgya cher dang gsol 'debs byed pa
NK133(po)003:2757: slob tshogs rnams 'od gsal 'khor yug 'dres pa sogs
NK133(po)003:2758: nyam rtogs 'phel skyed khyad par can byung /
NK133(po)003:2759: sku gdung zhugs 'bul skabs nam mkha' dwangs par 'ja' sprin gyis khyab pa dang /
NK133(po)003:2760: yig 'bru ring bsrel mang du byung /
NK133(po)003:2761: slob chen rnams la dngos nyams rmi lam du zhal
NK133(po)003:2762: mjal dbang bskur lung bstan bar chad sel ba byin
NK133(po)003:2763: rlabs rtogs pa spar ba sogs shin tu mang bar
NK133(po)003:2764: byung ngo // gdan rab gnyis pa pad+ma lhun grub rgya mtsho ni /
NK133(po)003:2765: bdud 'dul phur pa'i lung bstan las /
NK133(po)003:2766: lha dpal sprul pa thugs kyi sme ba can mdo
NK133(po)003:2767: khams shar nas rgyal gyi ming can 'byung zhes pa
NK133(po)003:2768: ltar sog po lha dpal gyi rnam 'phrul te rje
NK133(po)003:2769: 'di nyid byis pa'i dus su mgon rgyal bya ba
NK133(po)003:2770: dang / thugs ka'i sme ba sogs 'gyur ba med /
NK133(po)003:2771: rgya nag ra ba'i brgyud pa rig 'dzin grub thob
NK133(po)003:2772: bar ma chad par byon pa'i gdung rigs yul seng
NK133(po)003:2773: rgang du rga rje rgya ra bya bar lcags byi
NK133(po)003:2774: la 'khrungs / dgung lo brgyad nas 'bri klog sogs tshegs med par mkhyen /
NK133(po)003:2775: gter ston mi 'gyur rdo rje'i mdun nas gnam chos gtad rgya bcas nos so //
NK133(po)003:2776: bcu drug la dpal yul kun bzang shes rab mdun phebs /
NK133(po)003:2777: bka' lung chos kyi char phabs zab khrid nos brtson
NK133(po)003:2778: 'grus drag pos bsgom pas zhi gnas brtan cha thob
NK133(po)003:2779: cing bde gsal mi rtog pa'i ngang rtse gcig gnas
NK133(po)003:2780: pa byung / bcu dgu lor rig 'dzin kun bzang
NK133(po)003:2781: shes rab kyis mkhan po las slob bkra shis tshe
NK133(po)003:2782: brtan sogs dad pa'i dge 'dun grangs tshang ba las
NK133(po)003:2783: pa byung / bsnyen par rdzogs / sku btsun pa'ii mchog tu gyur /
NK133(po)003:2785: bar khyim shes rab rgya mtsho sogs yongs 'dzin nyer lnga tsam la brten nas /
NK133(po)003:2786: mdo mang sher phyin skor bka' 'gyur phal cher dang /
NK133(po)003:2798: gnam chos sogs gter chos phal mo che dang /
NK133(po)003:2799: ke 'dun klong chen pa'i chos skor /
NK133(po)003:2801: chags med gsung sogs chos bka' dpag med gsan /
NK133(po)003:2802: thos pa rnams bsam byung gis sgro 'dogs chod par mdzad /
NK133(po)003:2803: nyer gcig par las 'phro dang bla ma'i byin rlabs
NK133(po)003:2804: stobs kyis tshogs brgyad 'khrul pa'i dri mas ma gos
NK133(po)003:2805: pa'i rig stong rtsol bral gyi rang ngo mthong /
NK133(po)003:2806: rtsa rlung dang thod rgal gyi khrid nos so //
NK133(po)003:2807: mi 'gul ba gsum gyis gzhi bca' ba dang /
NK133(po)003:2808: thob pa gsum gyis gzer 'debs pa'i lta stangs la rgyun ldan du gnas /
NK133(po)003:2809: dka' spyad dang brtson 'grus 'gran zla bral bar mdzad pas snang ba'i 'phel tshad mthar phyin /
NK133(po)003:2810: 'khor yug kun tu tshogs drug rang grol bde stong spros bral chen po mngon du gyur /
NK133(po)003:2811: dgung lo nyer lnga nas snang srid 'khor 'das sogs
NK133(po)003:2812: gnyis snang thams cad mnyam nyid ro gcig pa'i rtogs
NK133(po)003:2813: pa 'khrungs / so lngar bla mas thod rgal /
NK133(po)003:2816: zhing khams lnga sbyong khrid sogs zab gnad brgyud gab sbas med par brtsal /
NK133(po)003:2817: gdul bya la nges don gyi khrid 'chad pa'i gtad rgya dang rdo rje slob dpon du mnga' gsol /
NK133(po)003:2818: so brgyad la 'phags pa'i gnas brtan gyi sprul par
NK133(po)003:2819: lung bstan cing so thar gyi sdom pa'i mkhan por
NK133(po)003:2820: mnga' gsol / sdom pa thags d+r+was 'bog par bka' gnang /
NK133(po)003:2821: lus snang sems gsum mnyam pa nyid kyi bsgom bya
NK133(po)003:2822: sgom byed spang gnyen med par bco lnga'i tshes bzhin
NK133(po)003:2825: stong gsum yungs 'bru mnyam pa'i dgongs pa mngon du gyur /
NK133(po)003:2826: shes bya kun la thogs pa med pa'i mkhyen pa rgyas /
NK133(po)003:2829: log sred can rnams kyang zhal mthong ba tsam gyis dad pa thob /
NK133(po)003:2830: mthong thos 'brel tshad don ldan byung ba 'di sgom med chen po'i mngon rtags gsungs /
NK133(po)003:2831: spros bcas spros med kyi bsnyen sgrub /
NK133(po)003:2832: bka' dgongs rat+na zhi khro sogs phal cher phyi nang gsang gsum sgrub pa them pa dang /
NK133(po)003:2835: gnam chos las gal chen rnams grangs bsnyen dang rtags thon mdzad /
NK133(po)003:2836: dgung lo so dgu na bla mas /
NK133(po)003:2837: kahthoga nges don brgyud pa'i bstan pa 'di //
NK133(po)003:2838: gang la babs pa de yis 'dzin dgos phyir //
NK133(po)003:2839: gzhan dag ma nyan gnas 'dir khyed bzhugs la //
NK133(po)003:2840: phyag rdzogs 'od gsal khrid dang sdom rgyud sogs //
NK133(po)003:2841: 'dzin skyong spel ba'i thugs bskyed ma g.yel dang //
NK133(po)003:2842: tshe sgrub mthar phyin bar chad mi 'byung zhing //
NK133(po)003:2843: don gnyis lhun grub 'byung ba phyi mtha' gsal //
NK133(po)003:2844: zhes sogs gsungs nas thugs sgrub gnam chos bka' gtad /
NK133(po)003:2845: chos skyong sde bdun la bka' bsgo mdzad nas gzugs sku bsdus /
NK133(po)003:2846: de nas bla ma'i bka' bzhin mdo sngags bka' gter gyi 'chad nyan /
NK133(po)003:2847: bskyed rdzogs kyi nyam khrid sgrub pa dus mchod sogs gong ma'i mdzad srol mi nub par bskyangs /
NK133(po)003:2848: nga bzhi nas gdan sa'i 'gan 'dzin mdzad /
NK133(po)003:2849: 'chad nyan sogs lhag par bskyangs te bstan pa phyogs kun tu rgyas par mdzad /
NK133(po)003:2850: shugs 'byung gi longs spyod zad pa med pa'ang drin
NK133(po)003:2851: chen rje dang karma pa sogs dge ba'i bshes gnyen
NK133(po)003:2852: rnams la mchod 'bul dge 'dun la bsnyen bskur rgya
NK133(po)003:2855: bka' dgongs sogs kyi bris sku mang po dang /
NK133(po)003:2857: gter chos rigs dang pan grub mang po'i gsung chos
NK133(po)003:2858: gsung rab dpag med bzhengs shing tshar grangs mang po
NK133(po)003:2859: sgrogs pa dang / thugs rten ka ni ka mthong grol chen mo dang /
NK133(po)003:2860: gser gdung dang dngul gyi mchod rten brgya rtsa brgyad /
NK133(po)003:2861: 'du khang gan+d+ho lar gser gyi rgyal mtshan /
NK133(po)003:2862: dkyil 'khor blos bslang tshogs zang chen po gsum /
NK133(po)003:2863: gzungs spar dang sku spar mang po bzhengs /
NK133(po)003:2864: dge 'dun brgya phrag mang pos tshom bu tshogs sgrub kyi sman sgrub lan drug /
NK133(po)003:2865: bum sgrub bcu gsum tsam dang gzhan sgrub pa che phra mang po dang /
NK133(po)003:2866: rten bzhengs 'gro don sogs gang yang dgongs gtad bka' gnang tsam gyis lhun gyi grub par gyur /
NK133(po)003:2867: btags grol nyi ma mkha' khyab myong reg mthong grol sogs 'gro phan phrin las dpag med mdzad /
