NK133(po)003:2868: rgya nag brag sgo nas ri chab man gyi bla dpon lha mi kun gyi gtsug tu bskur /
NK133(po)003:2869: slob tshogs dpag tu med pa dang dngos nyams rmi
NK133(po)003:2870: lam du mar rtsa ba'i bla mas dbang bskur lung
NK133(po)003:2871: bstan brda' chos ston pa dang /
NK133(po)003:2872: rtsa gsum chos srung lha tshogs zhal gzigs shing byin rlabs dngos grub rtsol ba dang /
NK133(po)003:2873: zag med thugs kyi dgongs pas gzhan rgyud mkhyen pa dang /
NK133(po)003:2874: dus gsum legs nyes sgrib med gzigs shing lung bstan gang gsung mngon du gyur /
NK133(po)003:2875: nad gdon gyis gzir bar byin rlabs dgongs gtad tsam
NK133(po)003:2876: gyis zhi ba sogs gzhan phan phrin las tshad med
NK133(po)003:2877: / bsnyen rdzogs sgrub pa stong phrag mang po dang /
NK133(po)003:2878: sha chang spang ba sogs rgyu 'bras mig bzhin bsrungs shing /
NK133(po)003:2879: chos brgyad dri mas ma gos shing bslab gsum rnam
NK133(po)003:2880: dag gi slob ma grangs med pa las rtogs pa
NK133(po)003:2881: mchog gyur gzhan don 'byung ba'i bla ma brgya phrag
NK133(po)003:2882: tsam gyis tha dad par dgon gnas bzung zhing nges
NK133(po)003:2883: don sgrub brgyud kyi bstan pa dkar 'byam du rgyas
NK133(po)003:2885: bdag ni lo ni mthar phyin bsam pa 'grub pas
NK133(po)003:2886: 'chi ba chos skur sbyong ba'i dus la babs gsungs
NK133(po)003:2887: te / dgung lo re brgyad me lug sa ga'i
NK133(po)003:2888: tshes brgyad nam lang la sku gser sku bzhag pa
NK133(po)003:2889: ltar gdeng tshad bzhi ldan 'od gsal dbyings su bsdus
NK133(po)003:2890: te / / nam mkha' g.ya' dag pa dang /
NK133(po)003:2891: shar phyogs nas sgra dang 'od 'khyugs pa dang /
NK133(po)003:2892: sku gdung zhugs la phul tshe sprin dang khu rlangs
NK133(po)003:2893: thams cad 'ja' tshon du gyur cing bum pa sku
NK133(po)003:2895: me sgra 'ur zhing me du lha sku phyag mtshan
NK133(po)003:2896: gzugs 'char zhing 'ja' tshon d+r+wa ba dang 'ja' rnams
NK133(po)003:2897: zug pa / gdung dang ring bsrel mang du byon
NK133(po)003:2898: cing mthong thos dran reg smin grol la 'god par
NK133(po)003:2899: zug pa / mdzad do // de dag rnam thar las bsdus so //
NK133(po)003:2900: kun bzang shes rab kyi dbon pad+ma rig 'dzin zhes
NK133(po)003:2901: dngos su rdzu 'phrul gyis mkha' spyod gnas yul rnams
NK133(po)003:2902: su gshegs bzhugs mdzad pa de'ang 'di dang dus mnyam
NK133(po)003:2903: yin / gdan rab gsum pa grub dbang pad+ma nor bu ni /
NK133(po)003:2906: kahthoga lho ru nor bu'i ming can 'byung zhes dang 'ja' tshon ma ning gter lung las /
NK133(po)003:2907: kahthoga lho ru nor bu'i ming ya mtshan shes rab
NK133(po)003:2908: snying rjer ldan dpal mgon chos dang 'di 'phrad na
NK133(po)003:2909: dngos grub myur du thob par 'gyur zhes dang gnam
NK133(po)003:2910: chos ma ning chos bdag tu /
NK133(po)003:2911: pad+ma ma ni mtshal gyi ming /
NK133(po)003:2912: zhes pa de nyid ngos 'dzin te /
NK133(po)003:2913: pan chen bi ma mi tra dang /
NK133(po)003:2914: rig 'dzin 'ja' tshon snying po'i sprul par zhal gyis
NK133(po)003:2915: bzhes 'dis rig 'dzin kun bzang shes rab las chos
NK133(po)003:2917: gtso cher pad+ma lhun grub rgya mtsho las bsnyen par
NK133(po)003:2918: rdzogs shing mdo sngags bka' gter thams cad bum pa
NK133(po)003:2920: mkhyen rab dang chos kyi gsan rgya che /
NK133(po)003:2921: karma zhwa dmar nag dang gnas gsar ba kun dga' legs pa'i 'byung gnas /
NK133(po)003:2922: kahthoga rgyal sras bsod nams lde'u btsan sogs las phan
NK133(po)003:2923: tshun gsar rnying gi bka' chos gsan res mang po
NK133(po)003:2924: dang / phyis su kun mkhyen si tu chos kyi
NK133(po)003:2925: 'byung gnas la bla ma dgongs 'dus dbang lung yongs
NK133(po)003:2928: tshur la 'dus pa'i bshad pa sogs gsan /
NK133(po)003:2929: sku tshe dang sgrub pa mnyam par mdzad /
NK133(po)003:2930: slob tshogs shin tu rgyas pa bskyed rdzogs drod rtogs
NK133(po)003:2931: pa'i rtsal rdzogs nas grub pa'i rtags mtshan ngom pa'i
NK133(po)003:2932: gang zag shin tu mang ba byung /
NK133(po)003:2933: lhun grub steng du chos rgyal bstan pa tshe ring
NK133(po)003:2934: gi bla mar phebs skabs shig la rdo rje phur
NK133(po)003:2935: pa'i rtsa 'cham 'khon lugs brgyud pa las byung ba
NK133(po)003:2936: ji lta zhig thol byung du mdzad pa'i tshe zhabs
NK133(po)003:2937: sa la mi reg pa skal ldan 'gas mthong ngo
NK133(po)003:2938: // de dus sa skya bdag chen gyis shar phyogs su gzigs te /
NK133(po)003:2939: de ring mdo khams shar gyi phyogs su sa la
NK133(po)003:2940: gnas pa'i 'phags pa zhig gis rdo rje phur pa'i
NK133(po)003:2941: gar gyis mthong thos sems can dpag med thar pa
NK133(po)003:2942: la bkod song gsungs pa 'di dang 'grigs skad /
NK133(po)003:2943: sde dge lcang ra'i ril sgrub kyi srol thog mar
NK133(po)003:2944: gtod kun bzang si tu zhus chen tshul khrims rin
NK133(po)003:2945: chen sogs kyis basngagasa brjod kyi me tog 'thor ba
NK133(po)003:2946: dam pa'i tshul dgu'i yon tan tshad bzung bral la
NK133(po)003:2947: dgung grangs don dgu bzhugs pa yin /
NK133(po)003:2948: gdan rab bzhi pa karma bkra shis sam karma chos dpal bzang po ste /
NK133(po)003:2949: 'di nyid kyi skye phreng sngon gnas rjes dran dang
NK133(po)003:2950: gzhan gyi lung bstan mthun par gsang bdag rdo rje
NK133(po)003:2954: ri bo dpal 'bar gyi rnal 'byor pa /
NK133(po)003:2958: rje bdun pa'i yongs 'dzin ngag dbang mchog ldan rnams kyi sprul pa gcig bsdus su gsungs /
NK133(po)003:2959: gzhan yang rig 'dzin bdud 'dul rdo rje'i sku gsung
NK133(po)003:2960: thugs kyi sprul pa rdzogs dbon pad+ma kun grol rnam
NK133(po)003:2961: rgyal / kahthoga dri med zhing skyong /
NK133(po)003:2962: dpal yul karma bkra shis gsum yin la /
NK133(po)003:2963: 'di ni rig 'dzin 'ja' tshon snying po'i gter lung las /
NK133(po)003:2964: 'bri chu'i brgyud nas karma'i ming can 'byung zhes dang /
NK133(po)003:2965: bdud 'dul gter lung las kho bo shud bu'i gsung
NK133(po)003:2966: sprul ni ma 'ongs kahthoga nye ba na mang ga'i
NK133(po)003:2967: ming can sgrub brgyud bstan pa btsugs zhes pa ltar
NK133(po)003:2968: rab byung bcu gnyis pa'i sa sprel la rig 'dzin
NK133(po)003:2969: kun bzang shes rab kyi dbon brgyud du 'khrungs /
NK133(po)003:2970: grub dbang pad+ma nor bu las bka' gter smin grol
NK133(po)003:2971: rgya matsho'o lta bu gsan cing thugs zin sras kyi
NK133(po)003:2973: rje de nyid dang karma bcu gsum pa bdud 'dul rdo rje /
NK133(po)003:2974: zhwa dmar chos grub rgya mtsho rnams kyis dpal yul chos khrir mnga' gsol /
NK133(po)003:2975: si tu chos kyi 'byung gnas las bsnyen par rdzogs /
NK133(po)003:2976: dpal yul sgrub khang 'go ma gsar du 'dzug pa
NK133(po)003:2977: dang rten bzhengs sogs gsang chen snying po'i bstan pa
NK133(po)003:2978: 'dzin skyong spel ba'i phrin las bsam gyis mi khyab
NK133(po)003:2980: rgya dang rgya rong mi lo bcu gsum 'khrugs mthar
NK133(po)003:2981: ni sngags pa nus pa can gyis 'dul zhes pa
NK133(po)003:2982: ltar rgya nag btsan lha rab brtan rgyal po sogs
NK133(po)003:2983: 'khrugs nas sems can sdug bsngal ba na /
NK133(po)003:2984: gong ma chan lung gis gdan 'dren bzhin phebs /
NK133(po)003:2985: der bon po'i nus pa'i rdo char dbab pa la gzigs stangs kyi bzlog pa dang /
NK133(po)003:2986: mtshon srung srung mdud shig shig 'gul zhing de phyogs
NK133(po)003:2987: kun la gnod pa med pa sogs grub pa'i mngon
NK133(po)003:2988: rtags mang pos pha rol po'i g.yul nyams te sems
NK133(po)003:2990: dgung grangs drug cu re gsum bzhugs so //
NK133(po)003:2991: gdan rab lnga pa rje dbon karma lha dbang dang /
NK133(po)003:2992: 'khrul zhig karma don dam gnyis nges don bstan pa'i srog shing du gyur /
NK133(po)003:2993: mtshan snyan che zhing 'khor slob dbyar mtsho ltar 'phel /
NK133(po)003:2994: khyad par karma don dam bya btang kun spang pa'i rnam thar can /
NK133(po)003:2995: gzim skyil shing lo'i rib ma rlung chen nam byung
NK133(po)003:2996: la 'thor ba slob ma tshos gso bzhin par bzhugs
NK133(po)003:2997: / nub mo me mi gso ba dang /
NK133(po)003:2998: gsol zhal sbub nas bzhag pa sogs bka' gdams pa'i
NK133(po)003:2999: rnam thar bzhin mi rtag pa'i gsung kho na dang
NK133(po)003:3000: slob tshogs snying po'i sgrub pa 'ba' zhig la dril
NK133(po)003:3001: du bcug / smin gling blo ldan las sgyu 'phrul
NK133(po)003:3002: zhi khro'i chog khrid slob tu brtsal ba sogs bka'
NK133(po)003:3003: ma'i sgrub mchod kyi bzhi tsam 'dzug par mdzad /
NK133(po)003:3004: gzhan sems mkhyen pa dang 'byung gyur gsung pa mang /
NK133(po)003:3005: rnam thar zhib par ma mjal yang /
NK133(po)003:3006: dam rdzas kha byang zhig tu karma don dam dgung
NK133(po)003:3007: lo brgya dang gsum bzhugs pa'i dbu ljon zhes 'dug
NK133(po)003:3008: pas dgung grangs shin tu mtho bar bzhugs pa'o //
NK133(po)003:3009: gzhan yang drug pa karma 'gyur med nges don bstan 'dzin dpal bzang po ni /
NK133(po)003:3010: bdud 'dul sprul sku snying tig las /
NK133(po)003:3011: sh+r+ai seng ha'i rnam 'phrul 'brel tshad don ldan pa
NK133(po)003:3012: yul ni ting ngam shod ces bya ba ru spang
NK133(po)003:3013: ljongs shing tshal ri'i zhol du karma 'gyur med ces
NK133(po)003:3014: pa'i skyes bu 'byung mchan g.yon mdun rgyab rnams su
NK133(po)003:3015: sme nag brgyan skyes mchog 'gro 'dul de la gtad
NK133(po)003:3016: rgya gyis mthong thos dran reg tshom bur bcas skye
NK133(po)003:3017: ba lnga 'das mngon dag'i zhing du gshegs zhes pa
NK133(po)003:3018: ltar rab 'dod shing stag la rme shod me chung
NK133(po)003:3020: karma bkra shis kyi skye srid du karma pa bdud 'dul rdo rje /
NK133(po)003:3021: sa skya 'jam mgon dbang sdud snying po /
NK133(po)003:3022: bdud 'dul rgyal sras pad+ma rnam rgyal /
NK133(po)003:3023: si tu pad+ma nyin byed rnams dgongs pa phyogs gcig tu babs /
NK133(po)003:3024: khyad par 'dzi sgar bka' brgyud phrin las rnam rgyal gyis /
NK133(po)003:3026: gter lhung gi tshu rol na chu de'i brgyud nas nyin lam na yab la don 'grub /
NK133(po)003:3027: yum la bsod nams ming can sras shing stag lo
NK133(po)003:3028: pa barla la stag ris yod pa zhig lung bstan
NK133(po)003:3029: / si tu pad+ma nyin byed las bsnyen par rdzogs /
NK133(po)003:3030: dpal yul karma lha dbang las bka' gter smin grol phal mo che gsan /
NK133(po)003:3031: khyad par zab khrid rnams karma don dam las bzhes /
NK133(po)003:3032: lha rtse pad+ma sbyin pa las khams lugs mdo dbang
NK133(po)003:3033: chen mo gsan pa'i gsang mtshan rig 'dzin ngag gi
NK133(po)003:3034: dbang po gsol / kahthoga dgon rnying sprul sku las bdud 'dul dbang lung /
NK133(po)003:3035: rdza khra ma bla ma rgyal ba'i myu gu dang /
NK133(po)003:3036: rdzogs chen bzhi pa las klong chen snying thig sogs gsan /
NK133(po)003:3037: sku tshe phal cher bcad rgya kho nar bzhugs /
NK133(po)003:3038: phur pa'i lha bdun cu rtsa lnga zhal gzigs pa dang /
NK133(po)003:3039: gu ru rin po ches lug lo nam 'char la
NK133(po)003:3040: sman sgrub tshug dgos pa'i lung bstan sogs dag snang
NK133(po)003:3041: mang / tshes bcu'i dus ston spros bcas rgyas par btsug /
NK133(po)003:3042: rdzogs chen gyi dgongs pa klong du gyur pas gsung thos pa tsam la'ang rtogs pa skyes skad /
NK133(po)003:3044: lkog gyur gzigs pa la thogs pa med /
NK133(po)003:3045: 'byung gdon la dgongs gtad kyis phyag gi rdo rje
NK133(po)003:3046: 'phang pa khang pa chod gsum bzhi tsam zang thal
NK133(po)003:3048: tis lhung tsha chu khar zhabs rjes sogs grub brtags kyang ci rigs bstan /
NK133(po)003:3049: gtsug lag khang steng gser gyi rgya phib 'dzug pa dang /
NK133(po)003:3050: gsung rab zhal thang sogs rten gsum dngos nams shin tu gtsang ba mang po bzhengs /
NK133(po)003:3051: dgung lo nga brgyad la phyag rdzas rnams tshogs bsags rgya chen por smin par mdzad /
NK133(po)003:3052: lcags phag s+n+ron zla'i tshes bcu gnyis nas phyogs thams
NK133(po)003:3053: cad bde bar gshegs pa'i sku kho nas gang 'dug
NK133(po)003:3055: bcu gsum la dgongs pa bsdus /
NK133(po)003:3056: sku gdung khru gang tsam zhal mdang gsal ba 'ja' sprin sogs ngo mtshar ba'i rtags mang byung /
NK133(po)003:3057: de ltar bstan 'dzin rim byon thams cad snga phyir
NK133(po)003:3058: rgyud gzhung rig gnas dang bcas par mkhas pa'ang ci
NK133(po)003:3060: gtso bor bla ma brten nas gdams ngag phu thag
NK133(po)003:3061: bcad cing sgrub tshugs mos gus kyi nyams len snying
NK133(po)003:3062: por mdzad / spyir rgyal bstan bshad sgrub gnyis kyis 'dzin dgos kyang /
NK133(po)003:3063: rang re sgrub brgyud pa rtogs pa'i bstan pas 'dzin
NK133(po)003:3064: pa rang skal te rdzogs pa chen po'i lta sgom
NK133(po)003:3065: shin tu'ang gzhan las khyad par 'phags shing rnyed dka'
NK133(po)003:3066: ba shes nas nor bu rnyed dus 'ching bu la
NK133(po)003:3067: re ba mi 'tshal ba bzhin lam 'khrul med sgom
NK133(po)003:3068: na 'bras bu 'khrul med thob bya ba de yin
NK133(po)003:3069: zhes kun bzang thugs kyi bstan pa la gtsig che
NK133(po)003:3070: bar mdzad / nges par brgyud pa 'di la rtsa
NK133(po)003:3071: ba bzhi sogs kyi srung sdom la gces che bas
NK133(po)003:3073: rgyu 'bras spang len la 'dzem bag che bas rnam thar gtsang /
NK133(po)003:3074: theg chen sems bskyed la blo 'byangs bas gzhan phan lhag par che /
NK133(po)003:3075: rab tu byung nas spang klog ma byas par le
NK133(po)003:3076: lo can dad rdzas la bu lon du 'gyur ba
NK133(po)003:3077: dang / dge 'dun rnams rten bzang chud mi za
NK133(po)003:3078: ba'i phyir sgrub sder zhugs so cog nas rdzogs chen
NK133(po)003:3079: sngon 'gro nas thod rgal bar dang /
NK133(po)003:3080: rlung khrid sogs rdzogs rim rnams ma sbyong mi chog
NK133(po)003:3081: pa'i khrims dang bsnyen sogs ma byas sngags kyi las
NK133(po)003:3082: la 'jug na sbom ltung dang rdo rje theg pa
NK133(po)003:3083: bon gyer gya tshom spang phyir bla ma sku gsum
NK133(po)003:3084: sgrub pa dang / mtshams khang lo gsum du bka'
NK133(po)003:3085: gter rtsa gsum gal che shos rnams kyi bsnyen sgrub
NK133(po)003:3086: dang so so'i khrid rim zhar la spyod pa dang
NK133(po)003:3087: sgrub pa dang / / lta sgom nyams myong bzang
NK133(po)003:3088: ba ma gtogs slob dpon gyi bya ba byed pa
NK133(po)003:3089: dang slob dpon gyi ming mi 'dogs /
NK133(po)003:3090: las spros bcas rnam bzhag gang la'ang thugs rtse mi
NK133(po)003:3091: gtogs pa sogs ngo mtshar ba'i khyad chos lta bur
NK133(po)003:3092: snang ba kun gyi spyod yul du gyur pa sogs
NK133(po)003:3093: chos bzhin spyod pa'i rnam thar bzang pos lha dang
NK133(po)003:3094: bcas pa'i rgyud bskul bas bstan pa gong 'phel du
NK133(po)003:3095: gyur pa'o // rje karma 'gyur med kyi slob ma dbon sprul rig 'dzin 'jigs med rang grol ni /
NK133(po)003:3096: rdza chu khar wa shul rigs las rab yid lcags 'brug la 'khrungs /
NK133(po)003:3097: pad+ma nyin byed dbang po las bsnyen par rdzogs pa'i mtshan karma bstan 'dzin chos kyi rgyal po gsol /
NK133(po)003:3098: rje karma 'gyur med khram bla ma 'jigs med rgyal ba'i myu gu /
NK133(po)003:3099: kahthoga 'gyur med tshe dbang mchog grub sogs las gsan bsam rgya cher dang gdams ngag rdzogs par mdzad /
NK133(po)003:3100: sku tshe stod la dpal yul bstan pa'i khur 'dzin dang de nas rmug sangs zla gam dbang phug /
NK133(po)003:3101: gtsang gshis rdo rje gro lod sogs su snying po'i sgrub pa mdzad /
NK133(po)003:3102: phyogs nges med du zab khrid kyis 'gro don bskyang /
NK133(po)003:3103: phyis nas sngon gyi gdan sa rnying pa rmugs sangs
NK133(po)003:3104: su bstan pa 'dzin skyong spel ba'i phrin las kyis
NK133(po)003:3106: 'dis spyod 'jug dang byams chos mngon mdzod sogs gsan
NK133(po)003:3107: sbyong dang 'chad spel ci rigs mdzad pa'i khrid lung
NK133(po)003:3109: gzugs can gzugs med kyi gdul bya 'dul ba'i grub pa'i dbang phyug zhig go //
NK133(po)003:3110: gdan rab bdun pa rgya sprul rin po che pad+ma
NK133(po)003:3111: mdo sngags bstan 'dzin nges gsang chos kyi snang ba
NK133(po)003:3112: ni / tsha kho rgya kha b+ho to stod phan
NK133(po)003:3113: btags zhes gong ma'i blon chen zhig gi rigs las
NK133(po)003:3114: rab yid lcags stag la ngo mtshar ba'i ltas bcas
NK133(po)003:3115: ni / 'khrungs / byis pa'i rtsed gral du rlung
NK133(po)003:3116: khug re bzung nas mtshon rnon po'i rtser zhabs mthil
NK133(po)003:3117: bzhag nas bzhengs thub pa dang /
NK133(po)003:3118: yi ge bri klog lugs kyi bstan bcos sogs brda bstan pa tsam gyis chub pa /
NK133(po)003:3119: skyes thob kyi grub rtags dang shes rab ldan /
NK133(po)003:3120: dgung lo bcu nas sa 'du pad+ma 'od gling du
NK133(po)003:3121: nyid kyi khu bo sa skya kun blo'i rnam 'phrul
NK133(po)003:3122: rdo rje phur pa'i grub brnyes sangs rgyas ye shes
NK133(po)003:3123: las gnam chos rdzogs chen sngon 'gro'i khrid zhus pas
NK133(po)003:3124: 'jig rten gyi phun tshogs la gting nas nges par
NK133(po)003:3125: 'byung ba dang / chos yang dag sgrub blo bcos min skyes /
NK133(po)003:3126: de skor nas gsang phu ne'u thang dang yul gyi chos sde'i bkod pa dang /
NK133(po)003:3127: rong ston gzhung brgya pa sh+aakya rgyal mtshan dang /
NK133(po)003:3128: rig 'dzin kun bzang shes rab sogs sngon gnas mang po thugs la shar ba dang /
NK133(po)003:3130: ma mos phrin las sgrub pa'i ltas mang po byung /
NK133(po)003:3131: rig 'dzin kun bzang shes rab kyi sprul par zhal
NK133(po)003:3132: gyis bzhes pa bzhin dgung lo bcu gnyis la dpal
NK133(po)003:3133: yul gdan sar spyan drangs te gong ma'i chos khrir
NK133(po)003:3134: bkod / rje karma 'gyur med las gnam chos rdzogs
NK133(po)003:3135: chen khrid gsan pas nges 'byung snying rje shugs drag
NK133(po)003:3136: skyes shing dngos gzhi sems nyid ngo bo rig stong
NK133(po)003:3137: rjen pa'i rtogs pa legs par 'khrungs /
NK133(po)003:3138: rtsa rlung khrid zhus pas zab khyad kyi nges pa rnyed /
NK133(po)003:3139: rgyud gsang snying zhus te spyi don legs bshad rol
NK133(po)003:3140: mtsho dang bskyed rim zung 'jug snye ma thugs la
NK133(po)003:3141: bzungs / rat+na'i sku gsum sgrub pa skabs rtags bzang mang po byung /
NK133(po)003:3142: sgrub dbang kho nas rat+na'i dbang lung rdzogs pa dang /
NK133(po)003:3143: sangs gling nor bu skor gsum /
NK133(po)003:3144: tshe sgrub nyi zla kha sbyor /
NK133(po)003:3151: chags med ri chos thugs chen dmar khrid /
NK133(po)003:3153: bder 'dus mgon po sogs nos so //
NK133(po)003:3154: dbon sprul dang rga rje bkra shis rgya mtsho las
NK133(po)003:3155: brgyud pa'i bka' brgyad bder 'dus tshar gnyis dang gsang
NK133(po)003:3156: rdzogs nos so // bla ma mgon srung dang don mchog las skar rtsis /
NK133(po)003:3157: rdzogs chen rdo rje rab brtan las /
NK133(po)003:3161: sgra k+aa l+aa pa ting sub mtha' bcas pa gsan /
NK133(po)003:3162: byams mgon t+aa'i si tu pad+ma nyin byed dbang po
NK133(po)003:3163: las bsnyen par rdzogs pa'i mtshan karma kun bzang bstan
NK133(po)003:3164: 'dzin gsol / 'jam mgon kong sprul rin po che'i mdun nas snga rjes sgra tsan+da pa /
NK133(po)003:3167: gzhan stong dbu ma'i lta khrid /
NK133(po)003:3170: rang byung ba'i gzhung chung gnyis /
NK133(po)003:3171: bka' brgyad sgrub dbang rin chen gter mdzod /
NK133(po)003:3172: mar lugs dgyes rdor gur rigs bsdus /
NK133(po)003:3173: chos drug zab lam snying khu /
NK133(po)003:3174: rjes gnang gcig shes kun grol /
NK133(po)003:3177: byang gter yongs rdzogs dang rig 'dzin yongs su 'dus /
NK133(po)003:3180: sbyor drug nyam khrid zhib mo /
NK133(po)003:3181: pad+ma don yod las 'grel chen dri med 'od dang bu ston dang sbyor ba'i mchan tika /
NK133(po)003:3184: thugs sras lo ts+aa ba'i gsung sgros pod gnyis rnams nos so //
NK133(po)003:3185: rdo rje 'dzin pa pad+ma bzod pa las mdo dbang rin chen phreng ba /
NK133(po)003:3191: ye shes dpal 'byor las 'ja' tshon chos skor /
NK133(po)003:3193: bla ma lhun grub las grub brgya'i rjes gnang /
NK133(po)003:3195: bla ma pad+ma sbyin pa las bka' 'gyur rin po che'i lung yongs rdzogs gsan /
NK133(po)003:3196: 'jam dbyangs mkhyen brtse'i dbang po'i mdun nas /
NK133(po)003:3197: thugs bskyed lta spyod srol gnyis /
NK133(po)003:3199: bshes springs dang rin chen phreng ba /
NK133(po)003:3200: snga 'gyur bka' ma'i rgyud sde'i dkyil 'khor sum cu tsam gyi dbang lung rgyun bzhugs tshad /
NK133(po)003:3201: gsang snyiing 'grel pa dgongs rgyan steng nas mthar chags /
NK133(po)003:3202: dge ba gsum gyi don khrid steng nas sgyu 'phrul khrid zab rgyas rgyud chog bcas /
NK133(po)003:3205: legs bshad rol mtsho sogs kyi khrid lung /
NK133(po)003:3206: ko nang khrid brgya mtshan gcig ring la rgyas bshad rdzogs par ngo mtshar bar mdzad /
NK133(po)003:3210: yon tan mdzod rtsa 'grel ljags bshad sogs mkhyen brtse
NK133(po)003:3211: pod dgu tshang ma'i dbang lung khrid tshang ma dang
NK133(po)003:3217: mchog gling thugs sgrub rnam gnyis /
NK133(po)003:3224: yig cha gsar rnying lung bcas gsan /
NK133(po)003:3226: wa shul bla ma bsod nams rnam rgyal las snga rjes sdom gsum rnam nges khrid dang 'grel chen /
NK133(po)003:3227: phyag chen man ngag rgya mtsho /
NK133(po)003:3236: rdzogs chen rdo rje rab brtan mdun nas gsang 'grel spar khab nam mkha' dpal ba'i mchan can /
NK133(po)003:3238: smin gling thugs chen bskyed rdzogs rnam bshad gnyis /
NK133(po)003:3240: dge mang gsol dpon pad+ma'i mdun nas jo bo'i chos chung brgya rtsa /
NK133(po)003:3241: ka ma shi la'i sgom rims /
NK133(po)003:3242: bka' ma rog phur dang rong phur 'bum nag /
NK133(po)003:3254: dge 'dun rgya mtsho'i mtshan brjod tika /
NK133(po)003:3256: klong chen bka' 'bum thor bu rnams nos so //
NK133(po)003:3257: mnga' ris bla ma kun dga' 'jam dbyangs mdun nas dpe chos rin spungs /
NK133(po)003:3260: khro phu'i man ngag brgya rtsa /
NK133(po)003:3261: jo nang dang sha ra ba'i lam rim /
NK133(po)003:3268: pod ser chos tshan nga bzhi /
NK133(po)003:3269: pod dmar chos tshan don lnga /
NK133(po)003:3272: mkhyen brtse'i bka' 'bum pod gnyis sogs phra zhib mang
NK133(po)003:3273: du gsan pa sogs de dag rag pa tsam smos
NK133(po)003:3274: pa'o // gsan pa de dag kyang bsam byung gis
NK133(po)003:3275: gtan la phab cing lhag pa'i lhas byin gyis rlabs
NK133(po)003:3276: pas mdo sngags kun la mkhyen rab thogs pa med
NK133(po)003:3277: pa'i gzung dang spobs pa'i gter kha rdol /
NK133(po)003:3278: khyad par gsang ba snying po sogs sngags skor la mkhyen rab 'gran zla bral /
NK133(po)003:3279: sgom pas nyams su blang pas bskyed rdzogs rdzogs chen gyi lam rtags ji bzhin brnyes /
NK133(po)003:3280: khyad par thugs rje chen po'i ljags bsnyen dung phyur
NK133(po)003:3281: sogs bsnyen sgrubs mthar phyin pas rmi lam sprul bsgyur
NK133(po)003:3282: dang 'brel ri bo gru 'dzin du 'phags pas rjes
NK133(po)003:3283: su bzung ba'i dag snang dang thugs bzhed thams cad
NK133(po)003:3284: mthar phyin pa'i lung bstan brtsal /
NK133(po)003:3285: zangs mdog dpal rir byon pas gtso bo gu ru
NK133(po)003:3286: rin po che nyid rje karma 'gyur med kyi rnam
NK133(po)003:3287: par mjal ba sogs dag zhing rnams su phebs /
NK133(po)003:3288: sku tshe bdun na mngon par sangs rgyas pa'i lung bstan brnyes pa ste /
NK133(po)003:3290: skye ba bdun na byang chub lung bstan thob //
NK133(po)003:3291: kun bzang bstan 'dzin zhabs la gsol ba 'debs //
NK133(po)003:3293: gser dngul sogs phyag rdzas snod du bcug pa dngos
NK133(po)003:3294: su mang du 'phel ba dang dam can rnams bran
NK133(po)003:3295: bzhin byed pa sogs rnam thar dpag dka'/
NK133(po)003:3296: gzhan don 'chad spel gyi phrin las kyang rab byung dge tshul slong stong phrag /
NK133(po)003:3297: rnying ma bka' ma'i chos skor dbang lung tshar brgyad /
NK133(po)003:3298: gsang snying rgyud bshad tshar kha shas /
NK133(po)003:3305: dgongs pa zang thal tshar gnyis /
NK133(po)003:3308: klong chen snying tig tshar bzhi bdud 'dul bzhi /
NK133(po)003:3311: rin chen gter mdzod tshar gnyis rnams gsungs /
NK133(po)003:3312: 'bum dang brgyad stong sogs chos tshan ci rigs las
NK133(po)003:3313: bka' 'gyur tshang ba dang gdams mdzod ni gsung rgyu
NK133(po)003:3314: ma byung 'dra / de min gang gsan tshar kha shas ma gsung pa med la /
NK133(po)003:3315: chos tshan thor bu dang dbang sna re tsam grangs mi chod pa'o //
NK133(po)003:3316: rdzogs chen sngon 'gro dang dngos gzhi'i khrid btab pa shin tu mang /
NK133(po)003:3317: 'go gser rgya rong go 'jo sogs snga rjes byon
NK133(po)003:3318: sa rnams su chos sgo skyel gyis dbang lung khrid
NK133(po)003:3320: gtsug lag khang dang mchod rten /
NK133(po)003:3321: rnying pa nyams gsos dang gsar 'dzug gi rten dang
NK133(po)003:3322: mchod rdzas dngos po tshogs rten gnang ba sogs shin
NK133(po)003:3323: tu mang / rang gi gdan sar rje kun bzang
NK133(po)003:3324: shes rab sku dus dge 'dun sum stong tsam byung
NK133(po)003:3325: yang 'di skor gnyug mar gnas pa'i dge 'dun lnga
NK133(po)003:3326: tu mang / brgya tsam dang / phyogs kyi grwa
NK133(po)003:3327: rgyun chos nyan rgyas skabs dgu brgya tsam byung ba
NK133(po)003:3328: la phyag 'gyed lan mang gnang zhing snga ma'i dgongs
NK133(po)003:3329: rdzogs rgya cher sgrub pa dang /
NK133(po)003:3330: khyad par sku gdung lha khang ka ba nyi shu
NK133(po)003:3331: pa gany+dzira bcas pa'i nang rten gtso bo gser gdung
NK133(po)003:3333: tshe dpag med kyi sku zhal mtho phyed gsum /
NK133(po)003:3334: dngul gyi mchod sdong thog tshad gnyis pa /
NK133(po)003:3335: gser zangs kyi sku stong phrag nye ba /
NK133(po)003:3336: bka' 'gyur sogs gsung rten mang po /
NK133(po)003:3337: bzang gos kyi bla bre phyi nang khebs pa /
NK133(po)003:3339: rgya dngul srang brgya dang lnga bcu'i mchod ting man+dala
NK133(po)003:3340: kong bu sogs mchod rdzas bzang zhing gya nom pa
NK133(po)003:3341: dang / rdo rje sems dpa'i lha khang gany+dzi ra dang /
NK133(po)003:3344: rten gtso rdor sems gtso bo zhal tshad mtho lnga
NK133(po)003:3345: pa seng khri rgyab yol rgyan drug bcas rgyang mtho
NK133(po)003:3346: lnga bcu yod pa'i 'khor gser zangs skal bzang rnam
NK133(po)003:3348: gter ston khyung drag rdo rje'i gter byon sangs rgyas
NK133(po)003:3349: kyi 'phel gdung mkha' 'gro'i gtad rgya lta bus phyag
NK133(po)003:3350: tu 'byor ba stong phrag snying por bzhugs pa dang
NK133(po)003:3351: / rgyan dang mchod rdzas bzang zhing gya nom pa dang /
NK133(po)003:3352: lha sar khang du kun bzang shes rab mchod sdong gser zangs thog tshad gsum pa /
NK133(po)003:3353: ston pa'i gos sku chen mo /
NK133(po)003:3354: bka' gter dgongs 'grel gyi glegs bam bshur yig gsar
NK133(po)003:3355: bzhengs pus sti bzhi brgya skor bka' bstan 'gyur sogs
NK133(po)003:3356: spar ma shin tu mang ba /
NK133(po)003:3357: sher phyin stong phrag brgya pa dang /
NK133(po)003:3358: brgyad stong sogs gsung spar mang po s+aats+tsha 'bum phrag brgya dang lnga bcu'i yon brtsal /
NK133(po)003:3359: dar cog stong phrag mang po 'dzug /
NK133(po)003:3360: dge 'dun sum brgyas thos grol nyin lnga bcu sogs tshogs gsogs mang po mdzad pa dang /
NK133(po)003:3361: dpal yul 'dir sngar mdo sgyu sems gsum sogs dbang
NK133(po)003:3362: lung 'chad spel dang bsnyen sgrub nyams len gyi rgyun
NK133(po)003:3363: yod kyang spros bcas sgrub mchod sogs kyi rgyun cher
NK133(po)003:3389: pad+ma brgya pa mdo tshogs chen 'dus pa /
NK133(po)003:3390: lung lugs tshe dpag med bcas dkyil 'khor sum cu
NK133(po)003:3391: tsam gyi sgrub mchod tshang ma rdul tshon la bten
NK133(po)003:3392: pa 'dzug pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi yo byad /
NK133(po)003:3394: sbyin sreg gi rdzas dang sku chas /
NK133(po)003:3395: sgyu 'phrul khro bo'i khrag 'thung rtsa 'chams dang brub 'chams /
NK133(po)003:3396: su ra to'i gar 'chams bcas kyi zhwa phod ka /
NK133(po)003:3399: phyag mtshan rnga rol 'bud 'khrol sogs dngos nams dag pa 'gran zlar dkon pa /
NK133(po)003:3400: de dag gi gtong rtsa'i chos gzhi sogs phun sum tshogs par mdzad /
NK133(po)003:3401: dpal yul 'dir mdo sngags kyi klog grwa zhig 'dzug par bzhed kyang re zhig ma 'grub pas /
NK133(po)003:3402: rmugs sangs su gsang snying rgyud bshad /
NK133(po)003:3403: sgyu 'phrul sgrub mchod bcas btsugs pa dang /
NK133(po)003:3404: phyiis nas dar thang mdo sngags bshad sgrub gling gsar
NK133(po)003:3405: 'debs mdzad pa der dge 'dun stong phrag tsam 'dus
NK133(po)003:3406: / dag pa'i gzigs snang la rin po che'i ljon
NK133(po)003:3407: shing lo 'bras phun sum tshogs pa can gzigs pas
NK133(po)003:3408: dgon der lung rtogs bstan pa dang bstan 'dzin dpag
NK133(po)003:3409: bsam shing ltar rgyas pa'i ltas su shar te /
NK133(po)003:3410: gu ru pad+ma'i ring lugs gsang chen snga 'gyur ba'i
NK133(po)003:3411: bstan pa byang phyogs su 'phel rgyas yun du brtan
NK133(po)003:3413: slar dpal yul du rten bzhengs tshogs gsogs rgya cher dang bcad rgya dam bzhugs /
NK133(po)003:3414: 'jam dbyangs mkhyen brtse gshegs pas thugs skyo che zhing
NK133(po)003:3415: gnam mthongs kyi skas ring zhig la 'jam mgon bla
NK133(po)003:3416: ma gshegs pa'i phyi bzhin song ba rmis pas /
NK133(po)003:3417: da ni gser gdung zhig bzhengs dgos gsungs nas gdan
NK133(po)003:3418: khri pa tra sogs grub mtshams bsnyun khams cung zad
NK133(po)003:3419: bzhes te / bgrang bya re gnyis s+n+ron zla'i nyer
NK133(po)003:3420: gcig la 'phags pa gnas brtan bcu drug zhal gzigs
NK133(po)003:3421: mtshan gung nas bzhugs stangs bcas dag pa'i zhing du
NK133(po)003:3422: sa lam mthon po'i rtags dang cho 'phrul bcas gshegs
NK133(po)003:3423: bzhes te / so // de nas khyad par gdan
NK133(po)003:3424: rab brgyad pa bdag cag gi 'dren mchog chos kyi
NK133(po)003:3425: rgyal po mchog gi sprul pa'i sku o rgyan mdo
NK133(po)003:3426: sngags chos kyi nyi ma phyogs las rnam par rgyal
NK133(po)003:3427: ba'i sde dpal bzang po ni /
NK133(po)003:3429: nga yi sprul pa kha yi steng du 'byung //
NK133(po)003:3430: zhes bris pa'i shog dril zhig mdun lcog steng bzhag
NK133(po)003:3431: ste rjes 'jug yid ches pa'i phyi tshig bzhag pa
NK133(po)003:3432: bzhin / sde dge a lo kha steng blon chen
NK133(po)003:3433: 'adi'u mgor kun mkhyen si tu chos kyi 'byung gnas
NK133(po)003:3434: sogs skyes chen mang po byon pa'irigasa las rab yid
NK133(po)003:3435: shing stag la 'ja' 'od sgra chen po sogs ngo
NK133(po)003:3437: de'i tshe 'jam dbyangs mkhyen brtse'i dbang po'i dag pa'i gzigs snang du /
NK133(po)003:3438: der dpa' bo mkha' 'gro'i tshogs kyis mchod sprin spro
NK133(po)003:3439: zhing 'dir dpal yul karma 'gyur med bltams yod pa
NK133(po)003:3440: 'dis nang rgyud sde gsum gyi bstan la sman par
NK133(po)003:3441: 'gyur ro // zhes lung bstan tshul pheb pa dang /
NK133(po)003:3444: pad+ma mdo sngags bstan 'dzin rang nyid bcas dgongs pa mthun par babs /
NK133(po)003:3445: karma bcu gnyis par gtsug phud phul bas mtshan karma
NK133(po)003:3446: kun bzang bde chen gsang sngags chos kyi rgyal po
NK133(po)003:3447: gsol / mchog gyur bde chen gling pas thugs rje chen po'i dbang dang tshe dbang brtsal /
NK133(po)003:3448: dpal yul gdan sar bkod de rje pad+ma mdo sngags bstan 'dzin las bsnyen par rdzogs /
NK133(po)003:3449: dpal yul lugs kyi khrid rim rnams dang bka' brgyad dgongs 'dus /
NK133(po)003:3455: bdud 'dul sogs gter chos phal mo che dang /
NK133(po)003:3456: bka' ma mdo dbang khams dbus bka' srol gnyis sogs
NK133(po)003:3457: bka' ma'i rgyud sde'i chos skor rgyun bzhugs so 'tshal
NK133(po)003:3458: / pu to ba'i dpe chos sogs bka' gdams chos
NK133(po)003:3459: skor sogs dbang lung mtha' yas pa phal cher tshar
NK133(po)003:3461: wa shul bla ma bsod nams rnam rgyal las sdom gsum rnam nges /
NK133(po)003:3464: mdo rgyan sogs gzhung bshad mang po dang /
NK133(po)003:3465: khang nang bkra shis phun tshogs las skar rtsis rdzogs
NK133(po)003:3466: chen rdo rje rab brtan las rgyud gsang snying 'grel
NK133(po)003:3467: pa dgongs rgyan zhal lung gnyis ka'i steng nas gsan
NK133(po)003:3468: / 'jam dbyangs mkhyen brtse'i dbang po las byang sdom srol gnyis /
NK133(po)003:3471: sems sde nyang lugs dang rdo rje zam pa /
NK133(po)003:3473: mchog gling nyid kyi gter gsar skor sogs mang po dang /
NK133(po)003:3474: 'jam mgon yon tan rgya mtsho las /
NK133(po)003:3475: rin chen gter mdzod chen mo /
NK133(po)003:3477: dgongs 'dus sgrub dbang la sogs pa dang /
NK133(po)003:3478: lha sprul pad+ma gar dbang bstan 'dzin las 'ja' tshon chos skor /
NK133(po)003:3479: grub brnyes sna tshogs rang grol las bla ma yang tig /
NK133(po)003:3480: dgongs pa zang thal theng gnyis sogs dang /
NK133(po)003:3481: dpal spung bla ma bkra shis chos 'phel las bka' 'gyur lung dang bka' brgyud sngags mdzod sogs dang /
NK133(po)003:3482: rmugs sangs mkhan po shes rab bzang po las /
NK133(po)003:3483: snying tig ya bzhi mdzod bdun /
NK133(po)003:3484: mkhan rgyal mtshan 'od zer las lta ba klong yangs /
NK133(po)003:3486: gter ston rin chen gling pa las rang gter thugs sgrub bla med don rdzogs 'dus pa /
NK133(po)003:3487: kahthoga rje dbon pad+ma rgyal mtshan las snga 'gyur rgyud 'bum yongs rdzogs gsan pa sogs /
NK133(po)003:3488: gsar rnying gter gsum gyi thos pa shin tu rgya che /
NK133(po)003:3489: rgya sprul rin po ches bstan jus gzigs skabs khong
NK133(po)003:3490: la phyag rdzas gang byung sku mdun rtsis 'bul mdzad
NK133(po)003:3492: thub dbang gnas bcu lha khang gser gyi gany+dzi ra
NK133(po)003:3493: mtho bcu gsum can nang rten gtso bo gser zangs
NK133(po)003:3494: thub pa'i sku tshad phyag mtho sum cu pa mchog
NK133(po)003:3495: zung mi tshad / gnas brtan bcu drug rgyal chen bzhi bcas mi tshad /
NK133(po)003:3496: gser sku mtho tshad brgya phrag kha shas /
NK133(po)003:3497: gser gyi mchod rten mtho sum cu'i sku tshad rgyan
NK133(po)003:3498: dang mchod rdzas spus nams gtsang zhing phun sum tshogs
NK133(po)003:3499: pa / skyes rab dpag bsam khri shing /
NK133(po)003:3501: dgongs 'dus grwa tshar sogs sku thang grangs mang /
NK133(po)003:3502: bla brang yar mar du gser zangs dang 'der sku rnam mang /
NK133(po)003:3503: gsung rabs gshar bris pod brgya skor dang /
NK133(po)003:3504: spar ma bcas glegs bam stong nye /
NK133(po)003:3505: tshes bcu'i 'cham chas gsar barje dang /
NK133(po)003:3506: mchod rdzas 'phan gdugs yo byad skor dang gur mo che gsar bzhengs /
NK133(po)003:3508: gu ru stong sku thugs sgrub yang snying 'dus pa'i sgrub skor spar dang /
NK133(po)003:3509: khyad par 'chad 'gyur bka' ma'i chos skor yongs su rdzogs pa spar du bkod pa dang /
NK133(po)003:3510: gzhan don gsung gi 'chad spel kyang rdzogs chen dang rtsa rlung sogs khrid rim rgyun chags dang /
NK133(po)003:3511: dge tshul slong drug brgya don lnga tsam dang /
NK133(po)003:3512: rin chen gter mdzod tshar gnyis /
NK133(po)003:3513: gnam chos tshar bcu gsum bka' brgyad bder 'dus /
NK133(po)003:3516: bka' ma'i chos skor tshar kha shas /
NK133(po)003:3517: 'ja' tshon tshar bzhi sogs gang gsan phal cher tshar
NK133(po)003:3518: mang gsungs pa dang spyir yang dam pa 'di nyid
NK133(po)003:3519: sku na gzhon pa'i dus nas dam pa'i rang gshis
NK133(po)003:3520: gser ltar bzang bas phan 'dogs dang yon tan gyi
NK133(po)003:3521: zhing la thugs gting nas gus shing /
NK133(po)003:3522: grub mtha' ris med kun la dag snang yangs pa dang /
NK133(po)003:3523: su la'ang smad dang zur za cung zad kyang mi mdzad /
NK133(po)003:3524: sku mdun du zhal nas rgyun du dgos med kyi
NK133(po)003:3525: ngag 'khyal chags sdang gi skad cha sogs nam yang
NK133(po)003:3526: mi 'byung / thugs gshis su sku tsher sgrub pa
NK133(po)003:3527: 'ba' zhig lhur bzhes dgongs kyang bla ma'i bka' lung
NK133(po)003:3528: lci bas bstan dgon khur bzhes dgos pa byung yang
NK133(po)003:3529: mi 'byung / / dus mchod dang chos 'chad nyan
NK133(po)003:3530: skabs min par sku mtshams bsnyen sgrub dge sbyor 'ba'
NK133(po)003:3531: zhig las sos dal du zhag shas kyang mi bzhugs
NK133(po)003:3532: mi 'byung / / / sku gshis rang bzhin gyis
NK133(po)003:3533: btsun zhing khyad par 'dul ba'i bcas mtshams la nan
NK133(po)003:3535: ril po der rgyun par mtshan gung yol tsam nas
NK133(po)003:3536: bzhengs te bka' gter gsar rnying thugs dam chags med
NK133(po)003:3541: bsang gsur tshun bstan don thugs brel bar med skabs su'ang nam yang thang lhod med pa mdzad /
NK133(po)003:3542: mar me zhal zas rgyun mchod dang 'phar ma /
NK133(po)003:3543: s+aats+tsha rdo 'bum dar lcog mang po dang /
NK133(po)003:3545: cho 'phrul zla bar phyi rgyud skor dang /
NK133(po)003:3546: sa zlar bla med skor bcas rgyud sde sum cu'i sgrub mchod /
NK133(po)003:3547: chu stod zla bar tshes bcu'i sgrub chen /
NK133(po)003:3548: 'das mchod zhi khro dang thugs gsang /
NK133(po)003:3550: dgun khar bka' brgyad nyi ldog dus gtor sogs sku rim rnam mang /
NK133(po)003:3552: sgrub grwa nyer lnga'i phog sogs dus mchod rnams kyi
NK133(po)003:3553: gtong thebs bar skabs nyams pa rnams gsar 'dzug dang
NK133(po)003:3554: / sgrub chen 'phar ma mang po snga rjes zhi
NK133(po)003:3555: khro'i zhe dgu sogs tshogs bsags mang po'i rgyur btang
NK133(po)003:3556: ba las dad rdzas gnas min du chud zos phra
NK133(po)003:3558: phyag rdzas rnams 'phral byung 'phral dag las phug nor du ci yang mi 'chang /
NK133(po)003:3559: bka' gter rtsa gsum chos skyong bcas pa'i bsnyen sgrub ma mdzad pa med pa lta bu la /
NK133(po)003:3560: de dag gi skabs su dngos grub brnyes pa'i rtags
NK133(po)003:3561: dngos nyams rmi lam ci rigs byung gsungs pa dang
NK133(po)003:3562: / sgrub chen rnams kyi skabs su bdud rtsi thod
NK133(po)003:3563: chang phyur ba dang byin 'bebs pa'i dngos rtags bzang
NK133(po)003:3564: po re rgyun par byung gsungs /
NK133(po)003:3565: rgyal bstan spyi rim gyi las sbyor rnams la rtags
NK133(po)003:3566: mtshan ci rigs dang srung mas bstan dgra'i sha khrag
NK133(po)003:3568: rig 'dzin sna tshogs rang grol gyis rje 'dis rdzogs
NK133(po)003:3569: chen tshad phebs kyi rtogs pa brnyes 'dug ces basngagasa
NK133(po)003:3571: snang sems 'dres pa'i rtags su rdo la zhabs rjes bzhag pa dang /
NK133(po)003:3572: khang pa ri brag gis sgrib pa'i pha rol gyi
NK133(po)003:3573: mi yi smras pa'i gtam dang byed spyod sogs gsal
NK133(po)003:3575: sprul sku ngos 'dzin mdzad pas bstan pa la phan
NK133(po)003:3576: pa mang po byung ba sogs thugs rje dang smon
NK133(po)003:3577: lam gyi mthu bsam gyis mi khyab /
NK133(po)003:3578: thun min zhal gzigs lung bstan sogs ngo mtshar gyi
NK133(po)003:3579: rnam thar mang du 'dug kyang thugs sgam pas gsang
NK133(po)003:3580: mdzad / slad nas bshad grwa 'dzug pa /
NK133(po)003:3582: sku tshe ji srid tshe mtshams bzhugs rtsis sogs thugs bzhed mang ba rten 'brel 'phro can song /
NK133(po)003:3583: dgung grangs nga gsum bzhes pa me rta zla ba
NK133(po)003:3584: gsum pa'i tshes nyer bzhi la zag med 'od gsal
NK133(po)003:3585: dbyings su bsdus / sku gdung zhugs 'bul skabs /
NK133(po)003:3586: nam mkha' g.ya' dag cing mdangs gsal ba /
NK133(po)003:3587: nam mkha' 'ja' sprin gyis gur phub pa /
NK133(po)003:3588: sbrang char zim bu babs pa /
NK133(po)003:3589: ring bsrel mang du byung ba sogs dang /
NK133(po)003:3590: dad ldan 'ga' la dag pa'i mthong snang /
NK133(po)003:3591: sna tshogs kyang byung bar snang ngo //
NK133(po)003:3592: dgongs rdzogs gser zangs byang chub mchod /
NK133(po)003:3593: na sku tshad mtho sum cu pa lo re bzhin
NK133(po)003:3594: dge 'dun sum cu skor gyis sku gsum sgrub pa
NK133(po)003:3596: bshad grwa tshug pa sogs bzang po'i phrin las gong 'phel du gyur to //
NK133(po)003:3597: rje karma 'gyur med kyi sku gsung thugs sprul du
NK133(po)003:3598: ngos 'dzin pa lha sprul pad+ma gar dbang bstan 'dzin
NK133(po)003:3599: zhes gtsang sgam grub pa'i sa mthor gshegs pa nyid
NK133(po)003:3600: rab yid chu byi la 'khrungs nas gya bzhi rab
NK133(po)003:3601: rgyal chu phag bar sku tshe dang mdzad phrin mtha'
NK133(po)003:3602: yas thugs bzhed thams cad lhun gyis grub /
NK133(po)003:3603: karma lha dbang gi yang srid gzi sprul 'jam dbyangs
NK133(po)003:3604: shes rab chos kyi snang ba rab tshes shing stag
NK133(po)003:3605: la 'khrungs nas mdo sngags rig gnas dang bcas pa
NK133(po)003:3606: la mkhyen pa gting zab cing mkhas pa chen po'i
NK133(po)003:3608: 'khrul zhig byang chub sems dpa' de dang /
NK133(po)003:3609: sa skya kun blo'i rnam 'phrul rgya kha sangs rgyas
NK133(po)003:3610: ye shes kyi sprul pa gyang sprul pad+ma theg mchog
NK133(po)003:3611: rim gnyis kyi rnal 'byor rtser son cing byang chub
NK133(po)003:3612: sems kyi mnga' bdag can de rnams dam pa'i rnam
NK133(po)003:3613: thar phul du byung ba sha stag go //
NK133(po)003:3614: 'di skabs kyi shes rab byams pa mtha' yas de'ang bar khyims shes rab rgya mtsho'i sprul par gsungs /
NK133(po)003:3615: sku btsun zhing sgrub tshug snying rus che /
NK133(po)003:3616: rje chos kyi nyi ma'i slob mar khrid dpon dang
NK133(po)003:3617: gshegs rjes dbang lung dang khrid rgyun bskyang ba sogs
NK133(po)003:3618: bstan pa la phan pa byung /
NK133(po)003:3619: sku gshegs skabs 'ja' 'od sogs ngo mtshar ltas dang
NK133(po)003:3620: gdung rus phra mo tsam yang ma byung ba klong
NK133(po)003:3621: sde'i brgyud pa sba sgom sogs bzhin 'ja' lus chung
NK133(po)003:3622: ngu yin zhes mkhan ngag dga' rin po ches gsungs
NK133(po)003:3623: / khyad par rje chos kyi nyi mas mnal lam
NK133(po)003:3624: du sku gdung bar khang lta bur bzhugs par rdzong
NK133(po)003:3625: nang bla ma lta bu zhig gis 'dir pad+ma nor
NK133(po)003:3626: bu bzhugs 'dug gsungs pas yar gzigs tshe mchod rten
NK133(po)003:3627: bum sgo zhig na pad+ma nor bu dbu dkar ba
NK133(po)003:3628: sogs ji lta ba bzhugs 'dug pa bzhengs nas sku
NK133(po)003:3629: rtsar phebs tshe byis pa zhig tu song ba rmis
NK133(po)003:3630: pa phyir nyin sprul sku 'di nyid ji lta bar
NK133(po)003:3631: / 'dug pa dang / grub dbang pad+ma nor bus
NK133(po)003:3632: sku gshegs khar nyid kyi gzim khang rtsar shug sdong
NK133(po)003:3633: yod pa 'di la shugs 'bras nam byung ba na
NK133(po)003:3634: nga yi skyes mtha' zhig 'ong gsung pa ltar shug
NK133(po)003:3635: 'bras byung nas lo shas gyur pa dang 'grigs pas
NK133(po)003:3636: 'jam mgon kong sprul rin po che sogs kyi dgongs
NK133(po)003:3637: brtags kyang babs pa bcas kyis sku bdag mdzad pa
NK133(po)003:3638: mkhan chen ngag dpal gyis mchan lha lung dpal gyi
NK133(po)003:3639: / 'dug pa dang / rdo rje / gter chen sangs rgyas gling pa /
NK133(po)003:3640: rdo grub kun bzang gzhan phan sku gong 'og sogs kyi sprul par lung bstan pa /
NK133(po)003:3641: gdan rab dgu pa pad+ma kun bzang /
NK133(po)003:3642: bstan 'dzin nor bu'i thub bstan chos kyi glang po ni rab tshes me phag la 'khrungs /
NK133(po)003:3643: dgung lo bdun nas dpal yul gdan sar bkod /
NK133(po)003:3644: dgu nas o rgyan rin po ches zhal gzigs shing byin gyis rlabs /
NK133(po)003:3645: rje chos kyi nyi ma las rab tu byung zhing /
NK133(po)003:3650: mdo sgyu sogs bka' ma'i chos skor ji snyed gsan /
NK133(po)003:3651: dpal spungs bla ma bkra 'phel las bka' 'gyur rin po che /
NK133(po)003:3652: bla ma stobs ldan rgyal mtshan 'od zer las rin chen gter mdzod sogs dang /
NK133(po)003:3653: dpal kahthoga tu byon nas mdo sngags kyi gzhung lugs
NK133(po)003:3654: che phra brgya phrag nye ba thugs la chub par
NK133(po)003:3655: mdzad / kahthoga si tu chos kyi rgya mtsho las
NK133(po)003:3656: gdams mdzod sogs gsan cing mdor na bka' gter gsar
NK133(po)003:3657: rnying skor gsan rgya shin tu che /
NK133(po)003:3658: khyad par nyid kyi rigs bdag thun min kun mkhyen
NK133(po)003:3659: klong chen pa'i rnam 'phrul mkhan chen ngag dbang dpal
NK133(po)003:3660: bzang las zhi 'tsho'i sdom rgyun las bsnyen par rdzogs
NK133(po)003:3662: rdzogs chen gyi khrid btab pas theg mchog rdo rje rtse mo'i dgongs pa rtsal rdzogs /
NK133(po)003:3663: brda go'i gtsug lag me skyon shor pa la lha
NK133(po)003:3664: sprul rin po ches cha rkyen brtsal ba bcas kyis
NK133(po)003:3665: slar gsos / dpal yul bshad grwa gsar 'dzug dang
NK133(po)003:3666: gter mdzod tshar bzhi sogs bka' gter dbang lung mdo
NK133(po)003:3667: rgyud 'chad nyan tshad med pa mdzad /
NK133(po)003:3668: snying tig chos bka' gtsang mar 'dzin pa'i dgon lag gsar 'debs gnyis dang /
NK133(po)003:3669: dpal yul nye phyogs lha khang brgyad gsar bzhengs dang
NK133(po)003:3670: so sor sgrub mchod rten thebs bzhag pa sogs bshad
NK133(po)003:3671: sgrub las gsum gyi bstan la bya ba rgya chen
NK133(po)003:3672: po mdzad / mthar phyag rdzas spong dag gis brda gor dpal chen 'dus pa dang /
NK133(po)003:3673: dpal yul grwa tshang khag bzhir smin gling rdor sems
NK133(po)003:3674: sgrub pa lo ltar gyi thebs bzhag sogs dge rtsar
NK133(po)003:3675: smin par mdzad / nyid rang bya bral kun gyi
NK133(po)003:3676: brtul zhugs kyis snying po'i sgrub pa la gzhol bzhin
NK133(po)003:3677: dgung lo zhe drug nas mngon dag'i zhing du thugs
NK133(po)003:3678: gtad bzhin zhi dbyings su gshegs /
NK133(po)003:3679: sku gdung sbyang tshe ngo mtshar ba'i rtags mtshan mang du byung /
NK133(po)003:3680: gsung rtsom kyang pu sti drug tsam bzhugs so //
NK133(po)003:3681: mchog sprul rin po che thub bstan chos kyi zla ba'am 'jam dpal dgyes pa'i rdo rje /
NK133(po)003:3682: rab tshes shing rta la rgya sprul 'khrungs yul rgya rong rgya kha phyogs 'khrungs /
NK133(po)003:3683: gzi sprul chos kyi snang ba'i sprul par ngos 'dzin
NK133(po)003:3684: kyang grub chen byams pa chos rgyal sogs kyis pad+ma
NK133(po)003:3685: mdo sngags bstan 'dzin gyi sprul pa 'khrul med yin
NK133(po)003:3686: par gsungs / sku na phra ba las gong ma'i gdan sa dpal yul gser khrir bkod /
NK133(po)003:3687: rje chos kyi nyi ma las bka' chos ci rigs gsan /
NK133(po)003:3688: mkhas dbang bsod nams dpal ldan sogs las mdo sngags kyi gzhung lugs rab 'byams gsan /
NK133(po)003:3689: skyes thob dang sbyor byung gi mkhyen rab tshad med /
NK133(po)003:3690: kahthoga si tu pan chen las smad 'dul gyi sdom rgyun gsan /
NK133(po)003:3692: lha sprul pad+ma gar dbang bstan 'dzin mtha' yas dang
NK133(po)003:3693: thub bstan chos kyi glang po las phyag rdzogs kyi
NK133(po)003:3694: khrid rim dang bka' gter smin grol rgya mtsho lta
NK133(po)003:3695: bu gsan / rgyun par rtsa ba gsum gyi bsnyen
NK133(po)003:3696: sgrub mdzad pa bka' gter smin grol gyi char 'bebs
NK133(po)003:3697: pa sogs dam pa'i tshul dgu'i yon tan rgya mtsho
NK133(po)003:3699: dpal dgon la phyag phreng gis rten gsum la gnod
NK133(po)003:3700: pa gso ba dang gser gyi rgya phib gsar bzhengs
NK133(po)003:3701: mdzad / 'go log dang gser thar skor gyi dgon
NK133(po)003:3702: pa 'ga' la snga rjes bad gzar byung ba rnams
NK133(po)003:3703: nyams gsos dang dbang lung khrid gsum gyi bka' drin
NK133(po)003:3705: a mdo'i yul tshun gyi gsar rnying ris med kyi chos sde rnams la bsnyen bskur phyag 'gyed /
NK133(po)003:3706: dbus gtsang gnas gzigs dang 'brel chos 'khor gsum sogs gnas dang rten la mchod 'bul /
NK133(po)003:3707: se 'bras dga' ldan bkra shis lhun po mtshur phu sogs la mang bskol phyag 'gyed /
NK133(po)003:3708: rdor smin dpal ri sogs rnying ma'i gdan sa rnams la bsnyen bskur zhib spros dang /
NK133(po)003:3709: rnying lugs dgon che phra ji snyed pa la 'gyed
NK133(po)003:3710: dang mang ja brtsal slar dpal yul du rin chen
NK133(po)003:3712: kahthoga mkhan po legs bshad 'byor ldan las dbang chos 'ga' yang gsan /
NK133(po)003:3713: dar thang dgon la nyams gsos rten gsum bzhengs pa
NK133(po)003:3714: bshad grwa gsar 'dzug sogs spang klog las gsum gyi
NK133(po)003:3715: mdzad pa rnams kyang yid bzhin nor bu dbang gi
NK133(po)003:3716: rgyal po bzhin 'tsho zhing bzhes pa slad kyang zhabs
NK133(po)003:3717: pad bskal pa rgya mtshor 'tsho gzhes g.yo med gsol
NK133(po)003:3719: gdan rab bcu pa karma bkra shis sku phreng bzhi pa ni /
NK133(po)003:3720: rab tshes phur bu sa sprel la yab yum grub
NK133(po)003:3721: pa'i rig 'dzin gyi gdung rigs rmad du byung ba
NK133(po)003:3722: la bltams / rgyal dbang bco lnga pa mkha' khyab
NK133(po)003:3723: rdo rjes rje chos kyi nyi ma'i yang srid du
NK133(po)003:3724: lung bstan cing karma theg mchog snying po dri med
NK133(po)003:3725: yongs grub sde zhes mtshan gyi cod pan dpyangs /
NK133(po)003:3726: dpal yul gdan sar gser khrir bkod /
NK133(po)003:3727: rje thub bstan chos kyi glang po la gtsug phud
NK133(po)003:3728: phul zhing rin chen gter mdzod sogs rang lugs bka'
NK133(po)003:3729: gter smin grol mtha' yas pa gsan /
NK133(po)003:3730: rdzogs chen bla ma rig 'dzin 'od zer las mdo sngags gzhung bshad mang zhig gsan /
NK133(po)003:3731: byams mgon t+aa'i si tu pad+ma dbang mchog rgyal po las bsnyen par rdzogs /
NK133(po)003:3732: mtshan karma mdo sngags bshad sgrub bstan pa'i nyi ma gsol /
NK133(po)003:3733: sku btsun pa'i mchog tu gyur /
NK133(po)003:3734: rje chos kyi glang po dang grub brnyes rig 'dzin
NK133(po)003:3735: sna tshogs rang grol gyis rdzogs chen khrid brtsal bas
NK133(po)003:3736: sngon sbyang gi 'phro dang dam pa'i byin rlabs stobs
NK133(po)003:3737: kyis thugs dgongs gtad med 'dzin med snang ba gdong
NK133(po)003:3738: 'ded chos sku khyab gdal gyi dus 'da'/
NK133(po)003:3739: rje gong ma'i phrin las kyi 'phro bskyang phyir bka'
NK133(po)003:3740: ma'i chos skor sgyu 'phrul phra mo drug cu sogs
NK133(po)003:3741: gzhung rnying skor pu sti bcu phrag spar bzhengs pa
NK133(po)003:3742: dang gtsug lag khang nyams gsos dang /
NK133(po)003:3743: bla brang khang pa gsar bzo /
NK133(po)003:3744: rten gsum mchod rdzas 'chams chas 'phan gdugs gsar bskrun /
NK133(po)003:3745: smin grol 'chad spel dang bskyed rdzogs nyams bzhes kyi
NK133(po)003:3746: sku mtshams bcad rgya bzhugs pa sogs dam pa'i rnam
NK133(po)003:3747: thar can nyid zhabs pad 'chi med mgon po'i ngo
NK133(po)003:3749: rnam thar phyi ma gsum me khyi la bsnan pa'o //
NK133(po)003:3750: mchan de ltar bstan 'dzin gyi skyes bu bstan pa'i
NK133(po)003:3751: rgyal mtshan srid rtser bsgreng ba'i phrin las can byon
NK133(po)003:3752: dang 'byung gyur gser ri'i phreng ba lta bu'o //
NK133(po)003:3753: chos brgyud 'dzin pa'i dgon lag ni rje kun bzang
NK133(po)003:3754: shes rab kyi zhal slob thugs kyi bu chen bzhi
NK133(po)003:3755: yi nang nas gser pa ye shes seng ge'i lha
NK133(po)003:3757: gtsang mda' rdo rje thar gyi gtsang mda' dgon /
NK133(po)003:3759: 400 shug sgang rba ding gi shug rgang dgon 40bzhi po dang /
NK133(po)003:3760: tsha kho brtson 'grus rgya mtsho'i tsha kho 'od gsal
NK133(po)003:3761: gling sogs las rim 'phel du song ba'i rgya stong
NK133(po)003:3762: phyogs / rgya kha sa 'du pad+ma 'od gling /
NK133(po)003:3770: gzi 'gag nor bu gling 400sogs 'bo jo stod smad dgon khag gsum /
NK133(po)003:3771: lcogs rtse dgon khag 'ga' re dang /
NK133(po)003:3790: thim du dgon dang lnga khog nas mtshas rin dgon /
NK133(po)003:3791: mgu log nas dar thang dgon 1000 smad rang dgon 300 'dzi stod bram sgang dgon /
NK133(po)003:3799: gser khog nas grub bzang dgon /
NK133(po)003:3806: gnub zo dgon300 rgya shug dgon /
NK133(po)003:3808: sing sing dung dkar dgon 600 rdo khog nas rta shugs dgon /
NK133(po)003:3811: rdo smad bkra shis chos gling 300 dbon po dgon /
NK133(po)003:3812: snyi khog nas gtsang chen dgon /
NK133(po)003:3814: sgo chen dgon 700 lcog keng dgon /
NK133(po)003:3816: mchog tshang stag lung dgon 700 snying lung ser dgon
NK133(po)003:3817: 1000 'bum shug dgon 300 li gtsang nas li stod
NK133(po)003:3818: mdo mang dgon 300 li smad a sug dgon /
NK133(po)003:3826: sde dge'i khul du rag khyab bstan nam gling /
NK133(po)003:3831: spo li 'gu ro rnam rgyal dgon /
NK133(po)003:3840: go 'jo'i phyogs su kha legs sgar /
NK133(po)003:3850: bal bod mtshams gangs ti se'i nye phyogs chos sde gsar /
NK133(po)003:3852: mdo smad kyi ljongs 'dir ri khrod dang dgon sde
NK133(po)003:3853: che chung shin tu mang zhing 'dir che lang tsam
NK133(po)003:3854: zhig bkod pa yin te mdor na rgya yul yan
NK133(po)003:3855: chad kyi dge 'dun thams cad bgrangs na deng dus
NK133(po)003:3856: dge 'dun nyis khri lhag tsam yod 'dug ces /
NK133(po)003:3857: mchog sprul rin po ches gsungs pa dgon sde de
NK133(po)003:3858: dag 'dul khrims gtsang mas gzhi bzung zhing mdo sngags
NK133(po)003:3859: rig gnas dang bcas par mkhas pa'i go sar dbang
NK133(po)003:3860: 'byor ba dang / khyad par tshe dang sgrub pa
NK133(po)003:3861: mnyam pa'i rtogs pa mchog ldan gyi gang zag mang
NK133(po)003:3862: po byon pa'ang rje kun bzang shes rab kyi thugs
NK133(po)003:3863: bskyed dang smon lam bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i stobs
NK133(po)003:3864: 'byor ba dang / las byung ba'o // gzhan yang
NK133(po)003:3865: kun mkhyen rnam 'phrul stag bla pad+ma blo gros dbon
NK133(po)003:3866: brgyud bcas pa'i gdan sa rnams dang /
NK133(po)003:3867: gnam bskos dgon rgya bla bkra shis lhun grub nas rim byon sogs snga 'gyur gyi bstan 'dzin /
NK133(po)003:3869: de dag ni bstan pa'i gzhi ma rab byung dge 'dun gyi sde rag rim smos pa ste /
NK133(po)003:3870: gzhan rnying chos 'dzin pa'i sngags sde ni /
NK133(po)003:3874: zab lung sogs mang po dang /
NK133(po)003:3875: khams phyogs re dkar sngags gra /
NK133(po)003:3876: sgo ma sngags gra khri phrag sogs shin tu mang
NK133(po)003:3877: la de dag tu gsang sngags lam la nus pa
NK133(po)003:3878: thob pa'ang ji snyed zhig yod par mngon te /
NK133(po)003:3880: khyim na gnas kyang yang dag lta ba dad //
NK133(po)003:3881: dkon mchog gsum la bla mar byed pa rnams //
NK133(po)003:3882: theg pa chen po'i gdul bya nyid yin phyir //
NK133(po)003:3883: gsung pa ltar 'di dag rtags tsam 'dzin pa phal las cung drag snyam sems so //
NK133(po)003:3884: khyad par rgyal bstan yongs su rdzogs pa'i mnga' bdag
NK133(po)003:3885: tu gyur kyang gsang chen snga 'gyur ba'i bstan pa
NK133(po)003:3886: la bka' drin tshad med pa'i 'jam mgon rnam gnyis
NK133(po)003:3887: su grags pa'i 'jam dbyangs mkhyen brtse'i dbang po ni
NK133(po)003:3888: / rgyal kun yab gcig rje btsun 'jam pa'i dbyangs /
NK133(po)003:3891: sgo mtha' yas pa'i blo gros /
NK133(po)003:3903: 'jigs med gling pa sogs gang 'dul gyi bkod pa
NK133(po)003:3904: mtha' yas ston pa'i mthar rab yid lcags 'brug la
NK133(po)003:3905: 'khrungs / sku chung ngu nas myur mdzad mgon po
NK133(po)003:3906: dang e ka dza tis rtag tu srung zhing dam
NK133(po)003:3908: skyes thob kyi glegs bam phal cher tshar re gzigs pas tshig don thugs su chud pa dang /
NK133(po)003:3909: bstod tshogs dang gsung mgur sogs sku na phra ba'i
NK133(po)003:3910: skabasakyi gsung brtsams rigs kyang mthong ba tsam gyis byang
NK133(po)003:3911: sems smon lam gyis skye ba bzhes pa gor ma
NK133(po)003:3912: chags / thar rtse mkhan chen nam mkha' 'chi med kyi sprul skur mnga' gsol /
NK133(po)003:3913: dgung lo bco brgyad nas ze chen mthu stobs rnam rgyal las rig gnas phal mo che dang /
NK133(po)003:3914: 'phan po na len+d+ra'i grwa sar gzim 'og bstan 'dzin
NK133(po)003:3915: snyan grags las mtshan nyid kyi gzhung rnams rdzogs par
NK133(po)003:3916: mdzad / nyer gcig grwa phyi smin grol gling du
NK133(po)003:3917: mkhan po rig 'dzin bzang po las smad 'dul gyi
NK133(po)003:3918: rgyun gsan bsnyen par rdzogs shing sdom pa gsum gyis
NK133(po)003:3919: thugs brgyud bltams sa skya bdag chen rdo rje rin
NK133(po)003:3920: chen sogs las sa ngor gyi smin grol gzhung lugs
NK133(po)003:3921: rdzogs par gsan pa sogs snga phyir dbus gtsang khams
NK133(po)003:3922: gsum gyi bla ma brgya dang lnga bcu tsam brten
NK133(po)003:3923: nas bzo gso sgra tshad yan lag bcas dang /
NK133(po)003:3925: dbu phar rnams kyi bshad srol ji snyed thams cad gsan /
NK133(po)003:3929: bka' brgyud sogs bshad brgyud ka chen bcu dang sgrub brgyud shing rta brgyad kyis rgyun bzhugs rigs dang /
NK133(po)003:3931: dus 'khor sgyu 'phrul gsang snying sogs kyi smin grol
NK133(po)003:3932: rgyud bshad bcas sngon gyi lugs srol ma nyams pa'i
NK133(po)003:3934: rgyab brten lung rgyun kyang pu sti ka bdun brgya tsam gsan /
NK133(po)003:3935: de dag rang rang gi lta grub khas len grub matha'i rnam bzhag sogs dpyis phyin par mdzad /
NK133(po)003:3936: sku tshe der 'dir snang gi bya bzhag cung zad
NK133(po)003:3937: kyang med par tshe blos btang ba'i bya bral gong
NK133(po)003:3938: ma'i rnam thar gyis lo bcu gsum bar bcad rgya'i
NK133(po)003:3939: dam bca' dang / slad nas sku tshe ji srid
NK133(po)003:3940: bar them spang gi dam bca' bcas sgrub pa snying
NK133(po)003:3941: dam bca' dang / por mdzad / sku na gzhon
NK133(po)003:3942: nu'i dus nas rim bgrod tsam min par rdzogs chen
NK133(po)003:3943: rang snang ris med kyi dgongs pa mngon du gyur
NK133(po)003:3944: pas snang spyod thams cad ye shes dag pa'i gzigs
NK133(po)003:3945: snang dus skad rig rer yang brjod las 'das shing
NK133(po)003:3946: dam bca' dang / por mdzad / / khyad par
NK133(po)003:3947: sgrub brgyud shing rta brgyad kyi rgyun gsan pa dang
NK133(po)003:3948: sgrub pa nyam bzhes mdzad tshe /
NK133(po)003:3953: lce btsun sogs rnying ma dang /
NK133(po)003:3958: mar pa sogs bka' brgyud kyi grub chen rnams dang /
NK133(po)003:3962: chos rgyal rigs ldan brgyud bcas /
NK133(po)003:3963: grub thob o rgyan pa sogs gdams pa so so'i
NK133(po)003:3964: srol 'byed kyi mkhas grub chen po rnams kyis mngon
NK133(po)003:3965: sum ye shes skus rjes su bzung zhing gdams ngag
NK133(po)003:3967: rang rang gi dgongs don rtogs pa'i gdeng thob pas bstan pa yongs rdzogs kyi bka' bab thob /
NK133(po)003:3974: snyan brgyud bcas bka' bab bdun la dbang 'byor /
NK133(po)003:3975: kar rnying sa dge sogs phyogs dang ris su ma chad pa'i 'dus pa tshad bzung med par /
NK133(po)003:3976: chos gang gsan thams cad phal cher yang nas yang
NK133(po)003:3977: du 'chad pa dang lan re ma gsung pa med
NK133(po)003:3978: / de dag gsar rnying gang gi lugs 'chad kyang
NK133(po)003:3979: de dang de'i grub mtha' rang gzhung gi dgongs don
NK133(po)003:3980: gting mthar phyin pa'i dgag sgrub sogs de'i lugs gtsang
NK133(po)003:3981: sing nge ba'i ljags bshad nyin mtshan bar med kyi
NK133(po)003:3982: / chos sbyin brtsal / gnas gzhi gsar 'debs ni /
NK133(po)003:3983: khams bye'i bshad grwa'i gzhi 'ding brtsam las gzhan ma mdzad kyang /
NK133(po)003:3984: nyag rong dmag zing skabs dgon sde mang po 'thor zhig rnams nyams gso sogs /
NK133(po)003:3985: phyogs tha dag gi bstan pa ris su ma chad
NK133(po)003:3986: par dngos brgyud nas phan pa tshad med pa dang
NK133(po)003:3987: / gser zangs kyi sku rten khyad mtshar stong phrag gnyis /
NK133(po)003:3988: gsung rten glegs bam bzhi bcu'i spar dang /
NK133(po)003:3989: dpe cha gsar bzhengs pu sti nyis stong /
NK133(po)003:3990: thugs rten mchod sdong chen mo sogs gser zangs kyi mchod rten brgya phrag /
NK133(po)003:3991: de rnams bzhugs pa'i lha khang khag bcu gsum bkod
NK133(po)003:3992: mdzes la dus dang rgyun gyi mchod pa phun sum
NK133(po)003:3993: tshogs pa dang / phyag rjes bstan bcos kyang rgyal
NK133(po)003:3994: bstan ris su ma chad pa sgo du ma nas
NK133(po)003:3995: tshogs pa dang / 'phel ba dang / khyad par
NK133(po)003:3996: rgyun phra ba rnams bstan rgyun mi nub par 'phel
NK133(po)003:3997: tshogs pa dang / 'phel ba dang / ba dang
NK133(po)003:3998: / sa dge sogs kyi lugs rgyas pa rnams kyang
NK133(po)003:3999: gdul bya ris med kyi spyod yul du bskal ba
NK133(po)003:4000: bzang po'i dga' ston 'gyed phyir 'chad 'gyur mdzod chen
NK133(po)003:4001: lnga dang gsang chen rgyud sde rab 'byams phyogs gcig
NK133(po)003:4002: tu dpon slob rin po che blo gter dbang pos
NK133(po)003:4003: bsgrigs pa'i rgyud sde kun btus rnams kyang rje 'di'i
NK133(po)003:4004: thugs bskyed tshad med pa'i nye bar len pa'i bdag
NK133(po)003:4005: rkyen las byung ba yin la /
NK133(po)003:4006: khyad par sgrub thabs rgya mtsho dang brgya rtsa sogs
NK133(po)003:4007: 'phags yul grub pa'i dbang phyug rnams kyi bka' srol
NK133(po)003:4008: gangs can na bzhugs so 'tshal phyogs gcig tu bsgrigs
NK133(po)003:4009: pa'i sgrub thabs kun 'dus chen mo ljags bsgrigs mdzad
NK133(po)003:4010: de spar du bkod pa sogs thugs rtsol chen pos
NK133(po)003:4011: sgrub ste rgyal bstan gzhir bzhengs su gsal zhing ris
NK133(po)003:4012: su ma chad pa'i gdul bya rnams skal ba bzang
NK133(po)003:4013: po'i dpal la bkod pa'i bka' drin gyi phyag rjes
NK133(po)003:4014: phyi ma'i dus 'dir 'gran zlas dben par mdzad de
NK133(po)003:4015: dgung grangs don gsum par sprul gzhi bi ma la'i
NK133(po)003:4016: thugs kar bsdus te slar yang ngo mtshar sprul pa'i
NK133(po)003:4017: zlos gar gyis ris med bstan 'gro'i don rlabs po
NK133(po)003:4018: che mdzad pa'i bslu med rdo rje'i lung gi mngon
NK133(po)003:4020: 'jam mgon bla ma yon tan rgya mtsho blo gros mtha' yas pa'i sde ni /
NK133(po)003:4021: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyis mdo ting 'dzin rgyal po /
NK133(po)003:4025: snga 'gyur kalba dum bu'i rgyud sogs dang /
NK133(po)003:4026: gter lung mang po nas gsal bar bstan cing /
NK133(po)003:4027: de'ang mtshan sgra mthun pa tsam ma yin par rnam
NK133(po)003:4028: thar mdzad phrin sogs tshad ldan gyi rigs pas dpyad
NK133(po)003:4044: gter bdag gling pa sogs dag pa'i skye srid mang
NK133(po)003:4045: po'i mthar rab yid chu bya la khyung po'i rigs
NK133(po)003:4046: las 'khrungs / klog ma bslab par mkhyen pa sogs
NK133(po)003:4047: sngon sbyang las 'phro sad tshul 'gran zla dkon par
NK133(po)003:4048: las 'khrungs / snang / dgung lo bco lnga nas
NK133(po)003:4049: gu ru rin po ches zhal gzigs shing byin gyis
NK133(po)003:4050: las 'khrungs / snang / brlabs / dgung lo bcu
NK133(po)003:4051: drug par ze chen mthu stobs rnam rgyal las tha
NK133(po)003:4052: snyad rig gnas yan lag bcas /
NK133(po)003:4053: grub mtha' rgya mtsho'i rnam bzhag /
NK133(po)003:4054: rdo rje theg pa'i man ngag bcas dang /
NK133(po)003:4056: bka' brgyad dgongs 'dus kun mkhyen yab sras bka' 'bum sogs gsan /
NK133(po)003:4057: dpal spungs yid dga' chos 'dzin du rdo rje 'chang
NK133(po)003:4058: pad+ma nyin byed las sdom pa gsum gyis rgyud bsdom
NK133(po)003:4059: zhing rgyal bka' rin po che sogs zab rgyas kyi
NK133(po)003:4060: gdams pa rgya mtshos rjes su bzung /
NK133(po)003:4061: ye shes kyi dgongs pas byin gyis rlabs shing snying
NK133(po)003:4062: po'i bstan pa gtad nas rgyal tshab tu dbang bskur
NK133(po)003:4064: gra smin grol gling sngags 'chang chen po sangs rgyas
NK133(po)003:4065: kun dga' mtshur phu rgyal ba'i dbang po yab sras
NK133(po)003:4066: sogs ris med kyi skyes chen brgya phrag phyed kyi
NK133(po)003:4067: zhabs pad brten nas bod 'dir yongs su grags pa'i
NK133(po)003:4068: bshad rgyun ka chen bcu dang sgrub brgyud shing rta
NK133(po)003:4069: brgyad rjes 'brang dang bcas pa'i ring lugs deng sang
NK133(po)003:4071: yang khrod kun bzang bde chen gling du kun spang ba'i dam bcas /
NK133(po)003:4072: gsar rnying gi dkyil 'khor chen po brgya phrag nye
NK133(po)003:4073: ba'i ljags bsnyen dang de dag gi rdzogs rim rnams
NK133(po)003:4074: nyam bzhes mthar phyin par mdzad pa'i tshe grub pa'i
NK133(po)003:4075: mngon rtags mtha' yas pa brnyes te 'gran bral gyi
NK133(po)003:4077: gnas chen rnams su snga rjes bka' gter gyi sgrub
NK133(po)003:4078: chen kho na'ang brgya dang lnga bcu lhag bcas bstan
NK133(po)003:4079: 'gro'i bde thabs mdzad cing ngo mtshar ba'i rtags mtshan
NK133(po)003:4080: mang po dang / sgrub khang nas zang thal du
NK133(po)003:4081: gshegs pa rdo la phyag zhabs kyi rjes 'jog pa
NK133(po)003:4082: mang po dang / / mngon shes sgrib med /
NK133(po)003:4083: 'ja' 'od me tog char sogs ngo mtshar ba'i rtags
NK133(po)003:4084: mtshan dang snyigs dus kyi dam sri gdug pa can
NK133(po)003:4086: bstan pa yun ring du gnas phyir mdo sngags rig
NK133(po)003:4087: gnas dang bcas pa spyi la khyab pa'i bstan bcos
NK133(po)003:4089: bde dgyes gsang gsum sgyu thod gdan bzhi yang phur
NK133(po)003:4090: gshin rje sogs bla med kyi rgyud sde zab cing
NK133(po)003:4091: dkon pa rnams phyogs gcig tu bsgrigs pa'i bka' brgyud
NK133(po)003:4092: sngags mdzod / rnying ma'i gter ston nyis brgyar nye
NK133(po)003:4093: ba'i gdams phran rigs phyogs gcig tu bsdus pa rin
NK133(po)003:4094: sngags mdzod / chen gter mdzod / kar rnying /
NK133(po)003:4099: o rgyan pa'i bsnyen sgrub bcas sgrub brgyud brgyad rjes
NK133(po)003:4100: 'brel dang bcas khrid phran mang po'i dbang dang gdams
NK133(po)003:4101: ngag phyogs gcig tu bsdus pa gdams ngag mdzod /
NK133(po)003:4102: thun min gsang mdzod nyid kyi zab gter skor rnams dang /
NK133(po)003:4103: gsung rtsom thor bu'i skor bcas phyogs su bsdoms pa
NK133(po)003:4104: rgya chen bka' mdzod bcas mdor na lhag pa'i lhas
NK133(po)003:4105: rjes su gnang bzhin glegs bam brgya phrag brgal ba
NK133(po)003:4106: legs bshad bla na med pa bstan pa mi nub
NK133(po)003:4108: thugs sras slob ma'i tshogs kyang mdo khams kyi bstan 'dzin phal mo che dang /
NK133(po)003:4109: phyogs dang ris su ma chad pa'i rig par smra
NK133(po)003:4110: ba'i mkhas pa sgrub pa'i rgyal mtshan 'dzin pa'i grub
NK133(po)003:4111: brnyes mang po sogs 'dus pa tshad bzung med par
NK133(po)003:4112: rig gnas dang mdo sngags kyi gzhung bshad mang po
NK133(po)003:4113: bka' 'gyur sogs gang gsan gyi bklag lung tshar grangs
NK133(po)003:4114: / mdzod lnga tshar grangs 'chad spel sogs mdor na gsan sbyang /
NK133(po)003:4117: rten bzhengs rnams mi phal pa'i tshe gcig la re
NK133(po)003:4118: re tsam yang gtan nas rdzog sa thabs med pa
NK133(po)003:4119: ni mngon sum gyis grub pa 'di lta bu ni
NK133(po)003:4120: grub pa'i spyod pa gong na med pa shes par
NK133(po)003:4122: de ltar sku tshe dang mdzad phrin mthar phyin nas
NK133(po)003:4123: dgung grangs gya bdun par sgra dang 'od dang sa
NK133(po)003:4124: g.yo ba sogs ngo mtshar ba'i ltas bcas gzugs sku'i
NK133(po)003:4125: bkod pa bsdus nas ma byon sangs rgyas mos pa
NK133(po)003:4126: sogs gang 'dul gyi rnam 'phrul 'khor ba ma stong
NK133(po)003:4127: bar du lhun gyis grub pa'o //
NK133(po)003:4128: snga 'gyur bka' ma theg rim dgu'i phrin chog gzhung
NK133(po)003:4129: phyi mo rnams dang bcas pa'i dkar chag bstan pa
NK133(po)003:4130: rgya mtsho'i gru gzings bkra shis dpal brgya'i 'byung gnas
NK133(po)003:4131: las / deng sang rnying ma'i gdan sa rnams kyi byung tshul brjod pa'i skabs te gnyis pa'o //
NK133(po)003:4132: de dag gis bstan pa'i babs tshul mdo tsam song
NK133(po)003:4133: nas skabs 'dir theg dgu'i lam rim ltar gyi so
NK133(po)003:4134: byang sngags gsum so so'i bla ma brgyud pa'i rim
NK133(po)003:4135: pa mtshan tho rag bsdus su 'god pa la gsum
NK133(po)003:4136: las / thog mar bstan pa'i gzhi ma 'dul ba
NK133(po)003:4137: so thar sdom brgyud la deng sang yod pa kha
NK133(po)003:4138: che'i lugs dang smad 'dul gyi rgyun gnyis las bdag
NK133(po)003:4139: cag gi mkhan po don gyi slad du mtshan nas
NK133(po)003:4140: smos te o rgyan mdo sngags chos kyi nyi ma
NK133(po)003:4141: phyogs las rnam par rgyal ba'i sde ni dpal sh+aakya
NK133(po)003:4142: sh+r+ai'i sdom rgyun las byon pa yin la /
NK133(po)003:4143: 'dir phyi ma snga 'gyur lugs kyi brgyud pa ni /
NK133(po)003:4144: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas /
NK133(po)003:4155: bla chen dgongs pa rab gsal /
NK133(po)003:4156: klu mes tshul khrims shes rab /
NK133(po)003:4158: sne bo grags pa rgyal mtshan /
NK133(po)003:4161: rtsis 'dul ba 'dzin pa gzhon nu seng ge /
NK133(po)003:4162: snar gro mo che bdud rtsi grags /
NK133(po)003:4164: snar thang grags pa shes rab /
NK133(po)003:4165: snar thang mchim blo bzang grags pa /
NK133(po)003:4167: grub pa shes rab ste snar thang mkhan por byon pa drug dang /
NK133(po)003:4168: pan chen thams cad mkhyen pa dge 'dun grub /
NK133(po)003:4169: gnas rnying kun dga' bde legs /
NK133(po)003:4170: thams cad mkhyen pa rgyal ba gnyis pa dge 'dun rgya mtsho /
NK133(po)003:4171: bde ba can pa dge legs dpal bzang /
NK133(po)003:4172: rgyal khang rtse pa dpal 'byor rgya mtsho grwa 'jam dbyangs dkon mchog chos 'phel /
NK133(po)003:4174: smin gling lo chen d+harma sh+r+ai /
NK133(po)003:4176: smin gling mkhan po 'gyur med chos ldan /
NK133(po)003:4177: lo chen sprul pa o rgyan bstan 'dzin rdo rje /
NK133(po)003:4179: rdzogs chen mkhan po pad+ma bkra shis /
NK133(po)003:4180: dge mang rin po che thub bstan pad+ma rgyas pa'i nyin byed /
NK133(po)003:4182: dza sprul kun bzang rnam rgyal /
NK133(po)003:4183: mkhan thub bstan rgyal mtshan 'od zer /
NK133(po)003:4184: mkhan chen ngag dbang dpal bzang nas /
NK133(po)003:4185: skyabs rje thub bstan chos kyi glang po'i zhal snga nas kyi bar byon pa'o //
NK133(po)003:4186: 'dul ba'i bshad rgyun ni ston pa sangs rgyas /
NK133(po)003:4195: phyir mi 'ong blos mi phebs pa /
NK133(po)003:4209: ko khyim ye shes bla ma /
NK133(po)003:4210: nyang mtshams rin chen bla ma /
NK133(po)003:4212: rma tshe byang chub rdo rje /
NK133(po)003:4221: dmar ston rgya mtsho rin chen nam /
NK133(po)003:4223: rma tshe'i slob ma skyid shod pa tshul khrims 'phags
NK133(po)003:4224: nas dmar ston dpal ldan rin chen bar bla ma
NK133(po)003:4225: brgyad brgyud de / dmar ston rgya mtsho rin chen de nas /
NK133(po)003:4236: de gnyis kas bkra shis rgyal mtshan /
NK133(po)003:4265: gnyis pa theg chen sems bskyed kyi brgyud pa la lugs gsum las /
NK133(po)003:4266: zab mo lta ba'i brgyud pa ni /
NK133(po)003:4275: byang sems zla ba rgyal mtshan /
NK133(po)003:4276: gro lung pa bdud rtsi grags /
NK133(po)003:4283: kun mkhyen tshul khrims blo gros sam klong chen rab 'byams so //
NK133(po)003:4301: bla brang chos dpal rgyal mtshan /
NK133(po)003:4309: rata sprul sna tshogs rang grol /
NK133(po)003:4311: mdo sngags bstan 'dzin phrin las lhun grub /
NK133(po)003:4313: rgyal sras rin chen rnam rgyal /
NK133(po)003:4316: rje btsun phrin las chos sgron /
NK133(po)003:4319: rje bla ma mdo sngags chos kyi nyi ma'am rgyal
NK133(po)003:4320: sras 'jam dbyangs theg mchog chos kyi rgya mtsho'i bar
NK133(po)003:4322: ku s+aa li che chung nas /
NK133(po)003:4323: gser gling pa chos kyi grags pa /
NK133(po)003:4331: mnyam med dag po rin po che /
NK133(po)003:4333: ras chen bsod nams grags pa /
NK133(po)003:4334: rgyal sras bsod nams rdo rje /
NK133(po)003:4335: grub chen chos kyi nyi ma /
NK133(po)003:4341: mkha' spyod dbang po de bzhin gshegs pa /
NK133(po)003:4360: rje bla ma mdo sngags chos kyi nyi ma'i bar du byon pa'o //
NK133(po)003:4361: rgya chen spyod pa'i brgyud pa ni /
NK133(po)003:4378: gzhon brtson dkar chung ring mo /
NK133(po)003:4388: zab dang rgya che'i brgyud pa ni /
NK133(po)003:4394: gser gling pa chos kyi grags pa /
NK133(po)003:4408: sangs rgyas dbon po chos rje zla grags /
NK133(po)003:4411: sna tshogs rang grol man gong bzhin no //
NK133(po)003:4412: de ltar brgyud tshul gsum ka kun mkhyen chos kyi rgyal po klong chen pa la babs shing /
NK133(po)003:4413: de nas rim par 'jam dbyangs mkhyen brtse'i dbang po /
NK133(po)003:4415: rje bla ma rgyal sras 'jam dbyangs theg mchog chos kyi rgya mtsho'i bar du'o //
NK133(po)003:4416: bstan pa snga dar gyi sems sdom rgyun 'dus mdo'i
NK133(po)003:4417: byang sems dang chu bo gcig 'dres gyur pa'i brgyud
NK133(po)003:4418: pa der gsal / gsum pa gsang sngags rdo rje
NK133(po)003:4419: theg pa'i smin grol lam gyi brgyud pa la'ang rgyud
NK133(po)003:4420: sde bzhi drug las bya ba'i rgyud du de bzhin
NK133(po)003:4421: gshegs pa'i rigs kyi gtso bor gtogs pa bzhag pa
NK133(po)003:4422: pa der gsal / / khri srong lde'u btsan nas
NK133(po)003:4423: bzung bod kyi rgyal po rnams kyi thugs dam du
NK133(po)003:4424: pa der gsal / / basngagasa pa / bder gshegs sman lha brgyad kyi cho ga'i brgyud pa ni /
NK133(po)003:4425: mnyam med thub pa chen po nas /
NK133(po)003:4429: rgyal sras sad na legs 'jing yon /
NK133(po)003:4431: lha lung dpal gyi rdo rje /
NK133(po)003:4442: ras chu lha dar ma rgyal mtshan /
NK133(po)003:4446: spru lung kun dga' rgyal mtshan /
NK133(po)003:4456: rje ngag dbang blo bzang rgya mtsho /
NK133(po)003:4457: rig 'dzin pad+ma phrin las rdo rje thogs med /
NK133(po)003:4459: o rgyan bde chen 'jigs med go cha /
NK133(po)003:4464: lnga pa chen pos mdzad pa'i mdo chog yid bzhin dbang rgyal gyi lung brgyud ni /
NK133(po)003:4465: ngag dbang blo bzang rgya mtsho /
NK133(po)003:4468: ka chen thabs mkhas rgya mtsho /
NK133(po)003:4469: zhi bzang dge legs rgyal mtshan /
NK133(po)003:4470: klong rdol ngag dbang blo bzang /
NK133(po)003:4471: mkhan chen blo bzang thugs rje /
NK133(po)003:4472: chu bzang skal bzang mkhas grub /
NK133(po)003:4473: mchog ye shes thub bstan rgya mtsho /
NK133(po)003:4476: mdo sngags chos kyi nyi ma la'o //
NK133(po)003:4477: 'dir sman lha brgyad tho brtsegs kyi rjes gnang yig cha yongs rdzogs kyi brgyud pa ni /
NK133(po)003:4478: mnga' ris dgra bcom yan gong dang 'dra la /
NK133(po)003:4479: de nas zhu ldan shes rab grags /
NK133(po)003:4480: rangs chu lhad pa dar ma rgyal mtshan /
NK133(po)003:4482: sangs rgyas sgom pa seng ge skyabs /
NK133(po)003:4484: spro lung pa kun dga' smon lam /
NK133(po)003:4485: spang sgang ba grags pa dpal /
NK133(po)003:4486: byang sems bsod nams grags pa /
NK133(po)003:4487: rgyal sras thogs med bzang po dpal /
NK133(po)003:4495: spyan sngar ngag gi dbang po /
NK133(po)003:4497: ngag dbang mchog legs rdo rje /
NK133(po)003:4499: byams pa ngag dbang lhun grub /
NK133(po)003:4500: rmor chen kun dga' lhun grub /
NK133(po)003:4501: gnas gsar ngag dbang kun dga' legs pa'i 'byung gnas /
NK133(po)003:4504: thams cad mkhyen pa kun dga' bstan 'dzin /
NK133(po)003:4505: rdo rje 'chang 'jam dbyangs mkhyen brtse'i dbang po /
NK133(po)003:4506: mdo sngags chos kyi nyi ma'i bar du'o //
NK133(po)003:4507: yang na mkhan chen zhi ba 'tsho nas /
NK133(po)003:4508: b+ho d+hi sa t+wa chung ba /
NK133(po)003:4513: byang sems zla ba rgyal mtshan /
NK133(po)003:4520: mkhan chen bsod nams grags pa man 'dra /
NK133(po)003:4521: bya rgyud de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs gtsug tor dri ma med pa lha lnga'i brgyud pa ni /
NK133(po)003:4524: nag tsho lo ts+aa ba tshul khrims rgyal ba /
NK133(po)003:4531: bde can ye shes mgon po /
NK133(po)003:4532: bla ma seng ge rgyal mtshan /
NK133(po)003:4533: thog ston shes rab rdo rje /
NK133(po)003:4535: bla chen grags pa rin chen /
NK133(po)003:4537: chos rje nam mkha' tshul khrims /
NK133(po)003:4542: khyab bdag dbang phyug rab brtan /
NK133(po)003:4543: rin chen bsod nams mchog grub /
NK133(po)003:4552: des bka' drin mnyam med mdo sngags chos kyi nyi ma la'o //
NK133(po)003:4553: ngag dbang legs grub yig cha rnams mdzad pa po nas /
NK133(po)003:4554: kun gzigs rdo rje 'chang mkhyen brtse'i dbang po /
NK133(po)003:4556: des mdo sngags chos rje nyi ma la'o //
NK133(po)003:4557: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs 'phags pa 'od zer dri ma med pa'i brgyud pa ni /
NK133(po)003:4575: mnga' ris dgra bcom pa tshul khrims /
NK133(po)003:4582: tshad ma'i skyes bu bsod nams mgon /
NK133(po)003:4583: kun mkhyen bu ston chen po /
NK133(po)003:4589: byang gling pa rin chen rgyal po /
NK133(po)003:4591: gnub sgom sbas pa'i rnal 'byor smon lam rgyal mtshan /
NK133(po)003:4594: rin chen bsod nams mchog grub /
NK133(po)003:4603: kun mkhyen mdo sngags chos kyi nyi ma'i bar ro //
NK133(po)003:4604: yang na zhwa lu lo chen nas /
NK133(po)003:4607: de nas mchod rten bzhengs chog bklag pas grub pa bcas rin chen rnam rgyal /
NK133(po)003:4613: mdo sngags chos kyi nyi ma'i bar ro //
NK133(po)003:4614: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs gtsug tor gdugs dkar can gyi brgyud pa ni /
NK133(po)003:4639: dkon mchog yan lag dbang phyug rdo rje /
NK133(po)003:4648: rgyal dbang theg mchog rdo rje /
NK133(po)003:4649: 'jam dpal mgon yon tan rgya mtsho /
NK133(po)003:4650: rdo rje 'chang mkhyen brtse'i dbang po /
NK133(po)003:4652: mdo sngags chos kyi nyi ma'i bar ro //
NK133(po)003:4653: bya rgyud rdo rje rigs kyi khro bo rnam 'joms dkar po lha bcu gsum gyi brgyud pa ni /
NK133(po)003:4660: gnubs ston bla ma rgya bo pa lung pa /
NK133(po)003:4671: dkon mchog yan lag dang yongs 'dzin rnam rgyal grags
NK133(po)003:4672: pa gnyis ka las rje dgu pa dbang phyug rdo
NK133(po)003:4673: rjes gsan / de nas rim par chos kyi dbang phyug /
NK133(po)003:4675: karma chags med man gdugs dkar dang 'dra /
NK133(po)003:4676: rdo rje'i rigs kyi bdag po rnam 'joms dkar po
NK133(po)003:4677: lha bcu pa bi ma la'i lugs dang phyi 'gyur
NK133(po)003:4678: grub chen sha wa ri pa'i lugs chu bo gcig
NK133(po)003:4679: 'dres su gyur pa rgya sdom ston pa seng ge'i
NK133(po)003:4680: yi ge ltar gyi brgyud pa ni /
NK133(po)003:4684: gnyags dz+ny+aa na ku m+aa ra /
NK133(po)003:4693: sgar ston shes rab gzhon nu dam pa bder gshegs /
NK133(po)003:4703: rgya sdong ston pa seng ge /
NK133(po)003:4709: la ston nam mkha' rin chen /
NK133(po)003:4712: he pa chos kyi 'byung gnas grub dbang chos nyid rgya mtsho /
NK133(po)003:4713: mtshungs med shes rab rgya mtsho /
NK133(po)003:4715: bla ma rdo rje kun bzang /
NK133(po)003:4721: rdo rje 'chang mkhyen brtse'i dbang po /
NK133(po)003:4723: mdo sngags chos kyi nyi ma'i bar du'o //
NK133(po)003:4726: grub thob sha ba ri pa /
NK133(po)003:4728: bal po'i pan+di ta de ba pur+na ma ni /
NK133(po)003:4730: smar sgang shes rab bla ma /
NK133(po)003:4732: mkhan po kun dga' dbang phyug /
NK133(po)003:4738: rje byang sems pa ston pa dbang 'byor man 'dra /
NK133(po)003:4739: rdo rje'i rigs kyi khro bo gnubs lugs rnam 'joms khro nag lha bcu dgu pa'i brgyud pa ni /
NK133(po)003:4742: bram ze bde byed bdag po /
NK133(po)003:4745: gnubs chen sangs rgyas ye shes /
NK133(po)003:4748: tho gar nam mkha' sde zur chen sh+aakya 'byung gnas /
NK133(po)003:4752: sgar ston shes rab gzhon nu /
NK133(po)003:4753: dam pa bde gshegs shes rab seng ge /
NK133(po)003:4754: gtsang ston rdo rje rgyal mtshan /
NK133(po)003:4766: gser pa rdo rje rgyal mtshan /
NK133(po)003:4779: chos kyi nyi ma'i bar ro //
NK133(po)003:4780: sha wa ra'i lugs kyi khrus byab srung gsum gtor dbang dang bcas pa'i brgyud pa gong bzhin no //
NK133(po)003:4781: rnam 'joms khro dkar nag gi sgrub thabs dkyil chog
NK133(po)003:4782: dbang bcas kyi yig cha 'jam mgon blo gros mtha'
NK133(po)003:4783: yas kyis mdzad pa po nas /
NK133(po)003:4784: 'jam dbyangs mkhyen brtse'i rin po che /
NK133(po)003:4786: chos kyi nyi ma'i bar ro //
NK133(po)003:4787: bya rgyud de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs kyi yum spyod rgyud du bkral ba gza' yum brgyud pa ni /
NK133(po)003:4802: sa chen kun dga' snying po /
NK133(po)003:4804: rje btsun grags pa rgyal mtshan /
NK133(po)003:4826: snyan mkhar slob dpon ngag dbang /
NK133(po)003:4830: gangs dkar po t+wa la pa mkhan chen bstan 'dzin tshul khrims /
NK133(po)003:4831: lha btsun ye shes don grub bstan pa'i rgyal mtshan /
NK133(po)003:4832: de gnyis las 'jam dbyangs mkhyen brtse'i dbang po /
NK133(po)003:4834: o rgyan mdo sngags chos kyi nyi ma'i bar ro //
NK133(po)003:4835: phyi 'gyur gyi brgyud pa ltar na /
NK133(po)003:4836: thub dbang rdo rje gdan pa /
NK133(po)003:4839: dkyil chog dbang bskur gyi yig cha phan bde'i nyi
NK133(po)003:4840: ma ngag dbang legs grub kyis mdzad pa'i lung brgyud
NK133(po)003:4842: rje 'jam dbyangs mkhyen brtse'i sogs gong bzhin no //
NK133(po)003:4843: spyod rgyud phyag na rdo rje dbang bskur dang /
NK133(po)003:4844: spyod rgyud rnam snang mngon byang /
NK133(po)003:4845: rnal 'byor gyi rgyud de nyid snang dbang gi brgyud
NK133(po)003:4846: pa ni 'dus mdo'i skabs su gsal ba ltar ro
NK133(po)003:4848: rnal 'byor bla na med pa'i rgyud sde la'ang gsum las /
NK133(po)003:4849: dang po pha rgyud ma h+aa yo ga'i skor la
NK133(po)003:4850: sku'i rgyud ma h+aa'i a nu ste rnal 'byor ma'i
NK133(po)003:4851: rgyud dpal sangs rgyas thams cad mnyam par sbyor ba
NK133(po)003:4852: mkha' 'gro sgyu ma bde mchog gi brgyud pa ni
NK133(po)003:4855: gsang ba'i bdag po l+ai ts+aa bi dri med grags pa /
NK133(po)003:4866: de las gye ro mchog skyong dang gtsug ru rin chen gzhon nu gnyis kyis gsan /
NK133(po)003:4867: gnyis ka las go bo tshul khrims byang chub /
NK133(po)003:4868: de las cog ro rgyal ba'i yon tan /
NK133(po)003:4870: rdo rje 'jam dpal gsum gyis gsan /
NK133(po)003:4871: gsum ka las khu byang chub 'od kyis zhus /
NK133(po)003:4872: de nas blo gros rgyal mtshan /
NK133(po)003:4873: rong ban rin chen tshul khrims /
NK133(po)003:4888: sa bzang 'phags pa gzhon nu blo gros /
NK133(po)003:4889: ngor chen kun dga' bzang po /
NK133(po)003:4892: bu ston kun dga' rnam rgyal /
NK133(po)003:4893: thugs sras kun dga' rgyal po /
NK133(po)003:4895: tshar chen blo gsal rgya mtsho /
NK133(po)003:4899: gangs dkar 'brus gling pa ngag dbang o rgyan /
NK133(po)003:4906: sgrol ston 'jam dbyangs chos kyi rgyal mtshan /
NK133(po)003:4910: chos kyi glang po sogs so //
NK133(po)003:4911: yang gangs dkar lugs kyi brgyud tshul ltar na /
NK133(po)003:4913: chos rje rig pa rnam rgyal /
NK133(po)003:4916: bla ma bkra shis rgya mtsho /
NK133(po)003:4918: chos rje phun tshogs rnam rgyal /
NK133(po)003:4919: byams pa kun dga' bstan dar /
NK133(po)003:4922: rje bla ma mkhyen brtse sogs gong bzhin no //
NK133(po)003:4923: yang zhwa lu'i lugs ltar na /
NK133(po)003:4925: bla ma tshul rgyal yon po pa /
NK133(po)003:4926: lam 'bras pa blo chen bsod nams dpal /
NK133(po)003:4927: nyang stod rtse chen chos rje pa /
NK133(po)003:4928: grub chen kun dga' blo gros /
NK133(po)003:4929: chos rje rong po blo bzang pa /
NK133(po)003:4930: rdo rje 'chang mkhyen rab chos rje /
NK133(po)003:4931: chos 'khor thar pa gling gi bla chen /
NK133(po)003:4936: rin chen bkra shis rgyal mtshan /
NK133(po)003:4938: rdo rje rin chen bsod nams mchog grub /
NK133(po)003:4939: bla chen bsod nams rgya mtsho /
NK133(po)003:4940: mkhan chen byams pa mkhas btsun /
NK133(po)003:4942: mkhas dbang rin chen don grub /
NK133(po)003:4943: chos rje rin chen blo gsal /
NK133(po)003:4945: rin chen blo gsal bstan skyong las 'jam dbyangs mkhyen brtse'i dbang po sogs gong ltar ro //
NK133(po)003:4946: 'jam dpal ma ru rtse gshed dmar ru mtshon dmar po'i brgyud pa ni /
NK133(po)003:4954: yon tan rgya mtsho ste snga 'gyur bka' babs so //
