NK133(po)003:4955: gnyis pa la gnyis kyi dang po /
NK133(po)003:4964: khu lung ba ste bar 'gyur bka' babs so //
NK133(po)003:4968: khu lung yon tan rgya mtsho /
NK133(po)003:4969: de nas bka' bab gsum ka dril ba yon tan
NK133(po)003:4970: rgya mtsho las sras pad+ma dbang rgyal chen po 'jam
NK133(po)003:4971: dpal / jo mo so rgad bza' rgen ne ma /
NK133(po)003:4973: de nas gnyis su gyes pa'i sras brgyud ni /
NK133(po)003:4985: lang gro bsod nams dbang rgyal /
NK133(po)003:4986: rngog ston rdo rje rgyal po /
NK133(po)003:4987: rgyal sras mthu chen nyi ma /
NK133(po)003:4990: nyin phug pa rdo rje tshe rab /
NK133(po)003:4991: lcags gtun pa mthu chen rnam rgyal bzang po /
NK133(po)003:4993: 'bum ram pa o rgyan skal bzang /
NK133(po)003:4997: dge sbyong o rgyan phun sum tshogs /
NK133(po)003:4998: pad sprul rin po che rig 'dzin pad+ma dbang rgyal rdo rje /
NK133(po)003:4999: rgyal sras gzhan phan mtha' yas /
NK133(po)003:5003: chos kyi nyi ma'i bar ro //
NK133(po)003:5010: gnubs dar ma seng ge man gong bzhin no //
NK133(po)003:5011: yang na gnubs lcags gtun pa /
NK133(po)003:5014: 'jam dpal gshin rje gshed nag po kha thun gyi brgyud pa la gsum ste /
NK133(po)003:5019: shin+tam gar+b+ha pad+ma sam b+ha wa /
NK133(po)003:5035: de nas rim par ye shes rgya mtsho /
NK133(po)003:5040: lha rje h'u chen bkra shis dar /
NK133(po)003:5043: de gnyis ka las gnubs nag po ye shes rgya mtsho /
NK133(po)003:5044: de nas 'dzam gling nag po sangs rgyas rin chen no //
NK133(po)003:5045: yang na yon tan rgya mtsho nas /
NK133(po)003:5057: yang na yon tan rgya mtsho /
NK133(po)003:5059: de sras rgya gar rdo rje /
NK133(po)003:5066: jo bo ye shes rdo rje /
NK133(po)003:5078: badz+ra k+sha ra 'gyur med rdo rje /
NK133(po)003:5088: rdo rje 'chang 'jam dbyangs mkhyen brtse'i dbang po /
NK133(po)003:5090: mdo sngags chos kyi nyi ma'i bar du'o //
NK133(po)003:5100: bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal gshin rje gshed gdong drug
NK133(po)003:5101: nag po gsang rdzogs thugs kyi sgrub pa'i chos skor
NK133(po)003:5135: se ston legs grub tshe ring /
NK133(po)003:5140: khri chen phrin las rnam rgyal /
NK133(po)003:5143: sprul sku 'gyur med sangs rgyas chos 'phel /
NK133(po)003:5146: chos kyi nyi ma'i bar du'o //
NK133(po)003:5147: thugs dpal he ru ka'i rgyud las yang dag zla gam dgu pa'i skor gyi brgyud pa ni /
NK133(po)003:5157: gnyag dz+ny+aa na sog po dpal ye /
NK133(po)003:5169: bde gshegs legs zhes kyang snang pad 'byung /
NK133(po)003:5177: spyan tshab pa mgon po zla ba /
NK133(po)003:5192: des chos kyi nyi ma la'o //
NK133(po)003:5193: phrin las phur pa rol pa'i rgyud la /
NK133(po)003:5197: sna nam lugs sogs mang du yod pa'i brgyud pa
NK133(po)003:5198: ci rigs 'dres pa phur pa rog lugs su grags
NK133(po)003:5200: khyab bdag kun bzang rdo rje gzhon nu /
NK133(po)003:5209: lang lab byang chub rdo rje /
NK133(po)003:5210: sna nam tshul khrims shes rab /
NK133(po)003:5214: sman chung bla ma dpal te stod las gtsor ston brgyud pa dang /
NK133(po)003:5218: go rub yang dag ste smad las gtsor ston brgyud pa dang /
NK133(po)003:5220: rog ston shes rab bla ma /
NK133(po)003:5233: sngags 'chang bdud 'dul chos rje in+d+ra'i mtshan /
NK133(po)003:5236: lo chen chos dpal rgya mtsho /
NK133(po)003:5247: pad sprul rin po che nas /
NK133(po)003:5254: rdo rje phur pa'i bshad pa 'bum nag slob dpon
NK133(po)003:5255: rnam gsum dgongs pa mkhar chen bza' la brgyud pa
NK133(po)003:5256: / skyid ston tshe ring yan ma rnyed /
NK133(po)003:5257: de nas zur chen chos dbyings rang grol /
NK133(po)003:5266: rong zom lugs kyi phur pa'i brgyud pa ni /
NK133(po)003:5270: rong ban yon tan rin chen /
NK133(po)003:5273: de nas sras slob gnyis las /
NK133(po)003:5280: rong pa kun dga' me dpung /
NK133(po)003:5286: slob dpon sra bstan rdo rje /
NK133(po)003:5296: de gnyis kas 'gyur med rdo rje /
NK133(po)003:5305: rong ban rin chen tshul khrims /
NK133(po)003:5309: yol dge bsnyen rdo rje dbang phyug /
NK133(po)003:5311: rnal 'byor gzhung pa pho rog mdo sde mgon /
NK133(po)003:5320: lo chen bsod nams rgya mtsho /
NK133(po)003:5321: chag lo rin chen chos rgyal /
NK133(po)003:5322: rdo rje seng ge man sngar bzhin no //
NK133(po)003:5325: gu ru lo ts+aa ba chos kyi shes rab yol dge bsnyen /
NK133(po)003:5331: kha rag bon phrug pa nam mkha'/
NK133(po)003:5339: rdo rje seng ge man sngar bzhin no //
NK133(po)003:5342: 'bum rab 'byams pa o rgyan skal bzang /
NK133(po)003:5346: dge sbyong o rgyan phun tshogs /
NK133(po)003:5347: rig 'dzin pad+ma dbang rgyal rdo rje /
NK133(po)003:5348: rgyal sras gzhan phan mtha' yas /
NK133(po)003:5350: 'jam dbyangs mkhyen brtse rin po che sogs gong bzhin no //
NK133(po)003:5351: spyi rgyud sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i skor la /
NK133(po)003:5352: dang po dbang ka'i brgyud pa ni /
NK133(po)003:5353: ston pa kun tu bzang po /
NK133(po)003:5356: dam pa'i rigs can d+r+wa ma lnga /
NK133(po)003:5357: rgyal po dzah slob dpon ku ku r+aa dza /
NK133(po)003:5365: rma lo rin chen mchog gtsug ru ye shes gzhon nu dang /
NK133(po)003:5366: gye re mchog skyong rnam pa gnyis /
NK133(po)003:5367: zhang ston rgyal ba yon tan /
NK133(po)003:5368: gnubs chen sangs rgyas ye shes /
NK133(po)003:5369: yang na go ma sa nas /
NK133(po)003:5370: rgyal po ku ku r+aa dza /
NK133(po)003:5373: za hor rgyal po pra b+ha hasti /
NK133(po)003:5374: rig 'dzin pad+ma sam b+ha ba dang bi ma la gnyis kas gnyag lo dz+ny+aa na ku ma /
NK133(po)003:5377: de nas 'dir brgyud srol 'ga' yod kyang gzhan du gsal /
NK133(po)003:5383: zur chung shes rab grags pa /
NK133(po)003:5385: sgro phug pa sh+aakya seng ge /
NK133(po)003:5404: zur ston rgyal sras pad+ma bdud 'dul /
NK133(po)003:5418: mkhyen brtse'i dbang po sogs so //
NK133(po)003:5419: yang zhi ba'i dbang brgyud ni /
NK133(po)003:5424: pad+ma gar dbang phrin las las rnam rgyal /
NK133(po)003:5429: mdo sngags chos kyi nyi ma sogs so //
NK133(po)003:5434: de gnyis kas rin chen rnam rgyal /
NK133(po)003:5437: byang sems rdo rje snying po /
NK133(po)003:5440: mkhyen brtse'i dbang po sogs gong ltar ro //
NK133(po)003:5441: sgyu 'phrul bshad rgyun dbang du na /
NK133(po)003:5442: rtsa rgyud gsang ba snying po'i 'grel pa n+aa len+d+ra'i
NK133(po)003:5443: pan+di ta chen po sgeg pa rdo rjes mdzad pa'i
NK133(po)003:5444: rin chen spar khab kyi brgyud pa ni /
NK133(po)003:5449: rgyal po dzah in+d+ra b+h+au ti /
NK133(po)003:5453: ku ku r+aa dza phyi ma /
NK133(po)003:5454: ro lang bde ba'i dngos grub /
NK133(po)003:5461: de las gtsug gyer rnam gnyis /
NK133(po)003:5462: gnyis ka las khyung po dbyig 'od /
NK133(po)003:5463: des zhang rgyal ba'i yon tan /
NK133(po)003:5466: ngag dbang byang chub rgyal mtshan /
NK133(po)003:5475: gtsang pa dbyis ston man rtsa rgyud kyi brgyud pa
NK133(po)003:5476: dang po dang nye ston chos seng gnyis kas gsan
NK133(po)003:5480: sro chen shes rab tshul khrims /
NK133(po)003:5489: rang grol nyi zla sangs rgyas /
NK133(po)003:5500: dge slong o rgyan phun tshogs /
NK133(po)003:5501: pad sprul dbang rgyal rdo rje /
NK133(po)003:5502: zhe chen mthu stobs rnam rgyal /
NK133(po)003:5504: dge mang gsol dpon bla ma pad+ma bzang po /
NK133(po)003:5505: pad+ma mdo sngags bstan 'dzin sogs gong ltar ro //
NK133(po)003:5506: gsang snying bshad brgyud gsang bdag dgongs rgyan ltar na /
NK133(po)003:5509: rab 'byams pa o rgyan chos grags /
NK133(po)003:5513: gnyos rigs rab 'byams 'gyur med kun ldan /
NK133(po)003:5514: pan+di ta 'gyur med bstan 'dzin 'phel rgyas dang /
NK133(po)003:5516: de gnyis ka las 'jam dbyangs mkhyen brtse'i dbang po /
NK133(po)003:5518: chos kyi nyi ma'i bar du'o //
NK133(po)003:5519: yang na o rgyan chos grags nas /
NK133(po)003:5522: 'gyur med kun bzang grub pa'i dbang phyug pad+ma gar dbang phrin las las rnam rgyal /
NK133(po)003:5525: 'gyur med mthu stobs rnam rgyal man gong ltar ro //
NK133(po)003:5526: sgyu 'phrul lam rim rin po che rnam par bkod
NK133(po)003:5527: pa slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang bas mdzad pa le'u
NK133(po)003:5528: dgu pa bi ma dang gnyag lo'i 'gyur ba'i brgyud
NK133(po)003:5529: pa ni / kun bzang rigs lnga /
NK133(po)003:5532: rgyal po dzah dge slong ku ku r+aa dza /
NK133(po)003:5537: sangs rgyas gsang ba bi ma la /
NK133(po)003:5541: nyang stod kyi 'bre khro chung ba /
NK133(po)003:5546: g.yu sangs rgyas rgya ston dga' sgrub /
NK133(po)003:5563: tre bo skal bzang dbang ldan /
NK133(po)003:5570: de gnyis kas shes rab bstan dar de las gus sogs kyis nos so //
NK133(po)003:5572: sgrol ma sangs rin nas 'gos lo gzhon nu dpal /
NK133(po)003:5573: lo chen bsod nams rgya mtsho /
NK133(po)003:5574: se rin chen rgyal mtshan man 'dra /
NK133(po)003:5575: sgyu 'phrul don khrid snying po kun mkhyen klong chen pa'i gsung ltar zhib khrid kyi brgyud pa ni /
NK133(po)003:5576: 'og tu dge ba gsum gyi don khrid du gsal /
NK133(po)003:5577: sgyu 'phrul gyi cha lag tu gtogs pa sangs rgyas
NK133(po)003:5578: gsang ba'i lugs kyi tshe sgrub skor gyi brgyud pa
NK133(po)003:5616: gzhan phan mtha' yas man sgyu 'phrul ltar ro //
NK133(po)003:5617: rnal 'byor spyi khrus na rag dong sprugs skor gyi brgyud pa ni /
NK133(po)003:5632: khu ston bsod nams rgyal mtshan /
NK133(po)003:5641: de gnyis kas sgrol chen bsam 'grub rdo rje /
NK133(po)003:5649: zur ston ngag dbang phun tshogs /
NK133(po)003:5662: chos kyi nyi ma'i bar du'o //
NK133(po)003:5663: yang na rin chen rnam rgyal nas /
NK133(po)003:5667: byang sems rdo rje snying po /
NK133(po)003:5668: gzhan phan mtha' yas pad+ma rdo rje /
NK133(po)003:5669: mkhyen brtse'i dbang po nas gong ltar ro //
NK133(po)003:5670: gur drag bka' ma 'o bran lugs kyi brgyud pa ni /
NK133(po)003:5674: dpal gyi dbang phyug chos kyi 'byung gnas /
NK133(po)003:5678: ri rab brtan pa ste bdun po 'o bran brgyud do //
NK133(po)003:5679: de nas nyi ma rgyal mtshan /
NK133(po)003:5681: chag lo rin chen chos rgyal /
NK133(po)003:5689: lho dkon mchog chos kyi rgya mtsho /
NK133(po)003:5690: gnas mdo rje dbon karma sangs rgyas sam shes rab grags pa /
NK133(po)003:5692: tham ka ngag dbang tshe ring /
NK133(po)003:5695: kam bla ma tshe dbang pad+ma nor bu /
NK133(po)003:5699: zhe chen kun bzang rnam rgyal /
NK133(po)003:5704: blo gros mtha' yas sogs so //
NK133(po)003:5705: yang kun bzang rnam rgyal nas /
NK133(po)003:5709: gnyis kas mthu stobs rnam rgyal /
NK133(po)003:5711: mdo sngags bstan 'dzin gnyis kas chos kyi nyi ma'i bar ro //
NK133(po)003:5712: de dag gi bstan srung dregs pa'i skor la rgyud
NK133(po)003:5713: mgon legs ldan tshogs kyi bdag po'i skor gyi brgyud
NK133(po)003:5717: rgyal po dzah ku ku r+aa dza /
NK133(po)003:5722: gnubs chen sangs rgyas ye shes /
NK133(po)003:5738: snar ston bud d+ha d+h+wa dza /
NK133(po)003:5743: de gnyis kas dpang bde legs rgyal mtshan /
NK133(po)003:5747: byams pa rin chen rdo rje /
NK133(po)003:5748: skyi ston tshe ring dbang po /
NK133(po)003:5752: bing bka' gter gyi brgyud pa ni /
NK133(po)003:5780: ngag dbang grags pa dpal ldan legs dbang /
NK133(po)003:5790: bsod nams chos dbang rab khu dbon /
NK133(po)003:5792: rje ngag dbang blo bzang rgya mtsho /
NK133(po)003:5793: des rig 'dzin chen po 'gyur med rdo rje la'o //
NK133(po)003:5794: yang lce blo ldan seng ge nas /
NK133(po)003:5800: lha mo re ma ti rang byung rgyal mo la bka' ma ltar na /
NK133(po)003:5802: o rgyan yab yum ngam 'bre sa le /
NK133(po)003:5818: chos bsam pa sogs las blo gros rgya mtshor brgyud pa'ang yod cing /
NK133(po)003:5821: gter ston phu rang pa zhang btsun /
NK133(po)003:5843: des rig 'dzin 'gyur med rdo rje la'o //
NK133(po)003:5844: rnam sras phyi sgrub ser chen sprin gseb ma la /
NK133(po)003:5850: gter ston gnyal pa nyi ma shes rab /
NK133(po)003:5860: mus chen rnam rgyal bzang po /
NK133(po)003:5861: sham b+har ba kun dga' sangs rgyas /
NK133(po)003:5865: mkhan chen zhwa lu ba bsod mchog des 'gyur med rdo rje la'o //
NK133(po)003:5866: nang sgrub mdung dmar can rta sngon ma ni bshad ma thag pa ltar ro //
NK133(po)003:5867: gsang sgrub drag po rta sngon ma /
NK133(po)003:5871: gnubs chen sangs rgyas ye shes gnubs rdo rje 'bar /
NK133(po)003:5880: gtso go lha ste 'di yan gnubs brgyud do //
NK133(po)003:5881: de nas sbas ti dgra bcom /
NK133(po)003:5884: yon tan tshul khrims shes rab rdo rje /
NK133(po)003:5894: yang gsang phyag mtshan bzhi pa la /
NK133(po)003:5904: gnyal pa nyi she nas thabs kyi blo gros yan phyi nang gnyis ltar las /
NK133(po)003:5914: tshar chen mkhyen brtse khu dbon gsum /
NK133(po)003:5916: 'gyur med rdo rje ste de nas legs ldan /
NK133(po)003:5919: rnam sras skor bcas gong gi 'o bran drag dmar ltar ro //
NK133(po)003:5920: gnyis pa lung a nu yo ga 'dus pa mdo
NK133(po)003:5921: 'og min tshogs chen 'dus pa'i skor gyi dbang chog
NK133(po)003:5922: rdo rje'i them skas ltar la /
NK133(po)003:5923: theg pa dgu kar bka' babs tshul tha dad re
NK133(po)003:5924: yod kyang 'dir gtso che ba bskyed rdzogs gsum gyi
NK133(po)003:5926: dang po ma h+aa yo ga'i brgyud pa ni /
NK133(po)003:5929: rdo rje sems dpa' phyag rdor /
NK133(po)003:5930: rgyal po dzah ku ku r+aa dza /
NK133(po)003:5933: sras mo go ma de bi /
NK133(po)003:5944: gnubs chen sangs rgyas ye shes so //
NK133(po)003:5945: lung a nu yo ga'i brgyud pa ni /
NK133(po)003:5952: srin po blo gros thabs ldan /
NK133(po)003:5954: li ts+aa bi dri med grags pa ste dam pa'i rigs can d+r+wa ma lnga /
NK133(po)003:5955: skal ldan rgyal po dzah u pa r+aa dza /
NK133(po)003:5957: klu rgyal na ga pu tra /
NK133(po)003:5958: rgyal po ga ya p+au tra /
NK133(po)003:5960: ku ku r+aa dza phyi ma /
NK133(po)003:5963: za hor rgyal po pra b+ha hasti /
NK133(po)003:5967: a tsar+ya bde ba gsal mdzad /
NK133(po)003:5970: bal po ba su d+h+aa ra /
NK133(po)003:5972: bru sha'i mkhan po che btsan skyes /
NK133(po)003:5974: rdzogs chen a ti yo ga'i brgyud pa ni /
NK133(po)003:5975: chos sku kun tu bzang po /
NK133(po)003:5976: longs sku rdo rje sems dpa'/
NK133(po)003:5980: rgyal po d+ha na ta la /
NK133(po)003:5986: slob dpon a k+sho b+h+yah ku ku r+aa dza /
NK133(po)003:5988: smad 'tshong ma bud d+ha sa man+ti /
NK133(po)003:5989: sras mo go ma de bi /
NK133(po)003:5992: slob dpon ma h+aa r+aa dza /
NK133(po)003:6001: dge slong ma kun dga' mo /
NK133(po)003:6005: gnyags dz+ny+aa na ku m+aa ra /
NK133(po)003:6007: gnubs sangs rgyas ye shes so //
NK133(po)003:6008: de ltar gnubs la bskyed rdzogs gsum gyi chu bo
NK133(po)003:6009: gcig tu 'dril ba de nas khu lung pa yon
NK133(po)003:6010: tan rgya mtsho / sras ye shes rgyal mtshan /
NK133(po)003:6011: glan tsha nyal ba rdo rje 'od /
NK133(po)003:6014: kha rag pa gnubs ye shes /
NK133(po)003:6015: de nas glan rdo rje 'od la'o //
NK133(po)003:6029: gnas sding pa nam mkha' rdo rje /
NK133(po)003:6034: gsang bdag phrin las lhun grub /
NK133(po)003:6037: lo chen chos dpal rgya mtsho /
NK133(po)003:6039: mkhan chen o rgyan bstan 'dzin rdo rje /
NK133(po)003:6042: gzhan phan rig pa'i rdo rje /
NK133(po)003:6046: chos kyi nyi ma'i bar du'o //
NK133(po)003:6047: gnyis pa khams lugs kyi brgyud pa ni /
NK133(po)003:6048: sgro phug pa sh+aakya seng ge nas /
NK133(po)003:6050: kahdama pa bde gshegs rdo rje ye shes nam mkha' rtsal /
NK133(po)003:6052: byams pa 'bum rdo rje nam mkha' rtsal /
NK133(po)003:6053: rtsa sde nam mkha' rdo rje /
NK133(po)003:6055: d+ho ri ba ston pa dbang 'byor dpal /
NK133(po)003:6056: dpal 'bar ba nam mkha' rdo rje /
NK133(po)003:6058: yang khrod pa tshul khrims rgyal mtshan /
NK133(po)003:6066: des kha ba dkar po nam mkha' rgya mtsho /
NK133(po)003:6067: kha ba dkar po kun dga' zla ba /
NK133(po)003:6068: des nag tsha ba bsod nams rgyal mtshan /
NK133(po)003:6069: hor po chos dbang ba gsum las /
NK133(po)003:6071: bla ma bsod nams rdo rjes gsan /
NK133(po)003:6072: des rgya sdom ston pa seng ge /
NK133(po)003:6073: nag tsha bkra shis rin chen /
NK133(po)003:6074: rong po rin chen rdo rje /
NK133(po)003:6076: rig 'dzin kun bzang shes rab thugs mchog drag po rtsal /
NK133(po)003:6079: karma bkra shis chos dpal bzang po /
NK133(po)003:6084: rje chos kyi nyi ma'i bar du'o //
NK133(po)003:6085: yang brgyud pa snga ma'i zur sh+aakya bshes gnyen nas /
NK133(po)003:6086: kahthoga bra bo chos 'bum pa ye shes rgyal mtshan sogs dang /
NK133(po)003:6087: kun bzang shes rab kyis rong po rin chen rdo rje las mdo dbang tshar gcig /
NK133(po)003:6088: bar khyim shes rab rgya mtsho las tshar gcig bcas thengs gsum gsan pa dang /
NK133(po)003:6089: kun bzang shes rab nas rmugs sangs rdo rje kun bzang rgya mtsho /
NK133(po)003:6094: rdo rje kun bzang rgya mtsho /
NK133(po)003:6095: skya thang sprul sku khyab bdal klong yangs /
NK133(po)003:6096: sang rgang pad+ma lhun grub rgya mtsho /
NK133(po)003:6097: pad+ma nor bu la brgyud pa'ang yod do //
NK133(po)003:6098: de ltar brgyud rim 'di nyid 'dzam ston 'gro ba'i mgon po dang /
NK133(po)003:6099: chos rje dam pa bde gshegs nas bzung bdag cag
NK133(po)003:6100: gi rtsa ba'i bla ma'i bar du byon pa'i bla
NK133(po)003:6101: ma thams cad rten dge slong sde snod gsum pa
NK133(po)003:6102: / lam nyams bzhes mdo sgyu sems gsum gyi sgo
NK133(po)003:6103: nas mchog gi dngos grub brnyes pa khyad par theg
NK133(po)003:6104: mchog rdzogs pa chen po'i lam nas kun bzang gdod
NK133(po)003:6105: ma'i rgyal sar gshegs pa phrin las bstan 'gro'i don
NK133(po)003:6106: rlabs po che mdzad pa sha stag ste ngo mtshar
NK133(po)003:6108: mdo mgon legs ldan tshogs kyi bdag po khams byon ma'i brgyud pa ni /
NK133(po)003:6114: rnam snang sprul pa bee ro tsa na /
NK133(po)003:6116: chos rgyal khri srong lde'u btsan /
NK133(po)003:6118: rgyal po mdo gzher nag po /
NK133(po)003:6122: bee ros d+hi ri chos kyi grags pa dang rol pa'i rdo rje /
NK133(po)003:6137: yang na chu pho rtogs ldan nas gter brgyud bla nag dge 'dun rgyal mtshan /
NK133(po)003:6138: de'i dbon dkon mchog bzang po /
NK133(po)003:6139: mdo sher ye shes rgyal mtshan /
NK133(po)003:6142: la ston nam mkha' rin chen /
NK133(po)003:6143: dar bu blo gros rab brtan /
NK133(po)003:6160: yang na brgyud pa gcig la nam mkha' rin chen nas /
NK133(po)003:6176: bee ro tsa nas 'brang rir sbas pa chu bar
NK133(po)003:6177: rtogs ldan gyis bton pa'i gter brgyud kyang chu bo
NK133(po)003:6179: 'di nyid 'dus mdo kahthoga brgyud pa'i bka' srung gcig
NK133(po)003:6180: pu dang spyi bor spyi mdo dgongs 'dus glegs bam
NK133(po)003:6181: ye shes sems dpa'i tshul du bzhugs pa sogs mdo
NK133(po)003:6183: lha 'di brten sgrub byed mthus mdo khams shar phyogs
NK133(po)003:6184: 'dir snga 'gyur ba'i bstan la rgud pa nam yang
NK133(po)003:6185: mi 'byung zhes dam pa dag gis basngagasa pa don
NK133(po)003:6186: la gnas pa mngon sum nyid do //
NK133(po)003:6187: rdor brag mdo dbang dkyil 'khor rgya mtsho'i 'jug ngog
NK133(po)003:6188: gi brgyud pa gzhung gsal ltar la mdo mgon legs
NK133(po)003:6189: ldan ljang nag drag po'i brgyud pa ni /
NK133(po)003:6190: snga ma rnams mdo dbang ltar la /
NK133(po)003:6194: rtsa sde rdzogs chen skal bzang pad+ma rdo rje /
NK133(po)003:6196: bya btang grub chen pa kun bzang rnam grol mgon po /
NK133(po)003:6200: si tu chos kyi rgya mtsho /
NK133(po)003:6201: mkhan chen ngag gi dbang po /
NK133(po)003:6202: chos kyi glang po'am pad+ma kun bzang bstan 'dzin nor bu sogs so //
NK133(po)003:6203: bskyed rdzogs gsum gyi man ngag tu grags pa gtso
NK133(po)003:6204: bor sems sde'i phyogs su gyur pa rgya bod mkhas
NK133(po)003:6205: pa mi bzhi'i dgongs bcud bka' brgyad bka' ma rdzong
NK133(po)003:6206: 'phrang du grags pa'i skor gyi brgyud rim ni /
NK133(po)003:6207: ston pa kun tu bzang po /
NK133(po)003:6208: rdor sems dga' rab rdo rje /
NK133(po)003:6212: gnubs chen yab sras sogs nas rig 'dzin 'gyur med
NK133(po)003:6213: rdo rje'i bar glegs bam dbu'i dkar chag tu gsal
NK133(po)003:6214: ba ltar la gter chen nas /
NK133(po)003:6217: theg mchog bstan pa'i rgyal mtshan /
NK133(po)003:6224: gsum pa rdzogs pa chen po a ti yo ga'i
NK133(po)003:6225: sems phyogs kyi skor la sems sde ma bu bco
NK133(po)003:6226: brgyad kyi dgongs pa btsan thabs su ngo sprad pa
NK133(po)003:6227: rig pa'i rtsal dbang bco brgyad kahthoga pa rmog ston
NK133(po)003:6228: rdo rje dpal bzang gi yig cha'i steng nas bskur
NK133(po)003:6230: chos sku kun tu bzang po /
NK133(po)003:6231: longs sku rgyal ba rigs lnga /
NK133(po)003:6232: sprul sku gsang ba'i bdag po /
NK133(po)003:6234: mkhas pa nyi shu rtsa gcig /
NK133(po)003:6235: sgra bsgyur bee ro tsa na /
NK133(po)003:6237: gnyags dz+ny+aa na ku m+aa ra /
NK133(po)003:6240: gnubs chen ye shes rgya mtsho /
NK133(po)003:6244: zur chung shes rab grags pa /
NK133(po)003:6246: sgro phug pa sh+aakya seng ge /
NK133(po)003:6248: mkhas pa lce ston yab sras /
NK133(po)003:6252: chos rje bla skyabs rdo rje /
NK133(po)003:6253: drin chen mkhas pa chen po /
NK133(po)003:6255: ma gcig drin can zur mo /
NK133(po)003:6260: bshes gnyen dkon mchog bzang po /
NK133(po)003:6261: dar lung pa rdo rje rnam rgyal khyung tshang pa blo gros dpal ldan /
NK133(po)003:6278: chos kyi nyi ma'i bar ro //
NK133(po)003:6282: ye shes rgyal mtshan sogs mdo dbang khams lugs ltar ro //
NK133(po)003:6290: dbon sprul bstan 'dzin 'phel rgyas kyis gsan pa'o //
NK133(po)003:6291: kun byed rgyal po'i le'u so bdun pa'i mchan dang /
NK133(po)003:6292: sems sde'i slob dpon bco brgyad kyi rdo rje'i glu dang /
NK133(po)003:6293: rdo la gser zhun rnams 'jam dbyangs mkhyen brtse nas /
NK133(po)003:6295: sems sde'i bka' srol gtso che ba gsum gyi nang
NK133(po)003:6296: tshan nyang lugs kyi khrid yig sog bzlog pa blo
NK133(po)003:6297: gros rgyal mtshan gyis mdzad pa'i steng nas bshad khrid
NK133(po)003:6319: skye med dam pa gnyam med sprul sku chen po /
NK133(po)003:6321: zur me mkhas btsun sangs rgyas /
NK133(po)003:6323: sgrol ma ba sangs rgyas rin chen /
NK133(po)003:6328: lha rje blo gros bzang po /
NK133(po)003:6331: gter chen rje man chad gong gi dbang brgyud dang 'dra la /
NK133(po)003:6332: mkhyen brtse chos kyi nyi mas kyang gsan pa'o //
NK133(po)003:6333: sems sde'i brgyud 'debs kyang de bzhin no //
NK133(po)003:6334: sems sde khams lugs kyi khrid kahthoga pa spyan snga
NK133(po)003:6335: nam mkha' rdo rjes mdzad pa'i khrid yig sgyu 'phrul
NK133(po)003:6336: pra khrid ltar khrid lung sbrags ma'i brgyud pa ni
NK133(po)003:6368: yang byams pa chen po nas /
NK133(po)003:6375: gsum ka las dpal 'bar ba nam mkha' rdo rjes zhus /
NK133(po)003:6389: dkon mchog thub bstan rgya mtsho /
NK133(po)003:6391: mchog sprul thub bstan rgyal mtshan /
NK133(po)003:6395: ze chen rgyal tshab pad+ma rnam rgyal /
NK133(po)003:6396: rje bla ma 'jam dbyangs chos kyi blo gros la'o //
NK133(po)003:6401: rdzogs pa chen po sems sde khams lugs a ro
NK133(po)003:6402: snyan brgyud kyi khrid zhwa dmar mkha' spyod dbang pos
NK133(po)003:6403: mdzad pa'i mkha' dbyings snying po'i don khrid kyi brgyud
NK133(po)003:6412: gnyag lo ye shes gzhon nu /
NK133(po)003:6413: sprul sku a ro ye shes 'byung gnas /
NK133(po)003:6415: cog ro zang dkar ba blo gros 'byung gnas /
NK133(po)003:6416: kong rab 'tsho ldan dar ma ba /
NK133(po)003:6419: dpal ldan dus gsum mkhyen pa /
NK133(po)003:6424: kun mkhyen rang byung rdo rje /
NK133(po)003:6425: rtogs ldan grags pa seng ge /
NK133(po)003:6426: ri khrod pa dar ma rgyal ba /
NK133(po)003:6430: 'di yan nyams khrid brgyud pa bar ma chad du byon /
NK133(po)003:6431: de nas rje mthong ba don ldan /
NK133(po)003:6440: ma ni ba karma gsung rab /
NK133(po)003:6442: d+h+ai tsha karma phrin las dbang po /
NK133(po)003:6447: karma ngag dbang yon tan rgya mtsho /
NK133(po)003:6449: chos kyi nyi ma sogs so //
NK133(po)003:6452: sba sgom bsod nams snying po /
NK133(po)003:6453: dus gsum mkhyen pa man gong ltar ro //
NK133(po)003:6464: sba sgom bsod nams snying po /
NK133(po)003:6465: dam pa mdzes sgom zhig po /
NK133(po)003:6469: de las dbus pa ston shaka dang /
NK133(po)003:6472: lha rje khang pa yon tan /
NK133(po)003:6477: rgyal dbang rol pa'i rdo rje /
NK133(po)003:6478: rtogs ldan mkha' spyod dbang po man gong dang 'dra /
NK133(po)003:6479: kun mkhyen klong chen pas mdzad pa'i byang chub sems
NK133(po)003:6480: kun byed rgyal po'i don khrid rin chen gru bo'i
NK133(po)003:6481: lugs khrid kyi brgyud pa ni /
NK133(po)003:6482: ston pa kun byed rgyal po /
NK133(po)003:6489: cog ro skyes bzang rmin legs /
NK133(po)003:6517: kun mkhyen gsum pa blo gros mtha' yas /
NK133(po)003:6519: chos kyi nyi ma'i bar gong bzhin no //
NK133(po)003:6521: rdzogs pa chen po nang klong sde'i skor la /
NK133(po)003:6522: klong chen rab 'byams rgyal po'i rgyud sogs kyi dgongs
NK133(po)003:6523: pa klong sde rdo rje zam pa pu sti gnyis
NK133(po)003:6524: / zhwa dmar spyan snga chos grags kyi snyan brgyud
NK133(po)003:6525: khrid yig sogs dbang lung khrid gsum yongs rdzogs kyi
NK133(po)003:6526: / brgyud pa ni / chos sku kun tu bzang po /
NK133(po)003:6527: longs sku rdo rje sems dpa'/
NK133(po)003:6528: sprul sku sems dag lha'i nor bu /
NK133(po)003:6534: ngan lam byang chub rgyal mtshan /
NK133(po)003:6539: sba sgom ye shes byang chub /
NK133(po)003:6540: 'di yan lhag med 'od phung du yal ba kho na'o //
NK133(po)003:6544: slob dpon kun bzang rdo rje /
NK133(po)003:6546: skye tshe ye shes byang chub /
NK133(po)003:6548: mkhan chen ngur pa bsod nams 'od /
NK133(po)003:6556: mtha' bzhi grags pa rin chen /
NK133(po)003:6559: zhwa dmar spyan snga chos grags shel brag pa chos kyi blo gros /
NK133(po)003:6560: khyung tshang pa blo gros dpal ldan /
NK133(po)003:6561: dpang ston karma gu ru pa /
NK133(po)003:6562: dpang ston chos dbang lhun grub /
NK133(po)003:6564: dag ston kun bzang chos rgyal /
NK133(po)003:6565: gter bdag gling pa rin chen rnam rgyal /
NK133(po)003:6570: mkhas grub rig pa'i rdo rje /
NK133(po)003:6571: kun mkhyen bla ma many+dzu g+ho sha las /
NK133(po)003:6572: rje chos kyi nyi mas gsan pa'o //
NK133(po)003:6573: gsum pa gsang ba 'od gsal rdzogs pa chen po man ngag sde /
NK133(po)003:6574: bi ma la'i snying thig gzhung dang /
NK133(po)003:6575: de'i dgongs gnad gsal bar ston pa kun mkhyen klong
NK133(po)003:6576: chen rab 'byams bzang pos mdzad pa'i bla ma yang
NK133(po)003:6577: tig yid bzhin nor bu bcas kyi dbang lung khrid
NK133(po)003:6579: chos sku kun bzang yab yum /
NK133(po)003:6589: dus gsum mkhyen pa pad+ma k+aa ra /
NK133(po)003:6590: chos rgyal khri srong lde'u btsan /
NK133(po)003:6602: khyab bdal lhun grub grags pa 'od zer /
NK133(po)003:6616: kun mkhyen bla ma 'jam dbyangs mkhyen brtse'i dbang po /
NK133(po)003:6619: mdo sngags chos kyi nyi ma'i bar ro //
NK133(po)003:6628: de gnyis kas sna tshogs rang grol lam pad+ma bkra shis /
NK133(po)003:6632: rig 'dzin sna tshogs rang grol sogs so //
NK133(po)003:6635: mkhas grub bde legs rgya mtsho /
NK133(po)003:6644: dbon po klong rdzogs bya bral /
NK133(po)003:6647: rdzogs chen gnyis pa theg mchog bstan 'dzin /
NK133(po)003:6649: gsum pa nges don bstan 'dzin bzang po rdo grub phrin las 'od zer /
NK133(po)003:6650: bzhi pa nam mkha'i rdo rje /
NK133(po)003:6651: yang na pad+ma kun grol rnam rgyal /
NK133(po)003:6652: nam mkha' tshe dbang mchog grub /
NK133(po)003:6656: rig 'dzin sna tshogs rang grol mdo sngags chos kyi nyi ma sogs so //
NK133(po)003:6661: gzhan phan mtha' yas sogs sngar dang 'dra /
NK133(po)003:6662: bstan srung e ka dza t+ai sde bdun sbrag grub la /
NK133(po)003:6663: kun mkhyen yan snying thig spyi brgyud ltar las /
NK133(po)003:6664: de nas bde legs rgya mtsho /
NK133(po)003:6676: rig 'dzin 'gyur med rdo rje man 'o bran drag dmar dang 'dra /
NK133(po)003:6677: rdzogs pa chen po sems nyid ngal gso'i gnas gsum
NK133(po)003:6678: dge ba gsum gyi don khrid kyi brgyud pa ni
NK133(po)003:6679: / mdo sngags so so'i brgyud lugs gong ma rnams ni gzhung gsal ltar la /
NK133(po)003:6680: dpal bsam yas pa klong chen rab 'byams bzang po nas /
NK133(po)003:6681: ldan sgom pa chos kyi grags pa /
NK133(po)003:6694: rdo grub byang chub rdo rje /
NK133(po)003:6698: kun mkhyen bla ma 'jam dbyangs mkhyen brtse'i dbang po /
NK133(po)003:6700: rje bla ma mdo sngags chos kyi nyi ma phyogs
NK133(po)003:6701: las rnam par rgyal ba'i sde la sogs par byon
NK133(po)003:6702: pa'o // de ltar brgyud pa rnams tshol sla phyir
NK133(po)003:6703: brjod pa yin pas slad nas brgyud pa snga ma
NK133(po)003:6704: rnams 'di bzhin la rang rang gis gang las nos
NK133(po)003:6705: pa'i brgyud pa'i gyes mtshams nas btsal shes par bya'o
NK133(po)003:6706: pa'o // // de ltar na bdag cag gi 'dren
NK133(po)003:6707: mchog bla ma dam par snga 'gyur theg pa rim
NK133(po)003:6708: dgu'i brgyud pa thams cad gcig tu 'dus shing bstan
NK133(po)003:6709: pa rin po che'i btsas su chos skor yongs rdzogs
NK133(po)003:6710: spar du bzhengs te rgyal bstan snga 'gyur ba'i bstan
NK133(po)003:6711: pa la sri zhu'i bya ba tshad med pa mdzad
NK133(po)003:6712: pa'o // // pas / da ni dpe lung gi rgyun btsal sla zhing /
NK133(po)003:6713: pusti nyi shu skor gyi dbang lung la dka' tshegs ci yang med pas /
NK133(po)003:6714: 'di dag tshang bar 'dzin skyong spel gsum gal che ste /
NK133(po)003:6715: snga 'gyur pa'i bstan 'dzin dam pa rnams kyis gzhung
NK133(po)003:6716: phyogs re dang gdams ngag phran tshegs tsam gyis chog
NK133(po)003:6717: shes mi mdzad par rnying ma'i grub mtha' theg pa
NK133(po)003:6718: rim dgu zhes yongs su grags pa ltar /
NK133(po)003:6719: slob dpon sangs rgyas gnyis pas /
NK133(po)003:6720: spyod pa mkhan po'i lugs su gyis lta ba klu sgrub lugs bzhin gyis zhes dang /
NK133(po)003:6721: phyi ltar lag len mdo sde'i lugs su spyad //
NK133(po)003:6722: rgyu 'bras spang blang zhib pa'i dgos pa yod //
NK133(po)003:6723: nang ltar gsang sngags thun mong lugs su spyad //
NK133(po)003:6724: bskyed rdzogs don dang 'brel ba'i dgos pa yod //
NK133(po)003:6725: gsang ba gsang chen a ti'i lugs su spyad //
NK133(po)003:6726: tshe gcig 'od skur grol ba'i dgos pa yod //
NK133(po)003:6728: bstan pa'i gzhi ma yon tan thams cad kyi gzhi
NK133(po)003:6729: rten 'dul ba so thar gyi tshul khrims rnam par
NK133(po)003:6731: rgyal ba'i gzhung lam theg chen sems bskyed kyis gzhung bsrang /
NK133(po)003:6732: lam gyi snying po bskyed rdzogs rdzogs pa chen pos rgyud smin par byas te /
NK133(po)003:6733: rgyal bstan yongs rdzogs 'gal med nyams su len pa
NK133(po)003:6734: rnying ma'i pan grub rig 'dzin chen po rnams kyi
NK133(po)003:6735: shing rta'i lam srol 'khrul med yin pa las /
NK133(po)003:6736: gzhan du skyabs 'gro'i bslab pa tsam ma bzung zhing
NK133(po)003:6737: bskyed rdzogs la nges pa ci yang med pa'i sgrub
NK133(po)003:6738: thabs phran tshegs klog shes pa tsam las /
NK133(po)003:6739: rgyal ba'i gsung rab mdo rgyud rnams gcan gzan mdun r+ts+wa bzhag pa ltar /
NK133(po)003:6740: byed pa ni rnying ma'i grangs su mi bgrang ste /
NK133(po)003:6742: chos lugs pad+ma 'byung gnas lugs su gyis //
NK133(po)003:6743: lta ba yas phub spyod pa mas nas 'dzeg /
NK133(po)003:6744: yid ches dpang po mdo sngags lung la gyis //
NK133(po)003:6746: rnying ma lugs mthun byed na /
NK133(po)003:6748: dbu phar sogs gzhung lugs 'chad nyan byed pa rnams
NK133(po)003:6749: snga 'gyur rnying ma ba zhes ming du chags pa
NK133(po)003:6750: ltar / bstan pa snga dar dus bsgyur mdzad pa'i
NK133(po)003:6751: rtsa 'grel tshad ma phyis kyis 'gyur bcos 'ga' re
NK133(po)003:6752: lta bu'i slad med pa rnams rgyal ba'i dgongs pa
NK133(po)003:6754: de dag gi dgongs don len shes par bya ba dang /
NK133(po)003:6759: rdzogs rim ste bka' babs kyi chu bo bzhi zhes yongs su grags pas /
NK133(po)003:6760: bka' ma'i rgyud lung man ngag gi gzhung bzang po mtha' dag dang /
NK133(po)003:6761: khyad par sgyu 'phrul gsang ba snying po'i rgyud bshad
NK133(po)003:6762: dang rdzogs chen snying thig ma bu sogs kun mkhyen
NK133(po)003:6763: klong chen pa'i gzhung lugs chen po rnams la sgro
NK133(po)003:6765: mdo rgyud gang yang don gnad gzhung 'dis 'grel shes pa dang /
NK133(po)003:6766: gter ma'i phyogs bka' dgongs sogs gnad don che ba rnams dang /
NK133(po)003:6767: de dag gi rgyab rten rgyud 'bum rin pa che
NK133(po)003:6768: yongs su rdzogs pa bcas la thos bsam gyis gzhir
NK133(po)003:6769: bzung nas / bka' mas gzhung bsrang /
NK133(po)003:6770: gter ma'i man ngag gis nyams su blang /
NK133(po)003:6771: yi dam mngon rtogs che phra gang nyams su len
NK133(po)003:6772: kyang rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid de bzhin nyid kyi
NK133(po)003:6774: rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid ting 'dzin gyis nyams su blang tshul /
NK133(po)003:6775: de las lam gyur gyi 'bras bu rig 'dzin rnam
NK133(po)003:6776: bzhi'i grub mtha' ji ltar snyogs pa'i tshul la nges
NK133(po)003:6777: pa gting tshugs pas gzhung gdams ngag tu 'char zhing
NK133(po)003:6778: / gdams ngag gzhung dang mi 'gal ba zhig gal
NK133(po)003:6779: che'o zhes shing rta'i srol 'byed chen po rnams kyis
NK133(po)003:6780: legs par gdams pa bzhin rjes su brjod pa yin
NK133(po)003:6781: / no // bka' ma theg rim dgu'i phrin chog
NK133(po)003:6782: gzhung phyi mo rnams dang bcas pa'i dkar chag bstan
NK133(po)003:6783: pa rgya mtsho'i gru gzings bkra shis dpal brgya'i 'byung
NK133(po)003:6784: / no // gnas las / theg dgu'i lam rim
NK133(po)003:6785: ltar gyi so byang sngags gsum so so'i bla ma
NK133(po)003:6786: brgyud pa'i mtshan tho brjod pa'i skabs te gsum pa'o
NK133(po)003:6787: / no // gnas las / //// gnyis pa ji
NK133(po)003:6788: ltar spar du bsgrubs tshul bzhugs byang dkar chag dngos
NK133(po)003:6789: 'god pa la gang gis spar du sgrub par mdzad
NK133(po)003:6790: pa po'i gang zag gi rnam thar shin tu mdor
NK133(po)003:6791: bsdus sa bon tsam ni gong du song la /
NK133(po)003:6792: ji ltar sgrub pa'i tshul ni /
NK133(po)003:6793: bdag cag gi 'dren mchog chos kyi rgyal po bka'
NK133(po)003:6794: drin mtshungs pa med pa'i bdag nyid can des rgyal
NK133(po)003:6795: ba'i bstan pa rin po che spyi dang khyad par
NK133(po)003:6796: snga 'gyur rdo rje theg pa'i bstan pa 'di nyid
NK133(po)003:6797: sgo du ma nas mi nyams zhing 'phel ba'i thabs
NK133(po)003:6799: 'di ltar rnying ma zhes ming gdags yul gyi mtshan
NK133(po)003:6800: gzhi ni rgyud sde bka' ma rnams yin 'dug kyang
NK133(po)003:6801: / deng sang chos la don gnyer chung zhing /
NK133(po)003:6802: bstan pa gnad gang gis che shes pa'ang dkon pa'i
NK133(po)003:6803: dbang gis bka' ma'i gzhung phal che ba zhig ni
NK133(po)003:6804: dbang lung gi rgyun chad song /
NK133(po)003:6805: da lta rgyun breng tsam yod pa 'di rnams kyang brgyud pa nyag phra bas /
NK133(po)003:6806: zab gsang bla na med pa'i rgyud sde rin po
NK133(po)003:6807: che 'di rnams snyigs ma'i dus 'dir mtshan tsam rnyed
NK133(po)003:6808: pa'ang don che ba la dgongs nas rgya sprul rin
NK133(po)003:6809: po che dang / khong mkhan slob nas deng sang
NK133(po)003:6810: rgyun bzhugs so 'tshal 'bad pas btsal nas dbang lung
NK133(po)003:6811: lan mang gsungs pa yin kyang /
NK133(po)003:6812: slob tshogs de dag nang nas slar 'chad pa ni
NK133(po)003:6813: mdo dbang sogs chos bka' 'ga' re tsam ma gtogs
NK133(po)003:6814: yongs rdzogs 'chad pa ni cher ma byung bas /
NK133(po)003:6815: de'i rgyu mtshan ni dpe cha dkon pa 'dis byung 'dug /
NK133(po)003:6816: gsar rnying gang la'ang dgon gnas nor rdzas kha rje
NK133(po)003:6817: gong 'phel la nus pa ci yod byed pa ni
NK133(po)003:6819: dam pa'i chos la don gnyer byed pa ni gang
NK133(po)003:6820: du'ang dkon par snang ba 'di sems can gyi bde
NK133(po)003:6821: skyid mi 'byung zhing rgyal bstan dbyings su gzim pa'i
NK133(po)003:6822: ltas shar bas / bya ba thams cad kyi nang
NK133(po)003:6823: nas gal chung ba ni chos 'chad nyan la byed
NK133(po)003:6824: ltas shar bas / pa dang / dngos rdzas bca'
NK133(po)003:6825: ka thams cad kyi nang nas za chog nyer mkho
NK133(po)003:6826: tsam las rgyud gzhung gsung rab rnams mkho med du
NK133(po)003:6827: byed pas dpe cha bri nus pa ni mi 'dug
NK133(po)003:6828: ltas shar bas / pa dang / / gzhung pod
NK133(po)003:6829: rgyun yod do cog spar la 'khod na dpe cha
NK133(po)003:6830: dka' tshegs med pas dbang lung 'chad spel byed pa
NK133(po)003:6831: ltas shar bas / pa dang / / re'ang 'byung
NK133(po)003:6832: / dbang lung thob na bsnyen sgrub nyams len byed
NK133(po)003:6833: pa re'ang 'byung srid pas spar zhig 'grub na don
NK133(po)003:6835: mdo khams snga 'gyur pa'i gdan sa gsum gyi ya
NK133(po)003:6836: gyal 'bri zla zal mo sgang ngam bu 'bor sgang
NK133(po)003:6837: gi cha stod na rtsub ri ljongs /
NK133(po)003:6839: smad na gye re ljongs sogs las /
NK133(po)003:6841: sgyu 'phrul mkhas pa gye re mchog skyong gis gdul
NK133(po)003:6842: bya skyong ba'i yul las grags zhes yig rnying las
NK133(po)003:6843: 'byung ba ltar gdod nas he ru kas byin gyis
NK133(po)003:6844: rlabs pa'i gnas / dpal ldan pad+ma k+aa ra'i bstan pa rgyas pa'i yul /
NK133(po)003:6845: rnam par rgyal ba'i byang chub chos kyi gling 'di nyid du /
NK133(po)003:6846: skal bzang rnam 'dren bzhi pa thub pa'i dbang po
NK133(po)003:6847: mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas te chos kyi 'khor
NK133(po)003:6848: lo thog mar bskor nas da lta'i bar bgrang bya'i
NK133(po)003:6849: 'khor lo nyis stong brgyad brgya go gsum /
NK133(po)003:6850: o rgyan sangs rgyas gnyis pa shing sprel la sin+d+hu'i
NK133(po)003:6851: mtsho gling du bltams nas nyis stong bdun brgya don
NK133(po)003:6852: bzhi / gsang bdag gi rigs can dra ma lnga
NK133(po)003:6853: la chos 'khor bskor nas rgyal po dza'i gnas su
NK133(po)003:6854: gsang sngags babs nas nyis stong bdun brgya lnga bcu
NK133(po)003:6855: bzhi / / gangs ri'i ljongs su mkhan slob chos
NK133(po)003:6856: gsum zhal 'dzoms nas sangs rgyas kyi mdo sngags bstan
NK133(po)003:6857: pa dar bar mdzad nas chig stong don gcig /
NK133(po)003:6858: mdo khams 'di na snga 'gyur pa'i rigs lugs dpal kahthoga btab nas bdun brgya so brgyad /
NK133(po)003:6859: rig 'dzin kun bzang shes rab kyis dpal yul chos sde btab nas nyis brgya sum cu son pa /
NK133(po)003:6860: rab tshes rnam 'phyang zhes pa sa pho khyi'i lo /
NK133(po)003:6861: rje de nyid dgung grangs zhe lnga bzhes pa'i tshe dbu 'dzug par mdzad do //
NK133(po)003:6862: thog mar dbu 'dzug pa nas rjes su bya ba
NK133(po)003:6863: mthar phyin nye bar do dam khur len rdzogs nang
NK133(po)003:6864: dbon po kun bzang 'gyur med rdo rje /
NK133(po)003:6866: dbon po dpal 'byor rnams dang spar yig bri ba'i
NK133(po)003:6867: 'go 'dom rmugs sangs gnas rgyab bla ma sman pa
NK133(po)003:6869: bla ma kun bzang dpal 'byor sogs kyis mdzad /
NK133(po)003:6870: ma phyi smin gling dang rdzogs chen gyi spar yod
NK133(po)003:6871: rigs de ltar dang gzhan rnams yig rnying khung btsun
NK133(po)003:6873: dpe rnying rnams tshig 'dra min mang zhing bcos dka'
NK133(po)003:6874: ba rnams dpe mthun mang ba dbang btsan du byas
NK133(po)003:6875: te / ma phyi'i zhu dag sdom brtson rdo rje
NK133(po)003:6876: 'dzin pa rnam dpyod blo gros kyi mthu phul du
NK133(po)003:6877: byung ba mkhan thub bstan rgyal mtshan 'od zer nas
NK133(po)003:6878: te / mdzad pa dang / spar du grub zin
NK133(po)003:6879: snga ma rnams zhu dag dang po rmugs sangs mkhan
NK133(po)003:6880: po pad+ma shes rab bzang po /
NK133(po)003:6883: brda go'i bla brang me skyon shor skabs chud zos yod rigs gso ba /
NK133(po)003:6884: rdzogs nang kun bzang 'gyur med kyis thugs btson chen po mdzad cing /
NK133(po)003:6885: skyabs rje thub bstan chos kyi glang pos ljags zhus dang mthun rkyen ci rigs brtsal ba dang /
NK133(po)003:6886: chos sde rgya che bas zhu dag 'phro lus dang
NK133(po)003:6887: sgyu 'phrul phra mo drug cu'i pod gzhung gtsos pa'i
NK133(po)003:6888: rnying skor tshad thub pod bcu skor kha bskang gi
NK133(po)003:6889: tshul du yang srid rin po che karma theg mchog
NK133(po)003:6890: snying pos gong ma'i phyag bzhes mjug skyong gis gsar
NK133(po)003:6891: bskrun bcas legs par grub pa yin no //
NK133(po)003:6892: gsum pa bzhugs byang dngos la ji ltar 'god pa'i
NK133(po)003:6893: go rim phal cher yas babs kyi lugs su bkod
NK133(po)003:6894: pa mang yang / 'dir ni dpal gsang ba'i snying po las /
NK133(po)003:6895: sa rnams khyad par bkod pa yang //
NK133(po)003:6896: gsang ba'i snying por 'gro ba'i lam //
NK133(po)003:6897: zhes pas sa dang lam gyi rnam par bzhag pa
NK133(po)003:6898: thams cad mthar thug gsang ba'i snying po rang bzhin
NK133(po)003:6899: rdzogs pa chen por 'jug pa'i lam stegs su gsungs
NK133(po)003:6900: shing / der ji lta bkri ba'i tshul yang phur pa zhe sdang khros pa'i rgyud las /
NK133(po)003:6901: so so thar pa dang po sbyin //
NK133(po)003:6902: de la nyan thos chos rnams bstan //
NK133(po)003:6903: de nas byang chub sdom chen sbyin //
NK133(po)003:6904: de la dbu ma'i chos rnams bshad //
NK133(po)003:6905: mthar ni 'bras bu theg chen gyi //
NK133(po)003:6908: kye rdo rje brtag pa phyi ma'i le'u las /
NK133(po)003:6909: dang po gso sbyong sbyin par bya //
NK133(po)003:6910: de rjes bslab pa'i gnas bcu nyid //
NK133(po)003:6911: de la bye brag smra ba bstan //
NK133(po)003:6912: mdo sde pa'ang de bzhin no //
NK133(po)003:6913: de nas rnal 'byor spyod pa nyid //
NK133(po)003:6914: de'i rjes su dbu ma bstan //
NK133(po)003:6915: sngags kyi rim pa kun shes nas //
NK133(po)003:6916: de rjes kye yi rdo rje bstan //
NK133(po)003:6917: slob mas gus pas blang nas ni //
NK133(po)003:6920: gdul bya'i gang zag rnams lam du ji ltar 'jug
NK133(po)003:6921: pa'i rim pa dang mtshungs par bkod pa yin te
NK133(po)003:6922: / dpal mgon klu sgrub zhabs kyis /
NK133(po)003:6923: thabs 'di rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyis //
NK133(po)003:6924: skas kyi sdong bu lta bur bstan //
NK133(po)003:6926: de la 'dir rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa dang
NK133(po)003:6927: 'bras bus rdo rje theg pa'i phyi nang gnyis las
NK133(po)003:6928: / dang po la'ang bstan pa'i gzhi ma 'dul ba
NK133(po)003:6929: so thar gyi skor rnams ni rim bzhin glegs bam
NK133(po)003:6931: snga 'gyur sdom rgyun mkhan brgyud kyi rnam thar nyung
NK133(po)003:6932: gsal sgron ma mkhan chen lo ts+aa ba chos dpal
NK133(po)003:6935: so sor thar pa'i sdom rgyun gsol 'debs ngag dbang
NK133(po)003:6936: blo bzang rgya mtshos mdzad pa la lo chen dang
NK133(po)003:6937: thub bstan pad+ma rgyas pa'i nyin byed kyis kha skong
NK133(po)003:6939: bsnyen gnas len pa'i cho ga mdo don gsal ba gzhan phan mtha' yas kyis mdzad pa ldeb 3 /
NK133(po)003:6940: khyim pa rjes su 'dzin pa so sor thar pa'i
NK133(po)003:6941: sdom chog thar lam rab gsal rig 'dzin 'gyur med
NK133(po)003:6943: rab byung gzhi'i cho ga rin chen them skas lo
NK133(po)003:6944: chen chos dpal rgya mtshos sbyar ba dus brjod kyi
NK133(po)003:6946: bslab pa yongs su sbyong ba gzhi gsum gyi cho
NK133(po)003:6947: ga thar gling du bgrod pa'i gru chen d+harma sh+r+ais
NK133(po)003:6949: dus nges pa'i gso sbyong gi 'das lus brjod tshul gyi re'u mig dang bcas pa /
NK133(po)003:6951: dge slong pha'i so thar gyi mdo gzhi thams cad
NK133(po)003:6952: yod par smra ba'i 'dul ba 'dzin pa slob dpon
NK133(po)003:6953: yon tan 'od kyis mdzad pa dzi na mi tra
NK133(po)003:6954: dang lo ts+aa ba cog ro klu'i rgyal mtshan gyis
NK133(po)003:6957: rnam mkhyen lam gyi dngos gzhi theg chen sems bskyed
NK133(po)003:6958: kyi phrin chog skor la smon 'jug sems bskyed kyi
NK133(po)003:6959: brgyud 'debs 'gyur med rdo rje'i gsung la gzhan phan
NK133(po)003:6960: mtha' yas kha skong mdzad pa ldeb 3 /
NK133(po)003:6961: theg pa chen po dbu ma lugs kyi sems bskyed
NK133(po)003:6962: kyi cho ga rgyal sras lam bzang 'gyur med rdo
NK133(po)003:6964: bi ma la'i shes rab snying po'i 'grel pa la ldeb 99 /
NK133(po)003:6965: gnyis pa thabs kyis che ba 'bras bu rdo rje
NK133(po)003:6966: theg pa'i skor la'ang spyir rgyud sde bzhi la nang
NK133(po)003:6967: gses kyi dbye ba bsam gyis mi khyab pa bzhugs
NK133(po)003:6968: pas 'di tsam zhes phyogs gcig tu tshad bzung bar
NK133(po)003:6969: mi nus kyang / dgos pa'i dbang gis rgyud sde so so'i gzhung tshad bshad pa ltar na /
NK133(po)003:6970: ye shes rdo rje kun las btus pa'i rgyud las /
NK133(po)003:6971: rnal 'byor chen po'i rgyud kyi ming stong phrag bcu
NK133(po)003:6972: gnyis zhes bya ba ste rgyas par byas na grangs
NK133(po)003:6973: med do // gnyis ka'i rgyud la stong phrag drug go //
NK133(po)003:6974: spyod pa'i rgyud stong phrag drug go //
NK133(po)003:6975: bya ba'i rgyud stong phrag bzhi'o //
NK133(po)003:6977: de yang rag pa tsam las zhib par na bya
NK133(po)003:6978: ba'i rgyud kyi de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs gcig pu
NK133(po)003:6980: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs kyi rgyud sde'i tshad //
NK133(po)003:6981: 'bum phrag lnga dang bye ba phrag gsum dag /
NK133(po)003:6983: de bzhin du rnal 'byor bla med kho na'i rgyud kyang sdom 'byung las /
NK133(po)003:6984: rnal 'byor rgyud rnams kyi ni tshad //
NK133(po)003:6985: bye ba phrag ni drug tu nges //
NK133(po)003:6986: de bzhin rnal 'byor ma rgyud grangs //
NK133(po)003:6987: bye ba phrag ni bcu drug grags //
NK133(po)003:6988: zhes sogs dpag tu med par gsungs pas de rnams kyang mdor bsdu na /
NK133(po)003:6989: gsang sngags phyi nang gi rim pa gnyis su 'du ba las /
NK133(po)003:6990: phyi rgyud la'ang bya spyod rnal 'byor gyi rgyud sde gsum du dbye zhing /
NK133(po)003:6991: bya rgyud la nang gses rigs kyi sgo nas dbye ba mang zhig mchis pa las /
NK133(po)003:6992: 'dir de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs kyi gtso bo'i phyogs
NK133(po)003:6993: su gtogs pa'i rgyud sde'i dgongs pa 'khrul med du
NK133(po)003:6994: phyung ba'i phrin chog skor la /
NK133(po)003:6995: bde gshegs sman rgyal bdun gyi mchod pa'i cho ga zhi ba 'tsho'i lugs /
NK133(po)003:6996: ngag dbang blo bzang rgya mtshos chog khrigs su gtab pa yid bzhin dbang rgyal ldeb 69 /
NK133(po)003:6997: mkhon ston dpal 'byor lhun grub kyi mdzad pa sman lha zhe bdun ma'i dbang chog ldeb 16 /
NK133(po)003:7001: shes pa thams cad mthar phyin par grub pa'i mchod rten zhes bya ba'i gzungs dang /
NK133(po)003:7002: 'phags pa kun nas sgor 'jug pa'i gtsug tor dri
NK133(po)003:7003: ma med pa'i gzungs bklag cing mchod rten brgya rtsa
NK133(po)003:7004: brgyad dam / mchod rten lnga gdab pa'i cho ga
NK133(po)003:7005: mdo sde las btus pa slob dpon chen po bo
NK133(po)003:7006: d+hi sa t+was mdzad pa bcas ldeb 69 /
NK133(po)003:7007: mchod rten bskor ba'i tshigs su bcad pa dang /
NK133(po)003:7008: gsal rgyal gyis tshigs su bcad pa bcas ldeb 11 /
NK133(po)003:7009: 'od zer dri ma med pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi cho
NK133(po)003:7010: ga 'chi med 'byung ba bu ston rin chen grub
NK133(po)003:7012: 'od zer dri med kyi dkyil chog gi lhan thabs
NK133(po)003:7013: dbang chog dang bcas pa mun sel nyin byed snang
NK133(po)003:7014: ba ldeb 36 / 'od zer dri med kyi dkyil
NK133(po)003:7015: chog gi kha skong dbang chog bdud rtsi'i chu rgyun
NK133(po)003:7016: zhwa lu bsod nams mchog grub kyis mdzad pa ldeb
NK133(po)003:7017: ba ldeb 36 / 11 / gtsug tor dri ma
NK133(po)003:7018: med pa lha lnga'i cho ga rin chen bsam 'phel
NK133(po)003:7019: zhes bya ba zhwa lu rin chen bsod nams mchog
NK133(po)003:7021: dri med rnam gnyis kyi gzungs la brten te mchod
NK133(po)003:7022: rten bzhengs pa la nye bar mkho ba'i cho ga
NK133(po)003:7023: bklag pas grub pa lo chen d+harma sh+r+ais mdzad pa
NK133(po)003:7024: ldeb 57 / 'phags pa 'od zer dri med kyi
NK133(po)003:7025: rgyun gyi bzlas pa bya tshul 'jam mgon yon tan
NK133(po)003:7027: gtsug tor dri ma med pa'i gzungs dang 'brel bar
NK133(po)003:7028: s+aats+tsha gdab pa'i cho ga'i lag len dri med kun
NK133(po)003:7029: snang yon tan rgya mtshos mdzad pa ldeb 13 /
NK133(po)003:7030: mchod rten brgya rtsa brgyad gdab pa'i cho ga mkhan
NK133(po)003:7031: chen zhi ba 'tshos mdzad pa las nyung ngur bsdus
NK133(po)003:7032: pa dri med lam 'jug yon tan rgya mtsho blo
NK133(po)003:7033: gros mtha' yas mdzad pa ldeb 26 /
NK133(po)003:7034: 'phags pa 'od zer dri ma med pa rnam par
NK133(po)003:7035: dag pa'i 'od ces bya ba'i sgrub mchod dkyus ma
NK133(po)003:7036: bya ba'i dkyil chog dri med rab gsal pad+ma mdo
NK133(po)003:7037: sngags bstan 'dzin bzang pos mdzad pa ldeb 52 /
NK133(po)003:7038: mchod pa byin rlabs dang 'bul tshig ldeb 3 /
NK133(po)003:7039: 'dus mdo'i byang sems dkyil 'khor yum chen mo'i sgrub thabs bcas /
NK133(po)003:7040: thub bstan chos kyi glang pos mdzad pa bcas 'bor bzhugs /
NK133(po)003:7042: bya rgyud rdo rje'i rigs kyi rdo rje rnam par
NK133(po)003:7043: 'joms pa dkar po bi ma la'i bka' srol las
NK133(po)003:7045: dpal rdo rje rnam par 'joms pa'i gzungs kyi cho
NK133(po)003:7046: ga karma pa rang byung rdo rje mdzad pa dang
NK133(po)003:7047: / gzungs chog rigs gtad bum sgrub dang bcas pa
NK133(po)003:7048: zla ba'i 'od zer blo gros mtha' yas kyis bsgrigs
NK133(po)003:7050: rnam 'joms bi ma la dang gnyags kyi 'gyur kahthoga pa dam gtsang byams gsum nas brgyud pa /
NK133(po)003:7051: rdo rje rnam par 'joms pa khro dkar gyi gzungs
NK133(po)003:7052: kyi cho ga dbang bskur dang bcas pa dag byed
NK133(po)003:7053: shel gyi bum bzang blo gros mtha' yas kyis bsgrigs
NK133(po)003:7054: pa ldeb 27 / slob dpon bram ze mchog sred
NK133(po)003:7055: kyis lugs gnubs chen nas brgyud kahthoga pa la bka'
NK133(po)003:7056: babs pa rdo rje rnam par 'joms pa khro nag
NK133(po)003:7057: lha bco lnga pa'i sgrub thabs gzungs kyi cho ga
NK133(po)003:7058: dang bcas sbyong byed rdo rje'i bum pa blo gros
NK133(po)003:7059: mtha' yas kyis mdzad pa ldeb 20 /
NK133(po)003:7060: rdo rje rnam par 'joms pa khro nag lha bco
NK133(po)003:7061: lnga'i dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur ba'i cho ga smin
NK133(po)003:7062: byed ye shes bum pa blo gros mtha' yas mdzad
NK133(po)003:7063: pa ldeb 25 / rnam 'joms khro dkar khro nag
NK133(po)003:7064: gnyis kyi gzhung rnying rgya sdong ston pa seng ge'i
NK133(po)003:7065: yig cha kha tshang la ldeb &&&/
NK133(po)003:7066: slob dpon zhi ba 'tsho'i bka' srol bya rgyud rigs
NK133(po)003:7067: kyi yum rje btsun ma gza' thams cad kyi yum
NK133(po)003:7068: rigs pa chen mo'i sgrub mchod slob dpon ngag dbang
NK133(po)003:7070: gza' yum dkyil chog bde legs kun phan pad+ma mdo sngags bstan 'dzin mdzad pa ldeb 26bcas dang /
NK133(po)003:7071: snga 'gyur bi ma mi tra'i lugs kyi gdugs dkar
NK133(po)003:7072: rtsa gzhung rgyal dbang karma pa rang byung rdo rjes
NK133(po)003:7075: spyod rgyud rnam snang mngon byang gi cho ga rje
NK133(po)003:7076: bla ma ris med bstan pa'i rgyal mtshan gyis mdzad
NK133(po)003:7077: pa rnams so // 'dir rnal 'byor rgyud las ngan
NK133(po)003:7078: song sbyong rgyud sogs kyi phrin chog 'god par 'os
NK133(po)003:7079: kyang sngon chad rang lugs chog khrigs ma byung bas
NK133(po)003:7080: slar bsgrigs zin pa dang 'dir 'dzud dgos shing /
NK133(po)003:7081: rang gzhung 'dus mdo'i yan lag gi cho ga dag
NK133(po)003:7082: ni 'og tu de nyid kyi skabs su gsal ba
NK133(po)003:7083: ltar ro // gnyis pa gsang chen bla ma med pa nang gi rgyud la yang /
NK133(po)003:7084: thabs bskyed pa'i rim pa gtso bor ston pa rgyud ma h+aa yo ga /
NK133(po)003:7085: shes rab rdzogs pa'i rim pa gtso bor ston pa lung a nu yo ga /
NK133(po)003:7086: brjod bral gnyis su med pa'i ye shes gtso bor
NK133(po)003:7087: ston pa man ngag a ti yo ga gsum la
NK133(po)003:7088: / dang po ma h+aa yo ga'i skor la sku
NK133(po)003:7089: gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga'i gzhi dang rtsa
NK133(po)003:7090: bar gyur pa'i rgyud sde lnga /
NK133(po)003:7091: sgrub pa lag len du ston pa rol pa'i rgyud sde lnga /
NK133(po)003:7092: spyod pa'i yan lag tu 'gro ba'i rgyud sde lnga /
NK133(po)003:7093: ma tshang kha skong gi rgyud sde gnyis /
NK133(po)003:7094: thams cad la khyab pa'i rgyud chen po gcig dang bco brgyad yod pa las /
NK133(po)003:7095: dang po rtsa ba'i rgyud sde lnga'i nang tshan sku'i
NK133(po)003:7096: rgyud dpal sangs rgyas thams cad mnyam par sbyor ba'i
NK133(po)003:7098: mnyam sbyor ku ku r+aa dza'i rgya gzhung gnyis la ldeb 151 /
NK133(po)003:7099: mnyam sbyor gyi brgyud 'debs gzhan phan mtha' yas mdzad pa ldeb 1 /
NK133(po)003:7100: dpal sangs rgyas thams cad mnyam par sbyor ba rigs bsdus pa'i sgrub thabs bde chen 'dod 'jo /
NK133(po)003:7101: de'i dkyil 'khor gyi cho ga kun tu bzang po'i zhal lung /
NK133(po)003:7102: dbang gi cho ga byin rlabs char 'bebs ldeb 27bcas
NK133(po)003:7103: rig 'dzin 'gyur med rdo rjes khrigs su bsdebs bcas
NK133(po)003:7104: 'bor bzhugs so // gnyis pa gsung gi rgyud zla gsang thigs le /
NK133(po)003:7105: gsum pa thugs kyi rgyud gsang ba 'dus pa /
NK133(po)003:7106: bzhi pa yon tan gyi rgyud dpal mchog dang po /
NK133(po)003:7107: lnga pa phrin las kyi rgyud karma ma le rnams
NK133(po)003:7108: la sngar chog khrigs ma byung bas slar 'dir 'dzud
NK133(po)003:7110: gnyis pa rol pa'i rgyud sde lnga las sku gshin
NK133(po)003:7111: rje rol pa'i phrin chog gi skor la'ang gsum las
NK133(po)003:7112: / dang po kha thun nag po'i skor la /
NK133(po)003:7113: sa gsum pa 'od byed brnyes pa'i gnubs chen sangs
NK133(po)003:7114: rgyas ye shes kyi thugs dam 'jam dpal gshin rje
NK133(po)003:7115: gshed kha thun nag po'i skor gyi gzhung pod yongs
NK133(po)003:7116: rdzogs bdud las rnam par rgyal ba'i rnga sgra zhes
NK133(po)003:7117: bya ba ldeb 280kha thun brgyud 'debs gzhan phan mtha'
NK133(po)003:7119: 'jam dpal gshin rje kha thun nag po'i sgrub thabs bklag pas don grub ldeb 28 /
NK133(po)003:7121: bcas rgyal sras rin chen rnam rgyal chog khrigs dbang chu pad+ma ldeb 7 /
NK133(po)003:7123: ri khrod pa ngag dbang grags pa'i chog khrigs ldeb 6 /
NK133(po)003:7126: gnyis pa gnubs lugs gshin rje ru mtshon dmar po'i skor la /
NK133(po)003:7127: bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal gshin rje gshed dmar po'i
NK133(po)003:7128: gzhung pod yongs rdzogs ze chen rgyal tshab kyi chog
NK133(po)003:7129: khrigs / bstan pa srung ba'i lcags ri chen po ldeb418 /
NK133(po)003:7130: brgyud 'debs gzhan phan mtha' yas mdzad pa ldeb 1 /
NK133(po)003:7131: gshed dmar las byang bdud dpung mthar byed rig 'dzin 'gyur med rdo rje'i chog khrigs ldeb 23 /
NK133(po)003:7132: de'i dkyil chog dngos grub len pa bcas rin chen rnam rgyal chog khrigs ldeb 7 /
NK133(po)003:7133: 'jam dpal gshin rje gshed dmar po'i phrin las rdo
NK133(po)003:7134: rje rtse brgya pa log rtog bdud dpung pham byed
NK133(po)003:7137: sku gsung thugs kyi rjes gnang nyung gsal ldeb 4 /
NK133(po)003:7138: bcas mkhan o rgyan bstan 'dzin rdo rje'i chog khrigs 'bor ldeb bzhugs /
NK133(po)003:7140: gsum pa gnubs lugs 'jam dpal gshin rje gdong drug skor la gzhung pod them byang /
NK133(po)003:7141: rgya gzhung gtso bor gyur pa'i yig cha yongs rdzogs ldeb 226 /
NK133(po)003:7142: bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal gshin rje gdong drug nag
NK133(po)003:7143: po gsang rdzogs thugs kyi sgrub pa'i las byang rdo
NK133(po)003:7145: gdong drug thugs kyi sgrub pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi cho ga rdo rje rnam par rol ba ldeb 11 /
NK133(po)003:7146: gdong drug thugs kyi sgrub pa'i dbang chog rdo rje'i chu rgyun ldeb 41 /
NK133(po)003:7147: rnams blo gros mtha' yas kyis mdzad pa dag go //
NK133(po)003:7148: gnyis pa gsung rta mchog rol pa'i phrin chog skor
NK133(po)003:7149: rnams rang byung zhabs kyi bde gshegs thugs dril sogs
NK133(po)003:7150: dang rgyal ba rgya mtsho lha lnga skor rnams slad
NK133(po)003:7152: gsum pa thugs he ru ka rol pa'i phrin chog skor la /
NK133(po)003:7153: yang dag gi brgyud 'debs gzhan phan mtha' yas mdzad pa ldeb 1 /
NK133(po)003:7154: dpal yang dag he ru ka'i sgrub thabs bde chen thig le ldeb 25 /
NK133(po)003:7155: de'i dkyil chog bdud rtsi'i nying khu ldeb 11 /
NK133(po)003:7156: dpal chen yang dag lha dgu'i dbang mchog bde chen 'jug ngogs ldeb 25 /
NK133(po)003:7157: rnams rig 'dzin 'gyur med rdo rjes mdzad pa /
NK133(po)003:7158: yang dag he ru ka tshom bu tshogs su sgrub
NK133(po)003:7159: pa'i pra khrid lag len gsal bar bkod pa bde
NK133(po)003:7162: bcas blo gros mtha' yas mdzad pa 'bor ldeb bzhugs /
NK133(po)003:7164: gu ru rin po che'i gsung yang dag gsang 'grel ldeb /
NK133(po)003:7165: bzhi pa yon tan bdud rtsi rol pa'i skor la /
NK133(po)003:7166: bdud rtsi sman gyi rtogs brjod rgya gzhung ldeb 9 /
NK133(po)003:7167: phrin chog skor rnams slad nas 'dzud dgos so //
NK133(po)003:7168: lnga pa phrin las phur pa rol pa'i phrin chog
NK133(po)003:7169: skor la brgyud pa'i khyad par las rgyal po lugs
NK133(po)003:7170: rig 'dzin 'jigs med gling pas chog khrigs mdzad pa
NK133(po)003:7171: dang mkhon lugs phur pa rnams gzhan du gsal la
NK133(po)003:7172: / 'jam mgon yon tan rgya mtshos mdzad pa phur pa rtsa dum 'grel ldeb 107 /
NK133(po)003:7175: sna nam lugs rog phur du grags pa'i skor la /
NK133(po)003:7176: dpal rdo rje phur pa'i sgrub skor las rog phur
NK133(po)003:7177: gyi gzhung pod phrin las rol pa'i bang mdzod ces
NK133(po)003:7179: rdo rje phur pa'i bshad 'bum slob dpon rnam gsum
NK133(po)003:7180: gyi dgongs pa slob dpon pad+mas mkhar chen gza' la
NK133(po)003:7182: dpal rdo rje phur pa'i tika nyi ma'i 'od zer
NK133(po)003:7183: snye mdo jo sras bsod nams dpal gyis sbyar ba
NK133(po)003:7187: rog lugs phur pa'i brgyud 'debs d+harma sh+r+ais mdzad pa ldeb 3 /
NK133(po)003:7188: rdo rje phur pa rog lugs kyi sgrub thabs dngos grub char 'bebs ldeb 34 /
NK133(po)003:7189: stod las kyi sgrub khog bde chen bdud rtsi'i bcud len ldeb 35 /
NK133(po)003:7190: dbang chog bde chen mchog ster ldeb 13 /
NK133(po)003:7191: smad las kyi sgrub khog gdug can mthar byed rdo rje 'bar ba'i 'khrul 'khor ldeb 21 /
NK133(po)003:7192: bcas lo chen d+harma sh+r+ais chog khrigs /
NK133(po)003:7193: gnyis pa jo mo lugs rong zom phur pa'i skor ni /
NK133(po)003:7194: dpal rdo rje phur pa'i sgrub skor las /
NK133(po)003:7195: rong zom lugs kyi phur pa'i gzhung pod bstan pa rgya mtsho'i snying bcud ldeb 285 /
NK133(po)003:7196: dbang chog jo bo lang lab lugs ldeb 12 /
NK133(po)003:7198: brgyud 'debs gzhan phan mtha' yas mdzad pa ldeb 1 /
NK133(po)003:7199: las byang dngos grub rgya mtsho'i snying po ldeb 40 /
NK133(po)003:7201: bcas rin chen rnam rgyal gyi chog khrigs bcas 'bor ldeb 449 /
NK133(po)003:7203: gsum pa spyod pa'i yan lag tu 'gro ba'i rgyud sde lnga dang /
NK133(po)003:7204: bzhi pa ma tshang kha skong gi rgyud sde gnyis
NK133(po)003:7205: bcas kyi phrin chog skor rnams slad nas 'dir 'dzud
NK133(po)003:7207: lnga pa spyi rgyud sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i skor la /
NK133(po)003:7208: thog mar rtsa brgyud gsang ba snying po ldeb 35 /
NK133(po)003:7209: brgyud 'debs dang rgyud 'chad thabs bcas ldeb 10 /
NK133(po)003:7212: dpal gsang ba snying po'i 'grel pa gsang bdag dgongs rgyan lo chen d+harma sh+r+ais mdzad pa ldeb 237 /
NK133(po)003:7213: chos grags zin bris rin chen phreng ba ldeb 120 /
NK133(po)003:7214: rgyud kyi dog gcod lung rig rdo rje'i rol rtsed ldeb bcas 'bor ldeb bzhugs /
NK133(po)003:7216: sgyu 'phrul gyi rgya gzhung rigs phyogs gcig tu bkod pa man ngag phra mo drug cu skor la /
NK133(po)003:7217: thog mar man ngag 'grel bshad skor las /
NK133(po)003:7218: sgeg rdor gsung gsang 'grel spar khab la kahthoga pa nam mkha' dpal gyi mchan can ldeb 216 /
NK133(po)003:7220: nyi 'od seng ge'i rgya cher 'grel ldeb 140 /
NK133(po)003:7223: rgyud kyi spyi don khog phub skor la /
NK133(po)003:7224: sgegs rdor sgyu 'phrul spyi gcod thugs thig /
NK133(po)003:7225: bi ma la'i khog gzhung gsal sgron /
NK133(po)003:7226: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba rin po che'i 'od snang bcas ldeb 27 /
NK133(po)003:7228: slob dpon bzhad pa rdo rjes mdzad pa'i la shan lta ba'i sgron me rtsa ba /
NK133(po)003:7230: 'jam dpal bshes gnyen phyi ma'i 'grel pa /
NK133(po)003:7231: g.yu sgra'i 'gyur klu sgrub kyi g.yu'i thang ma spras 'dren dgu /
NK133(po)003:7232: bi ma la'i mtshan nyid sgron ma /
NK133(po)003:7233: bi ma'i shes rab spyan 'byed kyi man ngag bcas ldeb 59 /
NK133(po)003:7234: sh+r+ai sing+ha'i thugs kyi sgo lcags ldeb 22 /
NK133(po)003:7235: pad+ma'i man ngag lta ba'i phreng ba rtsa 'grel ldeb 49 /
NK133(po)003:7236: bcas spyod pa'i skor gyi rgya gzhung ma rnyed /
NK133(po)003:7238: sangs rgyas gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor chos don /
NK133(po)003:7239: bi ma la'i thig gi pan+hir+tha bcas ldeb 11 /
NK133(po)003:7241: sems bskyed pa'i cho ga dzi na mi tra'i gsung /
NK133(po)003:7242: bi ma la'i bsre ba'i thob byang /
NK133(po)003:7243: sangs rgyas gsang ba'i zhi ba rdo rje las rim /
NK133(po)003:7244: de'i 'grel pa bi ma la'i gsung khro bo'i rdo rje las rim /
NK133(po)003:7245: sangs rgyas gsang ba'i dbang gis nges par 'byed pa /
NK133(po)003:7246: sangs rgyas gsang ba'i dbang gi gal po rtsa ba /
NK133(po)003:7248: dbang gi gal po'i 'bru 'grel rdo rje gro lod gsung /
NK133(po)003:7249: sgegs rdor thugs kyi thig pa sgeg rdor gyi sgyu 'phrul lhan cig skyes pa ye shes snang ba /
NK133(po)003:7255: bde ba chen po phyag rgya'i man ngag bcas bi ma'i gsung /
NK133(po)003:7256: s+thi ra ma tis mdzad pa'i byang chub sems kyi ljon shing bcas ldeb 165 /
NK133(po)003:7258: lta ba dang theg pa'i khyad bsdus ldeb 8 /
NK133(po)003:7261: sgeg rdor dam tshig gi gsal bkra /
NK133(po)003:7265: dur khrod bde ba'i dpe chung rang gnas /
NK133(po)003:7266: de'i 'grel pa bi ma la'i gsung /
NK133(po)003:7267: bi ma'i tshig rkang bcu dgu pa /
NK133(po)003:7269: gnas lung chen po'i tho yig /
NK133(po)003:7271: slob dpon chen po'i gnas chog las phreng /
NK133(po)003:7272: man ngag gi rim mdor bsdus pa /
NK133(po)003:7273: bi ma'i gnas kyi lung phran bcu drug pa /
NK133(po)003:7275: sbub bshig bi ma'i rus chog /
NK133(po)003:7277: sbyin bsreg gi rim pa gtan tshig gnyis pa /
NK133(po)003:7278: sbyin bsreg gi man ngag khong don bkrol ba /
NK133(po)003:7281: slob dpon rgyal ba bzang po'i rab gnas kyi cho ga bsreg pa gsum dang sbyar ba /
NK133(po)003:7282: gnas kyi gegs sel gzer bco brgyad pa slob dpon
NK133(po)003:7283: dri med zla shar gsung nam mkha'i snying po'i zhi
NK133(po)003:7284: khro'i las kyi gar phreng bcas ldeb 127 /
NK133(po)003:7287: sgrub pa'i bskyed rdzogs skor la /
NK133(po)003:7288: sangs rgyas gsang ba'i lam rim chen po ldeb /
NK133(po)003:7289: de'i dka' 'grel rog gi ban+de sh+aakya 'od kyi gsung ldeb 94 /
NK133(po)003:7290: rgyal po dza'i man ngag rnam bkod /
NK133(po)003:7291: sgeg rdor rim pa drug pa /
NK133(po)003:7292: de'i 'grel pa rin chen phra bkod bi ma'i gsung /
NK133(po)003:7293: bi ma la'i rim pa gsum pa /
NK133(po)003:7295: bi ma la'i sgyu 'phrul me long 'od ldan /
NK133(po)003:7296: rgyal po dza'i rim pa gnyis pa bcas ldeb 132 /
NK133(po)003:7297: sangs rgyas gsang ba'i lam rnam bkod chung ba ldeb 12 /
NK133(po)003:7299: ma mo gsang ba las kyi thig le ldeb 7 /
NK133(po)003:7300: bi ma la'i zhi ba lha rgyud 'grel pa zhi rgyud khro rgyud khro bo lha rgyud 'grel pa /
NK133(po)003:7301: bi ma'i zhi ba rgyas pa'i sgrub thabs 'od kyi rim pa /
NK133(po)003:7302: zhi ba 'bring po'i sgrub thabs rin chen d+r+wa ba /
NK133(po)003:7303: me long lta bu'i sgrub thabs /
NK133(po)003:7304: sangs rgyas gsang ba'i zhi ba 'bring po'i sgrub thabs rin chen d+r+wa chung /
NK133(po)003:7305: rgyal bzang gi bsdus pa'i sgrub thabs 'od kyi phyag rgya /
NK133(po)003:7306: bi ma la'i khro bo rgyas pa'i sgrub thabs he ru ka'i gal phreng /
NK133(po)003:7307: 'bring po'i sgrub thabs yang dag sgron ma /
NK133(po)003:7308: sangs rgyas gsang ba'i khro bo bsdus pa'i sgrub thabs dam pa rgyan /
NK133(po)003:7309: tshogs kyi 'khor lo thugs kyi sgrub thabs bcas ldeb 131 /
NK133(po)003:7310: ting 'dzin gtso bor ston pa'i skor la bi ma la'i spyod yul sbyong ba'i bsam bstan ldeb 3 /
NK133(po)003:7312: dur khrod bde ba'i gtor ma'i lung /
NK133(po)003:7313: gu ru'i za tshogs gtor ma'i lung /
NK133(po)003:7314: ru khu grong dpal 'byor gyi cha gsum sgom phreng bcas ldeb 8 /
NK133(po)003:7317: bee ro tsa na'i bstan pa'i snying po /
NK133(po)003:7318: gnyag dz+ny+aa na'i 'phrul gyi me long dgu skor /
NK133(po)003:7319: gnyag dpal dbyangs kyi thugs kyi sgron me /
NK133(po)003:7320: lta ba yang dag sgron ma /
NK133(po)003:7323: lta ba rin chen sgron ma /
NK133(po)003:7324: nges don ji bzhin pa'i sgom thabs kyi sgron ma bcas la ldeb 15 /
NK133(po)003:7328: zhi khro thun mong gi brgyud 'debs 'gyur med rdo rjes mdzad pa ldeb 1 /
NK133(po)003:7329: rdo rje sems dpa' sgru 'phrul d+r+wa ba zhi ba
NK133(po)003:7330: 'bring po'i sgrub thabs ye shes char 'bebs ldeb 35
NK133(po)003:7331: / de'i dkyil 'khor gyi cho ga rin chen phreng ba ldeb 20 /
NK133(po)003:7332: dbang gi cho ga dkyil 'khor rgya mtshor 'jug pa'i gru chen bcas /
NK133(po)003:7333: gter chen 'gyur med rdo rje'i chog khrigs rnams so //
NK133(po)003:7334: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba khro bo he ru ka'i dkyil
NK133(po)003:7335: 'khor bsdus pa'i sgrub thabs bde chen char 'bebs ldeb
NK133(po)003:7336: 46 / de'i dkyil 'khor gyi cho ga rdo rje'i
NK133(po)003:7337: phreng ba rig 'dzin 'gyur med rdo rje'i chog khrigs
NK133(po)003:7339: bo'i dbang gi cho ga khrag 'thung rdo rje'i gad
NK133(po)003:7341: pad+ma 'gyur med rgya mtshos chog khrigs mdzad pa zhi
NK133(po)003:7342: khro thun mong dbang gi rgyug byang sku zhabs gsung
NK133(po)003:7343: ldeb 23 / bsnyen pa'i skabs su mkho phyir rdzogs
NK133(po)003:7344: chen mkhan po pad+ma dam chos 'od zer gyis 'jug
NK133(po)003:7345: bder bsdeb pa zhi ba'i las byang ldeb 27 /
NK133(po)003:7346: sngags byang ldeb 1 zhi ba'i sbyin bsreg ldeb 7 /
NK133(po)003:7349: sgyu 'phrul zhi ba'i bsnyen yig dngos grub rin po che'i za ma tog /
NK133(po)003:7350: khro bo'i bsnyen yig rig pa 'dzin pa'i dga' ston
NK133(po)003:7351: bcas dpal kahthoga mkhan po ngag dbang dpal bzang ngam
NK133(po)003:7352: tshul khrims rgya mtshos mdzad pa bcas /
NK133(po)003:7353: 'dir kahthoga dam pa'i sgyu 'phrul zhi khro phur gsum 'dzud dgos /
NK133(po)003:7354: gzhan yang de'i cha lag tu gtogs pa /
NK133(po)003:7355: slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang ba'i lugs kyi tshe sgrub skor la /
NK133(po)003:7356: tshe sgrub kyi brgyud 'debs gzhan phan mtha' yas kyis mdzad pa ldeb 1 /
NK133(po)003:7357: bcom ldan 'das tshe dpag med pa'i sgrub thabs 'chi med mchog ster ldeb 16 /
NK133(po)003:7358: de'i dbang gi cho ga ldeb 10 /
NK133(po)003:7359: bcas gter chen 'gyur med rdo rje'i khrigs ma bcas 'bor ldeb /
NK133(po)003:7362: rnal 'byor spyi khrus mtshams med lnga sbyong gi phrin chog skor la /
NK133(po)003:7363: dong sprug gi brgyud 'debs gter chen mdzad pa la
NK133(po)003:7364: dge mang rin po ches kha skong mdzad pa ldeb
NK133(po)003:7365: 1 / na rag dong sprug zhi khro khrom dkrugs kyi las byang 'khor ba kun grol ldeb 43 /
NK133(po)003:7366: yang zhi ba pad+ma brgya ldan gyi las byang bde
NK133(po)003:7367: chen lam bzang bcas gter chen chog khrigs la ldeb
NK133(po)003:7369: na rag dong sprug dbang gi mtshams sbyor bde chen
NK133(po)003:7370: lam bzang mi 'gyur dpal sgron gyis mdzad pa ldeb
NK133(po)003:7372: na rag dong sprug phyag rgya gcig ma'i sgrub thabs
NK133(po)003:7373: zab don snying khu d+harma sh+r+ais mdzad pa ldeb 11
NK133(po)003:7374: / na rag dong sprug gi khrid yig d+harma sh+r+ais mdzad pa ldeb rnams so /
NK133(po)003:7375: de dag kun gyi rjes 'brel du 'gro ba'i phrin las sna tshogs kyi skor la /
NK133(po)003:7376: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i gzhal med khang gi rnam bzhag gsal ba'i sgron me rtsa 'grel ldeb 45 /
NK133(po)003:7377: dkyil 'khor spyi'i thig chog rab gsal kun dga' rtsa 'grel ldeb 28 /
NK133(po)003:7378: khrag 'thung khro bo'i 'cham gyi brjed byang kun bzang rnam par rtsen pa'i rol mo ldeb 47 /
NK133(po)003:7379: mchod gar mchod sprin rnam par spro ba'i rol mo ldeb 16 /
NK133(po)003:7380: rgyud lung la brten pa'i las bzhi'i sbyin bsreg ngag
NK133(po)003:7381: 'don bklag chog mar byas pa 'dod ster dbang gi
NK133(po)003:7384: rten gsum rab tu gnas pa'i cho ga dge legs 'dod 'jo ldeb 29 /
NK133(po)003:7385: rab gnas lag len legs bshad rol mtsho ldeb 26 /
NK133(po)003:7386: rab gnas yon bgo'i gtong thun che ba ldeb 14 /
NK133(po)003:7388: gshin po rjes 'dzin gyi cho ga thar pa'i myur lam /
NK133(po)003:7389: gtor ma cha gsum gyi cho ga ldeb 5 /
NK133(po)003:7390: gnubs lugs brgya bzhi'i cho ga 'dod don lhun grub ldeb 14 /
NK133(po)003:7391: rnams rig 'dzin 'gyur med rdo rjes mdzad pa /
NK133(po)003:7392: sgegs rdor lugs kyi bla bslu'i chog khrigs srog gi
NK133(po)003:7393: btsan rdzong blo gros mtha' yas bsgrigs pa ldeb 17
NK133(po)003:7398: gsar rnying spyi 'gro'i dbang bshad d+harma sh+r+ais mdzad pa ldeb 27 /
NK133(po)003:7399: bar do'i chos bshad lo chen gsung ldeb 52 /
NK133(po)003:7400: skong ba'i bshad pa rab 'byams pa o rgyan chos grags kyis mdzad pa ldeb 14 /
NK133(po)003:7401: rnying lugs bka' ma'i byin 'bebs kyi 'grel pa legs
NK133(po)003:7402: bshad sprin gyi rol mo pad+ma dam chos 'od zer
NK133(po)003:7404: smon lam rdo rje'i rgya mdud 'grel pa zab gsang
NK133(po)003:7405: bdud rtsi'i rol mtsho bya mkhar rgyal nang rgyal mtshan
NK133(po)003:7406: gsung ldeb 32 / bka' ma'i rgyun bshags dang /
NK133(po)003:7407: bdud rtsi gsang nan brjod med don bshags bcas kyi tika kun mkhyen a b+ha ya'i gsung ldeb 17 /
NK133(po)003:7408: bshad gsol tika gzhan phan mtha' yas mdzad pa /
NK133(po)003:7410: smon tshig rdo rje'i rgya mdud 'grel pa bla ma mi pham mdzad pa bcas so //
NK133(po)003:7411: rgyud kyi bka' srung gi skor la legs ldan tshogs
NK133(po)003:7412: kyi bdag po'i gong non du dgos pa'i dbang gis
NK133(po)003:7413: 'dir bzhag pa brag dmar 'o bran lugs kyi skor
NK133(po)003:7414: la / de'i brgyud 'debs gzhan phan mtha' yas mdzad pa ldeb 1 /
NK133(po)003:7415: sgrub thabs dbang chog dang bcas pa 'dod 'jo bum bzang las phyung ba rnams so //
NK133(po)003:7416: dpal legs ldan nag po'i brgyud 'debs gzhan phan mtha' yas mdzad pa ldeb 1 /
NK133(po)003:7417: legs ldan tshogs kyi bdag po'i sgrub thabs las bzhi'i
NK133(po)003:7418: rnam rol gter chen 'gyur med rdo rjes bsgrigs pa
NK133(po)003:7419: ldeb 25 / yang legs ldan gyi sgrub thabs dbang
NK133(po)003:7420: chog dang bcas pa 'dod bum las byung ba ldeb
NK133(po)003:7421: ldeb 25 / 18 / gter chen khrigs ma rnams so //
NK133(po)003:7422: legs ldan gyi rgyud mtshon cha 'khor lo ldeb 60 /
NK133(po)003:7423: gzhung pod yongs rdzogs ring bsgrigs ldeb bcas /
NK133(po)003:7424: rgyud mgon trag shad dang gur mgon phur zhabs can gyi phrin chog 'dir 'dzud dgos /
NK133(po)003:7425: bka' gter zung 'jug gi mgon po bing ldeb 3 /
NK133(po)003:7427: re ma ti rang byung rgyal mo ldeb 7 /
NK133(po)003:7428: rnam sras drag po rta sngon can ldeb 9 /
NK133(po)003:7430: rnams so so'i sgrub thabs dbang chog bcas 'dod 'jo
NK133(po)003:7431: bum bzang las phyung ba gter chen chog khrigs bcas
NK133(po)003:7433: gnyis pa lung a nu yo ga'i phyogs la /
NK133(po)003:7434: d+harma bo d+his mdo'i don bsdus /
NK133(po)003:7435: s+thi ra ma tis dka' 'grel bye brag tu bshad pa bcas ldeb 21 /
NK133(po)003:7436: gnubs chen po'i mdo 'grel mun pa'i go cha rnal 'byor nyi ma ldeb 615 /
NK133(po)003:7438: rtsa rgyud kun 'dus rig pa dang /
NK133(po)003:7439: bshad rgyud spyi mdo dgongs 'dus sogs kyi gzhung don dang /
NK133(po)003:7440: bde ba gsal mdzad kyi las tho sogs man ngag gi rgyun rnams phyogs gcig tu bsdebs nas /
NK133(po)003:7442: yan lag theg brgyad kyi dkyil 'khor so sor phye
NK133(po)003:7443: nas dbang bskur ba'i thabs 'dus pa mdo dbang chen
NK133(po)003:7445: 'dus pa mdo'i dbang gi spyi don rgyud lung man
NK133(po)003:7446: ngag gi gnad gsal byed sgron me d+harma sh+ris mdzad
NK133(po)003:7447: pa ldeb 130 / 'dus mdo'i brgyud 'debs gter chen gyis mdzad pa kha skong can ldeb 1 /
NK133(po)003:7448: yang de la thub bstan chos kyi glang pos khams
NK133(po)003:7449: lugs kyi rgyun ltar kha skong mdzad pa ldeb 1
NK133(po)003:7450: / tshogs chen 'dus pa'i sgrub thabs dngos grub char
NK133(po)003:7451: 'bebs rig 'dzin 'gyur med rdo rjes bsgrigs pa ldeb
NK133(po)003:7452: / 40 / 'dus pa mdo'i sgrub khog rin chen
NK133(po)003:7453: 'od kyi snang ba d+harma sh+r+ais bsgrigs pa ldeb 64
NK133(po)003:7455: gyi cho ga dri med 'od kyi phreng ba 'gyur
NK133(po)003:7457: rgyu'i rta bab kyi lha bskyed /
NK133(po)003:7458: tshogs chen 'dus pa'i rgyun khyer rig 'dzin 'jigs med
NK133(po)003:7459: gling pas mdzad pa la thub bstan chos kyi glang
NK133(po)003:7460: pos zhal bskang ba ldeb/&&& yan lag gi dkyil 'khor
NK133(po)003:7461: rnams kyi sgrub dkyil dngos grub 'dod 'jo ldeb 151
NK133(po)003:7465: 'dus mdo'i cho ga'i zur 'debs dpag bsam snye ma ldeb 85 /
NK133(po)003:7466: 'dus mdo'i dbang bskur rdo rje'i them skas ldeb 283 /
NK133(po)003:7467: tsakli'i tho yig gsal ba'i me long /
NK133(po)003:7468: d+harma sh+r+ais mdzad pa bcas 'bor ldeb /
NK133(po)003:7470: gnyal pa bde legs pa'i mdo dbang rin chen phreng
NK133(po)003:7471: ba rtsa bar bzung ste 'dus mdo rtsa ba yan
NK133(po)003:7472: lag tshang ma / sems sde a don bco brgyad /
NK133(po)003:7473: bka' srung legs ldan ljang nag drag po bcas phyogs
NK133(po)003:7474: gcig tu rdor brag rig 'dzin pad+ma phrin las kyis
NK133(po)003:7475: bsgrigs pa dbang chog dkyil 'khor rgya mtsho'i 'jug ngog
NK133(po)003:7476: / dza pod dang po bla ma brgyud pa'i rnam thar ldeb /
NK133(po)003:7477: wa pod gnyis pa la ldeb 422 /
NK133(po)003:7478: zha pod gsum pa la ldeb 328 /
NK133(po)003:7479: za pod bzhi pa la ldeb 325 /
NK133(po)003:7481: 'dus mdo'i bka' srung mgon po legs ldan tshogs kyi
NK133(po)003:7482: bdag po khams byon ma'i las byang dngos grub gter
NK133(po)003:7483: kahthoga pa la ston nam mkha' rin chen gyis bsgrigs
NK133(po)003:7484: pa / de'i dbang chog la ston gyis mdzad pa /
NK133(po)003:7485: rgyud drag sngags gsang ba spu gri ldeb bcas so //
NK133(po)003:7486: gsum pa man ngag a ti yo ga'i sems phyogs kyi skor la /
NK133(po)003:7487: sems klong man ngag sde gsum so so'i nang gses
NK133(po)003:7488: kyi dbye bas klong dgu bam po nyi khri chig
NK133(po)003:7489: stong dang / rgyud 'bum phrag drug cu rtsa bzhi sogs dpag tu med pa zhig bzhugs pa las /
NK133(po)003:7490: dang po sems phyogs su gtogs pa'i man ngag rgya
NK133(po)003:7491: bod mkhas pa mi bzhi'i dgongs nyams gcig tu dril
NK133(po)003:7492: ba bka' brgyad bka' ma rdzogs 'phrang du grags pa'i
NK133(po)003:7495: rdzong 'phrang gzhung pod dkar chags pad+ma 'gyur med rgya mtshos mdzad pa ldeb 4 /
NK133(po)003:7496: rdzong 'phrang gzhung pod yongs rdzogs ldeb 165 /
NK133(po)003:7497: rdzong 'phrang brgyud 'debs gzhan phan mtha' yas mdzad pa ldeb 2 /
NK133(po)003:7498: phrin las kyi chog khrigs he ru ka'i dgongs rgyan
NK133(po)003:7499: ces bya ba kahthoga pa 'gyur med tshe dbang mchog
NK133(po)003:7502: dbang bskur rdo rje'i phreng ba le'u bcu gsum pa
NK133(po)003:7503: o rgyan gyi mkhan po pad+ma 'byung gnas kyis sbyar
NK133(po)003:7505: sems sde dngos la bi ma la'i mtshan brjod 'grel pa ldeb 71 /
NK133(po)003:7506: rdzogs pa chen po sems sde'i rgyud lung gi rtsa ba gces par btus pa'i skor dang /
NK133(po)003:7507: kun byed don khrid kun mkhyen gsung /
NK133(po)003:7508: sems khrid nyang lugs sog zlog gsung /
NK133(po)003:7509: a ro lugs kahthoga pa nam mkha' dpal ba'i sems sde'i pra khrid bcas ldeb 166 /
NK133(po)003:7510: sems sde'i brgyud 'debs blo gros rgyal mtshan mdzad pa kha skong can ldeb 6 /
NK133(po)003:7511: byang chub kyi sems kun byed rgyal po dang /
NK133(po)003:7512: rdo rje sems dpa' nam mkha' che /
NK133(po)003:7514: rig pa'i khu byug sogs sems sde ma bu bco
NK133(po)003:7515: brgyad kyi dgongs pa ngo sprod pa'i thabs rig pa
NK133(po)003:7516: rtsal gyi dbang bskur bco brgyad bskur ba'i chog khrigs
NK133(po)003:7517: bla ma'i zhal gdams zhes bya ba rgyug byang smon
NK133(po)003:7518: lam bcas pa rmog ston rdo rje dpal bzang pos
NK133(po)003:7522: klong sde rdo rje zam pa'i skor las /
NK133(po)003:7523: rdo rje zam pa'i byin rlabs kyi cho ga rgyas
NK133(po)003:7524: pa khrigs su byas pa kahthoga pa 'gyur med tshe
NK133(po)003:7525: dbang mchog grub kyis mdzad pa ldeb 30 /
NK133(po)003:7527: rdo rje zam pa'i nyams len bzhi'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK133(po)003:7528: he ru ka mngon rdzogs rgyal po'i phrin las ye
NK133(po)003:7529: shes rgya mtsho 'jam mgon blo gros mtha' yas kyis
NK133(po)003:7531: klong sde rdo rje zam pa'i gzhung pod bla ma ldeb 305 /
NK133(po)003:7535: rdo rje zam pa'i gzhung pod phyi ma ldeb 210 /
NK133(po)003:7536: man ngag sde rgyud bcu bdun gyi dbang chog rdzogs
NK133(po)003:7537: pa rang byung rgyud kyi dgongs don bzhin zhig gling
NK133(po)003:7538: 'od gsal sgyu ma gter bzhad rtsal gyis bsgrigs pa
NK133(po)003:7539: ldeb 38 / rdzogs pa chen po sems nyid ngal
NK133(po)003:7540: gso'i gnad gsum dge ba gsum gyi don khrid byang
NK133(po)003:7541: chub lam bzang kun mkhyen chos kyi rgyal po klong
NK133(po)003:7542: chen rab 'byams bzang pos mdzad pa ldeb 64 /
NK133(po)003:7543: mkhan chen pad+ma rdo rje'i gsung la gzhi byas pa'i
NK133(po)003:7544: dkar chag bstan pa rgya mtsho'i gru gzings ldeb 137
NK133(po)003:7547: de ltar na spyir theg rim dgu dang bye brag
NK133(po)003:7548: nang rgyud bka' ma mdo sgyu sems gsum gyi phyogs
NK133(po)003:7549: su gtogs pa'i phrin chog mtha' dag gi rgyun dang
NK133(po)003:7550: gangs ljongs 'dir yod do cog phal che ba zhig
NK133(po)003:7552: bka' ma theg rim dgu'i phrin chog rnams kyi dkar
NK133(po)003:7553: chag bstan pa rgya mtsho'i gru gzings bkra shis dpal
NK133(po)003:7554: brgya'i 'byung gnas las ji ltar spar du sgrub tshul
NK133(po)003:7555: bzhugs byang dkar chag dngos 'god pa'i skabs te bzhi
NK133(po)003:7556: pa'o //// don gsum pa de ltar bsgrubs pa'i dgos
NK133(po)003:7557: ched phan yon bsngo smon shis brjod dang bcas pa
NK133(po)003:7558: pa'o //// la bzhi las / dang po dgos ched ni /
NK133(po)003:7559: deng sang gi dus 'dir spyir rgyal ba'i bstan pa
NK133(po)003:7560: la bshad sgrub kyis bya ba mdzad pa'i gang zag
NK133(po)003:7561: phyogs thams cad na dkon zhing /
NK133(po)003:7562: khyad par rgyal ba gong ma du ma'i mtshan snyan
NK133(po)003:7563: gyi cod pan gtsug tu dpyangs nas bstan 'dzin gyi
NK133(po)003:7564: skyes bur rlom pa'i chen po'i go sa 'dzin pa
NK133(po)003:7565: dag kyang / 'dir snang srid pa'i che thabs kho nar lhur bzhes nas /
NK133(po)003:7566: gser dngul gyi bang mdzod 'gengs pa dang /
NK133(po)003:7567: rta nor gyi ri lung gang ba /
NK133(po)003:7568: che btsan gyi grags pa sgrub pa sogs mi dpon chen po'i bya bas thugs g.yengs te /
NK133(po)003:7569: rang lugs kyi bstan pa dngos la 'khor lo gsum
NK133(po)003:7570: gyis mdzad pas 'dzin skyong spel ba'i phrin las sgrub
NK133(po)003:7571: dgos rgyu rnams gal chung g.yas chung du lus pa
NK133(po)003:7572: la brten nas / thub pa'i lung rtogs kyi bstan
NK133(po)003:7573: pa rin po chen spyi yi rnam bzhag yang gzugs
NK133(po)003:7574: brnyan tsam du 'gyur ba la nye zhing /
NK133(po)003:7575: yang dgos snga 'gyur bka' ma'i smin grol gyi rgyun rnams ni phal cher 'ja' lus grub zin cing /
NK133(po)003:7576: cung zad re yod pa rnams kyang snum zad kyi mar me ltar gyur pa'i skabs 'dir /
NK133(po)003:7577: rje btsun chos kyi rgyal po 'di nyid kyi thugs dgongs la /
NK133(po)003:7578: 'di ltar mtha' dang dbus med pa'i srid pa'i rgya
NK133(po)003:7579: mtsho chen por las nyon rnam smin gyi sdug bsngal
NK133(po)003:7580: drag po'i dba' la 'khyam pa'i mtha' yas pa'i skye
NK133(po)003:7581: rgu rnams la gnas skabs kyi phan pa dang mthar
NK133(po)003:7582: thug gi bde ba 'byung ba'i gzhir gyur pa ni
NK133(po)003:7583: rgyal ba'i bstan pa rin po che kho na yin
NK133(po)003:7584: la / de nyid yun ring du gnas pa'ang bstan 'dzin gyi skyes bu rnams la rag las shing /
NK133(po)003:7585: bstan 'dzin gyi skyes bu zhes pa'ang thub pa'i bstan
NK133(po)003:7586: pa la 'dzin skyong spel ba'i phrin las mdzad pa'i
NK133(po)003:7587: sgo nas bzhag dgos par snang na'ang /
NK133(po)003:7588: deng sang ni dbang lung dang dpe rgyun dkon rigs
NK133(po)003:7589: tsam yang btsal dgos pa'i thugs dgongs mnga' ba nam
NK133(po)003:7590: lang gi skar ma ltar dkon zhing /
NK133(po)003:7591: smin grol gyi gdams pa zab mo rnams kyang khron pas skom pa ded pa'i dpes /
NK133(po)003:7592: mas bu chung la nu zho bsnyod pa ltar byas kyang /
NK133(po)003:7593: da dung log rtog dang yul lugs ngan pa'i gshis
NK133(po)003:7594: la gom pas pha phor gtsang zhen gyi blo gros
NK133(po)003:7595: phyin ci log gi grub mtha' chags sdang gi gtam
NK133(po)003:7596: gyis 'dzin pa kho na las mi 'dug pas ji
NK133(po)003:7597: ltar bgyis na rgyal ba'i bstan pa rin po che
NK133(po)003:7598: cung zad re gnas pa'i rgyur 'gyur snyam du dgongs
NK133(po)003:7599: pa las / 'di ltar bka' ma theg rim dgu'i
NK133(po)003:7600: phrin chog mtha' dag phyogs gcig tu bsdebs nas glegs
NK133(po)003:7601: bam mi zad pa'i yi ge'i phyi mo spar gyi
NK133(po)003:7602: 'du byed du bsgrubs te bzhag na /
NK133(po)003:7603: tshegs med par glegs bam gyi rgyun mang por 'phel ba dang /
NK133(po)003:7604: tshul 'di la mos pa rnams kyis smin grol gyi rgyun rnyed sla ba dang /
NK133(po)003:7605: de la brten nas klog pa thos bsam dang /
NK133(po)003:7606: spang ba bsam gtan bya ba las kyi 'khor lo sogs 'byung zhing /
NK133(po)003:7607: tshul des rgyal bstan spyi dang bye brag snga 'gyur
NK133(po)003:7608: bka' ma'i skor rnams kyang 'jig rten gyi khams su
NK133(po)003:7609: yun ring zhig tu gnas pa'i rgyu dang rkyen du
NK133(po)003:7611: dgos pa'i gtso bo ni phan bde'i 'byung gnas rgyal
NK133(po)003:7612: bstan rin po che mi nyams shing 'phel ba'i ched
NK133(po)003:7614: de'i mthus lus can spyi dang bye brag bod chen
NK133(po)003:7615: po'i ljongs 'dir 'khod pa'i skye dgu mtha' dag gnas
