NK133(po)003:7616: skabs lha dang mi'i dpal la longs spyod nas /
NK133(po)003:7617: mthar thug rnam grol zhi ba mchog gi go 'phang mngon du byed pa dang /
NK133(po)003:7618: gzhan yang rig 'dzin gong ma rnams kyi dgongs pa yongs su rdzogs pa dang /
NK133(po)003:7619: rgyal ba'i sras kyi mdzad pa rlab po che sgrub pa dang /
NK133(po)003:7620: dus gsum gyi rgyal ba rnams kyi dam pa'i chos 'dzin pa dang /
NK133(po)003:7621: rjes 'jug slob ma'i tshogs la smin grol gyi pha phog 'bog pa dang /
NK133(po)003:7622: 'byor ldan sbyin pa'i bdag po rnams kyi bsod nams
NK133(po)003:7623: kyi tshogs gong nas gong du spel ba sogs dgos
NK133(po)003:7624: pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa la thugs gzhol nas
NK133(po)003:7625: sngon rabs du ma'i thugs bskyed dang smon lam dus
NK133(po)003:7626: su babs pa'i mngon rtogs gsal por ngom pa yin
NK133(po)003:7627: te / bzang po spyod pa las /
NK133(po)003:7628: rgyal ba rnams kyi dam pa'i chos 'dzin cing //
NK133(po)003:7629: byang chub spyod pa kun tu snang bar byed //
NK133(po)003:7631: snga 'gyur pun+da ri ka'i rgyud las /
NK133(po)003:7632: srid pa las dang rkyen gyi dbang gyur te //
NK133(po)003:7633: gang dang gang du dam chos 'jig pa der //
NK133(po)003:7634: me tshogs spu gri'i so yang brgal nas ni //
NK133(po)003:7635: phyi mthar thug gi bar du dam chos bzung //
NK133(po)003:7638: spyir bde bar gshegs pa'i gsung rabs rnams glegs bam
NK133(po)003:7639: la bris te rim gro bgyis pa la yang phan
NK133(po)003:7641: sdud pa tshigs su bcad pa las /
NK133(po)003:7642: la las bde gshegs yongs su mya ngan 'das pa yi //
NK133(po)003:7643: mchod rten rin chen bdun las byas shing mchod byed la //
NK133(po)003:7644: bde bar gshegs pa'i mchod rten de dag gang+ga yi //
NK133(po)003:7645: bye ma snyed kyi bye ba phrag stong zhing bkangs te //
NK133(po)003:7646: yongs su brtags bzung zhing rnams bye ba mtha' yas na //
NK133(po)003:7647: sems can ji snyed 'khod pa de dag thams cad kyis //
NK133(po)003:7648: las gzhan mi byed lha yi me tog spos rab dang //
NK133(po)003:7649: byug pas dus su bskal pa'am de bas lhag mchod la //
NK133(po)003:7650: gang zhig gang las rnam 'dren stobs bcu 'byung 'gyur ba //
NK133(po)003:7651: bde bar gshegs kyi yum 'di glegs bam la bris te //
NK133(po)003:7652: 'chang zhing me tog byug pas bsti stang byed gyur na //
NK133(po)003:7653: mchod rten byas mchod bsod nams des ni char mi phod //
NK133(po)003:7655: de bas kyang glegs bam bgyis te gzhan la byin pa'i bsod nams khyad par du 'phags te /
NK133(po)003:7657: la las gang+g+aa klung gi bye snyed zhing rnams na //
NK133(po)003:7658: sems can ji snyed mchog kun dgra bcom nyid btul bas //
NK133(po)003:7659: gang gis shes rab pha rol phyin 'di yig bris te //
NK133(po)003:7660: sems can mchog la glegs byin bsod nams khyad par 'phags //
NK133(po)003:7662: de ltar theg chen thun mong gi mdo sde rnams las kyang phan yon mang du gsung na /
NK133(po)003:7663: de las kyang gsang sngags kyi rgyud sde zab mo
NK133(po)003:7664: rnams bris shing bcang ba'i phan yon ni tshad med
NK133(po)003:7665: de / rin po che spungs pa'i rgyud las /
NK133(po)003:7666: de yi phyir na gsang ba'i rgyud //
NK133(po)003:7668: rang rig rnams kyi dbang thob ste //
NK133(po)003:7669: rgyud 'di bcang ba tsam gyis ni //
NK133(po)003:7671: rgyud 'di su yi bklag pa'i mi //
NK133(po)003:7672: lta ba'i don kun sems la 'char //
NK133(po)003:7673: 'di nyid su yis bris pa'i mi //
NK133(po)003:7674: sangs rgyas kun gyi gsung la rol //
NK133(po)003:7676: a ti bkod pa chen po las /
NK133(po)003:7677: gsang mchog bla na med pa 'di //
NK133(po)003:7678: mchod dang bstod pa bkur byas na //
NK133(po)003:7679: mchog dang thun mong dngos grub rnams //
NK133(po)003:7681: 'di nyid bcang ba tsam gyis kyang //
NK133(po)003:7684: khyad par bstan pa 'jigs pa'i tshe dam pa'i chos
NK133(po)003:7685: bzung ba'i phan yon ni bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i
NK133(po)003:7686: tshul / blo gros rgya mtshos zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK133(po)003:7687: rdzogs pa'i byang chub sems dang chos 'dzin dang //
NK133(po)003:7688: chos sgrub pa dang srog chags snying rje ba //
NK133(po)003:7689: chos bzhi 'di dag bsod nams mtha' yas te //
NK133(po)003:7690: de dag mtha' ni bde gshegs mi gsung ngo //
NK133(po)003:7692: 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs zhes bya ba theg pa chen po'i mdo las /
NK133(po)003:7693: gang dag phyin chad mdo sde 'di 'dzin pa //
NK133(po)003:7694: de dag rtag tu nga dang mthun pa'i sras //
NK133(po)003:7695: sangs rgyas bye ba de dag basngagasa brjod kyang //
NK133(po)003:7696: de dag basngagasa pa mthar ni phyin mi 'gyur //
NK133(po)003:7698: gang gis sangs rgyas stong rnams dang //
NK133(po)003:7699: brgya dang bye ba'i grangs dag la //
NK133(po)003:7700: bskal pa gang+ga'i bye ma snyed //
NK133(po)003:7701: de snyed bskal par bkur ba bas //
NK133(po)003:7702: 'jig rten mgon gyis gsung pa yi //
NK133(po)003:7703: dam chos 'jig tshe gang zhig gis //
NK133(po)003:7704: nyin dang mtshan du 'dzin byed pa //
NK133(po)003:7705: de ni bsod nams khyad par 'phags //
NK133(po)003:7707: 'jig tshe rgyal ba mchog gi chos bzung bas //
NK133(po)003:7708: mchog tu gzugs mdzes lta na sdug pa dang //
NK133(po)003:7709: skyes pa bud med lha rnams dga' ba dang //
NK133(po)003:7710: bde zhing mkhas la basngagasa shing shes rab ldan //
NK133(po)003:7711: ston pa stobs bcu mnga' ba lha yi lhas //
NK133(po)003:7712: gang gi mdun du mdo 'di rab bshad pa //
NK133(po)003:7713: mi de'i lag tu mdo sde 'di 'dra 'di //
NK133(po)003:7714: phyi ma'i dus kyi tshe na thob par 'gyur //
NK133(po)003:7716: gzhan yang 'phags pa dkon mchog brtsegs pa chen po'i chos kyi rnam grangs las kyang /
NK133(po)003:7717: de la sh+aa ri'i bu theg pa chen po la yang dag par zhugs pas /
NK133(po)003:7718: 'di lta bu'i mi bzad pa dang mi basngagasa pa dang /
NK133(po)003:7719: dam pa'i chos rab tu 'jig pa mthong nas brtson 'grus chen po'i shugs rab tu bskyed de /
NK133(po)003:7721: 'di lta bu'i mdo sde byang chub sems dpa'i sde
NK133(po)003:7722: snod kyi chos kyi rnam grangs 'di rab tu mnyan
NK133(po)003:7724: yi ger bris nas bcang bar bya /
NK133(po)003:7725: gzhan la yang go bar bya rgya cher yang dag par rab tu bstan par bya'o //
NK133(po)003:7726: des kyang 'du shes bzhi bskyed par bya ste /
NK133(po)003:7728: bdag gi pha'i nor gyi phung po 'di rab tu 'jig par 'gyur te /
NK133(po)003:7729: gang gis phyir bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa
NK133(po)003:7730: dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas
NK133(po)003:7731: sh+aakya thub pa des bskal pa bye ba khrag khrig
NK133(po)003:7732: brgya stong grangs med pa nas bzung ste dka' ba
NK133(po)003:7734: de'i phyir rab tu 'jig par mi 'gyur bar bzung par bya /
NK133(po)003:7740: dper na sh+aa ri'i bu skyes bu zhig la bu
NK133(po)003:7741: gcig cig yod de byams sdug yid du 'ong zhing
NK133(po)003:7742: mi mthun pa med par snang ba de g.yang sa
NK133(po)003:7743: chen por lhung bar gyur pa dang /
NK133(po)003:7744: des de lag gis bzung ste /
NK133(po)003:7745: sems can dmyal ba'i g.yang sa 'dir ltung bar ma
NK133(po)003:7746: gyur cig ces 'dzin rab tu 'dzin pa de bzhin
NK133(po)003:7747: du / sh+aa ri'i bu gang skyes bo bu dam
NK133(po)003:7748: pa de dag nga la dad cing chos dkon mchog
NK133(po)003:7749: bla na med pa 'di yang yongs su mi gtong
NK133(po)003:7750: du / zhing / mya ngan las 'das pa la
NK133(po)003:7751: yang re bar 'gyur ba de dag de'i dus na
NK133(po)003:7752: dam pa'i chos yongs su 'dzin par 'gyur bas ngas
NK133(po)003:7753: de dag la byang chub mchog 'di gtad par bya'o
NK133(po)003:7754: du / zhing / // 'di lta ste dper na
NK133(po)003:7755: sh+aa ri'i bu g.yul chen po'i nang na gang skye
NK133(po)003:7756: bo mang po bsrung ba'i phyir dmag gi mdun na
NK133(po)003:7757: 'dug par 'gyur ba'i sems can de dag ni nyung
NK133(po)003:7759: sh+aa ri'i bu gang dpa' ba 'os su gyur par
NK133(po)003:7760: byas pa g.yul las rnam par rgyal ba de dag
NK133(po)003:7761: de bzhin g.yul mi bzad pa chen po'i dus na
NK133(po)003:7762: skye bo mang po'i phyir dmag gi mdun na 'dug
NK133(po)003:7763: pa de bzhin du sh+aa ri'i bu de'i tshe dam
NK133(po)003:7764: pa'i chos 'jig par rab tu nye bar gnas pa
NK133(po)003:7766: / gang lhag pa'i bsam pas yongs su mya ngan
NK133(po)003:7768: dpa' bo brtson 'grus brtan par go cha sra ba
NK133(po)003:7769: bgos pa de dag brtson 'grus chen po'i stobs bskyed
NK133(po)003:7770: de bdud kyi dmag las rgyal zhing 'di lta bu'i
NK133(po)003:7771: chos dkon mchog 'di las snying po cung zad tsam
NK133(po)003:7774: sh+aa ri'i bu tshig bzhi pa'i tshigs su bcad pa
NK133(po)003:7775: gcig tsam yongs su spong ba la yang rjes su
NK133(po)003:7776: yi rang bar mi byed cing rtsod par byed la
NK133(po)003:7777: 'di ni sangs rgyas kyis bshad pa'o //
NK133(po)003:7778: zhes skye bo mang po la sgrogs shing shes par byed pa de ni 'das pa dang /
NK133(po)003:7780: da ltar gyi sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams kyis
NK133(po)003:7781: legs par bshad pa la rjes su yi rang ba
NK133(po)003:7782: ste / sh+aa ri'i bu de lta bu'i gang zag
NK133(po)003:7783: rnams la bsod nams kyi rnam par smin pa chung
NK133(po)003:7785: nam mkha' mnyam pa'i bsod nams kyi phung po dang ldan par 'gyur ro //
NK133(po)003:7787: sh+aa ri'i bu skyes bu dam pa de lta bu ni shin tu dkon te /
NK133(po)003:7788: skyes bu mchog ces brjod do //
NK133(po)003:7789: skyes bu rab ces brjod do //
NK133(po)003:7790: skyes bu dpa' bo zhes brjod do //
NK133(po)003:7791: skyes bu chen po zhes brjod do //
NK133(po)003:7792: de ni de bzhin gshegs pa'i chos kyi phyogs so //
NK133(po)003:7793: de dag sder mi smra mi 'khrug go //
NK133(po)003:7794: de dag nan tan snying por byed pa ste /
NK133(po)003:7795: sh+aa ri'i bu 'chi ba'i matha'i bar du nan tan snying por bya'o //
NK133(po)003:7796: 'chi ba'i matha'i bar du dam pa'i chos yongs su bzung bar bya'o //
NK133(po)003:7797: 'chi ba'i matha'i bar du stong pa nyid la mos par bya'o //
NK133(po)003:7798: sh+aa ri'i bu chos de bzhi dang ldan na de'i tshe de'i dus na /
NK133(po)003:7799: dam pa'i chos rab tu rnam par 'jig pa'i dus /
NK133(po)003:7800: dam pa'i chos nub par 'gyur ba'i dus tshul khrims 'chal ba'i phyogs mang ba'i dus /
NK133(po)003:7801: 'jig rten rgyang 'phen pa'i gsang tshig kun tu tshol ba mang ba'i dus /
NK133(po)003:7805: nyon mongs pa snyigs ma'i dus /
NK133(po)003:7807: dus gsum la gnas par bya /
NK133(po)003:7808: 'thab mo nye bar zhi ba la gnas par bya /
NK133(po)003:7809: sangs rgyas kyi byang chub dang 'bral bar mi 'gyur bar bya ste /
NK133(po)003:7810: sh+aa ri'i bu dus 'di gsum la rab tu gnas par bya'o //
NK133(po)003:7812: blo gros rgya mtshos zhus pa'i mdo las kyang /
NK133(po)003:7813: de bzhin gshegs pa'i dam pa'i chos 'dzin pa //
NK133(po)003:7814: de ni de bzhin gshegs la byas bzo yin //
NK133(po)003:7815: rgyal ba rnams kyi mdzod 'dzin yid brtan zhing //
NK133(po)003:7816: phyogs bcur rnams su sangs rgyas mchod pa yin //
NK133(po)003:7817: sangs rgyas spyan gyis gzigs pa'i zhing mang po //
NK133(po)003:7818: rin chen bkang ste de bzhin gshegs la phul //
NK133(po)003:7819: zad pa'i dus na ji ltar chos 'dzin ltar //
NK133(po)003:7820: bsod nams phung po de tsam 'phel ma yin //
NK133(po)003:7822: de dag rnams kyi yon tan phan yon rnams //
NK133(po)003:7823: bskal pa rgyun mi chad par brjod byas kyang //
NK133(po)003:7824: dam chos 'dzin pa'i phan yon 'di dag ni //
NK133(po)003:7825: brjod pas mtha' mar phyin par mi 'gyur ro //
NK133(po)003:7826: zhes sogs rgya cher gsung pa ltar ro //
NK133(po)003:7827: gsum pa de lta bu'i phan yon can gyi legs
NK133(po)003:7828: byas rgya chen po 'di nyid las byung ba'i bsod
NK133(po)003:7829: nams kyi dngos po dbye ba la gnyis te /
NK133(po)003:7830: 'khor gsum la bden zhen gyi blo dang bcas pas
NK133(po)003:7831: lha mi dang nyan rang gi sar bsngo ba ma
NK133(po)003:7832: dag pa dang / 'khor gsum la bden zhen bral
NK133(po)003:7833: ba'i blo mi gnas pa'i mya ngan las 'das par
NK133(po)003:7835: gang du ji ltar bsngo ba'i tshul la /
NK133(po)003:7838: bsngo ba tshul dang gsum las /
NK133(po)003:7841: nges tshig dbye ba dang gsum las /
NK133(po)003:7843: 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa'i dge rtsa
NK133(po)003:7844: tha dag gzhan don du rdzogs byang gi rgyur blo
NK133(po)003:7845: gros stobs kyis yongs su bsgyur ba'o //
NK133(po)003:7846: nges tshig ni pa ri na ta zhes pa'i sgra las yongs su bsgyur ba'am spel ba ste /
NK133(po)003:7847: dman pa mchog tu bsgyur ba dang /
NK133(po)003:7848: nyung ngu mang por spel ba'i don can no //
NK133(po)003:7849: gnyis pa bsngo dgos pa'i rgyu mtshan la gnyis las /
NK133(po)003:7850: dang po ma bsngosa pa'i nyes dmigs ni /
NK133(po)003:7851: 'dus byas kyi dge rtsa ji lta bu zhig yin
NK133(po)003:7852: kyang thabs shes zung du 'brel ba'i bsngo ba khyad
NK133(po)003:7853: par can zhig gis rgyas ma thebs na /
NK133(po)003:7854: mi mthun phyogs kyis bcom sla zhing bar ma dor chud 'dza' bar 'gyur te /
NK133(po)003:7856: bskal pa stong du bsags pa yi //
NK133(po)003:7857: sbyin dang bde gshegs mchod la sogs //
NK133(po)003:7858: legs spyad gang yin de kun kyang //
NK133(po)003:7859: khong khro gcig gis 'jom par byed //
NK133(po)003:7862: rigs kyi bu byang chub sems dpa' chos bzhi dang
NK133(po)003:7863: ldan pa rnams kyi sbyin pa zad par 'gyur te
NK133(po)003:7866: yongs su ma bsngosa pa dang thabs mi mkhas pa dang /
NK133(po)003:7867: dma' bar skye bar 'dod pa dang /
NK133(po)003:7868: sdig pa'i grogs po la brten pa ste rigs kyi
NK133(po)003:7869: bu byang chub sems dpa' chos bzhi po de dag
NK133(po)003:7870: dang ldan pa rnams kyi sbyin pa ni yongs su
NK133(po)003:7873: der ma zad bsngo bas ma zin pa ni theg pa chen po'i khyur yang mi tshud de /
NK133(po)003:7875: nyan thos theg pa de las ni //
NK133(po)003:7876: byang chub sems dpa'i smon lam dang //
NK133(po)003:7877: spyod pa yongs bsngo ma bshad des //
NK133(po)003:7878: byang chub sems dpa'i ga la 'gyur //
NK133(po)003:7880: gnyis pa bsngo ba'i phan yon ni /
NK133(po)003:7881: blo gros rgya mtshos zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK133(po)003:7882: blo gros rgya mtsho 'di lta ste /
NK133(po)003:7883: dper na mchil ma'i thal ba zhig bye ma'i steng du bor na myur du skam par 'gyur ro //
NK133(po)003:7884: de nyid rgya mtsho chen por bor na ni ji
NK133(po)003:7885: srid rgya mtsho chen po de nyid zad cing skam
NK133(po)003:7886: par ma gyur pa de srid bar du mchil ma'i
NK133(po)003:7887: thal ba de yang mi skam mo //
NK133(po)003:7888: blo gros rgya mtsho de bzhin du /
NK133(po)003:7889: dge ba'i rtsa ba sgrub pa de yang 'gyod pa dang 'phangs pa dang /
NK133(po)003:7890: dman pa dang log par bsngosa na ni 'dzad la /
NK133(po)003:7891: gang rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid kyi rgya
NK133(po)003:7892: mtsho chen por bsngosa na ni mi 'dzad cing gong
NK133(po)003:7896: dge ba gzhan kun chu shing bzhin du ni //
NK133(po)003:7897: 'bras bu bskyed nas zad par 'gyur ba nyid //
NK133(po)003:7898: byang chub sems kyi ljon shing rtag par yang //
NK133(po)003:7902: byang chub sems dpa' mkhas pa thabs mkhas gang zhig gis //
NK133(po)003:7903: de dag bsod nams bya ba'i dngos la yi rang nas //
NK133(po)003:7904: sems can don du byang chub mchog rab yongs bsngo na //
NK133(po)003:7905: yongs su bsngo bas 'gro ba thams cad zil gyis gnon //
NK133(po)003:7907: gsum pa bsngo ba'i tshul la /
NK133(po)003:7908: gang bsngo rgyu'i dge ba dang /
NK133(po)003:7909: gang du bsngo ba'i gnas dang /
NK133(po)003:7910: gang gi ched du bsngo ba dang /
NK133(po)003:7911: tshul ji ltar bsngo ba ste bzhi las /
NK133(po)003:7912: dang po ni gsang ba bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i mdo las /
NK133(po)003:7913: stong pa nyid la 'dir mos nas //
NK133(po)003:7914: byang chub sems kyang mi gtong dang //
NK133(po)003:7915: dam pa'i chos ni 'dzin bgyid pa //
NK133(po)003:7916: 'di ni bsod nams sdud pa lags //
NK133(po)003:7917: zhes pa ltar rnam par dkar ba'i legs byas kyi
NK133(po)003:7918: chu klung mang po phyogs gcig tu sdud pa'i bsod
NK133(po)003:7919: nams kyi rgya mtsho chen po chos sbyin mi zad
NK133(po)003:7920: pa'i phyi mo spar du bskrun pa las byung ba'i
NK133(po)003:7921: grags dkar gyi rlabs phreng srid rtser 'phyur ba 'di
NK133(po)003:7923: dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa'
NK133(po)003:7924: nyan thos rang rgyal so so'i skye ba'i tshogs dang
NK133(po)003:7925: bcas pa rnams kyi dge rtsa ji snyed mchis pa
NK133(po)003:7926: dang / rang gzhan mtha' dag gi lus longs spyod
NK133(po)003:7927: dge tshogs rgya mtsho rnams gcig tu bsdoms nas bsngo
NK133(po)003:7930: dang po byang chub mchog tu sems rab bskyed pa nas //
NK133(po)003:7931: rnam par 'dren pa rnams kyi dam chos zad kyi dus //
NK133(po)003:7932: de bar rgyal ba de dag bsod nams gang yin pa //
NK133(po)003:7933: pha rol phyin dang ldan dang sangs rgyas chos gang dang //
NK133(po)003:7934: gang yang sangs rgyas sras rnams dang ni nyan thos dang //
NK133(po)003:7935: slob dang mi slob dge ba zag bcas zag med pa //
NK133(po)003:7936: bsdus nas byang chub sems dpa' rjes su yi rang zhing //
NK133(po)003:7937: 'gro ba'i don rgyur byang chub phyir ni thams cad bsngo //
NK133(po)003:7939: rdo rje rgyal mtshan gyis bsngo ba'i le'u las /
NK133(po)003:7940: 'gro kun dge ba ji snyed yod pa dang //
NK133(po)003:7941: byas dang byed 'gyur de bzhin byed pa rnams //
NK133(po)003:7942: bzang po ji bzhin de 'dra'i sa dag la //
NK133(po)003:7943: kun nas kun kyang bzang por reg gyur cig /
NK133(po)003:7946: lus dang de bzhin longs spyod dang //
NK133(po)003:7947: dus gsum dge ba byed pa rnams //
NK133(po)003:7948: sems can kun gyi don sgrub phyir //
NK133(po)003:7949: 'phang pa med par btang bar bya //
NK133(po)003:7952: spang rtogs phun sum tshogs pa'i bdag nyid mi gnas
NK133(po)003:7953: pa'i mya ngan las 'das pa chen po'i go 'phang
NK133(po)003:7954: kho na te / yongs su bsngo ba'i mdo las /
NK133(po)003:7955: dge ba'i rtsa ba dag kyang sangs rgyas nyid kyis sar bsngo'o //
NK133(po)003:7957: dge ba'i rtsa ba de yang rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid ma gtogs pa /
NK133(po)003:7958: nyan thos dang rang sangs rgyas kyi sar yongs su bsngo bar mi gzhug go //
NK133(po)003:7961: thog ma med pa'i dus nas dgra gnyen bar ma'i
NK133(po)003:7962: rang bzhin du mar phan tshun du 'brel ba'i mtha'
NK133(po)003:7963: yas pa'i lus can thams cad kyi ched du ste
NK133(po)003:7965: dngos sam yang na brgyud kyang rung //
NK133(po)003:7966: sems can don las gzhan mi spyad //
NK133(po)003:7967: sems can kho na'i don gyi phyir //
NK133(po)003:7968: thams cad byang chub rgyur bsngo'o //
NK133(po)003:7970: de ltar bsngosa pas sems can gyi khams bzhin phan yon kyang tshad med de /
NK133(po)003:7972: sems can khams ni tshad med la //
NK133(po)003:7975: bsod nams kyis dngos po sems can gyi don du
NK133(po)003:7976: bsngo ba 'di ni gzhan la med pa'i sangs rgyas
NK133(po)003:7977: kyi bstan pa kho na'i khyad chos yin te /
NK133(po)003:7979: bsod nams bya ba'i tshogs dag ni //
NK133(po)003:7980: sems can rnams la yongs bsngo bar //
NK133(po)003:7981: bcom ldan khyod kyis gang gsung pa //
NK133(po)003:7982: de gzhan bstan bcos las ma bshad //
NK133(po)003:7986: ji ltar dug dang 'dres pa'i kha zas bzang za ba //
NK133(po)003:7987: dkar po'i chos la dmigs pa'ang de 'drar rgyal bas gsungs //
NK133(po)003:7988: de ltas 'di ltar yongs su bsngo ba bslab bya ste //
NK133(po)003:7989: ji ltar rgyal ba de dag dge ba de mkhyen pa'i //
NK133(po)003:7990: rnam pa gang yin 'byung gang mtshan nyid gang yin la //
NK133(po)003:7991: rjes su yi rang de lta de ltar yongs su bsngo //
NK133(po)003:7992: de ltar bsod nams byang chub yongs su bsngo byed na //
NK133(po)003:7993: dug med sangs rgyas mi spong rgyal bas gsung pa smra //
NK133(po)003:7994: zhes pa bzhin dmigs pa'i dug dang bral ba'i 'khor
NK133(po)003:7995: gsum yongs dag gi bsngo ba rgyal ba dgyes pa'i
NK133(po)003:7996: lam bzang la slob pa gal che ste /
NK133(po)003:7997: de la 'khor gsum yongs su dag pa ni /
NK133(po)003:7999: gal te 'di ltar chos 'di 'gags shing zad pa dang //
NK133(po)003:8000: gang du yongs su bsngo ba de yang zad pa dang //
NK133(po)003:8001: chos kyis chos la nam yang mi bsngo shes gyur na //
NK133(po)003:8002: de ltar rab tu shes pas yongs su bsngosa pa yin //
NK133(po)003:8004: blo gros rgya mtshos zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK133(po)003:8005: blo gros rgya mtsho gzhan yang 'khor gsum yongs su dag pa gang zhe na /
NK133(po)003:8006: gang la bdag tu 'dzin pa med pa dang /
NK133(po)003:8007: sems can du 'dzin pa med pa dang /
NK133(po)003:8009: zhes sogs gsungs pa bzhin rnam par mi rtog pa'i
NK133(po)003:8010: shes rab zab mos bden gnyis res 'jog tu ma
NK133(po)003:8011: song bar chos thams cad rang bzhin gyis nam mkha'i
NK133(po)003:8012: dkyil ltar spros pa'i mtha' thams cad dang bral ba
NK133(po)003:8013: mngon sum du mthong ba'i ngang nas lhun gyis grub
NK133(po)003:8014: pa'i snying rje chen po sems can gyi khams la
NK133(po)003:8015: blta ba'i bsngo ba mtshan nyid pa ni /
NK133(po)003:8016: sa dang po nas brtsams te 'phags pa rnams kho na la yod kyi /
NK133(po)003:8017: mos spyod kyi lam pas de nyid sgra ji bzhin par lam du slong dka' ba yang /
NK133(po)003:8019: chos rnams thams cad rkyen yin te //
NK133(po)003:8020: 'dun pa'i rtse la rab tu gnas //
NK133(po)003:8022: gang zhig sangs rgyas yid byed pa //
NK133(po)003:8023: de ni mdun na thub pa bzhugs //
NK133(po)003:8024: zhes pa ltar 'dun pa bsgyur ba kho na gtso che bas /
NK133(po)003:8025: 'di ltar bsngo ba'i dpang por rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams dang /
NK133(po)003:8026: sa chen po la gnas pa'i byang chub sems dpa' kun tu bzang po dang /
NK133(po)003:8027: 'jam dbyangs sogs rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor tshad med pas
NK133(po)003:8028: chos kyi dbyings kyi mtha' gtug pa'i zhing khams rgya
NK133(po)003:8029: mtsho rgyas par bkang ste bzhugs par mos pa de
NK133(po)003:8030: dag gi drung du bdag nyid mngon par snang bar
NK133(po)003:8031: byas te / thabs snying rje chen po dang shes
NK133(po)003:8032: rab stong pa nyid zung du 'brel ba'i blo gros
NK133(po)003:8033: byas te / / ji ltar sngon gyi sangs rgyas
NK133(po)003:8034: dang byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyis bsngo bar mdzad
NK133(po)003:8035: pa de bzhin du bdag gis kyang yongs su bsngo
NK133(po)003:8036: bar bagyi'o snyam pa'i 'dun pa drag po rtse gcig
NK133(po)003:8037: byas te / / tu bya ste / bzang po spyod pa las /
NK133(po)003:8038: 'jam dpal dpa' bos ji ltar mkhyen pa dang //
NK133(po)003:8039: kun tu bzang po de'ang de bzhin te //
NK133(po)003:8040: de dag kun gyi rjes su bdag slob phyir //
NK133(po)003:8041: dge ba 'di dag thams cad rab tu bsngo //
NK133(po)003:8042: dus gsum gshegs pa'i rgyal ba thams cad kyis //
NK133(po)003:8043: bsngo ba gang la mchog tu basngagasa pa de //
NK133(po)003:8044: bdag gi dge ba'i rtsa ba 'di kun kyang //
NK133(po)003:8045: bzang po spyod phyir rab tu bsngo bar bgyi //
NK133(po)003:8046: zhes pa'i tshul gyis bsngo ba ni 'phags pa'i lam
NK133(po)003:8047: dang rjes su mthun pa'i bsngo tshul rmad du byung
NK133(po)003:8049: de lta bu'i tshul gyis rje btsun bla ma mchog
NK133(po)003:8050: gis rgyal ba sras dang bcas pa'i rnam thar bsam
NK133(po)003:8051: gyis mi khyab par yang dag par bzhugs pa'i bsngo
NK133(po)003:8054: rtse mor phyin pa rgyas par spel zhing 'khor gsum dmigs pa med pas rgyas btab zin kyang /
NK133(po)003:8055: rang gis kyang bla ma rgyal ba sras bcas kyi
NK133(po)003:8056: rjes su slob par mos pas bsngo smon dang shis
NK133(po)003:8057: pa brjod pa'i tshigs su bcad pa cung zad spel
NK133(po)003:8058: ba ni / na mo gu ru rat+na tra y+aa ya /
NK133(po)003:8059: swa sti mang+ga lam sid+d+hi b+ha wan+tu /
NK133(po)003:8060: bsam gyis mi khyab chos kyi dbyings kun rgyas par bkod pa'i zhing rgya mtshor //
NK133(po)003:8061: sku bzhi'i dbang phyug dus gsum gshegs pa rab 'byams sras dang slob mar bcas //
NK133(po)003:8062: mos pa'i yul la 'char nub spang ba'i ye shes gzigs pa mi yol ba'i //
NK133(po)003:8063: zhabs kyi pad+mora gus pas btud de rdul snyed lus kyis phyag 'tshal zhing /
NK133(po)003:8065: 1 / dus gsum bsags yod legs byas kun bsdom rab 'byams mchod pa'i sprin rgya mtsho //
NK133(po)003:8066: kun nas mchod cing nyes pa'i dri ma stobs bzhi'i chus bkrus mtshan rtog bsal //
NK133(po)003:8067: mtha' gnyis spang pa'i byang chub chen por mkha' mnyam drin ldan 'god brtson na //
NK133(po)003:8068: chags thog bral ba'i mkhyen brtse nus pas rnam dkar smon don 'grub byin rlobs /
NK133(po)003:8070: 2 / bde gshegs mchod sogs legs byas gzhan gyis cha tsam mtshon min rgyal ba'i chos mdzod 'dzin pa'i gzhi //
NK133(po)003:8071: dpal ldan bla ma'i phrin las sprin las gsung rab rin chen glegs bam gru char 'bebs 'dis mtshon //
NK133(po)003:8072: phyogs bcu'i zhing gi 'phags dang so skye'i tshogs gnyis rgya mtshor gcig tu gus dang yi rang gi //
NK133(po)003:8073: chu skyes 'dzum pa'i bsti stang gis drangs kun mkhyen rgya mtshor 'jug pa'i bsam sbyor mchog la zhugs /
NK133(po)003:8075: 3 / nyin mo'i dpal gyi pad+ma'i tshal dang rgyu skar bdag pos chu gter bzhin //
NK133(po)003:8076: dam pa'i thugs bskyed phyag rjes bzang pos bstan pa'i gnad rnams 'phel mdzad pa'i //
NK133(po)003:8077: chos kyi sbyin pa 'byams su klas pa bsod nams klung chen 'di'i mthu yis //
NK133(po)003:8078: srid zhi'i dge legs mtha' yas 'od kyis zhing khams rab 'byams brgyan gyur cig 4 /
NK133(po)003:8079: mngon mtho nges legs kun gyi gzhir gyur dam chos 'dul ba'i gdugs dkar po //
NK133(po)003:8080: mdo sde rin chen dar sham gyis bklubs chos mngon nor bu'i d+r+wa bas mdzes //
NK133(po)003:8081: theg mchog nor bu'i tog gis gzi 'bar thub dbang bstan pa'i grib bsil du //
NK133(po)003:8082: byams chen chos rnga sgrogs pa de srid 'gro 'di bde bar 'tsho gyur cig 5 /
NK133(po)003:8083: tshul min mnar sems las kyis 'phang pa'i mi bzod tsha grang sdug bsngal dang //
NK133(po)003:8084: 'jungs sred ser snas kun nas nyam nga bkres skom tshor bas rab tu gzir //
NK133(po)003:8085: blang dor gnas la rmongs pa'i mun 'thum dam chos mig bral 'gro ji snyed //
NK133(po)003:8086: dge 'dis 'khrul snang gnyid las sad bzhin dag pa'i zhing du dbugs 'byin shog 6 /
NK133(po)003:8087: gzhan 'byor la rngams 'thab rtsod kyis mnar d+aa nu'i bu yi tshogs rnams ni //
NK133(po)003:8088: khros 'khrugs gdon zhi chog shes blo dang byams pa'i sems kyis bde bar 'tsho //
NK133(po)003:8089: lha rnams bag med 'dod pas rab myos 'tsho ba'i tha mas gdung gyur pa //
NK133(po)003:8090: sdom bzhi'i rngas bskul dam chos la spyod thar mchog zhi ba'i gnas thob shog 7 /
NK133(po)003:8091: mi yi 'jig rten ji snyed thub mchog legs gsung nyin mo'i dpal gyis sgeg /
NK133(po)003:8092: rnam dkar las bcu'i lang tsho dar babs rdzogs ldan dus ston mgron du khug /
NK133(po)003:8093: rgyal rnams sa chen chos bzhin skyong bas 'jig rten rgud pa'i ming yang stong //
NK133(po)003:8094: legs bris gnas kyi bde dag'i dpal 'byor rgya mtsho'i gos can 'dir smin shog 8 /
NK133(po)003:8095: snyigs spyod kyis bkug skye dgu'i gsos 'jom sad ser btsa' than mu ge dang //
NK133(po)003:8096: mi srun skye bos gzhan nor rku 'phrogs 'thab dang rtsod pas mnar ba sogs //
NK133(po)003:8097: legs byas 'di'i mthus 'jig rten khams 'dir ming yang mi grags byams sems ldan //
NK133(po)003:8098: lha klu dga' bas dus su char 'bebs sman ljongs lo tog rab rgyas smon /
NK133(po)003:8100: 9 / las dang nyon mongs bdo ba'i rang mtshan rlung mkhris bad kan gnyen rims sogs //
NK133(po)003:8101: lus sems rgud pa'i mi zad tsha gdung bsod nams bdud rtsi'i char 'dis gzhil //
NK133(po)003:8102: mnar sred kyis 'phangs brtse med gdon tshogs gzhan la 'tshe phyir rgyu rnams kyang //
NK133(po)003:8103: sdig sems las ldog snying rje'i blo skyes 'gro la phan pa spyod gyur cig 10 /
NK133(po)003:8104: ngur smrig 'dzin pa'i dge 'dun tshogs rnams spangs dang klog pas dus 'da' zhing //
NK133(po)003:8105: phan bde'i 'byung gnas thub bstan rin chen thos bsam sgom pas ches cher gsal //
NK133(po)003:8106: rig grol skyes bus sa chen yongs 'gengs zhi bsil chos kyi 'od stong brdal //
NK133(po)003:8107: nyes brgyas gdung ba'i nyam thag 'gro kun zab don chos kyis 'tsho bar shog 11 /
NK133(po)003:8108: skal ngan skye bos rgyal bstan dgrar blta 'gro 'di'i bde skyid 'phrogs byed pa //
NK133(po)003:8109: gzugs can gzugs med gang yang rung ste sde ris dpung bcas rming med stong //
NK133(po)003:8110: log smon bdud rigs rgyal bstan dkrugs byed lta spyod phyin ci log ston pas //
NK133(po)003:8111: bde gshegs bstan pa mog por byed pa'i skye bo sa 'dir mi 'byung shog 12 /
NK133(po)003:8112: gangs can 'di na chos rgyal mes dbon lam srol 'dzin sogs 'dzam gling 'dir //
NK133(po)003:8113: thub pa'i bstan la gus pa lhur len sa skyong tshogs dang khyad par du //
NK133(po)003:8114: rgyal bstan yongs rdzogs spyi bos 'degs mkhas sde bzhi dge bcu'i 'byor pa can //
NK133(po)003:8115: mnga' thang stobs dpal mi nyams gong 'phel phyogs las rnam par rgyal gyur cig 13 /
NK133(po)003:8116: o rgyan rgyal ba'i gsang gsum rnam rol lung dang rtogs pa'i 'od stong gzis //
NK133(po)003:8117: mdo sngags dam pa'i chos kyi pad tshal phyogs brgyar bzhad pa'i nyi ma che //
NK133(po)003:8118: bdud sde'i phyogs las rnam par rgyal ba sde gsum klong dgu'i mdzod 'dzin pa //
NK133(po)003:8119: bka' drin mnyam med 'gro ba'i mgon de'i thugs bzhed phrin las mthar rgyas smon /
NK133(po)003:8121: 14 / mgon de'i thugs rje dus las mi yol bstan 'gro'i dpal du byon pa rnams //
NK133(po)003:8122: zhabs pad bskal pa rgya mtshor brtan cing 'khor lo gsum gyi phrin las sgo //
NK133(po)003:8123: phyogs brgyar rab 'phel rnam thar bzang po sras bcas rgyal ba dgyes bskyed pas //
NK133(po)003:8124: thub bstan spyi dang rdo rje snying po'i rang lugs spel la dbang 'byor shog 15 /
NK133(po)003:8125: dpal ldan 'phags pa'i spyod yul theg mchog nges don snying po'i ring lugs che //
NK133(po)003:8126: srid dang zhi las rnam par rgyal ba rang byung byang chub snying po'i gnas //
NK133(po)003:8127: 'khrul med sgrub pa'i chos la gzhol ba'i grub pa'i gling 'dir rgyal ba dang //
NK133(po)003:8128: rgyal sras rnam 'phrul rim par byon pas bstan pa rtag brtan gong 'phel shog 16 /
NK133(po)003:8129: khrims gtsang ngur smrig 'dzin pa sh+aakya'i sras pos nor 'dzin yongs gang bas //
NK133(po)003:8130: bde gshegs chos kun thos bsam sgom pa'i chu gter mu mtha' med par bskyil //
NK133(po)003:8131: gzungs dang spobs pa'i nor bus yongs 'gengs 'chad rtsod rtsom pa'i rlabs phreng g.yo //
NK133(po)003:8132: thub pa'i bstan pa 'dzin skyong spel bas 'jig rten kun tu rgyas byed shog 17 /
NK133(po)003:8133: dri med bslab pa'i gzhi la rab gnas nges par 'byung ba'i blo shugs btsan //
NK133(po)003:8134: dal med brtson 'grus gru bor zhugs pas ting 'dzin rgya mtsho'i pha rol brgal //
NK133(po)003:8135: gdod ma'i grub mtha' tshe 'dir snyogs pas srid zhi las rgyal dpa' bo'i tshogs //
NK133(po)003:8136: u dum w+aa ra'i phreng ba bstar 'dras grub pa'i tshal 'di mdzes byed shog 18 /
NK133(po)003:8137: thub mchog bstan pa'i rin chen mdzod las zab don yid bzhin bye ba'i sgrom //
NK133(po)003:8138: chos sbyin mi bzad 'dod dgu'i mchog sbyin skal bzang skye bo'i dga' ston dbyig /
NK133(po)003:8139: sa gsum 'gro ba'i mchod sdong dam pa byams mgon 'byon par rtag gnas shing //
NK133(po)003:8140: nyi dang 'od bzhin 'dzin ma'i gzhi 'dir dge legs dpal brgyas brgyan gyur cig 19 /
NK133(po)003:8141: bdag kyang dam pa'i chos bzhin spyod pas ring por 'tsho ba'i skal bzang thob //
NK133(po)003:8142: chos brgyad blo dang chos min spyod pa'i dri ma rab spang 'di nas kyang //
NK133(po)003:8143: bde ldan mgon po'i zhing khams dam par zab rgyas chos kyi kun dgar rol //
NK133(po)003:8144: pad dkar 'chang dang mkhyen pa'i gter bzhin bzang po spyod pa rgya mtshor zhugs /
NK133(po)003:8146: 20 / byang chub snying po mngon du byas par tshangs par spyod pa'i rten mchog rnyed //
NK133(po)003:8147: tshul gnas thos bsam sgom pas rgyud phyug gcig tu dben par sgrub la gzhol //
NK133(po)003:8148: sde snod bye ba'i shing rta 'dren bzod theg mchog rin chen gru bzung nas //
NK133(po)003:8149: mkha' mnyam 'gro kun srid mtsho las brgal rgyal ba'i sar bkod mthu thob smon /
NK133(po)003:8151: 21 / bkra shis dge legs kun gyi 'byung gnas bla ma
NK133(po)003:8152: dkon mchog rtsa gsum chos srung rgya mtsho'i bden stobs
NK133(po)003:8153: dang // sgrib bral ye shes brtan g.yo'i srog zhugs
NK133(po)003:8154: 'gro khams rgyal ba'i snying po lhun gyis grub pa'i
NK133(po)003:8155: dang // mthu byin dang // bde gshegs rnam kun
NK133(po)003:8156: mya ngan mi 'da' dam chos nam yang nub med
NK133(po)003:8157: bden gsungs bkra shis dpal 'bar bas //
NK133(po)003:8158: rnam par dag pa'i smon lam rgya mtsho yongs su
NK133(po)003:8159: 'grub pa'i bkra shis rtag brtan rab tu rgyas gyur
NK133(po)003:8160: cig 22 / bka' ma theg rim dgu'i phrin chog
NK133(po)003:8161: gzhung phyi mo rnams dang bcas pa'i dkar chag bstan
NK133(po)003:8162: pa rgya mtsho'i gru gzings bkra shis dpal brgya'i 'byung
NK133(po)003:8163: cig 22 / gnas las / de ltar spar du
NK133(po)003:8164: sgrub pa'i dgos ched phan yon bstan pa bsngo smon
NK133(po)003:8165: shis brjod dang bcas pa'i skabs te lnga pa'o ////
NK133(po)003:8166: zhes pa 'di ni skyabs rje yongs rdzogs bstan pa'i
NK133(po)003:8167: mnga' bdag mkhyen sprul rin po che 'jam dbyangs chos
NK133(po)003:8168: kyi blo gros ris med bstan pa'i rgyal mtshan gang
NK133(po)003:8169: gi zhal snga nas bka' stsal spyi bor phebs pa
NK133(po)003:8170: dang / mchog sprul rin po che mdo sngags bstan
NK133(po)003:8171: pa'i nyi mas bka'i gnang ba stsal ba gus pas
NK133(po)003:8172: dang du blang ste rje bla ma o rgyan mdo
NK133(po)003:8173: sngags chos kyi nyi ma phyogs las rnam par rgyal
NK133(po)003:8174: ba'i sde dpal bzang po'i zhabs rdul spyi bos reg
NK133(po)003:8175: pa'i slob 'bangs yongs kyi tha shal du gyur pa
NK133(po)003:8176: sh+aakya'i dge slong rmong rtul 'jam dbyangs thub bstan bshad
NK133(po)003:8177: sgrub rgya mtshor 'bod pas rang gnas dben pa'i ri
